11304,simple,,,"CUTTER &amp; MIXER- SD01Y",1,0,visible,"<strong>CUTTER &amp; MIXER - SD01Y</strong>\nThe SD01Y Cutter &amp; Mixer is a versatile kitchen appliance designed for efficient chopping, mixing, and blending. With a powerful motor and durable construction, it delivers consistent results for a variety of food preparation tasks. Ideal for commercial kitchens and catering operations.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• CUTTER &amp; MIXER</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Capacity: 6L</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Motor power:0,37 Kw 1400 rpm -220V</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• voltage: 220V~</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• frequency: 50Hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• power: 900W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Package size: 320 x 320 x 345 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Bowl dimension(diameter/depth): 240 mm/180 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Stainless steel body and bowl</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Model : SD.01Y /EMPERO/TURKEY MADE</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,1874,"FOOD PROCESSING > Cutter Mixer, FOOD PROCESSING",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/sd01y.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Empero,Brand,Empero,1,1,"Type of Product","Cutter & Mixer",1,1,default,1,1,213,index,54,0,0,,"CUTTER & MIXER- SD01Y,ماكينة حمص,خلاط حمص",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,SD01Y,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596457,011111001111111000001100000100100011000100110111,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
11306,simple,,,"CUTTER MIXER-EMP.350",1,0,visible,"<strong>CUTTER MIXER - EMP.350</strong>\nThe EMP.350 Cutter Mixer combines precision and power to handle chopping, mixing, and emulsifying tasks with ease. Its high-capacity design and robust performance make it ideal for commercial kitchens. Durable and user-friendly, it ensures consistent results for a variety of food preparations.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• cap: 8 ltr</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• cutting and mixing</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• puree, mix, chop, blend, mix and knead dough</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Stainless steel body &amp; bowl</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Bowl dim: 240 x 180 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• motor speed: 900 rpm/min</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• power: 220v / 50hz / 0,37 kw</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• n.weight: 19kg / net m3:0.05</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• dim: 340 x 3260 x 550 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• EMP.350 /EMPERO\nTURKEY made</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,2054,"FOOD PROCESSING > Cutter Mixer, FOOD PROCESSING",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/emp.350.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Empero,Brand,Empero,1,1,"Type of Product","Cutter & Mixer",1,1,default,1,1,136,index,47,0,0,,"CUTTER MIXER-EMP.350,كتر خلاط,ماكينة حمص,خلاط حمص",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,EMP.350,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595316,011010110011011000010110011100111000110001100011,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
