11310,simple,,,"VEGETABLE PREP MACHINE-EMP300",1,0,visible,"<strong>VEGETABLE PREP MACHINE - EMP300</strong>\nThe EMP300 vegetable prep machine is a versatile and efficient solution for commercial kitchens. Designed to handle a variety of slicing, dicing, and shredding tasks, it ensures consistent results and saves valuable prep time. Durable, easy to operate, and perfect for high-volume food preparation.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• cap: 300 kg/h for slicing</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• with four multi discs</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Stainless steel blades &amp; body</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Blades can be easily removed for cleaning</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Safety switch</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Motor power:0.37 Kw 900 rpm -220 V</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• N.W; 29 kg / net m3 0.07 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• dim: 260 x 560 x 500 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• EMP.300 / TURKEY made</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,2199,3300,"FOOD PROCESSING, FOOD PROCESSING > Vegtable Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/VEGETABLE-PREP-MACHINE-EMP300.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Empero,Brand,Empero,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,index,47,0,0,,"VEGETABLE PREP MACHINE-EMP300,ماكينة تحضير الخضار,ماكينة تقطيع الخضار للمطاعم,قطاعة خضار",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,EMP300,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595284,100111011011000110001001001011000110011010011110,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
