11343,simple,,,"GAS PIZZA OVEN G4",1,0,visible,"The GAS PIZZA OVEN-G4 is a high-efficiency pizza oven designed for commercial use. It features a gas-powered heating system that provides consistent and even heat distribution, ensuring perfectly cooked pizzas every time. The G4 model includes a spacious cooking chamber with a durable, heat-resistant interior, allowing for multiple pizzas to be baked simultaneously. Its user-friendly controls and adjustable temperature settings offer precise cooking control, making it ideal for pizzerias and restaurants. The oven's sleek design and robust construction ensure both reliability and style in any kitchen setting.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Baking chamber 1</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Pizza Cap: 4 / Pizza Dim: 30cm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Working temp: 50 - 500 °c</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Voltage: 230/ 1/50 V/Hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Absorption: 11.954 kCal/h</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Natural gas consumption: 1470 (m3 / h)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• LPG consumption: 1087 (Kg / h)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight: 115 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Internal dim: 620 x 620 x 155 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• External dim: 1000 x 840 x 470 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• G4/ GGF s.r.l./ italy made</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,9781.2,"BAKERY LINE, BAKERY LINE > Bakery Oven",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/GAS-PIZZA-OVEN-G4.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,GGF,Brand,GGF,1,1,Electric/Gas,Gas,1,1,default,1,1,0,index,25,0,0,,"GAS PIZZA OVEN-G4,فرن بيتزا,فرن بيتزا غاز",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,G4,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595