11393,simple,,,"ICE CUBE MAKER MACHINE CB416A",1,0,visible,"The ICE CUBE MAKER MACHINE CB416A is a high-capacity appliance designed to produce up to 44 kilograms of ice cubes per day. With its efficient production capabilities, it ensures a steady supply of ice for various needs. Additionally, the machine comes equipped with a spacious storage capacity of 16 kilograms, allowing you to keep a sizable amount of ice readily available for immediate use. Whether it's for commercial establishments or large gatherings, this ice cube maker machine is a reliable and convenient solution to meet your ice requirements.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Production: kg. 44 kg/day</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Storage cap: kg. 16</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Air condensing system</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Voltage: 220-240/ 50hz/ 1 phase/ kw 0.45</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Made in AISI 304 18/10 stainless steel</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 500 x 580 x h.790 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight (net/gross)43 / 51 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• CB416A / BREMA / ITALIA</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,5852,"REFRIGERATION LINE > ICE MAKER & FLAKES, REFRIGERATION LINE, Top Brands",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ICECUBE-MAKER-MACHINE-CB416A.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Brema,Brand,Brema,1,1,"Type of Product","Ice Cube Maker Machine",1,1,default,1,1,130,index,62,0,0,,"ICE CUBE MAKER MACHINE,آلة صنع مكعبات الثلج,ماكينة صنع مكعبات الثلج",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,CB416A,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595175,001001100101101101101101100011011001100110011000,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
