11459,simple,,,"DAIRY PRODUCTS DISPLAY-V80150SL",1,0,visible,"<strong>Dairy Products Display-V80150SL</strong>\n\nIntroducing the Dairy Products Display-V80150SL – the ultimate solution for showcasing your dairy items with style and efficiency. This sleek, modern display unit is designed to keep your dairy products fresh and attractively presented, ensuring maximum visibility and accessibility.\n\n<strong>Key Features:</strong>\n<ul>\n 	<li><strong>Spacious Design:</strong> Offers ample storage space for a wide variety of dairy products, including milk, cheese, yogurt, and more.</li>\n 	<li><strong>Advanced Cooling Technology:</strong> Equipped with state-of-the-art cooling systems to maintain optimal freshness and extend shelf life.</li>\n 	<li><strong>Energy-Efficient:</strong> Designed with energy-saving features to reduce operational costs and environmental impact.</li>\n 	<li><strong>Adjustable Shelving:</strong> Flexible shelving options allow for customizable organization to suit your specific product needs.</li>\n 	<li><strong>Elegant Display:</strong> Features a contemporary design with clear, tempered glass doors that enhance product visibility and appeal.</li>\n 	<li><strong>Easy Maintenance:</strong> Removable shelves and easy-to-clean surfaces ensure hassle-free upkeep and sanitation.</li>\n 	<li><strong>User-Friendly Controls:</strong> Simple and intuitive controls for temperature adjustments and display settings.</li>\n</ul>\nPerfect for supermarkets, convenience stores, or specialty dairy shops, the Dairy Products Display-V80150SL combines functionality with modern aesthetics to elevate your product presentation. Experience the perfect blend of efficiency and elegance – choose the V80150SL for your dairy display needs.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px;"">• vertical muti-deck displays</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px;"">• self-service sale of dairy products, cold-cuts, beverages</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px;"">• temperature is controlled by electronic thermostat</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px;"">• upper interior lighting</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px;"">• autorolling night blind is standard supplied</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px;"">• gas refrigeration: R404A / R507</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px;"">• temp: -3 ~ +5 °c</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px;"">• 4 shelves made of atossic white-painted steel sheet or S/S</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px;"">• power: 220 v / 50 hz / 1595 w</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px;"">• total gross weight: 240 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px;"">• dim: 1580 x 764 x 2040 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px;"">• V80150SL / DGD / italy made</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(476px, 7px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,11281,"REFRIGERATION LINE > Display Chiller, REFRIGERATION LINE, SUPERMARKET EQUIPMENT",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/V80100SLINOX.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Tecnodom,Brand,Tecnodom,1,1,"Type of Product","Dairy Products Display",1,1,default,1,1,0,index,54,0,0,,"DAIRY PRODUCTS DISPLAY-V80150SL,ثلاجة عرض بقالة مشروبات,عرض منتجات الألبان",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,V80150SL,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110101100111111000000110000100101100111101001001,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
