11474,simple,,,"MEAT MINCER TR12C",1,0,visible,"<strong>MEAT MINCER TR12C</strong>\nA meat mincer, in general, is a kitchen appliance designed to grind or mince meat into smaller pieces. These devices are commonly used in households and commercial kitchens to prepare ground meat for various dishes like burgers, sausages, meatballs, and more. They typically consist of a hopper where you feed the meat, a mechanism to push the meat through blades for grinding, and various settings to control the coarseness of the ground meat.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• cap: 160 kg / h</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• power: 0.75 kW (1 HP)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Supply: 230V / 1N / 50Hz - 230-400V / 3 / 50Hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• package volume: 0.078 m³</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• package dim: 540 x 300 x 480 h (mm)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• n.weight: 22 kg / g.w: 24 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• dimension: 440 x 270 x 450 h (mm)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• TR12CEN0I235M/monofase / fimar/ italy made</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,4221.36,"FOOD PROCESSING, FOOD PROCESSING > Meat Mincer, Special Offer",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/TR22C.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/TR12C-1.jpg",,,,,,,,,0,,Fimar,Brand,Fimar,1,1,"Type of Product","Meat Mincer",1,1,default,1,1,0,index,68,0,0,,"MEAT MINCER TR12C,مفرمة لحم ايطالي,مفرمة لحم",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,TR12CEN0I235M,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596400,000010011011010110000111001011000100110111001111,false,,,,,,,,salescountdowntimer,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
