11510,simple,,,"VACUUM CHAMBER MACHINE CAM300",1,0,visible,"The VACUUM CHAMBER MACHINE CAM300 is a device designed for creating a vacuum environment to process or package various materials. It’s commonly used in industries such as packaging, electronics, and food processing. Key features typically include precise vacuum control, durable construction, and the ability to handle different sizes and types of items.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Stainless steel casing</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Automatic lid opening at the end of the cycle</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• LCD control panel with 20 storable programs with ""pump oil cleaning"" and ""soft air"" function included as standard</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Predisposition for inert gas injection</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• BUSH pump (made in Germany)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Step vac"" and ""extra vaccum"" functions included</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power : 0.75 kW / 230V / 1N / 50-60Hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• N.Weight 38 Kg / G. Weight : 44 Kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Vacuum pump : 8 m³ / h</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Sealing bar 300 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Useful room dim : 310 x 350 x 190h (mm)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Maximum Achievable vacuum : 0.98</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dimension: 410 x 460 x 430h (mm)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• CAM300 / fimar/ italy made</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,8759.52,"FOOD PROCESSING > Bar Vacuum Machine, FOOD PROCESSING",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/CAM300.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Fimar,Brand,Fimar,1,1,"Type of Product","Vacuum Chamber Machine",1,1,default,1,1,0,index,58,0,0,,"VACUUM CHAMBER,VACUUM CHAMBER MACHINE CAM300",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,CAM300,field_6