11512,simple,,,"VACUUM CHAMBER MACHINE CAM400",1,0,visible,"The <strong>VACUUM CHAMBER MACHINE CAM400</strong> is likely a piece of equipment designed for vacuum packaging. It creates a sealed, airtight environment around food or other products, extending their shelf life by reducing oxygen exposure.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Stainless steel casing</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Automatic lid opening at the end of the cycle</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• LCD control panel with 20 storable programs with ""pump oil cleaning"" and ""soft air"" function included as standard</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Predisposition for inert gas injection</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• BUSH pump (made in Germany)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Step vac"" and ""extra vaccum"" functions included</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power : 1.1 kW / 230V / 1N / 50-60Hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• N.Weight 60 Kg / G. Weight : 67 Kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Sealing bar 400 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Useful room dim : 410x450x220h (mm)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Maximum Achievable vacuum : 0.98</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dimension: 510 x 460 x 450h (mm)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• CAM400 / fimar/ italy made</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,10074.24,"FOOD PROCESSING > Bar Vacuum Machine, FOOD PROCESSING",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/CAM300.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Fimar,Brand,Fimar,1,1,"Type of Product","Vacuum Chamber Machine",1,1,default,1,1,0,index,65,0,0,,"VACUUM CHAMBER MACHINE CAM400",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,CAM400,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595851,110111010110