11735,simple,,,"CONFECTIONERY AND BAKERY OVENS EPP01S",1,0,visible,"<p style=""text-align: left; margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">The EPP01S confectionery and bakery oven is a versatile and high-performance appliance designed to meet the specific needs of professional bakers and confectioners. This oven is meticulously engineered to deliver exceptional baking and confectionery results with precision and consistency. Below is a detailed description of the EPP01S confectionery and bakery oven:</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" style=""transform: translate(935px, 9px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","• Layout: 1x3,13kw\n\n• POWER : 6 kW 1 x 2/1 GN\n\n• voltage: 400 V / 3N / 50 Hz\n\n• Heat regulation 50 – 300°C\n\n• GN 2/1 oven\n\n• N/G weight: 60,9 - 71,4 kg\n\n• Dim: 950 x 902 x 660 mm\n\n• EPP 01 S / RM GASTRO / europe made",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,5918,"BAKERY LINE, BAKERY LINE > Bakery Oven",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/EPP-01_Visualization.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"RM Gastro",Brand,"RM Gastro",1,1,Electric/Gas,Electric,1,1,default,1,1,0,index,56,0,0,,CONFECTIONERY,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,EPP01S,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,15715,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595758,100101100111100111100110110011001001100001100001,true,backend,,,,,,,,"Type of Product",Oven,1,1,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
