11958,simple,,,"DOUGH MIXER. HY.03.K",1,0,visible,"<strong>DOUGH MIXER - HY.03.K</strong>\nThe HY.03.K dough mixer is a reliable and efficient solution for kneading and mixing dough. With a powerful motor and adjustable speed settings, it ensures consistent results for various dough types. Perfect for bakeries and pizzerias looking for quality dough preparation.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• flour cap : 20 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• capacity : 40 ltr</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Motor Power:0.75 Kw 1400 rpm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• 220 V opeating voltage</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Bowl dim(diameter/depth): 500 mm/270 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• S/S bowl and dough mixer arm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• N.W.:83 kg. Net m3 : 0.41</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• dim : 593 x 908 x 772 m</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• HY.03.K /EMPERO/ Turkey made</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,3600,"BAKERY LINE, BAKERY LINE > Bakery Mixers",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/HY.05.K.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Empero,Brand,Empero,1,1,Electric/Gas,Electric,1,1,default,1,1,0,index,58,0,0,,"DOUGH MIXER,DOUGH MIXER. HY.03.K",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,HY.03.K,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110110011001110010011001100000110000110011110110,false,,,,,,,,,"Type of Product","Dough Mixer",1,1,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
