11988,simple,,,"PLANETARY MIXERS (3 SPEED) MK.04",1,0,visible,"The MK.04 Planetary Mixer is a versatile and robust mixing solution, ideal for commercial kitchens and bakeries. It features a three-speed motor, allowing for precise control over mixing processes, from gentle stirring to vigorous beating. The planetary mixing action ensures thorough and consistent mixing of ingredients, making it perfect for dough, batters, and various other mixtures. Designed for durability and efficiency, the MK.04 is equipped with a sturdy bowl and a range of attachments to cater to diverse culinary needs. This reliable mixer enhances productivity and ensures high-quality results in demanding food preparation environments.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• PLANETARY MIXERS (3 SPEED) MK.04</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• cap: 40 lt</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Two-speed operating option</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• accesorries: 2 of whisks/ 1 of dough hook/ 1 of mixing paddle</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Double circuit timer and digital control panel</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Stainless steel bowl, Safety switch</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Motor power: 1.1-1.5 Kw/ 950-145 rpm/ 380 V/ 3 phase</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• N. weight: 200 kg./ net m3: 0.84</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 690 x 888 x 1366 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• MK.04 / EMPERO/ turkey made</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,8353,10442,"BAKERY LINE, BAKERY LINE > Bakery Mixers",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/MK.04.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Empero,Brand,Empero,1,1,"Type of Product","Planetary Mixers",1,1,default,1,1,0,index,51,0,0,,"PLANETARY MIXERS (3 SPEED) MK.04",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,MK.04,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default