12025,simple,,,"RATIONAL  ELECTRIC SELF COOKING CENTER SCC 101 E",1,0,visible,"The RATIONAL Electric Self Cooking Center SCC 101 E is a state-of-the-art, versatile cooking solution designed for professional kitchens. With innovative technology and user-friendly features, this electric oven streamlines the cooking process, ensuring consistent and high-quality results.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• RATIONAL ELECTRIC SELF COOKING CENTER SCC 101 E</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Capacity: 10 x 1/1 GN ( 10 x 12""x 20"")</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Hinging rack: 68 mm (2 5/8)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Number of meals per day 80 - 150</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Lengthwise loading: 1/1, 1/2, 2/3, 1/3, 2/8 GN</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Water inlet: R 3/4</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Water outlet: DN 50</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Water pressure: 150-600 kPa or 0.15-0.6 Mpa</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight: 152 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Connected load: 18,6 kw</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Fuse: 3 x 32 A</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Main connection: 3 NAC 400 V / 50-60 hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Steam output: 18 kw</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Hand shower w/ automatic reacting system</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Interface USB (standard</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dimensions: 847 x 771 x 1042 (w*d*h)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• SCC 101 E/ Rational / germany made</p>",,,taxable,,0,,,0,0,,,,,1,,39950,42500,"COOKING LINE > Combi Oven, COOKING LINE, sale, SALE RATIONAL, Special Offer, Top Brands",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/RATIONAL-ELECTRIC-SELF-COOKING-CENTER-SCC-101-E.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Rational,Brand,Rational,1,1,Electric/Gas,Electric,1,1,default,1,1,129,index,13,0,0,,,,"kitchen equipment dubai",,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"SCC 101 E",field_6387359a51f50,yes,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596255,110110001101010010010110001110000101011111100010,false,,9419975431387284,yes,yes,,product,no,salescountdowntimer,"Type of Product","Electric Self Cooking",1,1,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12027,simple,,,"WORK TOP CHILLER-GN2100TN",1,0,visible,"<strong>WORK TOP CHILLER - GN2100TN</strong>\nThe GN2100TN Work Top Chiller combines functionality and refrigeration, offering a durable stainless steel work surface with efficient cooling storage underneath. Designed for commercial kitchens, it ensures optimal temperature control to keep ingredients fresh while maximizing workspace efficiency. Perfect for high-demand food preparation environments.","• WORK TOP CHILLER-GN2100TN\n\n• automatic closing door w/ magnetic gasket, 90° reversible w/ 4 castor wheels\n\n• injected polyurethane insulation, CFC free, density: 40 kgs / m3\n\n• Cap: 260 ltr\n\n• w/ 2 shelves &amp; 2 drs\n\n• working Temp: +2˚ ~ +8° at 32° temp\n\n• Power Supply: 230v / 50 Hz / 1Ph\n\n• frige power: 336 Watt\n\n• refrigerant : R134a\n\n• Net Weight: 92 Kg\n\n• Dim: 1365 x 700 x 850 mm (WxDxH)\n\n• Digital: DIXELL / ITALY MADE\n\n• compressor : ASPERA / EMBRACO / ITALY / GN2100TN / Inofrigo / Mariot made\n\n• ISO9001, CE&amp; ROHS approved",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,3327,3660,"REFRIGERATION LINE > Freezer & Chillers, REFRIGERATION LINE",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/WhatsApp-Image-2022-03-31-at-5.43.16-PM.jpeg,,,,,,,,,0,,Inofrigo,Brand,Inofrigo,1,1,Series,"Work Top",1,1,default,1,1,0,index,60,0,0,,"WORK TOP CHILLER-GN2100TN",,"• WORK TOP CHILLER-GN2100TN
