12083,simple,,,"HOT TOPPING (TWIN PUMP/ LADLE WARMER)-TWIN FS 81220",1,0,visible,"The HOT TOPPING (TWIN PUMP/LADLE WARMER) - TWIN FS 81220 is a versatile and efficient appliance designed to keep two types of toppings warm and easily accessible. Featuring dual pumps or ladles, this warmer allows for simultaneous dispensing of two different sauces, syrups, or condiments, making it ideal for busy commercial kitchens, cafes, and food service establishments. The unit ensures consistent heating and maintains optimal temperature for both toppings, enhancing service speed and quality. Its durable construction and user-friendly design make it a practical addition to any food service operation.",". Stainless steel construction\n. Adjustable, pre-calibrated thermostats for accurate heat control\n. Water fill lines eliminate overflow accidents\n(2) S/S lids, 30 mL ladles and 2.8 L jars\n. black knobs are standard.\n. 230V with UK type power cord",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,2800,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Food Warmers",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/TWIN-FS-81220.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,"Server USA",Brand,"Server USA",1,1,"Type of Product","Twin Warmer",1,1,default,1,1,0,index,57,0,0,,"HOT TOPPING (TWIN PUMP/ LADLE WARMER)-TWIN",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"TWIN FS 81220",field_6387359a51f50,yes,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110110101100010010000100111110100101100100011110,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
