12102,simple,,,"COMMERCIAL ICE CRUSHER-WARIIC20K",1,0,visible,"The COMMERCIAL ICE CRUSHER-WARIIC20K is a high-performance appliance designed to efficiently crush large quantities of ice for commercial use. With its robust construction and powerful motor, this ice crusher is ideal for bars, restaurants, and other foodservice establishments that require a consistent supply of crushed ice. Its user-friendly interface and quick operation make it a valuable addition to any beverage or food preparation setup. The durable design ensures reliable performance even during peak hours, helping to enhance the overall efficiency of your business operations.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(570px, 91px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","• Portable and Compact IC20\n\n• Quiet heavy duty 120 watt motor\n\n• Special height adjustment dispenses into 1Lt or 1.5Lt bar blender container or a variety of other containers\n\n• 2.4 Lt bowl and funnel included\n\n• Large chute opening for safe continuous ice cube feed\n\n• Size: 190mm (w) x 250mm (d) x 565mm (h)\n\n• Power: 120 watt. 10 amp\n\n• WARING / WARIIC20K / USA made",,,taxable,,0,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,1499,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Ice Crusher, REFRIGERATION LINE","COMMERCIAL ICE CRUSHER",,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/COMMERCIAL-ICE-CRUSHER-WARIIC20K.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,"Waring USA",Brand,"Waring USA",1,1,"Type of Product","Commercial Ice Crusher",1,1,default,1,1,0,index,60,0,0,,"COMMERCIAL ICE CRUSHER",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,WARIIC20K,field_6387359a51f50,yes,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596384,110011100110110011001001100110111000110001001100,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
