12130,simple,,,"MILK SHAKE-54A",1,0,visible,"The Milk Shake-54A is a delightful and creamy beverage that's perfect for satisfying your sweet cravings. This classic milkshake offers a rich and smooth blend of milk, ice cream, and a choice of delectable flavors. Whether you prefer chocolate, vanilla, or fruit-infused options, the Milk Shake-54A delivers a refreshing and indulgent experience. With its balanced combination of flavors and a touch of nostalgia, it's a timeless treat that's sure to bring joy to any moment.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• MILK SHAKE-54A</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Electric Shaker</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Cap: 0.675 L Speed: 8,000- 16,000 rpm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Power: 220/240v-50/60hz-230W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Weight: 6 Kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Dim: 186x182x530 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Made by Santos, France</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,2105,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Juice Maker",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/MILK-SHAKE-54A.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Santos,Brand,Santos,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,index,79,0,0,,"MILK SHAKE",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,54A,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011001110011011001100011001110011000110011001100,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
