12138,simple,,,"Patented Centrifugal Juice Extractor - 50A",1,0,visible,"The Patented Centrifugal Juice Extractor - 50A is an advanced, high-efficiency appliance designed for commercial use. This juice extractor utilizes patented centrifugal technology to maximize juice yield from fruits and vegetables while minimizing waste. Its robust motor and sharp blades ensure quick and effective juicing, perfect for busy juice bars, cafes, and restaurants. The 50A is easy to clean and maintain, featuring durable construction and user-friendly operation. Ideal for producing fresh, high-quality juices with consistent performance.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• Painted Centrifugal Juice Extractor- easy\nclean sys. with removable bowl</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Cap: 100 L/h Speed: 3,000 rpm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Power: 220/240v-50/60hz-800 W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Weight: 14 Kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Dim: 470x260x450 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Made by Santos, France</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""true"">\n<div id=""tippy-1"" style=""z-index: 100000200;position: absolute;margin: 0px"" data-tippy-root="""">\n<div class=""tippy-box"" style=""max-width: 350px"" role=""mtttooltip"" data-state=""visible"" data-theme=""custom"" data-animation=""fade"" data-placement=""top"">\n<div class=""tippy-content"" data-state=""visible""><span dir=""rtl"">• الوزن: 14 كجم</span></div>\n<div class=""tippy-arrow"" style=""position: absolute;left: 0px""></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,5632,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Juice Maker",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/PAINTED-CENTRIFUGAL-JUICE-EXTRACTOR-50A.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Santos,Brand,Santos,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,index,59,0,0,,"Patented Centrifugal Juice Extractor - 50A",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,50A,field_6387359a51f50,no