12167,simple,,,"TANGO BAR BLENDER-HBH450-UK",1,0,visible,"<strong>Container Capacity</strong>: 48oz / 1.4L Polycarbonate Container\n<strong>Controls</strong>: Speed/ Timer Pulse\n<strong>Voltage</strong>: 220V-240V~, 50-60 hz\n<strong>Power</strong>: 600W\n<strong>Motor</strong>: 1 Hp\n<strong>Weight</strong>: 5.1 kg\n<strong>Size</strong>: 22.9x 16.5 x 43.2 cm\nHBH450-UK/ Hamilton Beach- USA Brand /Assembled in China","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Time-saving controls at an aggressive price. Rather than having to attend your bar blender, the tangos adjustable timer automatically stops the blender so\nyou can get other work done</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Patented Wave ~Action system</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Powerful 1Hp motor</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Timer; two speeds, pulse</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Durable metal drive clutch</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Container Capacity: 48oz / 1.4L Polycarbonate Container</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Controls: Speed/ Timer Pulse</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Voltage: 220V-240V~, 50-60 hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power: 600W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Motor: 1 Hp</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight: 5.1 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Size: 22.9x 16.5 x 43.2 cm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• HBH450-UK/ Hamilton Beach- USA Brand /Assembled in China</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,2080,"COFFEE & BAR LINE > Blenders, COFFEE & BAR LINE",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/TANGO-BAR-BLENDER-HBH450-UK.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,"Hamilton Beach USA",Brand,"Hamilton Beach- USA",1,1,"Type of Product","Bar Blender",1,1,default,1,1,261,index,5,167,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,HBH450-UK,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe