12169,simple,,,"FURY BLENDER- HBH550‐UK",1,0,visible,"The <strong data-start=""4"" data-end=""30"">HBH550-UK Fury Blender</strong> is a high-performance commercial blender designed for fast and efficient blending of smoothies, cocktails, and frozen drinks. Equipped with a powerful motor, stainless steel blades, and easy-to-use controls, it ensures smooth and consistent results in high-demand environments. Ideal for bars, cafés, and restaurants, the Fury Blender delivers reliability and precision with every blend.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;""><strong>FURY BLENDER- HBH550‐UK</strong>\n(International) Fury™ High Performance Blender,\n. Two-speed motor,\n. 64 oz. (1.8 liter) capacity,\n. Stackable polycarbonate container, paddle switches,\n. Variable timer, jump cycle, pulse switch, auto shutoff,\nremovable filler cap,\n. Wave‐Action™ System, Sure Grip™ feet,\n. Stainless steel blades,\n. 3 Hp, 220‐240v/50/60/1‐ph, 880 watts\nHamilton Beach Model No. HBH550‐UK</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,3080,"COFFEE & BAR LINE > Blenders, COFFEE & BAR LINE",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/HBH550.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,"Hamilton Beach USA",Brand,"Hamilton Beach- USA",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,261,index,62,167,0,,"FURY BLENDER,FURY BLENDER- HBH550‐UK",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,HBH550‐UK,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,15735,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110011100110110011000110011100110010011001001100,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12171,simple,,,"TEMPEST BLENDER- HBH650-UK",1,0,visible,"<strong>Container Capacity:</strong> 64oz / 1.8L Polycarbonate Jar\n<strong>Controls</strong>: 2 speeds, jump cycle and timer\n<strong>Voltage</strong>: 220V-240V~, 50-60 hz\n<strong>Power</strong>: 880 W\n<strong>Motor</strong>: 3Hp\n<strong>Shipping Gross Weight</strong>: 6.3 kg\n<strong>Size</strong>: 20.3 x 17.8 x 45.7 cm\nHBH650-UK/ Hamilton Beach- USA Brand / Assembled in China","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• From an adjustable jump cycle that delivers an amazing drink consistency with reduced noise levels, to our unique jar pad sensor and a temperature gauge that helps to increase the life of your blender.\n•Patented Wave~Action system</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Powerful 3 Hp motor</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Two speeds, jump cycle, pulse and timer</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Durable metal drive clutch; jar pad sensor</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Easy in-counter use (kit)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Temperature gauge</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• strong&gt;Container Capacity: 64oz / 1.8L Polycarbonate Jar</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• strong&gt;Controls: 2 speeds, jump cycle and timer</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• strong&gt;Voltage: 220V-240V~, 50-60 hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• strong&gt;Motor: 3Hp</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• strong&gt;Shipping Gross Weight: 6.3 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• strong&gt;Size: 20.3 x 17.8 x 45.7 cm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• HBH650-UK/ Hamilton Beach- USA Brand / Assembled in China</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" style=""transform: translate(1263px, 82px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,3640,"COFFEE & BAR LINE > Blenders, COFFEE & BAR LINE",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/up