12173,simple,,,"SINGLE-SPINDLE DRINK MIXER-HMD200P-UK",1,0,visible,"<strong>The unit comes with a base, motor, spindle, solid agitators, and staineless steel cup.</strong>\n<strong>Controls</strong>: 3-speed rocker switch\n<strong>Voltage</strong>: 220V-240 V, 50-60 hz\n<strong>Motor</strong>: 1/3 Hp\n<strong>Power</strong>: 300 W\n<strong>Weight</strong>: 6.9kg\n<strong>Size</strong>: 17.1 x 16.5 x 52.1H cm\nHMD200P-UK/ Hamilton Beach- USA Brand /Assembled in China","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Versatile drink and food prep. A single spindle drink mixer that is great for everything from mixing ice cream shakes to ""flashing"" bar drinks to blending eggs, pancake, and waffle batter. Operators can start and stop mixing action by inserting the cup into the cup guide or by using the pulse switch on the top of the mixer</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Metal bar extends from the base for added stability</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cup activated or convenient pulse feature</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Hands-free operation</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 3-speed universal motor</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Die cast housing</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Easy to clean</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Sealed rear housing</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Standard agitator: Wavy</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Alternate agitator: 928</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Alternate agitator: 929</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• strong&gt;The unit comes with a base, motor, spindle, solid agitators, and staineless steel cup.&lt;/strong</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• strong&gt;Controls: 3-speed rocker switch</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• strong&gt;Voltage: 220V-240 V, 50-60 hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• strong&gt;Motor: 1/3 Hp</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• strong&gt;Power: 300 W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• strong&gt;Weight: 6.9kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• strong&gt;Size: 17.1 x 16.5 x 52.1H cm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• HMD200P-UK/ Hamilton Beach- USA Brand /Assembled in China</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,2080,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Juice Maker",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Single-Spindle-Drink-Mixer-HMD200P-UK.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,"Hamilton Beach USA",Brand,"Hamilton Beach- USA",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,125,index,5,167,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,HMD200P-UK,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011001100110110001100110010110011010010011100110,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
