12224,simple,,,"MENUMASTER COMMERCIAL MICROWAVE MEDIUM VOLUME-RCS511DSEU",1,0,visible,"<p style=""text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• MENUMASTER COMMERCIAL MICROWAVE\nMEDIUM VOLUME</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• usable cavity space: 34 ltr (1.2 cubic ft.)</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• User friendly ten minute dial timer</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Timer must be manually reset to zero if door is opened during heating</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• See-through door and lighted interior for monitoring without opening the door</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• S/S exterior &amp; interior, easy cleaning &amp; commercial look</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Non-removable air filter protects oven components</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• door depth: 832 (32 3/4""), 900+ door open</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• power consumption: 1550 W, 13 A</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• power output: 1100W ** microwave</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• plug configuration/cord: CEE 7/7""sCHUKO""1.5m(5ft)</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• frequency: 2450 Mhz</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• cavity dim: H 216 (8 1/2"") W 368 (14 1/2"")</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• exterior dim: H 352 (13 7/8"") W 559 (22"")</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• RCS511DSEU / USA made</p>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• MENUMASTER COMMERCIAL MICROWAVE\nMEDIUM VOLUME</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• usable cavity space: 34 ltr (1.2 cubic ft.)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• User friendly ten minute dial timer</p>\n<p s