12229,simple,,,"COMMERCIAL MICROWAVE MEDIUM VOLUME-RCS511TSU",1,0,visible,"The RCS511TSU is a high-quality commercial microwave proudly made in the USA. Designed to handle medium volume demands, this microwave offers reliable performance and efficiency in a compact and sleek design. With its advanced features and user-friendly controls, it ensures quick and consistent cooking, making it an ideal choice for businesses looking to enhance their food service operations. Trust in its American craftsmanship to deliver exceptional results and meet the demands of your commercial kitchen with ease.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• MENUMASTER COMMERCIAL MICROWAVE\nMEDIUM VOLUME</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• usable cavity space: 34 ltr (1.2 cubic ft.)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Accomodates a 14″ (356 mm) platter</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Tempered glass outer oven door, competition uses plastic</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Reliable, long lasting. Monitor cooking w/out oven light</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• S/S exterior &amp; interior, easy cleaning &amp; commercial look</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Touch controls / Versatile program options</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 100 programmable menu items, 4 stages of cooking,\n5 microwave power levels and Braille touch pads</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• door depth: 832 (32 3/4""), 900+ door open</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• power supply: 240V /50hz / 10amp / single phase</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• power output: 1100W ** microwave</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• plug configuration/cord: CEE 7/7""sCHUKO""1.5m(5ft)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• frequency: 2450 Mhz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• internal dim: 368w x 381d x 216h mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• exterior dim: 559w x 483d x 349h mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• RCS511TSU / USA made</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,2500,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Microwave",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/MENUMASTER-COMMERCIAL-MICROWAVE-MEDIUM-VOLUME-RCS511TSU.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"Menu Master",Brand,"Menu Master",1,1,"Type of Product","Commercial Microwave Medium",1,1,default,1,1,129,index,5,166,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,RCS511TSU,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595813,011010101010101001001101010001111100011111010000,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12231,simple,,,"MINI PAN CAKE 25 PCS-Model: WF - 25 C",1,0,visible,"<p style=""margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; text-align: right;"">• Volts: 220V/50-60 Hz / Power: 1.5 KW</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: right;"">• PAN size: 45 x 45 x 10mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: right;"">• Packing size : 520 x 390 x 330 mm Material: stainless steel (#201)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: right;"">• N/W : 8.3 Kg / G/W : 9.5 Kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: right;"">• S/S body, w/ high conductivity, quick heating, more energy-efficient</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: right;"">• Automatic temp. control function, non-stick surface, low-power, w/ the temp. control knob as well as time knob 3.Commercial PAN</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: right;"">• Toaster designed for baking PAN w/ independent heat control &amp; cast-iron molds</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: right;"">• safe &amp; more environmental protection</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: right;"">• advanced technology &amp; high-grade durable</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: right;"">• Upper &amp; lower module plates are enameled &amp; are easy to be 440 x 320 x 190 mm x 310 x 200mm</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(28px, 77px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","• Volts: 220V/50-60 Hz / Power: 1.5 KW\n\n• PAN size: 45 x 45 x 10mm\n\n• Packing size : 520 x 390 x 330 mm Material: stainless steel (#201)\n\n• N/W : 8.3 Kg / G/W : 9.5 Kg\n\n• S/S body, w/ high conductivity, quick heating, more energy-efficient\n\n• Automatic temp. control function, non-stick surface, low-power, w/ the temp. control knob as well as time knob 3.Commercial PAN\n\n• Toaster designed for baking PAN w/ independent heat control & cast-iro