12257,simple,,,"Electric Pressure Fryer MDXZ-16",1,0,visible,"The Electric Pressure Fryer MDXZ-16 is a high-performance kitchen appliance designed for commercial use, offering fast and efficient frying with even heat distribution. With a robust stainless steel construction, it features a user-friendly interface for precise temperature and pressure control, ensuring perfectly cooked, crispy results every time. Ideal for restaurants and catering services, the MDXZ-16 combines durability, safety, and superior frying capabilities to meet the demands of a busy kitchen.","[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text css=""""]Capacity: 16 L\n. All stainless steel body, easy to wash and wipe, long\nservice life.\n. Power：3 kw\n. Control temperature range ：90-190℃\n. Voltage : 220V/50 - 60 Hz\n. Net weight: 19 kg\n. Dim: 520 x 397 x 500 mm\nModel No. MDXZ-16/ CAPINOX[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,2547.1,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Fryers",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Electric-Pressure-Fryer-MDXZ-16.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Mariot,Brand,Mariot,1,1,"Type of Product","Electric Pressure Fryer",1,1,default,1,1,129,index,62,185,0,,"Electric Pressure Fryer,Electric Pressure Fryer MDXZ-16",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,MDXZ-16,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,111000100100110011010110010110011001100110010110,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
