12265,simple,,,"Electrical Pressure Fryer PFE-600",1,0,visible,"The Electrical Pressure Fryer PFE-600 is a high-performance kitchen appliance designed for commercial use. With its electric-powered system, it efficiently fries food under pressure, resulting in faster cooking times and crispier textures. Ideal for restaurants, catering services, and other food establishments, the PFE-600 offers consistent and delicious fried dishes with ease. Its durable construction and advanced safety features make it a reliable choice for busy kitchen environments.","[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text css=""""]Capacity: 25 L\nComputer control panel\n. All S/S body, easy to wash and wipe, long service life.\n. Alum lid, rugged &amp; light weight, easy to open &amp; close.\n. Four casters carrying capacity together with brake\nfunction, ease of movement and positioning.\n. Digital display control panel,\n. Machine has a total of 10 storage keys 1-0 for 10 categories\nof food frying use.\n. Built-in automatic filtration system, easy to use, energy\nefficient.\n. Control temperature range：20~200℃\n. Voltage: ~3N380v/50Hz（~3N220v/60Hz）\n. Net / Gross weight: 135 kg / 155 kg\n. Dim: 460 × 960 × 1230 mm\n. Packing size: 1030 × 510 × 1300 mm\nModel No. PFE-600/ PFE/MAR-H600E /CAPINOX[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,9780,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Fryers",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Gas-Pressure-Fryer-PFE-600.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Mariot,Brand,Mariot,1,1,"Type of Product","Electric Pressure Fryer",1,1,default,1,1,129,index,59,185,,,"Electrical Pressure Fryer PFE-600",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"PFE-600/ PFE/MAR-H600E",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011000001100110011011100100110001111000111001110,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
