12303,simple,,,"Slush Machine-OASIS 1-10 STD",1,0,visible,"Slush Machine\n. Capacity : 1 x 10 ltr\n. 1 Transparent removable bowls\n. Total Bowls Capacity: 10 lt.\n. Mixing system by patented magnetic transmission\n. 1 Adjustable thermostat.\n. Shock proof, non toxic polycarbonate container\n. Stainless steel body\n. Overload protector\n. Noise level lower than 70 dB (A)\n. Ele. Power: 530 W/ 230 V/ 50 Hz\n. Net weight: 32 kg\n. Dimension : 270 x 530 x 840 mm\nOASIS 1-10 STD/ cofrimell / italy made.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• Slush Machine</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Capacity : 1 x 10 ltr</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• 1 Transparent removable bowls</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Total Bowls Capacity: 10 lt</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Mixing system by patented magnetic transmission</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• 1 Adjustable thermostat</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Shock proof, non toxic polycarbonate container</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Stainless steel body</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Overload protector</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Noise level lower than 70 dB (A)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Ele. Power: 530 W/ 230 V/ 50 Hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Net weight: 32 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Dimension : 270 x 530 x 840 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• OASIS 1-10 STD/ cofrimell / italy made</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,5504,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Slush Machine",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/111.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/222.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/333.png",,,,,,,,,0,,Cofrimell,Brand,Cofrimell,1,1,"Type of Product","Slush Machine",1,1,default,1,1,125,index,9,171,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"OASIS 1-10 STD",field_6387359a51f50,yes,