12307,simple,,,"Juice dispenser-CAPRI 4S BLU",1,0,visible,"Juice dispenser\n. cap: 4 x 10 ltr.\n. bowl and cover: polycarbonate.\n. double cover for a better insulation of the product.\n. mixing system: electromagnetic pump.\n. compressor: hermetic, france made.\n. temperature control: adjustable thermostatic system.\n. tap two piece: no-drip, all stainless steel.\n. chassis and panels: all stainless steel.\n. power: 230 v / 50 hz / 330 w.\n. weight: 41 kg.\n. dim: 560 x 400 x 680 mm.\nCAPRI 4S BLU / cofrimell / italy made.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Juice dispenser</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• cap: 4 x 10 ltr</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• bowl and cover: polycarbonate</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• double cover for a better insulation of the product</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• mixing system: electromagnetic pump</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• compressor: hermetic, france made</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• temperature control: adjustable thermostatic system</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• tap two piece: no-drip, all stainless steel</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• chassis and panels: all stainless steel</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• power: 230 v / 50 hz / 330 w</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• weight: 41 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• dim: 560 x 400 x 680 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• CAPRI 4S BLU / cofrimell / italy made</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,4400,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Juice Maker",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/13.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/14.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/15.png",,,,,,,,,0,,Cofrimell,Brand,Cofrimell,1,1,"Type of Product","Juice Dispenser",1,1,default,1,1,125,index,7,171,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"CAPRI 4S BLU",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,001000110001000111100001111011010100111010100111,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12311,simple,,,"RATIONAL Electric iCombi Pro- ICP 6E-1/1",1,0,visible,"The RATIONAL Electric iCombi Pro ICP 6E-1/1 is a state-of-the-art kitchen appliance designed for professional cooking environments. With advanced electric operation, it offers precise control and versatile cooking capabilities. The iCombi Pro ICP 6E-1/1 features a 1/1 GN (Gastronorm) capacity, allowing efficient cooking of a diverse range of dishes. Its user-friendly interface empowers chefs to achieve consistent, high-quality results with ease. Whether you're baking, roasting, grilling, steaming, or more, this appliance provides the features and convenience needed to take your culinary creations to the next level of excellence.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• RATIONAL Electric iCombi Pro 6-1/1 3NAC400 V 50-60hz Electric unit Capacity: 6 × 1/1 GN</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• 6 lengthwise insertion for 1/1 GN Accessories</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Removable standard racks with 68 mm insertion distance</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Wide range of accessories for various cooking processes such as grilling, braising or baking</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• For use with 1/1, 1/2, 2/3, 1/3 GN-Accessories Combi-steamer mode</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Steam 30 °C – 130 °C</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Convection 30 °C – 300 °C</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Combination of steam &amp; convection from 30 °C - 300 °Cmm²</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• N. - G. Weight: 99 / 117 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Dim : 850 x 842 x 804 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• ICP 6E-1/1 / RATIONAL/ Germany made</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,38146,"COOKING LINE > Combi Oven, COOKING LINE, Top Brands","RATIONAL Electric iCombi Pro",,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/RATIONAL-Electric-iCombi-Pro.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Rational,Brand,Rational,1,1,Electric/Gas,Electric,1,1,default,1,1,131,index,81,150,0,,"RATIONAL Electric iCombi Pro",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"ICP 6E-1/1",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596592,011111100101011100001100000100100101101111001010,,,,,,,,,,"Type of Product","Electric Self Cooking",1,1,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12313,simple,,,"RATIONAL GAS iCombi Pro- ICP 6G-1/1",1,0,visible,"The RATIONAL GAS iCombi Pro ICP 6G-1/1 is an advanced kitchen appliance designed for professional cooking environments. Powered by gas, it offers precise control and versatile cooking capabilities. The iCombi Pro ICP 6G-1/1 features a 1/1 GN (Gastronorm) capacity, allowing efficient cooking of a diverse range of dishes. Its user-friendly interface empowers chefs to achieve consistent, high-quality results with ease. Whether you're baking, roasting, grilling, steaming, or more, this appliance provides the features and convenience needed to take your culinary creations to the next level of excellence using gas as the energy source.","RATIONAL iCombi Pro 6-1/1\n1NAC230 V 50-60hz GAS unit LPG 3 B/P\nCapacity: 6 × 1/1 GN\n* 6 lengthwise insertion for 1/1 GN Accessories\n* Removable standard racks with 68 mm insertion distance\n* Wide range of accessories for various cooking processes such as\ngrilling, braising or baking\n* For use with 1/1, 1/2, 2/3, 1/3 GN-Accessories\nCombi-steamer mode;\n* Steam 30 °C – 130 °C\n* Convection 30 °C – 300 °C\n* Combination of steam &amp; convection from 30 °C - 300 °Cmm²\nGas Connection / gas system / Natural gas\n* Nominal thermal load convection mode 52 MJ/h\n* Dynamic gas pressure 1.13 – 2.5 kPa\n* N. - G. Weight: 99 / 117 kg\n• Dim : 850 x 842 x 754 mm\nICP 61G / RATIONAL/ Germany made",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,45467,"COOKING LINE > Combi Oven, COOKING LINE, Special Offer","RATIONAL GAS iCombi Pro",,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/RATIONAL-Electric-iCombi-Pro.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Rational,"Type of Product","Gas Self Cooking",1,1,Brand,Rational,1,1,default,1,1,131,index,76,150,0,,"RATIONAL GAS iCombi Pro",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"ICP 6G-1/1",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011111100101011100001100000100100101101111001010,,,,,,,,,salescountdowntimer,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12314,simple,,,"RATIONAL Electric  iCombi Pro- ICP 10E-1/1",1,0,visible,"The RATIONAL Electric iCombi Pro ICP 10E-1/1 is an advanced and versatile kitchen appliance designed for professional cooking environments. With cutting-edge technology, it offers precise control and innovative cooking capabilities. The iCombi Pro ICP 10E-1/1 features electric operation and a 1/1 GN (Gastronorm) capacity, allowing for efficient and flexible cooking of a wide range of dishes. Its intuitive interface enables chefs to create consistent and high-quality results with ease. Whether you're baking, roasting, grilling, steaming, or even frying, this appliance provides the tools and convenience needed to elevate your culinary creations to a new level of excellence.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• RATIONAL iCombi Pro 10-1/1</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• 3NAC400 V 50-60hz Electric unit</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Capacity: 10 × 1/1 GN</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• 10 lengthwise insertion for 1/1 GNAccessories</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Removable standard racks with 68 mm insertion distance</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Wide range of accessories for various cooking processes such as\ngrilling, braising or baking</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• For use with 1/1, 1/2, 2/3, 1/3 GN-Accessories\nCombi-steamer mode</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Steam 30 °C – 130 °C</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Convection 30 °C – 300 °C</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Combination of steam &amp; convection from 30 °C - 300 °Cmm²</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• N. - G. Weight: 127 / 155 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Dim : 850 x 842 x 1014 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• ICP 10E-1/1 / RATIONAL/ Germany made</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,53594,"COOKING LINE > Combi Oven, COOKING LINE, Special Offer, Top Brands","RATIONAL Electric iCombi Pro- ICP 10E-1/1",,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/RATIONAL-Electric-iCombi-Pro-ICP-10E-1-1.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/rational-10e-1-1.jpg",,,,,,,,,0,,Rational,Electric/Gas,Electric,1,1,Brand,Rational,1,1,default,1,1,131,index,29,150,0,,"RATIONAL Electric iCombi Pro",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"ICP 10E-1/1",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596592,010111100111000000111100000100100101101111101001,,,,,,,,,salescountdowntimer,"Type of Product","Electric Self Cooking",1,1,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12317,simple,,,"RATIONAL GAS iCombi Pro - ICP 10G-1/1",1,0,visible,"The RATIONAL GAS iCombi Pro ICP 10G-1/1 is an advanced professional kitchen appliance designed for precision cooking. Utilizing gas power, it offers exceptional control and versatility for culinary tasks. With a 1/1 GN (Gastronorm) capacity, this iCombi Pro model enables efficient cooking of a wide array of dishes. Its user-friendly interface empowers chefs to consistently achieve high-quality results with ease. Whether you're baking, roasting, grilling, steaming, or more, this appliance equips you with the features and convenience needed to elevate your culinary creations to a superior level of excellence using gas as the energy source.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">1NAC230 V 50-60hz GAS unit LPG 3 B/P\nCapacity: 10 × 1/1 GN\n* 10 lengthwise insertion for 1/1 GN Accessories\n* Removable standard racks with 68 mm insertion distance\n* Wide range of accessories for various cooking processes such as\ngrilling, braising or baking\n* For use with 1/1, 1/2, 2/3, 1/3 GN-Accessories\nCombi-steamer mode;\n* Steam 30 °C – 130 °C\n* Convection 30 °C – 300 °C\n* Combination of steam &amp; convection from 30 °C - 300 °Cmm²\nGas Connection / gas system / Natural gas\n* Nominal thermal load convection mode 52 MJ/h\n* Dynamic gas pressure 1.13 – 2.5 kPa\n* N. - G. Weight: 127 / 155 kg\n• Dim : 850 x 842 x 1014 mm\nICP 101G/ RATIONAL/ Germany made</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,62197,"COOKING LINE > Combi Oven, COOKING LINE, Special Offer","RATIONAL GAS iCombi Pro",,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/RATIONAL-GAS-iCombi-Pro-ICP-10G-1-1.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Rational,Brand,Rational,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,198,index,68,150,0,,"RATIONAL GAS iCombi Pro",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"ICP 10G-1/1",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,0