12319,simple,,,"RATIONAL Electric iCombi Pro- XS 6-2/3 Electric",1,0,visible,"The RATIONAL Electric iCombi Pro XS 6-2/3 is a cutting-edge electric oven engineered for professional kitchens seeking precision, versatility, and efficiency. This compact powerhouse is designed to meet the demands of culinary experts by combining intelligent technology with user-friendly controls.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">RATIONAL iCombi Pro XS 6-2/3\n1NAC230V 50-60hz Electric unit\nCapacity: 6 × 2/3 GN\n&gt; 6 lengthwise insertion for 2/3 GN Containers\n&gt; Removable, swivelling hinging rack with flexible rack options on 11 levels per cooking system\n&gt; Wide range of accessories for various cooking processes such as\ngrilling, braising or baking\n&gt; For use with 1/2, 2/3, 1/3 GNAccessories\nCombi-steamer mode;\n&gt; Steam 30 °C – 130 °C\n&gt; Convection 30 °C – 300 °C\n&gt; Combination of steam and convection from 30 °C - 300 °C\n* N. - G. Weight: 67 / 76 kg\n• Dim : 655 x 621 x 567 mm\niCombi® Pro XS 6-2/3 / RATIONAL/ Germany made</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,33353,"COOKING LINE > Combi Oven, COOKING LINE, Special Offer",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/RATIONAL-Electric-iCombi-Pro-1.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Rational,Electric/Gas,Electric,1,1,"Type of Product","Electric Self Cooking",1,1,default,1,1,198,index,6,150,0,,,,"Shop now Rational online in Dubai UAE Mariot Group all kind of rational oven in uae abu dhabi duabi sharjah al ain",,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"XS 6-2/3",field_6387359a51f50,yes,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595498,010111100101111010000110010110100011010001110010,,,,,,,,,salescountdowntimer,Brand,Rational,1,1,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
