12477,simple,,,"ICE CUBE MAKER MACHINE-CB184A",1,0,visible,"The CB184A Ice Cube Maker Machine is a reliable and efficient appliance designed to produce ice cubes quickly and conveniently. With its user-friendly interface and compact design, it fits perfectly in various settings, including homes, offices, and small businesses. This machine ensures a steady supply of ice cubes to meet your cooling needs, making it an ideal addition to any space. Enjoy the convenience and refreshing coolness with the CB184A Ice Cube Maker Machine.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Production: kg. 22 kg/day</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Storage cap: kg. 4</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Air condensing system</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Voltage: 220-240/ 50hz/ 1 phase/ kw 0.32</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Made in AISI 304 18/10 stainless steel</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight (net/gross)27 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 355 x 404 x h.590 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• CB184A / BREMA / ITALIA</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,3100,4136.44,"REFRIGERATION LINE > ICE MAKER & FLAKES, REFRIGERATION LINE, sale 11.11",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/CB184A.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Brema,Type,"Ice Cube Machine",1,0,"Type of Product","Ice Cube Maker Machine",1,1,default,1,1,130,index,62,142,0,,"ICE CUBE MAKER",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,CB184A,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,001101101100101101101100110011001100110000011001,false,,,,,,,,,Brand,Brema,1,1,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12479,simple,,,"Meat mincer -SELF-SHARP DEP.TR32RSQAX235M",1,0,visible,"<strong>Meat mincer -SELF-SHARP DEP.TR32RSQAX235M</strong>\nA meat mincer, also known as a meat grinder, is a kitchen appliance designed for the purpose of grinding or mincing meat. It provides a convenient and efficient way to process various types of meat, allowing users to control the texture and freshness of the ground meat they prepare.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• cap: 500 Kg / h</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• power: 2.2 kW (3 HP)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Supply: 230V / 1N / 50Hz - 230-400V / 3 / 50Hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• package volume: 0.163 m³</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• package dim: 570 x 420 x 680h (mm)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• n.weight: 53 Kg (230V / 1N) - 43 Kg (230-400V / 3)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• g.weight: 59 Kg (230V / 1N) - 49 Kg (230-400V / 3)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• dimension: 490 x 340 x 530h (mm)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• TR32RSQAX235M/ Monofase / fimar/ italy made</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,5900.4,"FOOD PROCESSING, FOOD PROCESSING > Meat Mincer",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/32RS_tritacarne_meat_mincer_fimar-1-1.jpg, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/32RS_tritacarne_meat_mincer_fimar.jpg",,,,,,,,,0,,Fimar,"Type of Product","Meat Mincer",1,1,Brand,Fimar,1,1,default,1,1,211,index,54,161,0,,"Meat mincer -SELF-SHARP DEP.TR32RSQAX235M",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,TR32RSQAX235M,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595653,011100000111011000110100111100110000111001100011,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
