12493,simple,,,"BAR VACUUM Machine BAR300P",1,0,visible,"The <strong>BAR VACUUM Machine BAR300P</strong> is likely a vacuum sealing machine designed specifically for use in bars or similar settings. These machines are commonly used to preserve the freshness of food and beverages, particularly in bars or restaurants.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Machine aimed at prolonging food preservation times, keeping intact the organoleptic characteristics.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• The use of specific embossed bags or containers creates a vacuum level that keeps intact the organoleptic characteristics &amp; prevents the proliferation of bacteria at low temperatures: Robust ABS &amp; S/S casing – dry pump – digital control panel.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• All vacuum machines can be used for vacuum in bags or containers w/ lids specifically designed for this purpose.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power : 0.45 kW (0.6 HP)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Supply : 230V / 1N / 50-60Hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• N.Weight 6 Kg / G. Weight : 7 Kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Vacuum pump : 1,2 m³ / h</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Sealing bar 300 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Useful room dim : 320 x 260 x 140h (mm)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; paddintext-align: left; padding-top: 0;"">• Dimension: 420 x 290 x 210h (mm)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• BAR300P / fimar/ italy made.</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,1338.48,"FOOD PROCESSING > Bar Vacuum Machine, FOOD PROCESSING, Special Offer",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/BAR300P_Macchina_sottovuoto-Fimar-3.jpg, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/0-ff768b19-800-BAR300P-Digital-manual-vacuum-sealing-machine-30cm.jpg, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/BAR300P_Macchina_sottovuoto-Fimar-2.jpg",,,,,,,