12561,simple,,,"COFFEE ESPRESSO MACHINE SEMI AUTOMATIC APPIA LIFE - S",1,0,visible,"The Semi-Automatic APPIA LIFE - S Coffee Espresso Machine offers a blend of control and craftsmanship in coffee preparation. With its intuitive design and manual operation, it empowers baristas to create personalized espresso shots. Engineered for consistency and precision, this machine caters to both professional cafes and home setups. It allows users to adjust various parameters to achieve the perfect extraction, resulting in a rich and flavorful cup every time. The APPIA LIFE - S Semi-Automatic Espresso Machine strikes a balance between tradition and modernity, making it an excellent choice for those who appreciate hands-on coffee-making with a touch of innovation.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">•Single Group-Semi Automatic</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Boiler Tank Capacity: 5 Ltr</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Stainless Steel Steam Wands With Push &amp; Pull Command</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• With Soft Infusion System SIS System Makes More Efficient Extraction</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• 230 Volt / 50 - 60 Hz / 1 Ph / 1900 Watts</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Dim : 404 x 545 x 498 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Weight: 42 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Model/ APPIA LIFE-S / Nuova Simonelli/ Made in Italy</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(451px, 89px); text-align: left;"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,7531,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Coffee Machines",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uplo