12564,simple,,,"COFFEE ESPRESSO MACHINE AUTOMATIC  APPIA LIFE 1Gr SEMI",1,0,visible,"The Automatic APPIA LIFE 1Gr SEMI Coffee Espresso Machine combines innovation and convenience for a superior coffee experience. With its advanced automatic features, it simplifies the espresso-making process without compromising quality. Designed to deliver consistent and rich espresso shots, this machine is ideal for busy coffee shops and commercial setups. It offers programmable settings for different coffee profiles, ensuring a customized and flavorful cup every time. The APPIA LIFE 1Gr SEMI Automatic Espresso Machine represents the pinnacle of automated espresso preparation, making it the perfect choice for those seeking both efficiency and exceptional taste.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(430px, 8px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Single Group-Automatic</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Boiler Tank Capacity: 5 Ltr</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Volumetric Dosage</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Stainless Steel Steam Wands With Push &amp; Pull Command</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• With Soft Infusion System-SIS System Makes</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• More Efficient Extraction</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• 230 Volt / 50-60 Hz / 1 Ph / 1900 Watts</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Weight 41kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Dim : 404 x 545 x 498 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Model/ APPIA LIFE-V/ Nuova Simonelli/ Made in Italy</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(813px, 2