12567,simple,,,"COFFEE ESPRESSO MACHINE/ APPIA LIFE COMPACT-S",1,0,visible,"The APPIA LIFE COMPACT-S Coffee Espresso Machine blends simplicity and excellence in espresso crafting. With its compact design and user-friendly features, it's perfect for small spaces like cafes, offices, and homes. This machine ensures a consistent and flavorful espresso experience, offering manual control for those who appreciate hands-on brewing. The APPIA LIFE COMPACT-S brings professional-grade espresso-making within reach, delivering both convenience and high-quality results for coffee enthusiasts and baristas alike.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Two Group-Semi Automatic</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Boiler Tank Capacity: 7.5 Ltr</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Stainless Steel Steam Wands With Push &amp; Pull Command</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• With Soft Infusion System - SIS System Makes</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• More Efficient Extraction</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• 230 Volt / 50 - 60 Hz / 1 Ph / 2900 Watts</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Dim : 554 x 545 x 498 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Model/ APPIA LIFE COMPACT/Nuova Simonelli/ Made in Italy</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(850px, 122px); text-align: left;"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,10656,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Coffee Machines",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/COFFEE-ESPRESSO-MACHINE-APPIA-LIFE-COMPACT-–-S-Two-Group.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/nuova-simonelli-appia-life-compact-2-group-volumetric-espresso-machine-2_grande.png",,,,,,,,,0,,"Nuova Simonelli","Type of Product","Coffee Espresso Machine",1,1,Brand,"Nuova Simonelli",1,1,default,1,1,366,index,60,364,0,,"COFFEE ESPRESSO",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"APPIA LIFE COMPACT - S",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,111101011111110000101001111100000011000000010110,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12570,simple,,,"ESPRESSO MACHINE APPIA LIFE COMPACT - V Two Group - Automatic",1,0,visible,"The APPIA LIFE COMPACT - V Two Group Automatic Espresso Machine combines compact design and advanced automation for exceptional espresso. With its automatic features, it simplifies the espresso-making process while delivering top-notch quality. Designed for efficiency in smaller spaces, this machine offers consistent and precise coffee extraction. Its programmable settings allow for customization, ensuring a personalized cup of espresso every time. The APPIA LIFE COMPACT - V Two Group Automatic Espresso Machine strikes a balance between space-saving convenience and professional-grade performance, making it an ideal choice for cafes and setups where space is at a premium.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Nuova Simonelli</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Made in Italy</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Model : APPIA LIFE COMPACT - V</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Two Group - Automatic</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Volumetric Dosage</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Boiler Tank Capacity : 7.5 Ltr</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Stainless Steel Steam Wands With Push &amp; Pull\nCommand</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• With Soft Infusion System - SIS System Makes</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• More Efficient Extraction</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Dim : 554 x 545 x 498 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Weight: 94 Kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Witho