12574,simple,,,"COFFEE ESPRESSO MACHINE  APPIA LIFE COMPACT Semi Automatic",1,0,visible,"The APPIA LIFE COMPACT Semi-Automatic Coffee Espresso Machine combines simplicity and excellence in espresso crafting. With its compact design and user-friendly features, it's perfect for smaller spaces like cafes, offices, and home setups. This machine ensures a consistent and flavorful espresso experience, allowing users to control various brewing parameters. The APPIA LIFE COMPACT brings professional-grade espresso-making within reach, delivering both convenience and high-quality results for coffee enthusiasts and baristas alike.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Two Group-Semi Automatic</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Boiler Tank Capacity : 11 Ltr</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Two Stainless Steel Steam Wands With Push &amp;amp</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Pull Command</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• With Soft Infusion System - SIS System Makes</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• More Efficient Extraction</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Weight 133 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• 230 Volt / 50 - 60 Hz / 1 Ph / 3350 Watts</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Dim: 784 x 544 x 500 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Model/APPIA LIFE-S/ Nuova Simonelli/ Made in Italy</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(766px, 289px); text-alig