12581,simple,,,"COFFEE ESPRESSO MACHINE-  APPIA LIFE - S",1,0,visible,"The APPIA LIFE - S Coffee Espresso Machine offers a premium brewing experience for coffee enthusiasts. With advanced features and sleek design, it's designed to deliver consistently exceptional espresso. This machine combines modern technology with ease of use, making it perfect for both professional baristas and coffee lovers at home. Its precision allows for customizable coffee extraction, ensuring the perfect balance of flavors in every cup. The APPIA LIFE - S Espresso Machine is a reliable choice for those seeking high-quality espresso with style and convenience.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(379px, 55px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• COFFEE ESPRESSO MACHINE Three Group-Semi Automatic</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Tank Capacity: 15 Ltr</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Two Stainless Steel Steam Wands With Push &amp; Pull Command With Soft Infusion System - SIS System Makes More Efficient Extraction</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Without Water Softner 230 Volt / 50-60 Hz / 1 Ph / 5400 Watts</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Dim : 1014 x 544 x 500 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Model/ APPIA LIFE-S/ Nuova Simonelli/ Made in Italy</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(22px, 147px); text-align: left;"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,18593,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Coffee Machines",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/111-1-scaled.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"Nuova Simonelli","Type of Product","Coffee Espresso Machine",1,1,Series,"Table Top",1,1,default,1,1,125,index,61,364,0,,"COFFEE ESPRESSO",,,