12583,simple,,,"COFFEE ESPRESSO MACHINE  APPIA LIFE - V THREE GROUP",1,0,visible,"The APPIA LIFE - V Three Group Coffee Espresso Machine redefines the art of espresso-making. With cutting-edge features and a stylish design, it ensures a consistent and outstanding espresso experience. This machine is engineered to cater to high-volume environments, making it an ideal choice for busy cafes and coffee shops. Its precision extraction technology allows baristas to craft customizable coffee profiles, resulting in rich and balanced flavors in every cup. The APPIA LIFE - V Three Group Espresso Machine combines performance, innovation, and aesthetics, making it the ultimate solution for those seeking top-tier espresso quality with efficiency.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• COFFEE ESPRESSO MACHINE THREE GROUP</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Boiler Tank Capacity: 15 Ltr</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Two Stainless Steel Steam Wands With Push &amp; Pull Command With Soft Infusion System - SIS System Makes More Efficient Extraction</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Without Water Softner 230 Volt / 50 - 60 Hz / 1 Ph / 5400 Watts</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Dim : 1014 x 544 x 500 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Model/ APPIA LIFE-V/ Nuova Simonelli/ Made in Italy</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(797px, 81px);"" aria-expanded=""true"">\n<div id=""tippy-1"" style=""z-index: 100000200; visibility: visible; position: absolute; inset: 0px auto auto 0px; margin: 0px; transform: translate(399px, 20px);"" data-tippy-root="""">\n<div class=""tippy-box"" style=""max-width: 350px; transition-duration: 300ms;"" tabindex=""-1"" ro