12588,simple,,,"UPRIGHT CHILLER GN1410TN",1,0,visible,"<strong>UPRIGHT CHILLER - GN1410TN</strong>\nThe GN1410TN Upright Chiller is a high-capacity cooling solution designed for commercial kitchens. With adjustable shelving and precise temperature control, it provides efficient storage for perishable items. Its durable stainless steel construction ensures long-lasting performance, making it ideal for busy food service operations.","<p style=""text-align: left; margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• UPRIGHT CHILLER GN1410TN</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left; margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• AISI 304 18/10 S/S interior &amp; exterior w/ sanitary corner except rear panel &amp; part of bottom</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left; margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• automatic closing door w/ magnetic gasket, 90° reversible w/ 4 castor wheels</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left; margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• injected polyurethane insulation, CFC free, density: 40 kgs / m3</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left; margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cap: 1285 ltr</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left; margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• w/ 3+3 shelf &amp; 2 Drs</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left; margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Temp: +2˚ ~ +8° at 32° C</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left; margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power Supply: 230v / 50 Hz / 1Ph</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left; margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• fridge power: 1130 Watt</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left; margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• refrigerant : R404a</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left; margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Net Weight: 197 Kg</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left; margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 1480 x 830 x 2040mm (WxDxH)</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left; margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Digital: DIXELL / ITALY MADE</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left; margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• compressor : ASPERA / EMBRACO / ITALY</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left; margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• GN1410TN / <a href=""https://mariotstore.comold/brand/inofrigo/"">Inofrigo</a> / MARIOT MADE</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left; margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• ISO9001, CE&amp;ROHS approved</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,5771,"REFRIGERATION LINE > Freezer & Chillers, REFRIGERATION LINE",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/WhatsApp-Image-2022-03-31-at-5.55.48-PM.jpeg,,,,,,,,,0,,Inofrigo,"Type of Product","Chillers & Freezers",1,1,Brand,Inofrigo,1,1,default,1,1,222,index,63,373,0,,"UPRIGHT CHILLER GN1410TN",,"• UPRIGHT CHILLER GN1410TN
