12629,simple,,,"DOUGH MIXER DH-20GA",1,0,visible,"The DOUGH MIXER DH-20GA is a versatile and efficient appliance designed for both home and small-scale commercial use. Featuring a 20-liter capacity, it is perfect for mixing medium-sized batches of dough for bread, pastries, and more. The DH-20GA boasts a powerful motor with multiple speed settings, ensuring thorough and consistent mixing. Its durable stainless steel bowl and attachments are built to withstand regular use, while the easy-to-use control panel simplifies operation. Whether you're a home baker or a small business, the DH-20GA provides reliable performance and convenience for all your dough mixing needs.","[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text css=""""]\n<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">. bowl cap: 20 ltr\n. flour cap: 8 kg.\n. drawn stainless steel bowl.\n. mixing speed: 158 RPM\n. voltage: 220V - 50-60Hz / 1 Ph\n. power: 1.1 kw.\n. net.weight: 70 kg.\n. dim: 690×380×730 mm.\nDH-20GA / capinox / Italian model.</p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,2860,"BAKERY LINE, BAKERY LINE > Bakery Mixers",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/DOUGH-MIXER-DH-GA.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/DOUGH-MIXER-DH-GA-20.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/DOUGH-MIXER-DH-GA-SIDE.png",,,,,,,,,0,,Capinox,"Type of Product","Dough Mixer",1,1,Brand,Capinox,1,1,default,1,1,213,index,70,259,0,,"DOUGH MIXER,DOUGH MIXER DH-20GA",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,DH-20GA,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595659,001101001111001001101100101001110010011100110010,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12633,simple,,,"DOUGH MIXER DH-30GA",1,0,visible,"The DOUGH MIXER DH-30GA is a powerful and reliable appliance tailored for medium to large-scale dough preparation. With a 30-liter capacity, it is ideal for bakeries, pizzerias, and large kitchens. This mixer features a robust motor with adjustable speed settings, ensuring thorough and consistent mixing for various types of dough. The DH-30GA is constructed with a heavy-duty stainless steel bowl and durable attachments, designed to withstand frequent use and ensure longevity. Its user-friendly control panel makes operation straightforward and efficient. The DH-30GA is the perfect solution for professional bakers and chefs seeking quality and performance in their dough mixing tasks.","[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text css=""""]\n<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">. bowl cap: 30 ltr\n. flour cap: 12 kg.\n. drawn stainless steel bowl.\n. mixing speed: 158 RPM\n. voltage: 220 v: 50-60Hz / 1 Ph\n. power: 1.5 kw.\n. net.weight: 90 kg.\n. dim: 770×430×810 mm.\nDH-30GA / capinox / Italian model.</p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,3084,"BAKERY LINE, BAKERY LINE > Bakery Mixers",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/DOUGH-MIXER-DH-GA.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/DOUGH-MIXER-DH-GA-30.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/DOUGH-MIXER-DH-GA-SIDE.png",,,,,,,,,0,,Capinox,"Type of Product","Dough Mixer",1,1,Brand,Capinox,1,1,default,1,1,213,index,64,259,0,,"DOUGH MIXER,DOUGH MIXER DH-30GA",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,DH-30GA,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595665,001101001111001001101100101001110010011100110010,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12635,simple,,,"DOUGH MIXER DH-40GA",1,0,visible,"The DOUGH MIXER DH-40GA is an industrial-strength appliance designed for large-scale dough preparation in commercial kitchens and bakeries. With a generous 40-liter capacity, it is perfect for mixing substantial batches of dough with ease and efficiency. Equipped with a powerful motor and adjustable speed settings, the DH-40GA ensures thorough and consistent mixing for all types of dough. Its heavy-duty construction, including a robust stainless steel bowl and attachments, guarantees durability and long-lasting performance. The intuitive control panel makes operation simple and precise, making the DH-40GA an essential tool for professional bakers and large-scale food production environments.","[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text css=""""]\n<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">. bowl cap: 40 ltr\n. flour cap: 15 kg.\n. drawn stainless steel bowl.\n. mixing speed: 90 RPM\n. voltage: 380 v: 50-60Hz / 3 Ph\n. power: 1.5/2.2 kw.\n. net.weight: 125 kg.\n. dim: 870×480×940 mm.\nDH-40GA / capinox / ITALIAN model .</p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,3867,"BAKERY LINE, BAKERY LINE > Bakery Mixers",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/DOUGH-MIXER-DH-GA.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/DOUGH-MIXER-DH-GA-40.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/DOUGH-MIXER-DH-GA-SIDE.png",,,,,,,,,0,,Capinox,"Type of Product","Dough Mixer",1,1,Brand,Capinox,1,1,default,1,1,213,index,69,259,0,,"DOUGH MIXER,DOUGH MIXER DH-40GA",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,DH-40GA,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595665,001101001111001001101100101001110010011100110010,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12637,simple,,,"DOUGH MIXER DH-50GA",1,0,visible,"The DOUGH MIXER DH-50GA is a top-tier industrial appliance designed for high-volume dough production in commercial kitchens and bakeries. With an impressive 50-liter capacity, it is ideal for mixing large quantities of dough efficiently and consistently. This mixer features a powerful motor with multiple speed settings, allowing for precise control over different dough types. The DH-50GA is built with a durable stainless steel bowl and attachments, ensuring longevity and reliability under heavy use. Its user-friendly control panel simplifies operation, making it an indispensable asset for professional bakers and large-scale food production facilities.","[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text css=""""]\n<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">. bowl cap: 50 ltr\n. flour cap: 20 kg.\n. drawn stainless steel bowl.\n. mixing speed: 90 RPM\n. voltage: 380 v: 50-60Hz / 3 Ph\n. power: 1.5/2.2 kw.\n. net.weight: 130 kg.\n. dim: 890×540×940 mm.\nDH-50GA / capinox / ITALIAN model</p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,4205,"BAKERY LINE, BAKERY LINE > Bakery Mixers",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/DOUGH-MIXER-DH-GA.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/DOUGH-MIXER-DH-GA-50.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/DOUGH-MIXER-DH-GA-SIDE.png",,,,,,,,,0,,Capinox,"Type of Product","Dough Mixer",1,1,Brand,Capinox,1,1,default,1,1,213,index,70,259,0,,"DOUGH MIXER,DOUGH MIXER DH-50GA",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,DH-50GA,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595665,001101001111001001101100101001110010011100110010,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12639,simple,,,"DOUGH MIXER DH-80",1,0,visible,"The DOUGH MIXER DH-80 is a robust and efficient commercial-grade dough mixer designed for high-volume baking operations. With a powerful motor and 80-liter capacity, it effortlessly handles large batches of dough, ensuring consistent mixing for breads, pastries, and other baked goods. Ideal for bakeries, restaurants, and food production facilities, this mixer is built for durability and ease of use, featuring adjustable speeds and safety features for optimal performance.","[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text css=""""]\n<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">. bowl cap: 80 ltr\n. Max Kneading cap: 25 kg.\n. drawn stainless steel bowl.\n. mixing speed: 210/107 rpm/min.\n. bowl speed: 16 rpm / min.\n. voltage: 3~380 v / 50-60Hz / 3 phase\n. power: 1.5/2.4 kw.\n. net.weight: 439 kg.\n. dim: 1122 x 682 x 1305 mm.\nDH-80 / capinox / France model .</p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]",,,taxable,,0,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,10215,"BAKERY LINE, BAKERY LINE > Bakery Mixers",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/DOUGH-MIXER-DH.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/DOUGH-MIXER-DH80.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/DOUGH-MIXER-side-DH.png",,,,,,,,,0,,Capinox,"Type of Product","Dough Mixer",1,1,Brand,Capinox,1,1,default,1,1,15,index,72,259,0,,"DOUGH MIXER,DOUGH MIXER DH-80",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,DH-80,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595665,100111011001011001010011010001101010110110011000,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12643,simple,,,"DOUGH MIXER DH-100",1,0,visible,"The DOUGH MIXER DH-100 is a heavy-duty industrial dough mixer with a 100-liter capacity, tailored for large-scale baking and food production. Equipped with a high-powered motor, it efficiently mixes large quantities of dough, ensuring uniform texture and quality. Perfect for bakeries, pizzerias, and food processing plants, this mixer offers variable speed settings and robust safety features, providing reliable and consistent performance in demanding environments.","[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text css=""""]\n<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">. bowl cap: 100 ltr\n. Max Kneading cap: 40 kg.\n. drawn stainless steel bowl.\n. mixing speed: 210/107 rpm/min.\n. bowl speed: 16 rpm / min.\n. voltage: 3~380 v / 50-60Hz / 3 Ph\n. power: 3/4.5 kw.\n. net.weight: 482 kg.\n. dim: 1160 x 650 x 1340 mm.\nDH-100 / capinox / France model .</p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,12616,"BAKERY LINE, BAKERY LINE > Bakery Mixers",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/DOUGH-MIXER-DH.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/DOUGH-MIXER-DH100.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/DOUGH-MIXER-side-DH.png",,,,,,,,,0,,Capinox,"Type of Product","Dough Mixer",1,1,Brand,Capinox,1,1,default,1,1,213,index,68,259,0,,"DOUGH MIXER,DOUGH MIXER DH-100",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,DH-100,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595659,100111011001011001010011010001101010110110011000,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12645,simple,,,"DOUGH MIXER DH-130",1,0,visible,"The DOUGH MIXER DH-130 is a powerful industrial-grade mixer with a 130-liter capacity, engineered for extensive dough mixing tasks in large-scale bakeries and food production facilities. Featuring a high-capacity motor and advanced mixing technology, it ensures thorough and consistent dough preparation for a variety of baked goods. This mixer is designed for durability, ease of operation, and safety, making it an essential asset for high-demand culinary environments.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• bowl cap: 130 ltr</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Max Kneading cap: 50 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• drawn stainless steel bowl</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• mixing speed: 210/107 rpm/min</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• bowl speed: 16 rpm / min</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• voltage: 3~380 v / 50Hz / 3 Phz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• power: 2.8/5.6 kw</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• net.weight: 522 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• dim: 750 x 1222 x 1430mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• DH-130 / capinox / France model</p>",,,taxable,,0,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,15090,"BAKERY LINE, BAKERY LINE > Bakery Mixers",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/DOUGH-MIXER-DH.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/DOUGH-MIXER-DH120.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/DOUGH-MIXER-side-DH.png",,,,,,,,,0,,Capinox,"Type of Product","Dough Mixer",1,1,Brand,Capinox,1,1,default,1,1,213,index,65,259,0,,"DOUGH MIXER,DOUGH MIXER DH-130",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,DH-130,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595659,100111011001011001010011010001101010110110011000,true,backend,,,,,,,,,