12714,simple,,,"POPCORN MACHINE AB-1808",1,0,visible,"<strong>POPCORN MACHINE - AB-1808</strong>\nThe AB-1808 Popcorn Machine is a reliable and efficient solution for making delicious, freshly popped popcorn. With a durable design, easy operation, and high-capacity output, it’s perfect for cinemas, concession stands, and events. Add a touch of nostalgia and aroma to any setting with this classic machine.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Cap : 4.5 kg / hr</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Power supply: ~220V / 50 hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Power : 1.3 kw</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Dim : 560 x 420 x 680 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• AB-1808</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(760px, 8px); text-align: left;"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,550,"COOKING LINE, FOOD PROCESSING, Limited Sale, Special Offer",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/popcornN-MACHINE.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Mariot,"Type of Product","Popcorn Machine",1,1,Brand,Mariot,1,1,default,1,1,136,index,60,185,0,,"POPCORN MACHINE AB-1808,POPCORN MACHINE",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,AB-1808,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734597028,011100011010111001001001110100100111000011100011,false,,,,,,,,salescountdowntimer,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12716,simple,,,"GAS ROTARY OVEN GCXZ - 16",1,0,visible,"The Gas Rotary Oven GCXZ-16 is a reliable and efficient baking appliance crafted for professional kitchens. Featuring a rotary design, it ensures even baking and consistent results for a variety of baked goods. Powered by gas, this oven offers quick and precise temperature control, making it ideal for busy commercial settings. With its compact size and robust construction, the GCXZ-16 is a perfect choice for bakeries and restaurants seeking high-quality baking performance.","[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text css=""""]\n<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">. Capacity : 16 trays\n. with one trolley\n. Tray dim: 40 x 60 mm.\n. Plc touch screen control panel (option)\n. Adjust door seal rubber\n. 5 adjustable section of hot wind outputing, even baking.\n. Interior and exterior all stainless steal easy clean\n. Gas operated LPG\n. Net weight: 1950 kg.\n. Dim: 1280 x 2250 x 2400 mm.\nGCXZ - 16 / Capinox / France model</p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,37753,"BAKERY LINE, BAKERY LINE > Bakery Oven",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/gas-rotary-oven.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/gas-rotary-oven-front.png",,,,,,,,,0,,Capinox,"Type of Product","Gas Rotary Oven",1,1,Brand,Capinox,1,1,default,1,1,198,index,11,259,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"GCXZ - 16",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595671,011100101100111000110100111100001011001111001000,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12719,simple,,,"GAS ROTARY OVEN GCXZ - 32",1,0,visible,"The Gas Rotary Oven GCXZ-32 is a powerful and efficient baking solution designed for professional kitchens. With its rotary design, it ensures even baking and consistent results across a wide variety of baked goods. Powered by gas, this oven offers rapid heat-up times and precise temperature control, making it ideal for high-volume production. Its spacious interior accommodates large batches of baked goods, perfect for busy commercial settings such as bakeries and restaurants. The GCXZ-32 combines reliability, efficiency, and versatility to deliver superior baking performance.","[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text css=""""]\n<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">. Capacity : 32 trays\n. with two trolley\n. Tray dim: 40 x 60 mm.\n. Plc touch screen control panel (option)\n. Adjust door seal rubber\n. 5 adjustable section of hot wind outputing, even baking.\n. Interior and exterior all stainless steal easy clean\n. Gas operated LPG\n. Net weight: 1950 kg.\n. Dim: 1660 x 2730 x 2400 mm.\nGCXZ - 32 / Capinox / France model</p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,54201,"BAKERY LINE, BAKERY LINE > Bakery Oven",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/gas-rotary-oven.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/gas-rotary-oven-front.png",,,,,,,,,0,,Capinox,"Type of Product","Gas Rotary Oven",1,1,Brand,Capinox,1,1,default,1,1,198,index,11,259,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"GCXZ - 32",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595671,011100101100111000110100111100001011001111001000,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12720,simple,,,"ELECTRIC ROTARY OVEN GCXZ - 16E",1,0,visible,"The Electric Rotary Oven GCXZ-16E is a versatile and efficient baking appliance designed for professional kitchens. With its rotary feature, it ensures even baking and consistent results for a variety of baked goods. Its electric operation makes it convenient to use, while its compact size saves valuable kitchen space. Perfect for bakeries or restaurants, the GCXZ-16E delivers high-quality baked goods with ease and precision.","[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text css=""""]\n<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">. Capacity : 16 trays\n. with one trolley\n. Tray dim: 40 x 60 mm.\n. Plc touch screen control panel (option)\n. Adjustable door rubber seal, saving energy\n. 5 adjustable section of hot wind outputing, even baking.\n. Interior and exterior all stainless steal easy clean\n. Electric power: 380V/ 50-60hz/ 3phase / 33 kW\n. Net weight: 1950 kg.\n. Dim: 1280 x 2250 x 2400 mm.\nGCXZ - 16E / Capinox / France model</p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,31682,"BAKERY LINE, BAKERY LINE > Bakery Oven",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/gas-rotary-oven.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/gas-rotary-oven-front.png",,,,,,,,,0,,Capinox,"Type of Product","Electric Rotary Oven",1,1,Brand,Capinox,1,1,default,1,1,198,index,7,259,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"GCXZ - 16E",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595665,011100101100111000110100111100001011001111001000,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
