12802,simple,,,"GAS COUNTERTOP CHARBROILER 6024CBF",1,0,visible,"The GAS COUNTERTOP CHARBROILER 6024CBF is a high-performance cooking appliance designed for commercial kitchens. It features a durable stainless steel construction and adjustable grates, allowing for precise heat control and efficient cooking. The charbroiler uses gas burners to deliver consistent, high-heat output, making it ideal for grilling meats, vegetables, and other foods to perfection. Its compact, countertop design maximizes kitchen space while providing robust grilling capabilities, ensuring it meets the demanding needs of busy culinary environments.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px;"">• Grid Area: 496 sq. in</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px;"">• With 2 control knobs</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px;"">• Highly polished 1” thick polished steel or chrome plate</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px;"">• Modulating thermostat inserted into the griddle plate 3/16” from the cooking surface, adjusts from 150° to 450°F providing quick response to surface temperature change</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px;"">• Heavy duty chrome plated cast zinc knobs</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px;"">• grease trough &amp; S/S drawer</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px;"">• welded steel frame with S/S front, 4"" legs</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px;"">• 70,000 BTU, cULus, UL EPH</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px;"">• Natural gas includes LP conversion kit</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px;"">• N. G. weight: (85.7 kg/63.5 kg) - (99.3 kg/75.3 kg)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px;"">• Dim: 610 x 737 x 391 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px;"">• Star Model No. 6024CBF / USA made</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,10146,"COOKING LINE",,,,,,,,,,,,0,,"Star Manufacturing USA","Type of Product","Gas Countertop Charbroiler",1,1,Brand,"Star Manufacturing USA",1,1,defaul