12832,simple,,,"GAS COOKER (6 GAS RANGE ON LARGE GAS OVEN) E-RQB-900-6A",1,0,visible,"The GAS COOKER E-RQB-900-6A is a powerful and versatile cooking appliance designed for high-capacity kitchen environments. This model features six high-performance gas burners on top, providing ample space and heat for multiple cooking tasks simultaneously. Beneath the burners, a large gas oven offers excellent baking and roasting capabilities with precise temperature control. Constructed with durable stainless steel, the cooker is built for longevity and easy cleaning. Its ergonomic design and reliable performance make the E-RQB-900-6A an ideal choice for busy restaurants, hotels, and catering services seeking to enhance their cooking efficiency and productivity.",". GAS COOKER (6 GAS RANGE ON LARGE GAS OVEN) E-RQB-900-6A\n. 6 gas range on large gas oven.\n. enameled oven with isolated chamber and door.\n. the temperature is adjustable from 150 to 300 °c.\n. lateral grid holders with 3 positions.\n. extractable for easy cleaning.\n. adjustable legs.\n. cooker power: 4 x 5.5 kw + 2 x 7.5 kw.\n. oven power: 12 kw.\n. total poer: 49 kw.\n. net weight: 900 kg.\n. dim: 1200 x 900 x 850+120 mm.\n. E-RQB-900-6A""",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,7840,"COOKING LINE > Cooker, COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Cooker > Series 900",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/E-RQB-900-6s.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,"Type of Product","Gas Cooker",1,1,Brand,Stilco,1,1,default,1,1,129,index,79,380,0,,"GAS COOKER,GAS COOKER (6 GAS RANGE ON LARGE GAS OVEN) E-RQB-900-6A",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E-RQB-900-6S,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110101011100111000001000010100101100001110011111,false,,,,,,,,,Electric/Gas,Gas,1,1,Series,"Series 90",1,1,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12837,simple,,,"GAS COOKER (4 GAS RANGE ON GAS OVEN) E-RQB-900",1,0,visible,"The Gas Cooker E-RQB-900 is a professional-grade kitchen appliance designed for efficient cooking in commercial settings. Featuring four gas burners on a spacious cooking surface and a dedicated gas oven, this cooker provides versatility for various culinary tasks. The appliance is equipped with precise heat controls, allowing chefs to achieve optimal results with ease. Its sturdy construction ensures durability in demanding kitchen environments, while the user-friendly design enhances operational efficiency. Ideal for commercial kitchens, the Gas Cooker E-RQB-900 combines multiple burners and a gas oven, making it a reliable and efficient choice for chefs seeking performance and versatility in their cooking equipment.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(805px, 14px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",". GAS COOKER (4 GAS RANGE ON GAS OVEN) E-RQB-900\n. 4 gas range on gas oven.\n. enameled oven with isolated chamber and door.\n. heating by means of stabilized fl ame burner with\n. piezoelectric lighting.\n. the temperature is adjustable from 150 to 300 °c.\n. lateral grid holders with 3 positions.\n. extractable for easy cleaning.\n. adjustable legs.\n. cooker power: 2 x 5.5 kw + 2 x 7.5 kw.\n. oven power: 7.7 kw.\n. total poer: 33.7 kw.\n. net weight: 524 kg.\n. dim: 800 x 900 x 850+120 mm.\n. E-RQB-900""",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,5951,"COOKING LINE > Cooker, COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Cooker > Series 900",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/E-RQB-900.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Gas-Style-Range-with-4-Burner-Oven-E-RQB-900-.webp",,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,"Type of Product","Gas Cooker",1,1,Brand,Stilco,1,1,default,1,1,129,index,79,380,0,,"GAS COOKER,GAS COOKER (4 GAS RANGE ON GAS OVEN) E-RQB-900",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E-RQB-900,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110101011010110010101010010110000110010101001101,,,,,,,,,,Electric/Gas,Gas,1,1,Series,"Series 90",1,1,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12839,simple,,,"ELECTRIC FRYER ON CABINET E-DZ-900",1,0,visible,"The Electric Fryer on Cabinet E-DZ-900 is a professional-grade kitchen appliance designed for efficient and high-capacity frying. Mounted on a sturdy cabinet, this electric fryer is equipped with a powerful heating system, making it ideal for commercial kitchens and food establishments. With user-friendly controls and a spacious frying area, it allows for the quick and simultaneous preparation of large batches of crispy and flavorful fried foods. The E-DZ-900 features precise temperature regulation for consistent cooking results and is built with durability in mind. Easy to clean and maintain, this electric fryer on cabinet is a reliable solution for those seeking a robust and efficient frying option in a commercial setting.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",". ELECTRIC FRYER ON CABINET E-DZ-900\n. oil cap: 24+24 ltr.\n. high capacity containers entirely built in s/steel.\n. equipped with drain tap in the tank.\n. container fi lter to collect used oil.\n. stainless steel horizontal burners with thermostatic safety valves.\n. bowl dim: 280 x 335 x 320 mm.\n. basket dim: 290 x 260 x 140 mm.\n. Voltage: 380 V / 50 Hz\n. Power: 24 kw\n. net weight: 78 kg\n. dim: 800 x 900 x 850+120 mm.\n. E-DZ-900",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,5601,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Fryers",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/E-DZ-900.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Electric-Style-Two-Fryer-Include-Two-Basket-with-Cabinet-E-DZ-900-.webp",,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,"Type of Product","Electric Fryer",1,1,Brand,Stilco,1,1,default,1,1,129,index,79,380,0,,"ELECTRIC FRYER ON CABINET,ELECTRIC FRYER ON CABINET E-DZ-900",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E-DZ-900,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110101011010110010100011010100001110001110001101,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12842,simple,,,"GAS FRYER ON CABINET E-RQZ-900",1,0,visible,"The Gas Fryer on Cabinet E-RQZ-900 is a professional-grade kitchen appliance designed for efficient and high-capacity frying in commercial settings. Mounted on a sturdy cabinet, this gas fryer features precise temperature controls for optimal frying results. With its durable construction and spacious frying area, it is well-suited for handling large batches of crispy and flavorful fried foods. The user-friendly design and easy-to-clean components make it a reliable choice for busy kitchens, providing chefs and food establishments with a convenient and efficient solution for their frying needs.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(853px, 6px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",". GAS FRYER ON CABINET E-RQZ-900\n. oil cap: 20+20 ltr.\n. high capacity containers entirely built in s/steel.\n. equipped with drain tap in the tank.\n. container fi lter to collect used oil.\n. stainless steel horizontal burners with thermostatic safety valves.\n. bowl dim: 280 x 335 x 320 mm.\n. basket dim: 290 x 260 x 140 mm.\n. basket qty: 2.\n. gas power: 31 kw.\n. net weight: 363 kg\n. dimension: 800 x 900 x 850 mm.\n. E-RQZ-900 .""",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,6434,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Fryers",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/E-DZ-900.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,"Type of Product","Gas Fryer on Cabinet",1,1,Brand,Stilco,1,1,default,1,1,129,index,79,380,0,,"GAS FRYER ON CABINET,GAS FRYER ON CABINET E-RQZ-900",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E-RQZ-900,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110101011010110010100011010100001110001110001101,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12843,simple,,,"GAS LAVA STONE GRILL ON CABINET E-RQH-900",1,0,visible,"The Gas Lava Stone Grill on Cabinet E-RQH-900 is a versatile outdoor cooking appliance designed for professional grilling experiences. With its durable construction and lava stone cooking surface, this gas grill offers even heat distribution, imparting a distinctive smoky flavor to your dishes. The inclusion of a convenient cabinet enhances storage and operational efficiency. The E-RQH-900 features user-friendly controls, making it suitable for various grilling applications. Ideal for both residential and commercial use, this gas grill provides ample space for cooking a variety of dishes with an authentic touch. Whether you're hosting a barbecue or seeking a reliable solution for professional grilling, the Gas Lava Stone Grill on Cabinet E-RQH-900 delivers versatility and precision for flavorful outdoor cooking.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(452px, 6px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",". GAS LAVA STONE GRILL ON CABINET E-RQH-900\n. stainless steel aisi 304 work surface 15/10 thick.\n. removable &amp; adjustable in height respect to the burners.\n. stainless steel aisi 304 adjustable feets.\n. work surface with wide extension.\n. gas valve with safety thermocouple &amp; pilot flame.\n. piezoelectric ignition.\n. easily extractable waste collection drawer.\n. grill size: 2x390*600 mm.\n. power: 14.4 kw.\n. volume: 1 m³.\n. weight: 136 kg.\n. dimension: 800 x 900 x 850+120 mm.\n. E-RQH-900",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,6043,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Fryers",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/E-RQH-900.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,"Type of Product","Gas Lava Stone Grill",1,1,Brand,Stilco,1,1,default,1,1,129,index,79,380,0,,"GAS LAVA STONE,GAS LAVA STONE GRILL ON CABINET,GAS LAVA STONE GRILL ON CABINET E-RQH-900",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E-RQH-900,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_651