12845,simple,,,"GAS GRILL ON CABINET E-RQP-900*4Y",1,0,visible,"The Gas Grill on Cabinet E-RQP-900*4Y is a high-capacity, commercial-grade grilling unit designed for demanding kitchen environments. It features four powerful gas burners and a spacious grilling surface, allowing for simultaneous cooking of large quantities of food. The unit is mounted on a sturdy cabinet with ample storage space, providing convenience and organization in busy kitchens. The grill's robust construction, including a durable stainless steel finish, ensures longevity and ease of cleaning. With precise temperature control and efficient heat distribution, the E-RQP-900*4Y delivers consistent and high-quality grilling results, making it ideal for restaurants, hotels, and catering operations.",". GAS GRILL ON CABINET E-RQP-900*4Y\n. full smooth plate.\n. steel tubular burners with pilot light.\n. safety thermocouple and piezoelectric lighter.\n. removable splashguard on three sides.\n. safety gas valves.\n. fat collecting tray with fall-prevention block.\n. adjustable legs.\n. plate size: 700 x 580 x 20 mm\n. power: 28 kw.\n. net weight: 142 kg / gross weight: 168 kg.\n. dim: 800 x 900 x 850+120 mm.\n. E-RQP-900*4Y""",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,6043,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Grills",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/E-RQP-E-900-Electric-Griddle-500x500-1.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,Brand,Stilco,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,129,index,79,380,0,,"GAS GRILL,GAS GRILL ON CABINET,GAS GRILL ON CABINET E-RQP-900*4Y",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E-RQP-900*4Y,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110100011010110010010011010100101110000111000111,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12847,simple,,,"GAS GRILL ON CABINET  (1/2 SMOOTH + 1/2 GROOVED PLATE) E-RQP-900",1,0,visible,"The Gas Grill on Cabinet E-RQP-900 is a versatile outdoor cooking appliance designed for professional grilling. Featuring a unique 1/2 smooth and 1/2 grooved plate configuration, this gas grill provides chefs with the flexibility to cook a variety of dishes. The robust construction ensures durability, while the powerful burners deliver even heat distribution across the cooking surface. With user-friendly controls and ample cooking space, the E-RQP-900 is suitable for both residential and commercial use. Whether you prefer the precision of a smooth plate or the distinctive grill marks from the grooved side, this gas grill on cabinet offers a reliable and efficient solution for outdoor grilling.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(741px, 19px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",". GAS GRILL ON CABINET (1/2 SMOOTH + 1/2 GROOVED PLATE) E-RQP-900\n. 1/2 smooth + 1/2 grooved plate.\n. steel tubular burners with pilot light.\n. safety thermocouple and piezoelectric lighter.\n. removable splashguard on three sides.\n. safety gas valves.\n. fat collecting tray with fall-prevention block.\n. adjustable legs.\n. plate size: 795 x 70 mm\n. power: 28 kw.\n. net weight: 250 kg.\n. dim: 800 x 900 x 850+120 mm.\n. E-RQP-90",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,6043,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Grills",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/E-DP-900.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,Brand,Stilco,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,129,index,79,380,0,,"GAS GRILL,GAS GRILL ON CABINET,GAS GRILL ON CABINET (1/2 SMOOTH + 1/2 GROOVED PLATE)",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E-RQP-900,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110101010010110010100011010100101010101101001101,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12849,simple,,,"ELECTRIC GRILL ON CABINET E-DP-900",1,0,visible,"The Electric Grill on Cabinet E-DP-900 is a professional-grade kitchen appliance designed for versatile grilling in a commercial setting. Mounted on a robust cabinet, this electric grill offers a spacious cooking surface, making it suitable for high-capacity food preparation. With precise temperature controls, it ensures even and efficient grilling for a variety of dishes. The E-DP-900 is equipped with features for ease of use and maintenance, providing a reliable solution for businesses seeking a durable and efficient electric grill. Whether cooking meats, vegetables, or other grillables, this appliance delivers consistent and flavorful results, making it a valuable addition to commercial kitchens and food establishments.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",". ELECTRIC GRILL ON CABINET E-DP-900\n. (2/3flat &amp; 1/3 Grooved)\n. steel tubular burners with pilot light.\n. safety thermocouple and piezoelectric lighter.\n. removable splashguard on three sides.\n. safety gas valves.\n. fat collecting tray with fall-prevention block.\n. adjustable legs.\n. plate size: 700 x 580 x 20 mm\n. power: 12 kw.\n. voltage: 380V / 50 hz\n. net weight: 130 kg.\n. dim: 800 x 900 x 850+120 mm.\n. E-DP-900""",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,4791,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Grills",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/E-DP-900.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,"Type of Product","Electric Grill",1,1,Brand,Stilco,1,1,default,1,1,129,index,79,380,0,,"ELECTRIC GRILL ON CABINET,ELECTRIC GRILL ON CABINET E-DP-900",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E-DP-900,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110101010010110010100011010100101010101101001101,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12850,simple,,,"FOUR ROUND EGO HOT PLATE WITH OVEN E-DBJ-900-4Y",1,0,visible,"The FOUR ROUND EGO HOT PLATE WITH OVEN E-DBJ-900-4Y is a versatile kitchen appliance designed for efficient cooking and baking. Featuring four EGO hot plates, this appliance allows you to simultaneously cook multiple dishes with precision temperature control. The integrated oven adds functionality, enabling you to bake and roast with ease. The compact and stylish design makes it a convenient addition to any kitchen, offering a seamless blend of functionality and modern aesthetics for an enhanced cooking experience.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",". FOUR ROUND EGO HOT PLATE WITH OVEN E-DBJ-900-4Y\n. with 4 German EGO round hot plate.\n. with under oven.\n. over-temperature protection &amp; flame failure protection adjustable feet.\n. heating temp: 10.4 + 4.8 kw.\n. total heating temp: 20.8 kw.\n. temperature controlling range: 0~300°c.\n. power: 380v/50hz\n. net weight: 112 kg.\n. Dim: 800*900*850+120 mm.\n. E-DBJ-900-4Y",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,14000,"COOKING LINE > Cooker, COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Cooker > Series 900",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/FOUR-ROUND-EGO-HOT-PLATE-WITH-OVEN-E-DBJ-900-4Y.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/FOUR-SQUARE-EGO-HOT-PLATE-WITH-OVEN-E-DBJ-900.png",,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,"Type of Product","Four Round Ego Hot Plate with Oven",1,1,Brand,Stilco,1,1,default,1,1,195,index,63,380,0,,"FOUR ROUND EGO HOT PLATE WITH OVEN,FOUR ROUND EGO HOT PLATE WITH OVEN E-DBJ-900-4Y",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E-DBJ-900-4Y,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110101110000110000100011111100101010011101001100,true,backend,,,,,,,,Electric/Gas,Electric,1,1,Series,"Series 90",1,1,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12853,simple,,,"FOUR SQUARE EGO HOT PLATE WITH OVEN E-DBJ-900",1,0,visible,"The FOUR SQUARE EGO HOT PLATE WITH OVEN E-DBJ-900 combines convenience and versatility in a compact kitchen appliance. Equipped with four square EGO hot plates, it enables simultaneous cooking of various dishes with precise temperature regulation. The integrated oven enhances its functionality, allowing for baking and roasting, making it a multi-purpose solution for diverse culinary needs. The appliance's sleek design and space-saving features make it an attractive and efficient addition to any kitchen, offering a seamless blend of practicality and modern style.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(569px, 48px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",". FOUR SQUARE EGO HOT PLATE WITH OVEN E-DBJ-900\n. with 4 German EGO square hot plate.\n. with under oven.\n. over-temperature protection &amp; flame failure protection adjustable feet.\n. heating temp: 10.4 + 4.8 kw.\n. total heating temp: 20.8 kw.\n. temperature controlling range: 0~300°c.\n. power: 380v/50hz\n. net weight: 126 kg.\n. Dim: 800*900*850+120 mm.\n. E-DBJ-900""",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,13635,"COOKING LINE > Cooker, COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Cooker > Series 900",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/FOUR-SQUARE-EGO-HOT-PLATE-WITH-OVEN-E-DBJ-900.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,"Type of Product","Four Square Ego Hot Plate and Oven",1,1,Brand,Stilco,1,1,default,1,1,195,index,81,380,0,,"FOUR SQUARE EGO HOT PLATE WITH OVEN,FOUR SQUARE EGO HOT PLATE WITH OVEN E-DBJ-900",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E-DBJ-900,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110101011100111010100110010100100110000111000101,,,,,,,,,,Electric/Gas,Electric,1,1,Series,"Series 90",1,1,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12854,simple,,,"GAS STYLE LAVA ROCK GRILL E-RQH-900S",1,0,visible,"The Gas Style Lava Rock Grill E-RQH-900S is a high-performance outdoor cooking appliance designed for professional grilling experiences. Featuring a lava rock cooking surface and a robust construction, this gas grill ensures even heat distribution, enhancing the flavor of your dishes with a smoky touch. The E-RQH-900S is equipped with user-friendly controls for precise temperature management, making it suitable for various grilling applications. Ideal for both residential and commercial use, this grill provides ample space for cooking a variety of dishes with an authentic and distinctive flavor. Whether you're hosting a barbecue or seeking a reliable solution for professional grilling, the Gas Style Lava Rock Grill E-RQH-900S offers versatility and precision for an exceptional outdoor cooking experience.",". with under cabinet.\n. Power: 18 kw.\n. Voltage: 380 V / 50 hz.\n. Net Weight: 160 kg.\n. Dim: 400 x 900 x 850 + 120 mm.\nItaly SIT valve with CE certificate.\nE-RQH-900S",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,2975,3500,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Grills, Special Offer",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/E-RQH-900S.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,"Type of Product","Gas Style Lava Rock Grill",1,1,Brand,Stilco,1,1,default,1,1,199,index,10,380,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E-RQH-900S,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110010011001010010010000110100011110011111100110,,,,,,,,,salescountdowntimer,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12856,simple,,,"GAS STYLE ONE FRYER E-RQZ-900S",1,0,visible,"The Gas Style One Fryer E-RQZ-900S is a professional-grade kitchen appliance designed for efficient and high-capacity frying in commercial settings. With a sleek and durable design, this gas fryer is equipped with advanced features to ensure optimal performance. The E-RQZ-900S offers precise temperature control for consistent and perfect frying results, making it suitable for various culinary applications. Its spacious frying area and user-friendly controls, combined with easy-to-clean components, make it a reliable choice for busy kitchens. The Gas Style One Fryer E-RQZ-900S seamlessly combines style with functionality, providing chefs and food establishments with a convenient and efficient solution for their frying needs.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(108px, 1px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","• GAS STYLE ONE FRYER\n\n• Cap: 1 basket\n\n• Oil tank Volume: 24 to 28 ltr\n\n• Oil tank is made from SUS 304 S/S\n\n• Fryer basket size: 140 x 320 x 140 mm\n\n• with under cabinet\n\n• Power: 15.5 kw\n\n• Net weight: 146 kg\n\n• Dim: 400 x 900 x 850 + 120 mm\n\n• Italy SIT valve with CE certificate\n\n• E-RQZ-900S",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,3230,3800,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Fryers, Special Offer",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/E-RQZ-900S.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Single-Tank-Fryer-with-Cabinet-E-RQZ-700S-.webp",,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,"Type of Product","Gas Style One Fryer",1,1,Brand,Stilco,1,1,default,1,1,129,index,10,380,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E-RQZ-900S,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110110011011010010010110010100011010110010110010,,,,,,,,,salescountdowntimer,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12859,simple,,,"ELECTRIC STYLE ONE FRYER E-DZ-900S",1,0,visible,"The Electric Style One Fryer E-DZ-900S is a high-capacity kitchen appliance designed for professional-grade frying. With its sleek and efficient design, this electric fryer is equipped with advanced features to ensure optimal performance. The E-DZ-900S offers precise temperature control for consistent and perfect frying results, making it suitable for various culinary applications. Its durable construction and user-friendly interface make it an ideal choice for commercial kitchens. Easy to clean and maintain, the Electric Style One Fryer E-DZ-900S combines style with functionality, providing chefs and food establishments with a reliable solution for large-scale frying needs.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","• ELECTRIC STYLE ONE FRYER E-DZ-900S\n• Cap: 1 basket\n• Oil tank Volume: 24 to 28 ltr\n• Oil tank is made from SUS 304 S/S\n• Fryer basket size: 140 x 320 x 140 mm\n• with under cabinet\n• Power: 12 kw\n• voltage: 380 V / 50 hz\n• Net weight: 108 kg\n• Dim: 400 x 900 x 850 + 120 mm\n• The heater and control with CE certificate\n• E-DZ-900S",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,2874,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Fryers",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/E-DZ-900S.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,"Type of Product","Electric Style One Fryer",1,1,Brand,Stilco,1,1,default,1,1,129,index,79,380,0,,"ELECTRIC STYLE ONE FRYER,ELECTRIC STYLE ONE FRYER E-DZ-900S",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E-DZ-900S,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,010010011011011010010011001110010100110011100110,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
