12862,simple,,,"GAS GRILL ON CABINET E-RQP-900S",1,0,visible,"The Gas Grill on Cabinet E-RQP-900S is a versatile outdoor cooking appliance designed for grilling enthusiasts. With its powerful gas-powered burners, this grill provides quick and efficient heat for cooking a variety of foods. The grill features a spacious cooking surface, allowing you to prepare multiple items simultaneously, making it ideal for gatherings and outdoor events. The integrated cabinet provides convenient storage space for grilling accessories and utensils. The E-RQP-900S is equipped with user-friendly controls, enabling you to easily adjust the heat for precise grilling. Its durable construction and sleek design make it a stylish and practical addition to any outdoor cooking area, delivering a delightful grilling experience.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(80px, 40px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",". GAS GRILL ON CABINET E-RQP-900S\n. smooth plate.\n. steel tubular burners with pilot light.\n. safety thermocouple and piezoelectric lighter.\n. safety gas valves.\n. fat collecting tray with fall-prevention block.\n. adjustable legs.\n. plate size: 325 x 580 mm\n. power: 14 kw.\n. net weight: 150 kg.\n. dim: 400 x 900 x 850+120 mm.\n. Italy SIT valve w/ CE certification &amp; CE approved.\n. E-RQP-900S""",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,3538,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Grills",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ELECTRIC-GRILL-ON-CABINETSMOOTH-PLATE-E-DP-900S.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,Brand,Stilco,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,199,index,79,380,0,,"GAS GRILL,GAS GRILL ON CABINET,GAS GRILL ON CABINET E-RQP-900S",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E-RQP-900S,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110110011011010010010010110100100100110111000011,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,