12864,simple,,,"ELECTRIC GRILL ON CABINET(SMOOTH PLATE) E-DP-900S",1,0,visible,"The Electric Grill on Cabinet (Smooth Plate) E-DP-900S is a sleek and efficient kitchen appliance designed for convenient indoor grilling. Featuring a smooth cooking plate, this electric grill provides a non-stick surface for easy food release and hassle-free cleaning. The integrated cabinet offers a stable base for the grill, ensuring safety and practicality in your kitchen. With its user-friendly controls, this electric grill allows you to adjust the temperature to achieve the perfect grilling results for a variety of foods. Whether you're preparing delicious grilled vegetables, meats, or sandwiches, the E-DP-900S Electric Grill on Cabinet offers a convenient and enjoyable cooking experience.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(509px, 11px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",". ELECTRIC GRILL ON CABINET(SMOOTH PLATE) E-DP-900S\n. smooth plate.\n. steel tubular burners with pilot light.\n. safety thermocouple and piezoelectric lighter.\n. safety gas valves.\n. fat collecting tray with fall-prevention block.\n. plate size: 325 x 580 mm\n. power: 5 kw.\n.voltage: 380V / 50hz.\n. net weight; 140\n. dim: 400 x 900 x 850+120 mm.\n. the heater &amp; control w/ CE certification.\n. the oil tank is made by SUS 304, 1.2mm completely welding tank.\n. E-DP-900S",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,2985,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Grills",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ELECTRIC-GRILL-ON-CABINETSMOOTH-PLATE-E-DP-900S.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,"Type of Product","Electric Grill",1,1,Brand,Stilco,1,1,default,1,1,199,index,81,380,0,,"ELECTRIC GRILL ON CABINET,ELECTRIC GRILL ON CABINET(SMOOTH PLATE) E-DP-900S",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E-DP-900S,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,11011001