12877,simple,,,"GAS FRYER  E-RQZ-400",1,0,visible,"The Gas Fryer E-RQZ-400 is a high-performance kitchen appliance designed for efficient and reliable frying. Powered by gas, this fryer quickly heats up, allowing for fast and consistent cooking of a variety of foods. With a spacious frying basket and a large capacity, it's suitable for both small and large-scale food preparation. The E-RQZ-400 features easy-to-use controls for adjusting temperature, ensuring precise frying results. Its robust construction and durable materials make it suitable for commercial kitchens, providing a reliable solution for frying crispy and delicious food items. Whether you're frying appetizers, main courses, or snacks, the Gas Fryer E-RQZ-400 offers a convenient and effective solution for achieving the perfect crispy texture.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",". GAS FRYER E-RQZ-400\n. Gas fryer.\n. cap: 14 ltr.\n. 1 outlet valves.\n. temp: 60 ~ 200 °c\n. power: 5 kw.\n. weight: 62 kg.\n. dimension: 400 x 600 x 300 mm.\n. E-RQZ-400 .""",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,2095,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Fryers",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/E-DZ-6L.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,"Type of Product","Gas Fryer",1,1,Brand,Stilco,1,1,default,1,1,201,index,77,380,0,,"GAS FRYER,GAS FRYER E-RQZ-400",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E-RQZ-400,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,111101010000111000101001111100100000111000111100,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12879,simple,,,"Electric fryer (capacity: 6 ltr) E-DZ-6L",1,0,visible,"The Electric Fryer E-DZ-6L is a high-capacity kitchen appliance designed for efficient frying. With a generous 6-liter capacity, this electric fryer is perfect for preparing large batches of crispy and delicious fried foods. The appliance features a user-friendly design with temperature control settings, allowing you to achieve optimal frying results for various recipes. The durable construction and easy-to-clean components make maintenance a breeze. Whether you're cooking for a family gathering or hosting an event, the E-DZ-6L Electric Fryer ensures a hassle-free and enjoyable frying experience with ample capacity and convenient controls.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(131px, 2px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","""Electric fryer.\n. capacity: 6 ltr.\n. temp: 0 ~ 180 °C\n. power: 2.5 kw.\n. Voltage: 220-240V / 50 hz.\n. net weight: 60 kg / gross weight: 70 kg.\n. Dim: 260 x 410 x 340 mm.\nall stainless steel body w/ heavy duty element and temperature control function.\nE-DZ-6L",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,396,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Fryers",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/E-DZ-6L.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,"Type of Product","Electric Fryer",1,1,Brand,Stilco,1,1,default,1,1,129,index,56,380,0,,"Electric fryer,Electric fryer (capacity: 6 ltr) E-DZ-6L",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E-DZ-6L,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,111101010000111000101001111100100000111000111100,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12880,simple,,,"ELECTRIC FRYER E-DZ-6L-2",1,0,visible,"The Electric Fryer E-DZ-6L-2 is a versatile kitchen appliance designed for efficient and convenient frying. With a substantial 6-liter capacity and a double basket configuration, this electric fryer allows you to fry multiple batches simultaneously, making it ideal for preparing larger quantities of crispy and flavorful fried foods. The appliance features user-friendly temperature control settings for precise cooking, ensuring consistent results. Its durable construction and easy-to-clean components simplify maintenance, providing a hassle-free frying experience. Whether you're cooking for a crowd or seeking versatility in your kitchen, the E-DZ-6L-2 Electric Fryer offers a reliable solution for delicious fried dishes.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",". ELECTRIC FRYER E-DZ-6L-2\n. capacity: 6 + 6 ltr.\n. temp: 0 ~ 180 °C\n. power: 2.5 kw * 2\n. Voltage: 220-240V / 50 hz.\n. net weight: 110 kg / gross weight: 120 kg.\n. Dim: 540 x 410 x 285 mm.\nall stainless steel body w/ heavy duty element and temperature control function.\nE-DZ-6L-2",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,691,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Fryers",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/E-DZ-8L-2.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,"Type of Product","Electric Fryer",1,1,Brand,Stilco,1,1,default,1,1,129,index,84,380,0,,"ELECTRIC FRYER,ELECTRIC FRYER E-DZ-6L-2",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E-DZ-6L-2,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,010101011010011010101001011000110101111000010101,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12882,simple,,,"ELECTRIC FRYER E-DZ-8L",1,0,visible,"The Electric Fryer E-DZ-8L is a powerful and efficient kitchen appliance designed for professional-grade frying. Boasting an impressive 8-liter capacity, this electric fryer enables you to prepare large quantities of crispy and delicious fried foods with ease. The appliance features precise temperature control settings for optimal frying results, ensuring a perfect finish every time. Its sturdy construction and user-friendly design make it a reliable choice for both home and commercial kitchens. Easy to clean and maintain, the E-DZ-8L Electric Fryer is a versatile solution for those seeking high-capacity frying capabilities without compromising on quality.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(92px, 58px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",". ELECTRIC FRYER E-DZ-8L\n. capacity: 8 ltr.\n. temp: 0 ~ 180 °C\n. power: 3.25 kw.\n. Voltage: 220-240V / 50 hz.\n. net weight: 60 kg / gross weight: 70 kg.\n. Dim: 260 x 410 x 340 mm.\nall stainless steel body w/ heavy duty element and temperature control function.\nE-DZ-8L",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,461,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Fryers, Limited Sale",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/E-DZ-8L.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,"Type of Product","Electric Fryer",1,1,Brand,Stilco,1,1,default,1,1,129,index,60,380,0,,"ELECTRIC FRYER,ELECTRIC FRYER E-DZ-8L",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E-DZ-8L,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110110110000110010010011110100110010110010100011,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12884,simple,,,"ELECTRIC FRYER E-DZ-8L-2",1,0,visible,"The Electric Fryer E-DZ-8L-2 is a high-capacity and versatile kitchen appliance designed for professional-grade frying. With an impressive 8-liter capacity and a convenient double-basket configuration, this electric fryer allows for efficient cooking of large batches of crispy and delicious fried foods. The appliance features precise temperature control settings, ensuring consistent results for a variety of recipes. Its robust construction and user-friendly design make it suitable for both home and commercial kitchens, providing reliable performance. Easy to clean and maintain, the E-DZ-8L-2 Electric Fryer is an ideal choice for those who require ample frying capacity without compromising on quality and convenience.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",". ELECTRIC FRYER E-DZ-8L-2\n. capacity: 8 + 8 ltr.\n. temp: 0 ~ 180 °C\n. power: 3.25 kw * 2\n. Voltage: 220-240V / 50 hz.\n. net weight: 110 kg / gross weight: 120 kg.\n. Dim: 540 x 410 x 285 mm.\nall stainless steel body w/ heavy duty element and temperature control function.\nE-DZ-8L-2",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,783,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Fryers, Limited Sale",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/E-DZ-8L-2.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,"Type of Product","Electric Fryer",1,1,Brand,Stilco,1,1,default,1,1,129,index,60,380,0,,"ELECTRIC FRYER,ELECTRIC FRYER E-DZ-8L-2",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E-DZ-8L-2,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,010101011010011010101001011000110101111000010101,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
