12887,simple,,,"CONTACT GRILL E-DPX-11E",1,0,visible,"<strong>CONTACT GRILL - E-DPX-11E</strong>\nThe E-DPX-11E Contact Grill is a high-performance, electric grill designed for cooking a variety of foods quickly and efficiently. With adjustable temperature settings and a non-stick surface, it ensures even cooking and easy cleanup. Perfect for cafes, restaurants, and commercial kitchens.","• Electric single head.\n\n• Temp: 50 ~ 300 °C.\n\n• Power: 2.8 kw.\n\n• Voltage: 220 - 240v/ 50 hz\n\n• Weight: 25 kg.\n\n• Dim: 410 x 310 x 200 mm.\n\n• E-DPX-11E",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,778,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Sandwich Maker",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/E-DPX-11ZE.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,"Type of Product","Contact Grill",1,1,Brand,Stilco,1,1,default,1,1,129,index,65,380,0,,"CONTACT GRILL,CONTACT GRILL E-DPX-11E",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E-DPX-11E,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011111110001011000000110101110000110010100010111,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12888,simple,,,"CONTACT GRILL E-DPX-13Z",1,0,visible,"The CONTACT GRILL E-DPX-13Z is a versatile and high-performance grilling appliance designed for commercial and heavy-duty kitchen use. Equipped with a large grilling surface and dual-sided heating elements, it efficiently cooks a variety of foods, including sandwiches, meats, and vegetables, ensuring even and thorough grilling. The grill features adjustable temperature controls, a durable non-stick surface, and a robust stainless steel construction, making it ideal for restaurants, cafes, and catering services seeking consistent results and ease of cleaning.","• CONTACT GRILL E-DPX-13Z\n• Electric double head.\n• Temp: 50 ~ 300 °C.\n• Voltage: 220 – 240V / 50 hz\n• Power: 4.4 kw.\n• Weight: 35 kg.\n• Dim: 570 x 310 x 200 mm.",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,1714,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Sandwich Maker",,,,,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,"Type of Product","Contact Grill",1,1,Brand,Stilco,1,1,default,1,1,129,index,72,380,0,,"CONTACT GRILL E,CONTACT GRILL E-DPX-13Z",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E-DPX-13Z,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,010111100100111000000110110001111110010011110000,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12890,simple,,,"CONTACT GRILL E-DPX-13E",1,0,visible,"The CONTACT GRILL E-DPX-13E is a high-quality, commercial-grade grill designed for efficient cooking in busy kitchens. It features a large, dual-sided grilling surface, allowing for simultaneous cooking on both sides for faster and more even results. With adjustable temperature controls and a durable non-stick cooking surface, this grill is perfect for preparing sandwiches, meats, and vegetables. Its sturdy stainless steel construction ensures longevity and ease of cleaning, making it a reliable choice for restaurants, cafes, and catering operations looking to enhance their menu offerings.","• CONTACT GRILL E-DPX-13E\n• Electric double head.\n• Temp: 50 ~ 300 °C.\n• Voltage: 220 – 240V / 50 hz\n• Power: 5.6 kw.\n• Weight: 35 kg.\n• Dim: 860 x 310 x 200 mm.\n• E-DPX-13E",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,1467,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Sandwich Maker",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/E-DPX-13E-1.webp,,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,"Type of Product","Contact Grill",1,1,Brand,Stilco,1,1,default,1,1,129,index,67,380,0,,"CONTACT GRILL,CONTACT GRILL E-DPX-13E",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E-DPX-13E,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,010111100100111000000110110001111110010011110000,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12891,simple,,,"CONVEYER BREAD TOASTER E-DTT-300",1,0,visible,"The Conveyor Bread Toaster E-DTT-300 is a high-performance kitchen appliance designed for efficient and consistent toasting of bread. Featuring a conveyor belt system, this toaster allows for a continuous and even toasting process, ensuring a perfect result every time. The E-DTT-300 is equipped with adjustable speed and temperature controls, offering versatility for various types of bread and toasting preferences. Ideal for commercial kitchens, cafes, and breakfast buffets, this toaster is designed to handle high volumes with ease. Its user-friendly design and easy maintenance make the Conveyor Bread Toaster E-DTT-300 a reliable solution for consistently achieving golden, crispy toast.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(447px, 72px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","• CONVEYER BREAD TOASTER E-DTT-300• Conveyer belt width: 260 mm\n• Crumb tray collecting\n• Adjustable speed.\n• Stainless steel structure.\n• Power: 220-240 v / 50 hz / 1.94 kw.\n• Net weight: 21 kg.\n• Dim: 368 x 418 x 400 mm.\n• E-DTT-300",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,1474,"BAKERY LINE, COOKING LINE, BAKERY LINE > Toaster",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/CONVEYER-BREAD-TOASTER-E-DTT-300.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ttc_1.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/H32a4f54353e04181a6dc8b10466296daC.png",,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,"Type of Product","Conveyor Bread Toaster",1,1,Brand,Stilco,1,1,default,1,1,129,index,10,380,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E-DTT-300,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596763,011111110110011100100010101110000000110101001001,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12895,simple,,,"CONVEYER BREAD TOASTER E-DTT-450",1,0,visible,"The Conveyor Bread Toaster E-DTT-450 is a professional-grade kitchen appliance designed for efficient and consistent toasting of bread. Featuring a conveyor belt system, this toaster allows for a continuous and even toasting process, ensuring a perfect result every time. The E-DTT-450 is equipped with adjustable speed and temperature controls, providing versatility for various types of bread and toasting preferences. Ideal for commercial kitchens, cafes, and breakfast buffets, this toaster is built to handle high volumes with ease. Its user-friendly design and easy maintenance make the Conveyor Bread Toaster E-DTT-450 a reliable solution for consistently achieving golden, crispy toast.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","• CONVEYER BREAD TOASTER E-DTT-450\n• Conveyer belt width: 360 mm\n• Crumb tray collecting\n• Adjustable speed.\n• Stainless steel structure.\n• Power: 220-240 v / 50 hz / 2.64 kw.\n• Net weight: 29 kg.\n• Dim: 468 x 418 x 400 mm.\n• E-DTT-450",,,taxable,,0,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,1750,"BAKERY LINE, COOKING LINE, BAKERY LINE > Toaster",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/CONVEYER-BREAD-TOASTER-E-DTT-300.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/H122559d9478e4cdbab2026c358ec90e5x.webp",,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,"Type of Product","Conveyor Bread Toaster",1,1,Brand,Stilco,1,1,default,1,1,129,index,5,380,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E-DTT-450,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596763,011111110110011100100010101110000000110101001001,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12897,simple,,,"ELECTRIC GRILL  E-DP-818-1000",1,0,visible,"The ELECTRIC GRILL E-DP-818-1000 is a premium, commercial-grade grilling appliance tailored for high-performance cooking in professional kitchens. With a spacious grilling surface, it efficiently cooks a wide range of foods, from meats to vegetables, ensuring even heat distribution and consistent results. The grill features adjustable temperature settings, allowing for precise control over cooking, and a durable non-stick surface for easy food release and cleaning. Its robust stainless steel construction guarantees longevity and ease of maintenance, making it an ideal choice for restaurants, cafes, and catering businesses seeking reliable and versatile grilling solutions.",". ELECTRIC GRILL E-DP-818-1000\n. Smooth plate\n. Power: 3 kw.\n. Voltage: 220V-240V / 50hz.\n. Dim: 1000 x 450 x 230 mm.\n. All S/S body w/ iron griddle, heavy duty heating element &amp; temp. control function.\n. E-DP-818-1000",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,1800,2400,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Grills, Special Offer",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/1-1-1.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,"Type of Product","Electric Grill",1,1,Brand,Stilco,1,1,default,1,1,129,index,72,380,0,,"ELECTRIC GRILL,ELECTRIC GRILL E-DP-818-1000",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E-DP-818-1000,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110111000110010000001010011000101111001110110110,,,,,,,,,salescountdowntimer,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12899,simple,,,"GAS GRILL E-RQP-12",1,0,visible,"The Gas Grill E-RQP-12 is a powerful and efficient outdoor cooking appliance designed for grilling enthusiasts. With its robust construction and high-performance burners, this gas grill delivers quick and even heat distribution, ensuring perfect grilling results. The E-RQP-12 features a spacious cooking area, making it suitable for preparing a variety of grilled dishes. Its user-friendly controls and durable design make it an ideal choice for outdoor gatherings, barbecues, or professional use. Whether you're grilling meats, vegetables, or other favorites, the Gas Grill E-RQP-12 provides a reliable and versatile solution for flavorful outdoor cooking.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(319px, 0px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",". GAS GRILL E-RQP-12\n. American style 12"""" Gas grill.\n. Stainless steel 430\n. 20 mm griddle thickness\n. temp: 50 ~ 300 °c.\n. power: 8.8 kw\n. Weight: 24 kg.\n. dimension: 306 x 734 x 390 mm.\n. E-RQP-12""",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,1354,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Grills",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/E-RQP-12.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/E-RQP-24.png",,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,"Type of Product","Gas Grill",1,1,Brand,Stilco,1,1,default,1,1,129,index,77,380,0,,"GAS GRILL,GAS GRILL E-RQP-12",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E-RQP-12,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011101011100111000101100110000011010001100001111,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12902,simple,,,"GAS GRILL E-RQP-24",1,0,visible,"The Gas Grill E-RQP-24 is a robust and high-capacity outdoor cooking appliance designed for professional grilling. With its durable construction and powerful burners, this gas grill offers efficient and even heat distribution across its expansive cooking surface. The E-RQP-24 is equipped with user-friendly controls, making it suitable for various grilling applications. Whether you're cooking for a large gathering or seeking a reliable solution for commercial use, this gas grill provides versatility and precision for preparing a wide range of grilled dishes. Enjoy the convenience and performance of the Gas Grill E-RQP-24 for your outdoor culinary needs.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(273px, 66px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",". American style 24"""" Gas grill.\n. Stainless steel 430\n. 18 mm griddle thickness\n. temp: 50 ~ 300 °c.\n. power: 8.8 kw*2 = 17.6 kw.\n. N/G weight: 72 - 82 kg.\n. dimension: 610 x 730 x 400 mm.\n. E-RQP-24 """,,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,1946,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Grills",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/E-RQP-24.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,"Type of Product","Gas Grill",1,1,Brand,Stilco,1,1,default,1,1,129,index,77,380,0,,"GAS GRILL,GAS GRILL E-RQP-24",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E-RQP-24,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011101001100111000001110010001011110001110111000,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12903,simple,,,"GAS GRILL E-RQP-36",1,0,visible,"The Gas Grill E-RQP-36 is a high-performance commercial grill designed for professional kitchens and outdoor catering. With its 36-inch cooking surface, this grill provides ample space for grilling a variety of foods, from meats and seafood to vegetables. Its powerful gas burners ensure quick and even heat distribution, delivering consistent grilling results. Built with durable stainless steel, the E-RQP-36 is designed for longevity and ease of cleaning. Ideal for restaurants, cafes, and catering services, this gas grill offers reliable performance and versatility, making it an essential tool for any culinary operation.",". American style 36"""" Gas grill.\n. Stainless steel 430\n. 18 mm griddle thickness\n. temp: 50 ~ 300 °c.\n. power: 8.8 kw*3 = 26.4 kw.\n. N/G weight: 101 - 111 kg.\n. dimension: 910 x 834 x 390 mm.\n. E-RQP-36 """,,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,2594,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Grills",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/E-RQP-36A.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,"Type of Product","Gas Grill",1,1,Brand,Stilco,1,1,default,1,1,129,index,77,380,0,,"GAS GRILL,GAS GRILL E-RQP-36",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E-RQP-36A,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110111100100110000000110111001110110011001110000,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12905,simple,,,"GAS LAVA STONE GRILL E-RQH-600",1,0,visible,"The Gas Lava Stone Grill E-RQH-600 is a powerful and compact outdoor cooking appliance designed for professional grilling experiences. With a robust construction and lava stone cooking surface, this gas grill ensures even heat distribution, imparting a distinctive smoky flavor to your dishes. The E-RQH-600 features user-friendly controls, making it suitable for various grilling applications. Ideal for both residential and commercial use, this grill provides ample space for cooking a variety of dishes with an authentic touch. Whether you're hosting a barbecue or seeking a reliable solution for on-the-go grilling, the Gas Lava Stone Grill E-RQH-600 delivers versatility and precision for flavorful outdoor cooking.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",". GAS LAVA STONE GRILL E-RQH-600\n. temp: 50 ~ 300 °c.\n. power: 16.8 kw.\n. weight: 55 kg.\n. dimension: 600 x 650 x (300+150) mm.\n. italy PEL valve w/ CE certifiacation.\n. E-RQH-600",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,2893,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Grills",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/E-RQH-24.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,"Type of Product","Gas Lava Stone Grill",1,1,Brand,Stilco,1,1,default,1,1,129,index,72,380,0,,"GAS LAVA STONE GRILL,GAS LAVA STONE GRILL E-RQH-600",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E-RQH-600,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110111011010111000001001010000111100011010110010,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12907,simple,,,"FOOD WARMER CART  E-DBW-11-21",1,0,visible,"The FOOD WARMER CART E-DBW-11-21 is a versatile, commercial-grade solution for keeping food warm and ready to serve. This cart features multiple shelves with adjustable temperature controls, ensuring that different dishes can be kept at the ideal serving temperature. Its robust stainless steel construction provides durability and ease of cleaning, while the built-in wheels allow for easy mobility across your restaurant, catering event, or buffet setup. With its efficient heating system and practical design, the E-DBW-11-21 is perfect for maintaining the quality and freshness of food in high-volume service environments.",". FOOD WARMER CART E-DBW-11-21\n. Food warmer cart.\n. cap: 11 gn 1/1 size.\n. system with humidity.\n. 2 sides handles.\n. temp: 30 ~ 85 °c.\n. digital control.\n. structure: stainless steel.\n. Voltage: 220 - 240 v / 50 hz\n. Power: 2.62 kw.\n. weight: 182 kg.\n. 2 wheels w/ breaks\n. dim: 670 x 940 x 1860 mm\n. E-DBW-11-21.""",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,5509,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Food Warmers",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Hc4b8da7748ba4236b95bac4ec67addbbT_300x300.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,"Type of Product","Food Warmer Cart",1,1,Brand,Stilco,1,1,default,1,1,199,index,72,380,0,,"FOOD WARMER CART,FOOD WARMER CART E-DBW-11-21",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E-DBW-11-21,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110010100100110010010011000100110111001101100111,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12909,simple,,,"DOUBLE DOOR FOOD WARMER CART E-DBW-22-21",1,0,visible,"The Double Door Food Warmer Cart E-DBW-22-21 is a versatile and efficient solution for keeping your food warm and ready to serve. With two spacious doors, this cart provides easy access to the interior, allowing you to store and organize a variety of dishes. The cart is equipped with a heating system that ensures even and consistent warming throughout, maintaining the desired temperature for your food. Its durable construction and mobility make it suitable for catering events, banquets, or any setting where keeping food at an optimal temperature is essential. The E-DBW-22-21 Double Door Food Warmer Cart combines functionality and convenience to enhance your food service operations.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(264px, 3px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","• DOUBLE DOOR FOOD WARMER CART E-DBW-22-21\n• system with humidity\n• CAP: 22 GN 1/1 SIZE OR 2/1\n• 2 sides handles\n• temp: 30 ~ 85 °c\n• digital control\n• structure: stainless steel\n• Voltage: 220 – 240 v / 50 hz\n• Power: 2.52 kw\n• weight: 325 kg\n• 4 wheels w/ breaks\n• dim: 1540 x 940 x 1860 mm\n• E-DBW-22-21",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,10594,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Food Warmers",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/DOUBLE-DOOR-FOOD-WARMER-CART-E-DBW-22-21-1.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,"Type of Product","Double Door Food Warmer Cart",1,1,Brand,Stilco,1,1,default,1,1,200,index,80,380,0,,"DOUBLE DOOR FOOD WARMER CART E-DBW-22-21",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E-DBW-22-21,field_6387359a51f50,yes,field_6540c7c45e610,yes,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596931,010111110001011010000110111100100000101111001010,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12911,simple,,,"GAS COOKER E-RQB-600",1,0,visible,"The GAS COOKER E-RQB-600 is a compact yet powerful cooking appliance designed for professional kitchen environments. It features multiple high-efficiency gas burners that provide quick and consistent heating for various cooking tasks. The sturdy construction ensures durability and longevity, while the stainless steel finish offers easy cleaning and maintenance. The cooker's precise temperature control allows for accurate cooking, making it ideal for restaurants, cafes, and catering services looking for a reliable and efficient solution to meet their diverse culinary needs.",". GAS COOKER E-RQB-600\n. 4 range table top.\n. 4 low pressure valves.\n. power: 16 kw.\n. Net weight: 144 kg.\n. dimension: 600 x 650 x 360 mm.\n. E-RQB-600""",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,2893,"COOKING LINE > Cooker, COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Cooker > Series 600",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/unnamed-1-1.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,"Type of Product","Gas Cooker",1,1,Brand,Stilco,1,1,default,1,1,129,index,72,380,0,,"GAS COOKER,GAS COOKER E-RQB-600",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E-RQB-600,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110101011100100010101001010010011101100100111100,,,,,,,,,,Electric/Gas,Gas,1,1,Series,"Series 60 Table Top",1,1,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
