12917,simple,,,"Electric crepe machine  E-DE-1",1,0,visible,"The Electric Crepe Machine E-DE-1 is a high-efficiency, commercial-grade appliance designed to create perfect crepes with ease. It features a large, smooth, non-stick cooking surface that ensures even heat distribution for consistent and precise cooking. The machine offers adjustable temperature control, allowing chefs to achieve the ideal cooking conditions for a variety of crepe recipes. Built with durable materials and a sleek design, this crepe machine is easy to clean and maintain, making it an excellent choice for restaurants, cafes, and food trucks that want to deliver high-quality crepes efficiently.",". Electric crepe machine  E-DE-1\n. 1 hot plate: Ǿ 400 mm.\n. temp: 50 ~ 300°c.\n. power: 220 v / 50 hz / 3 kw.\n. weight: 26 kg.\n. dim: 450 x 515 x 333 mm.\n. E-DE-1 """,,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,820,"SNACK MAKER > Crepe Maker, SNACK MAKER",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/images-2.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,"Type of Product","Electric Crepe Machine",1,1,Brand,Stilco,1,1,default,1,1,129,index,72,380,0,,"Electric crepe machine,Electric crepe machine E-DE-1",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E-DE-1,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596342,011110001011011000101101001010000100111100011110,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12919,simple,,,"GAS CREPE MACHINE E-DG-2",1,0,visible,"The Gas Crepe Machine E-DG-2 is a high-capacity, commercial-grade appliance designed for producing large quantities of crepes efficiently. Featuring dual cooking plates, it allows for simultaneous cooking of two crepes, significantly increasing productivity in busy kitchen settings. The machine’s gas-powered system ensures rapid heating and precise temperature control, offering flexibility and consistency in cooking. Its durable construction and non-stick cooking surfaces facilitate easy cleaning and maintenance. Ideal for restaurants, cafes, and food trucks, the E-DG-2 is a reliable tool for creating delicious crepes quickly and efficiently.",". GAS CREPE MACHINE E-DG-2\n. 2 hot plates: Ǿ 400 mm.\n. temp: 50 ~ 300°c.\n. gas power: lpg 4+4 kw.\n. weight: 26 kg.\n. dim: 900 x 515 x 333 mm.\n. E-DG-2""",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,1935,"SNACK MAKER > Crepe Maker, SNACK MAKER",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/quattro-electric-double-crepe-machine-heavy-duty-2-x-13amp-plugs-39-p.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,"Type of Product","Gas Crepe Machine",1,1,Brand,Stilco,1,1,default,1,1,129,index,72,380,0,,"GAS CREPE MACHINE,GAS CREPE MACHINE E-DG-2",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E-DG-2,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596342,010101001111011010101100000001011101110010111000,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12921,simple,,,"ELECTRIC CREPE MACHINE E-DE-1",1,0,visible,"The ELECTRIC CREPE MACHINE E-DE-1 is a high-efficiency, commercial-grade appliance designed for creating perfect crepes with ease. Featuring a large, smooth, non-stick cooking surface, this machine ensures even heat distribution for consistent cooking results. The adjustable temperature control allows for precise cooking, while the robust stainless steel construction ensures durability and easy maintenance. Ideal for cafes, restaurants, and catering services, this crepe machine offers reliable performance and versatility, making it a valuable addition to any professional kitchen.","• ELECTRIC CREPE MACHINE E-DE-1\n• 1 hot plate: Ǿ 400 mm\n• temp: 50 ~ 300°c\n• power: 220 v / 50 hz / 3 kw\n• weight: 26 kg\n• dim: 450 x 515 x 333 mm\n• E-DE-1",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,820,"SNACK MAKER > Crepe Maker, SNACK MAKER",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/E-DE-1-scaled.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/E-DE-1-1-scaled.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/E-DE-1-2-scaled.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/E-DE-1-3-scaled.png",,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,"Type of Product","Electric Crepe Machine",1,1,Brand,Stilco,1,1,default,1,1,129,index,72,380,0,,"ELECTRIC CREPE MACHINE,ELECTRIC CREPE MACHINE E-DE-1",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E-DE-1,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596342,011101111000011000001001111100100101101000011110,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12926,simple,,,"ELECTRIC CREPE MACHINE E-DE-2",1,0,visible,"<p style=""text-align: center;"">The Electric Crepe Machine E-DE-2 is a professional-grade appliance designed for effortlessly creating delicious crepes. With its efficient electric heating system, this machine ensures quick and consistent cooking, allowing you to achieve perfect crepes every time. The non-stick cooking surface promotes easy flipping and removal of crepes, making the cooking process smooth and hassle-free. The compact and user-friendly design of the E-DE-2 makes it suitable for both commercial kitchens and home use. Whether you're a professional chef or a cooking enthusiast, this electric crepe machine offers a convenient and reliable way to prepare thin, delectable crepes with ease.</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(188px, 13px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","• ELECTRIC CREPE MACHINE E-DE-2\n• Electric crepe machine\n• 2 hot plates: Ǿ 400 mm\n• temp: 50 ~ 300°c\n• power: 220 v / 50 hz / 3+3 kw\n• weight: 42 kg\n• dim: 900 x 515 x 333 mm\n• E-DE-2",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,1566,"SNACK MAKER > Crepe Maker, SNACK MAKER",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ELECTRIC-CREPE-MACHINE-E-DE-2.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ED-E-3-scaled.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ED-E-2-scaled.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ED-E-2-1-scaled.png",,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,"Type of Product","Electric Crepe Machine",1,1,Brand,Stilco,1,1,default,1,1,129,index,74,380,0,,"ELECTRIC CREPE MACHINE,ELECTRIC CREPE MACHINE E-DE-2",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E-DE-2,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596342,111101001111010000101100001010101100111001010100,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12931,simple,,,"FOOD WARMING CABINET E-BWP-400",1,0,visible,"The FOOD WARMING CABINET E-BWP-400 is a high-capacity, commercial-grade appliance designed to keep food at optimal serving temperatures. Featuring multiple adjustable shelves, this cabinet can accommodate a variety of dishes, ensuring they stay warm and ready to serve. Its precise temperature control system allows for consistent heat distribution throughout the cabinet. Constructed with durable stainless steel, the E-BWP-400 is easy to clean and built to last. Ideal for restaurants, catering services, and large-scale events, this warming cabinet offers reliable performance and convenient mobility with its built-in wheels.",". FOOD WARMING CABINET E-BWP-400\n. Single Light\n. Power: 0.275 kw.\n. Voltage: 220-240V / 50 hz.\n. Net Weight: 20 kg. Gross weight: 25 kg.\n. Dim: 400 x 285 x 560 mm.\n. E-BWP-400""",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,488,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Food Warmers",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/H30a0d41178964c2c97e9836e2930a0c8f.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,"Type of Product","Food Warming Cabinet",1,1,Brand,Stilco,1,1,default,1,1,200,index,72,380,0,,"FOOD WARMING CABINET,FOOD WARMING CABINET E-BWP-400",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E-BWP-400,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011110111001110010000100101110110010011100100100,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12933,simple,,,"FOOD WARMING CABINET E-BWP-600",1,0,visible,"The FOOD WARMING CABINET E-BWP-600 is a robust, commercial-grade appliance designed to maintain the ideal serving temperatures for a large variety of dishes. With an expansive interior and adjustable shelves, this cabinet can accommodate a significant volume of food, making it perfect for high-demand environments. The precise temperature control system ensures even heat distribution throughout the cabinet, preserving the quality and freshness of your meals. Constructed with high-quality stainless steel, the E-BWP-600 offers durability and ease of cleaning. Its built-in wheels provide easy mobility, making it an excellent choice for restaurants, catering services, and banquet halls.",". FOOD WARMING CABINET E-BWP-600\n. Double Light\n. Power: 0.55 kw.\n. Voltage: 220-240V / 50 hz.\n. Net Weight: 40 kg. Gross weight: 45 kg.\n. Dim: 600 x 330 x 560 mm.\n. E-BWP-600""",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,737,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Food Warmers",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Heb0298fd3ef64217af511d8ca1d4ef0fw.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,"Type of Product","Food Warming Cabinet",1,1,Brand,Stilco,1,1,default,1,1,129,index,72,380,0,,"FOOD WARMING CABINET,FOOD WARMING CABINET E-BWP-600",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E-BWP-600,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011100111001010001100100111110100010011110100001,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12935,simple,,,"Food Warming Cabinet -BWD-4B",1,0,visible,"The Food Warming Cabinet BWD-4B is a professional-grade kitchen appliance designed to keep your prepared dishes at the perfect serving temperature. With a sleek and compact design, this warming cabinet features four separate compartments, allowing you to warm multiple dishes simultaneously. The BWD-4B is equipped with precise temperature controls, ensuring that your food stays warm without compromising its quality. Ideal for catering events, buffets, or busy kitchens, this warming cabinet is a reliable solution for maintaining the freshness and temperature of your culinary creations. Easy to operate and maintain, the BWD-4B Food Warming Cabinet is an essential tool for food service professionals.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(198px, 14px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",". Food Warming Cabinet -BWD-4B\n. 4 Lights\n. Power: 1.1 kw.\n. Voltage: 220-240V / 50 hz.\n. Net Weight: kg. Gross weight: kg.\n. Dim: 985 x 500 x 870 mm.\n. E-BWD-4B""",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,1603,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Food Warmers",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/E-BWD-4B.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,"Type of Product","Food Warming Cabinet",1,1,Brand,Stilco,1,1,default,1,1,129,index,72,380,0,,"Food Warming Cabine,Food Warming Cabinet -BWD-4B",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E-BWD-4B,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,010111011010111010011100001100100000111100110100,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12937,simple,,,"2 LAYER DISPLAY SHOWCASE E- BWP-6P",1,0,visible,"The 2 LAYER DISPLAY SHOWCASE E- BWP-6P is a modern and functional display unit crafted for retail spaces. Featuring two layers of display shelves, it offers a versatile solution for presenting a diverse range of products in an organized manner. The showcase is designed with a contemporary aesthetic, combining style and functionality seamlessly. With its durable construction and thoughtful design, the E-BWP-6P provides an efficient and visually appealing platform to showcase merchandise, making it an excellent choice for businesses looking to enhance their product presentation in a retail setting.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(356px, 27px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","• Keep humidity even temperature.\n\n• The progress is clear at a glance.\n\n• Power: 3.5 kW.\n\n• Voltage: 220-240V / 50 Hz.\n\n• Net weight: 118 kg gross weight: 144 kg.\n\n• Dim: 1500 x 755 x 850 mm.\n\n• E-BWP-6P",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,4422,"REFRIGERATION LINE > Display Chiller, REFRIGERATION LINE",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/E-BWP-6P.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,"Type of Product","2 Layer Display Show Case",1,1,Brand,Stilco,1,1,default,1,1,381,index,10,380,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E-BWP-6P,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595655,111111000101110000000110100000101011001010110111,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12939,simple,,,"2 LAYER DISPLAY SHOWCASE E- BWP-6P-B",1,0,visible,"The 2 LAYER DISPLAY SHOWCASE E- BWP-6P-B is a versatile and modern display unit designed for showcasing products in retail environments. With two layers of display space, this showcase provides ample room to present a variety of items, allowing for an organized and visually appealing presentation. The sleek design and high-quality materials make it a durable and stylish choice for businesses looking to enhance their product displays. The E-BWP-6P-B is equipped with advanced features to highlight merchandise effectively, making it an ideal solution for creating an attractive and engaging shopping experience.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","• Keep humidity even temperature.\n\n• The progress is clear at a glance.\n\n• Power: 3.5 kW.\n\n• Voltage: 220-240V / 50 Hz.\n\n• Net weight: 100 kg. Gross weight: 120kg.\n\n• Dim: 1200 x 755 x 850 mm.\n\n• E- BWP-6P-B",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,3869,"REFRIGERATION LINE > Display Chiller, REFRIGERATION LINE",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/E-BWP-6P-B.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/E-BWP-6P.png",,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,"Type of Product","2 Layer Display Show Case",1,1,Brand,Stilco,1,1,default,1,1,381,index,10,380,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"E- BWP-6P-B",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595655,111111000101110000000110100000101011001010110111,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
12941,simple,,,"GAS ROAST CHICKEN RKJ-3C",1,0,visible,"The Gas Roast Chicken RKJ-3C is a commercial-grade rotisserie designed for efficient and flavorful roasting of chicken. It features multiple skewers for roasting several chickens simultaneously, ensuring even cooking and a perfect golden-brown finish. The unit's gas-powered system provides precise temperature control and consistent heat distribution, delivering juicy and tender results every time. Constructed with durable materials, including stainless steel, the RKJ-3C is built to withstand heavy use and is easy to clean. Ideal for restaurants, rotisseries, and catering services, this roast chicken machine enhances efficiency and quality in high-volume cooking environments.",". GAS ROAST CHICKEN RKJ-3C\n. cap: 3 skewer / 3 chickens each.\n. gas operated.\n. digital thermostat.\n. Voltage: 220V-240V / 50 hz\n. Power: 18 kw.\n. dim: 1185*490*720 mm.\n. RKJ-3C",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,5426,"COOKING LINE",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Vigevr-3-Rods-Gas-Rotisserie-Grill-for-Roast-Chicken-Wings.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,"Type of Product","Gas Roast Chicken",1,1,Brand,Stilco,1,1,default,1,1,129,index,77,380,0,,"GAS ROAST CHICKEN,GAS ROAST CHICKEN RKJ-3C",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,RKJ-3C,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011101100101011000110110100000110100111011001010,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
