12952,simple,,,"Cone Baker E-XGP-1",1,0,visible,"The Cone Baker E-XGP-1 is a specialized appliance designed for efficient and uniform baking of ice cream cones. It features precise temperature control and even heat distribution, ensuring consistently crispy and perfectly shaped cones every time. With a user-friendly interface and durable construction, this cone baker is ideal for both commercial and home use, catering to the needs of ice cream shops, bakeries, and dessert enthusiasts alike.","• Cone Baker E-XGP-1\n\n• Single Head\n\n• Power : 1 kw.\n\n• Voltage : 220 – 240 V\n\n• Dim : 280 x 400 x 290 mm.\n\n• E-XGP-1",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,930,"SNACK MAKER > Cone Baker, SNACK MAKER",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Cone-Baker-E-XGP-1.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,"Type of Product","Cone Baker",1,1,Brand,Stilco,1,1,default,1,1,386,index,79,380,0,,"Cone Baker,Cone Baker E-XGP-1",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E-XGP-1,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011011110001110011001000100100110010001110110011,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
