13021,simple,,,"UNDERCOUNTER FREEZER RTD-99L",1,0,visible,"The UNDERCOUNTER FREEZER RTD-99L is a space-saving freezing solution designed to fit seamlessly beneath counters or workspaces. With a capacity of 99 liters, this freezer offers compact yet efficient storage for frozen goods. Its sleek design and easy-to-access compartments make it a convenient addition to commercial kitchens, laboratories, or any setting where space optimization is essential. The UNDERCOUNTER FREEZER RTD-99L ensures reliable freezing capabilities while maintaining a streamlined and organized environment for your frozen storage needs.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(579px, 0px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Storage Volume: 90 ltr</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Black glass+Stainless steel bottom+4pcs LED+Digital controller+Chrome plated shelves</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• one hinged doors</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• temperature: -13/-22</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Rated Current(A): 0.8</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Refrigerant&amp;Injection(g): R134a &amp; 110</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Foaming agent:C5H10</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• 3 coated movable shelves</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Lamp Power(W)：3(LED)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• power: 220-240 v / 50 Hz / 160 w</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Defrost Power(W):250</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• weight: 41 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• dim: 620 x 575 x 712 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• RTD-99L/mariot made</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""text-align: left;"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(731px, 402px); text-align: left;"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,4500,"BAKERY LINE > Bakery Display, BAKERY LINE, REFRIGERATION LINE > Display Chiller, REFRIGERATION LINE",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/RTD-99L.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Mariot,"Type of Product","Undercounter Freezer",1,1,Brand,Mariot,1,1,default,1,1,381,index,65,185,0,,"UNDERCOUNTER FREEZER",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,RTD-99L,field_6387359a51f50,yes,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,111101100001110010100110101100001000110001100111,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
13024,simple,,,"UPRIGHT CHILLER GN650TN",1,0,visible,"<strong>UPRIGHT CHILLER - GN650TN</strong>\nThe GN650TN Upright Chiller offers efficient cooling and ample storage capacity for commercial kitchens. Designed with adjustable shelves and precise temperature control, it ensures optimal freshness for perishable goods. Its durable stainless steel construction makes it a dependable choice for busy food service operations.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• UPRIGHT CHILLER GN650TN</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• AISI 304 18/10 S/S interior &amp; exterior w/ sanitary corner except rear panel &amp; part of bottom</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• automatic closing door w/ magnetic gasket, 90° reversible</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• injected polyurethane insulation, CFC free, density: 40 kgs / m3</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cap: 580 ltr</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• w/ 3 shelf &amp; 1 Drs + 4 castor wheels</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• working Temp: +0˚ ~ +5° at 32° temp</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power Supply: 230v / 50 Hz / 1Ph</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• fridge power: 460 Watt</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• refrigerant : R134a</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Net Weight: 130 Kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 830 x 740 x 2040 mm (WxDxH)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Digital : DIXELL / ITAL+C8Y MADE</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• compressor : ASPERA / EMBRACO / ITALY</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• GN650TN / <a href=""https://mariotstore.comold/brand/inofrigo/"">Inofrigo</a> / MARIOT MADE</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• ISO9001, CE&amp;ROHS approved</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,3695,"REFRIGERATION LINE > Freezer & Chillers, REFRIGERATION LINE, Special Offer",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-c