13036,simple,,,"Espresso cappuccino machine",1,0,visible,"The JOLLY AUTO 1-GR Espresso Cappuccino Machine is a compact and efficient appliance designed for brewing delicious espresso and creamy cappuccino with ease. Its automatic functionality simplifies the brewing process, delivering consistent and flavorful coffee beverages at the touch of a button. With a single group, it is perfect for home use or smaller-scale environments where space is limited. Its user-friendly design and reliable performance make it an ideal choice for coffee lovers seeking convenience and quality in their daily brews.","<p style=""text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• Espresso cappuccino machine</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• 1 group / AUTOMATIC</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• boiler capacity: 5.0 lt</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Automatic portion control</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Bodywork all stainless steel or with painted iron – stainless steel arms</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Copper boiler (Cu 99,5) with anti-oxidation treatment.\nwww.sabcoffeemachines.it</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Warning to lack the water in tank</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Thermosiphon system</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Weight : 34 kg</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• thermal power : 2000 watt</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• voltz : 220-240 Vac 1N 50-60 Hz</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Dim: 370 x 540 x 510 mm ( w+d+h)</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Model: JOLL1AT3IL / JOLLY AUTO 1-GR / SAB ESPRESSO italy made</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,5499,7428.96,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Coffee Machines, Special Offer",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/image-removebg-preview-1.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Untitled-1.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Untitled-5.png",,,,,,,,,0,,SAB,Brand,SAB,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,366,index,4,137,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"JOLL1AT3IL / JOLLY AUTO 1‐GR / SAB ESPRESSO ",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596904,101000011110000101111011010011010110000110011100,true,backend,,,,,,,salescountdowntimer,,,,,,,,,00:00,00:00,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
13040,simple,,,"Espresso cappuccino machine",1,0,visible,"The SEMI-AUTOMATIC 1-GR Espresso Cappuccino Machine offers simplicity and precision for espresso and cappuccino lovers. With its semi-automatic function, users can control the brewing process, ensuring a customized and flavorful experience. Designed with a single group, it is compact and suitable for home or small-scale use. Its intuitive interface and durable construction make it an excellent choice for those seeking quality coffee without compromising on convenience.","<p style=""text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• Espresso cappuccino machine</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• 1 group / SEMI-AUTOMATIC</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• boiler capacity: 5.0 lt</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Manual portion control</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Bodywork all stainless steel or with painted iron – stainless steel arms\nCopper boiler (Cu 99,5) with anti-oxidation treatment</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Warning to lack the water in tank</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Thermosiphon system</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Weight : 34 kg</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• thermal power : 2000 watt</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• voltz : 220-240 Vac 1N 50-60 Hz</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Dim: 370 x 540 x 510 mm ( w+d+h)</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Model: JOLL1PM3IL / JOLLY AUTO 1-GR / SAB ESPRESSO italy made</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,4499,5781.6,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Coffee Machines, Offer",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/image-removebg-preview.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Untitled-6.png, h