13046,simple,,,"Espresso cappuccino machine ELEG2AT3N20",1,0,visible,"The ELEG2AT3N20 Espresso Cappuccino Machine is a sophisticated and versatile appliance designed for espresso and cappuccino aficionados. With its elegant design and advanced features, it offers precise control over the brewing process, ensuring consistently rich and flavorful espresso and creamy cappuccino. Its user-friendly interface and high-quality construction make it an excellent choice for both home and professional use, providing coffee enthusiasts with the perfect cup every time.","<p style=""text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• Espresso cappuccino machine</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• 2 group / ELEGANCE AUTOMATIC</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• boiler capacity: 13.5 lt / / color: BLACK</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Automatic coffee and hot water portion control</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• W/ display to view alarms, drinks &amp; operative funcions</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Painted iron side/back panel (WHITE or MATT BLACK) w/ stainless\nsteel finishes</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Stainless steel steam and water wands</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Coffee pre-infusionsystem and thermosiphon system</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Copper boiler (Cu 99,5) with anti-oxidation treatment</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Weight : 70 kg</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• thermal power : 3000 watt</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• voltz : 220-240 V / 1 N / 50-60 hz</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Dim: 795 x 575 x 560 ( w+d+h)</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Model: ELEG2AT3N20/ SAB ESPRESSO/ italy made</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,13464,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Coffee Machines, Special Offer",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/sab-1.webp,,,,,,,,,0,,SAB,Color,Black,1,1,Brand,SAB,1,1,default,1,1,125,index,47,137,0,,"Espresso cappuccino machine ELEG2AT3N20",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"ELEG2AT3N20/ SAB ESPRESSO",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596904,110101011110110010101010111110000010000001001011,true,backend,,,,,,,salescountdowntimer,Series,"Table Top",1,1,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
13050,simple,,,"Espresso cappuccino machine",1,0,visible,"The Espresso Cappuccino Machine JOLLY AUTO 3-GR is a professional-grade appliance crafted for coffee enthusiasts and businesses. With its automatic operation, it streamlines the brewing process, consistently producing rich espresso and creamy cappuccino with minimal effort. Featuring three groups, it enables simultaneous brewing, making it ideal for high-demand environments like cafes and restaurants. Its user-friendly interface and robust construction ensure durability and ease of use, making it a dependable choice for delivering quality coffee beverages efficiently.","<p style=""text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• Espresso cappuccino machine</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• 3 group /AUTOMATIC</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• boiler capacity: 20.5 lt/ color: Polished S/S</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Automatic coffee and hot water portion control (AUTOMATIC version)\nor manual portion control (SEMI AUTOMATIC version)</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Bodywork all stainless steel or with painted iron – stainless steel arms</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Copper boiler (Cu 99,5) with anti-oxidation treatment</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Warning to lack the water in tank</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Thermosiphon system</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Weight : 70 kg</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• thermal power : 5000 watt</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• voltz : 220-240 Vac 1N 380-415 Vac 3N 50-60 Hz\nVac 3N 50-60 Hz</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Dim: 900 x 540 x 510 mm ( w+d+h)</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0""></p>",,,taxab