13071,simple,,,"Espresso cappuccino machine VERA2AT3N",1,0,visible,"The VERA2AT3N Espresso Cappuccino Machine is a premium appliance designed to bring the authentic café experience into the comfort of your own home. Crafted with precision and sophistication, this coffee machine is a perfect addition to any coffee lover's kitchen.","<p style=""text-align: left; margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Espresso cappuccino machine</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left; margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 2 group / VERA AUTOMATIC</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left; margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• boiler capacity: 11.5 lt / / color: INOX</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left; margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Automatic coffee and hotwaterportion control</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left; margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Display touch to accede &amp; manage all the machine function</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left; margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Side panel in plexiglass w/ customizable colors/pictures</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left; margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Coffeepre-infusionsystemandthermosiphonsystem</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left; margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Copperboiler(Cu99,5)withanti-oxidationtreatment</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left; margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• The drip tray can be set to fourdifferenthighlevels</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left; margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight : 68.5 kg</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left; margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• thermal power : 3000 watt</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left; margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• voltz : 220-240 V / 1 N / 50-60 hz</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left; margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 900 x 620 x 500 ( w+d+h)</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left; margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Model: VERA2AT3N/ SAB ESPRESSO/ italy made</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,23760,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Coffee Machines","Espresso cappuccino machine",,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/espress