13091,simple,,,"Coffee grinder / MDFIO64ELG",1,0,visible,"The MDFIO64ELG Coffee Grinder is a high-quality and efficient appliance for coffee enthusiasts. With its sleek and durable design, it precisely grinds coffee beans to perfection every time. Users can adjust the grind size according to their preferences, allowing for the preparation of exceptional-tasting coffee. This grinder is an ideal choice for homes, cafes, and restaurants that prioritize coffee quality.","<p style=""text-align: left; margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Coffee grinder</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left; margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Automatic, color: silver</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left; margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Coffee bean hopper capacity: 1,5 kg</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left; margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Blades revs: 1350/min (50 Hz) – 1550/min (60 Hz</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left; margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Blades diameter: Ø 64 mm</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left; margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Blades type: flat</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left; margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Doses adjustment: in seconds</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left; margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Fork: adjustable, with support</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left; margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• automatic version</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left; margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Varnishing: standard</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left; margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power supply 230 / 50 hz. / W 350</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left; margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Gross weight: kg 13</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left; margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 230 x 615 x 270 mm</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left; margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Model: MDFIO64ELG/ SAB ESPRESSO/ italy made</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,3896.64,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Coffee Grinder, Offer, Special Offer",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/4-1-scaled.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/2-3-scaled.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/3-4-scaled.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/1-4-scaled.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/coffee-sab.jpg, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Untitled-1.jpg, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/coffee-grinder.jpg",,,,,,,,,0,,SAB,Brand,SAB,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,125,index,16,137,0,,"Coffee grinder/MDFIO64ELG",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"MDFIO64ELG/ SAB ESPRESSO",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011001110011111001100010000001100001100111100111,true,backend,9357098057668051,yes,yes,,product,no,salescountdowntimer,,,,,,,,,10:00,10:00,,,,,,,,,2707.425,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
13099,simple,,,"Rational iCombi Classic - ICC 10E-1/1",1,0,visible,"The Rational iCombi Classic - ICC 10E-1/1 is a versatile and advanced combi oven designed for commercial kitchens and professional cooking environments. Combining precision cooking technology with user-friendly features, this appliance is an essential tool for chefs and culinary professionals looking to elevate their cooking processes and expand their menu options.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• Rational iCombi Classic ICC 10E-1/1</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• 3NAC400 V 50-60hz Electric unit</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Power 18.9 kW</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Power Supply3 Phase - This unit requires a 3 phase electrical</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Power Type-Electric</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• 10 lengthwise insertion for 1/1 GNAccessories</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Removable standard racks with 68 mm insertion distance</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Wide range of accessories for various cooking processes such as\ngrilling, braising or baking</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• For use with 1/1, 1/2, 2/3, 1/3 GN-Accessories\nCombi-steamer mode</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Steam 30 °C – 130 °C</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Convection 30 °C – 300 °C</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Combination of steam &amp; convection from 30 °C - 300 °Cmm²</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• N. - G. Weight: 155 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Dim: Width 850 x Depth 842 x Height 1014mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• ICC 10E-1/1 / RATIONAL/ Germany made</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,42136,"COOKING LINE > Combi Oven, COOKING LINE, sale, SALE RATIONAL, Special Offer",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/2090879.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Rational,Brand,Rational,1,1,Electric/Gas,Electric,1,1,default,1,1,15,index,68,150,0,,"Rational iCombi Classic",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"ICC 10E-1/1",field_6387359a51f50,yes,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596255,110111100111000001101100010100100101101101001001,,,,,,,,,salescountdowntimer,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
13101,simple,,,"Rational iCombi Classic- ICC 6E-1/1",1,0,visible,"The Rational iCombi Classic ICC 6E-1/1 is a versatile and advanced combi oven designed to cater to the needs of professional kitchens. With its innovative features and precise cooking capabilities, this oven is an asset for chefs and culinary establishments seeking to achieve consistent and high-quality results.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• Rational iCombi classic ICC 6E-1/1/Electric 6 3NAC400 V400 50-60hz Electric unit</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Capacity: 6 × 1/1 GN</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Meals Per Day 30-100</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Power 10.8 kW</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Weight 99 KG</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Power Supply 3 Phase - This unit requires a 3-phase electrical</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• 6 lengthwise insertion for 1/1 GNAccessories</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Removable standard racks with 68 mm insertion distance</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Wide range of accessories for various cooking processes such as\ngrilling, braising or baking</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• For use with 1/1, 1/2, 2/3, 1/3 GN-Accessories\nCombi-steamer mode</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Steam 30 °C – 130 °C</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Convection 30 °C – 300 °C</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Combination of steam &amp; convection from 30 °C - 300 °Cmm²</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• N. - G. Weight: 99 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Dim : Width 850 x Depth x 842 x Height 754mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• ICC 6E-1/1 / RATIONAL / Germany made""</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,29982,34100,"COOKING LINE > Combi Oven, COOKING LINE, sale, SALE RATIONAL, Special Offer",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Rational-iCombi