13104,simple,,,"Rational iCombi Classic - ICC 6G-1/1",1,0,visible,"The Rational iCombi Classic - ICC 6G-1/1 is a versatile, high-performance combi oven designed for professional kitchens. With its intuitive controls and advanced cooking technology, it offers unparalleled efficiency and precision. Ideal for a variety of cooking methods including steaming, roasting, baking, and grilling, this robust appliance ensures consistent, high-quality results every time. Its durable construction and energy-efficient operation make it a valuable addition to any culinary environment.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• Rational iCombi Classic ICC 6G-1/1\n3NAC400 V230 50-60hz GAS unit LPG 3 B/P</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0"">• Capacity: 6 × 1/1 GN</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0"">• Meals Per Day 30-100</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0"">• Weight 99 KG</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0"">• Power Type LPG Gas</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0"">• 6 lengthwise insertion for 1/1 GNAccessories</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0"">• Removable standard racks with 68 mm insertion distance</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0"">• Wide range of accessories for various cooking processes such as\ngrilling, braising, or baking</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0"">• For use with 1/1, 1/2, 2/3, 1/3 GN-Accessories\nCombi-steamer mode</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0"">• Steam 30 °C – 130 °C</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0"">• Convection 30 °C – 300 °C</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0"">• Combination of steam &amp; convection from 30 °C - 300 °Cmm²\nGas Connection / gas system / Natural gas</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0"">• Nominal thermal load convection mode 52 MJ/h</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0"">• Dynamic gas pressure 1.13 – 2.5 kPa</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0"">• N. - G. Weight: 99 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0"">• Dim : Width 850x Depth 842x Height 754</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0"">• ICC 6G-1/1 / RATIONAL/ Germany made""</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,35729,"COOKING LINE > Combi Oven, COOKING LINE, sale, SALE RATIONAL, Special Offer",,,https://mari