13108,simple,,,"SINGLE DOOR CHILLER - CL 380 SDC",1,0,visible,"The SINGLE DOOR CHILLER - CL 380 SDC is a compact and efficient refrigeration unit designed to keep perishable items fresh in commercial settings. With its single-door configuration, this chiller offers convenient storage for a variety of chilled products, making it ideal for cafes, convenience stores, and small businesses. The sleek design and transparent door provide visibility to the contents, allowing for easy product identification. Equipped with reliable cooling technology, the CL 380 SDC chiller ensures consistent temperature control, helping businesses maintain the quality of their chilled merchandise while optimizing space utilization.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(801px, 2px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Volume: 360 Ltr / 5 shelves</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Vertical LED</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Aluminum frame grey</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Embraco compressor</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Low-e glass</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Self closing door</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Mechanical thermostat</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Integrated handle</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Long roll bond evaporator</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Analog thermometer</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Lock and key</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Refrigerant Gas: R600a</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Temperature: 0 - 