13113,simple,,,"TRIPLE DOOR CHILLER - CL 1600 H3",1,0,visible,"The TRIPLE DOOR CHILLER - CL 1600 H3 is a high-capacity refrigeration unit designed for commercial use. With its three spacious doors, it provides ample storage for chilled items, making it ideal for restaurants, grocery stores, and other food-related businesses. The chiller offers efficient cooling performance, helping to maintain the freshness and quality of perishable goods. Its advanced features and durable construction make it a reliable choice for businesses seeking effective cold storage solutions.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• TRIPLE DOOR CHILLER - CL 1600 H3s</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Volume: 1326 Ltr / 4 x 3 Pcs shelve</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Vertical LED Light strips 6 pcs on sides</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Aluminum door frame</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Embraco compressor</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Digital thermostat</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Lock and key</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Double tempered &amp; Low-E coated glass door</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Refrigerant Gas: R290a</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Temperature: 0 - +10°C</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Net Weight: 247 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Voltage: 220 - 240V/ 50 Hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Internal Dim: 1500 x 623 x 1545 mm