13115,simple,,,"SINGLE DOOR FREEZER - CL 380 VDFS",1,0,visible,"The SINGLE DOOR CHILLER - CL 380 VDFS C is a compact and efficient refrigeration unit designed to keep perishable items fresh in commercial settings. With its single-door configuration, this chiller offers convenient storage for a variety of chilled products, making it ideal for cafes, convenience stores, and small businesses. The sleek design and transparent door provide visibility to the contents, allowing for easy product identification. Equipped with reliable cooling technology, the CL 380 VDFS chiller ensures consistent temperature control, helping businesses maintain the quality of their chilled merchandise while optimizing space utilization.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(638px, 30px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• SINGLE DOOR FREEZER - CL 380 VDFS</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Volume: 361 Ltr / 5 static freezing shelves</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Horizontal LED Light x 2 Sides</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Aluminum frame black</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Embraco compressor</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Analog thermometer</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Mechanical thermostat</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Integrated handle</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Self closing door</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Refrigerant Gas: R290a/ R404a</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Temperature: -18 / -24°C</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Net Weight: 98 kg</p>\n<p styl