13126,simple,,,"Electric Fryer - RE 114 CSE",1,0,visible,"The Electric Fryer RE 114 CSE is a high-quality fryer made in the USA. This commercial electric fryer is designed to deliver outstanding frying performance with its advanced features and durable construction. It offers efficient and consistent frying of various food items, making it an excellent choice for restaurants, food establishments, and catering businesses. With its ""Made in USA"" craftsmanship and reliability, the RE 114 CSE electric fryer ensures that you can serve delicious and crispy fried dishes to your customers with confidence.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Frymaster stainless steel single tank</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Full pot twin basket electric fryer with stainless steel pot and door cabinet</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Multi-computer</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Solid-state controls</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Automatic melt cycle</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 22 - 28 liters shortening capacity and 32 kgs French fries output per hour</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 14 kW</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 380V/50Hz/3P</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Oil Cap: 25ltr</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Frying area: 35.6 x 39.4 cm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 397 x 786 x 1149 mm (H)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Model: RE 114 CSE / Frymaster / USA Made</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,31500,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Fryers, Top Brands",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/111-2-scaled.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Electric-Fryer-RE-114-CSE.jpg",,,,,,,,,0,,Frymaster,Electric/Gas,Electric,1,1,Brand,Frymaster,1,1,default,1,1,129,index,13,146,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"RE 114 CSE",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field