13132,simple,,,"Gas Fryer - FPPH255 CSE",1,0,visible,"The Frymaster Gas Fryer FPPH255 CSE is a high-quality fryer made in the USA by the renowned brand Frymaster. This commercial fryer is designed to deliver exceptional frying performance with its advanced features and reliable construction. It offers efficient and consistent frying of various food items, making it a top choice for restaurants, food establishments, and catering businesses. With its made-in-USA quality and Frymaster's reputation for excellence, the FPPH255 CSE gas fryer ensures that you can serve delicious and crispy fried dishes to your customers with confidence.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Frymaster stainless steel gas fryer high efficiency</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 50 lb capacity each</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• CM3.5 controller</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• built-in filtration</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• includes: rack-type basket support, basket hanger &amp; twin baskets</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• stainless steel frypots &amp; doors cabinet</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 240,000 BTU/HR</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 240V/50H/1P</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• LPG Gas</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight 492 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 798 x 752 x 1159 mm (H)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Model: FPPH255 CSE / Frymaster / USA Made</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,60700,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Fryers, Top Brands",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Gas-Fryer-FPPH255-CSE.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Frymaster,Electric/Gas,Gas,1,1,Brand,Frymaster,1,1,default,1,1,129,index,13,146,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"FPPH255 CSE",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,de