13323,simple,,,"Ice Cream Powder Blueberry Flavour",1,0,visible,,"<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Ice Cream Powder Blueberry Flavor</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Quantity: 1kg / Price For 1kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Ingredients</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Fat-filled milk powder, Sugar</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Stabilizer (Guar gum E 412, Dextrose</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Calcium Sulphate E516, E510</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Disodium Phosphate E339, E339</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Locust bean gum E410, E410</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• (E401 Sodium alginate E401)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Tricalcium Phosphate, Blueberry Flavor</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• allowed colors E133, E13</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Creamer Powder</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• May have an adverse impact on the activity and attention of children.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">Measures:</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Mix 1 kg of the powder with 3 liters of water and mix it well.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Put the mixture in the ice cream machine and follow the machine instructions.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Store in a cool place below +4 C. Dry powder storage:</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Store in a dry place below +25 C.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Store in a dry place below +25 C.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left;"">• Blueberry Flavor/ <a href=""https://mariotstore.comold/brand/3mf/"">3MF</a> / Mariot.</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,55,"REFRIGERATION LINE > Ice Cream Display, SNACK MAKER > Ice Cream powder, REFRIGERATION LINE, SNACK MAKER",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2