13359,simple,,,"Ice Cream Powder Lolus Flavour",1,0,visible,,"<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Ice Cream Powder Lolus Flavour</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Quantity: 1kg/ Price For 1kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Ingredients</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Fat filled milk powder, sugar,</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Stabilizer (Guar gum E412, Dextrose,</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Calcium Sulphate E516, Disodium Phosphate E339,</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Locust bean gum E410, Sodium alginate E401),</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Pure Vanillin, Creamer powder, wheat flour,</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• vegetable oils (palm, rapeseed), candy sugar syrup, raising agent (sodium hydrogen carbonate),</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• soya flour, salt, cinnamon.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• ***Contains wheat and soya which may cause hypersensitivity.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">Measures:</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Mix 1 kg of the powder with (2-2.5) liters of water and mix it well.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Put the mixture in the ice cream machine and follow the machine's instructions.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Store in a cool place below +4 C. Dry powder storage:</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Store in a dry place below +25 C.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Lolus Flavour/ <a href=""https://mariotstore.comold/brand/3mf/"">3MF</a> / Mariot.</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,55,"REFRIGERATION LINE > Ice Cream Display, SNACK MAKER > Ice Cream powder, REFRIGERATION LINE, SNACK MAKER",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/lolus-icecream-scaled-1.jpg, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ice-Cream-lolus.png",,,,,,,,,0,,3MF,Brand,3MF,1,1,,,,,de