13382,simple,,,"Glo-Ray High Wattage Infrared Food Warmer with Toggle Controls Light - GRAH-54",1,0,visible,"<strong>GLO-RAY HIGH WATTAGE INFRARED FOOD WARMER WITH TOGGLE CONTROLS & LIGHT - GRAH-54</strong>\nThe GRAH-54 Glo-Ray Infrared Food Warmer combines powerful heating with toggle controls for precise temperature management. Featuring a built-in light for enhanced visibility and durable construction, it keeps food warm and appetizing in busy food service settings. Ideal for buffets, restaurants, and catering operations.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Glo-Ray High Wattage Infrared Food Warmer with Toggle Controls Light</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Safely hold the temperature of your product without drying or further cooking</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Continuous aluminum housing and heavy-duty mountings ensure durability and quality</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Even heat distribution - no cold spots</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Reflector does not blacken, maintains a consistent heat pattern</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Reinforced wire guard provides operator safety</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Pre-focused heat pattern</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power wattage: 1,250Watts/ 220V / 50hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 1354 x 152 x 165 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• GRAH-54 / HATCO / USA made</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,2190,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Food Warmers",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/000000024998649-00000-20160307.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Hatco,Brand,Hatco,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,200,index,80,247,0,,"Glo-Ray High Wattage Infrared Food Warmer with Toggle Controls Light",,"• Glo-Ray High Wattage Infrared Food Warmer with Toggle Controls Light
