13383,simple,,,"TWIN TANK GAS FRYER/SOLSTICE SUPREME HIGH EFFICIENCY FRYER - SSH55TC",1,0,visible,"The Twin Tank Gas Fryer, specifically the Solstice Supreme High Efficiency Fryer SSH55TC, is a top-of-the-line commercial kitchen appliance designed to meet the demanding needs of professional frying in busy foodservice establishments. This fryer is known for its exceptional performance, energy efficiency, and user-friendly features.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• TWIN TANK GAS FRYER/SOLSTICE SUPREME HIGH-EFFICIENCY FRYER</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• (C) INTELLIFRY Computer controller</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cap: 2 basket / Fry pots: 2</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Oil cap: 20 - 25 lbs</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Frying area: 177.8 x 356 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Electric power: 240V / 1 hp / 50Hz, / 0.4 amps</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Ship weight: 230 lbs. (104.3 kg)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Legs: 9"" (228.6 mm) stainless steel</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 397 x 875.5 x 1197 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Model No. SSH55TC / <a href=""https://mariotstore.comold/brand/pitco/"">PITCO</a> / USA made</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,30066,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Fryers",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/1429160-600x595-removebg-preview.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Pitco,Brand,Pitco,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,201,index,65,148,0,,"TWIN TANK GAS FRYER/SOLSTICE SUPREME HIGH-EFFICIENCY FRYER",,"• TWIN TANK GAS FRYER/SOLSTICE SUPREME HIGH-EFFICIENCY FRYER
• (C) INTELLIFRY Computer controller
• Cap: 2 basket / Fry pots: 2","TWIN TANK GAS FRYER/SOLSTICE SUPREME HIGH-EFFICIENCY FRYER %sep% %sitename%",,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,SSH55TC,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,100111110011001100101001100001100100110011001101,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
13385,simple,,,"Espresso cappuccino machine/ ALIC1MN3IS/ ALICE",1,0,visible,"The ALIC1MN3IS Espresso Cappuccino Machine, also known as ALICE, is a versatile and efficient appliance designed to deliver delicious espresso and creamy cappuccino with ease. With its user-friendly interface and reliable performance, it offers precise control over the brewing process, ensuring consistently flavorful results. Its sleek design and compact size make it suitable for home kitchens or small cafes. ALICE is the perfect choice for coffee lovers seeking quality and convenience in their daily brews.","<p style=""text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• Espresso cappuccino machine/ ALIC1MN3IS/ ALICE</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Espresso cappuccino machine</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• 1 group / manual</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• boiler capacity: 1.5 lt</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Manual portion control</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Bodywork all stainless steel or with painted iron – stainless steel arms</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Water tank capacity 2.2 lt</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Warning to lack the water in tank</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Thermosiphon system</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Weight : 19 kg</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• thermal power : 1100 watt</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• voltz : 220-240 Vac 1N 50-60 Hz</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Dim: 235 x 430 x 395 mm ( w+d+h)</p>\n<p style=""text-align: left;margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Model: ALIC1MN3IS/ ALICE / <a href=""https://mariotstore.comold/brand/sab/"">SAB ESPRESSO</a>\nitaly made.</p>",,,taxable,,1