13482,simple,,,"Gas Conveyor Pizza Oven - EMP.50G-1340",1,0,visible,"The EMP.50G-1340 Gas Conveyor Pizza Oven is a professional-grade oven designed specifically for pizzerias and restaurants. Its gas-powered conveyor system ensures consistent and efficient baking of pizzas. With a spacious cooking chamber, it can accommodate multiple pizzas at once, making it perfect for high-demand environments. This oven is equipped with precise temperature controls, allowing for customized baking settings to achieve the perfect crust and toppings. Built for durability and performance, it's a reliable choice for producing delicious, evenly cooked pizzas quickly and efficiently.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Gas Conveyor Pizza Oven - EMP.50G-1340</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Microprocessor (PLC) controlled programming</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Programmed memory or non-program manual working</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Complete S/S body, Easy to use w/ LCD touchscreen</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Low gas consumption &amp; homogeneous cooking</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Baking time range from 1 min to 60 min</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Save time with fast and efficient work</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Band Dim: 535 x 1360 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Adaptable to operate w/ gas or wood, to LPG or NG</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power: 18 kW</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• N. W. : 141 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Net m3: 1.05</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 1710 x 1075 x 575 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• EMP.50G-1340/ <a href=""https://mariotstore.comold/brand/empero/"">EMPERO</a></p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,26000,"BAKERY LINE, BAKERY LINE > Bakery Oven",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024