13501,simple,,,"Vertical gas chicken rotisseries - G6S A",1,0,visible,"The Vertical Gas Chicken Rotisserie - G6S A is a high-performance cooking appliance designed for evenly roasting chicken and other poultry. It features a vertical design that allows for efficient heat distribution, ensuring that each piece of chicken is cooked to perfection. The G6S A model is powered by gas, providing consistent and reliable heat for optimal roasting results. Its spacious interior can accommodate multiple chickens, making it ideal for restaurants and foodservice establishments. The rotisserie is built for durability and ease of use, with user-friendly controls and a sleek design that fits well in any commercial kitchen.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Vertical gas chicken rotisseries - G6S A</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Capacity: 6 axles</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Chicken cap: 24 - 30</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power: 230v/ 1hp /50hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Single-phase motor power: 0,36 kw</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• LPG GAS: 2.82 Kg/h</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight: 144 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 1100*480*h.1750 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• G6S A / <a href=""https://mariotstore.comold/brand/ggf/"">GGF</a> s.r.l./ italy made</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,12936,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Grills",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/G6S-A.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,GGF,Brand,GGF,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,129,index,58,138,0,,"Vertical gas chicken rotisseries - G6S A",,"• Vertical gas chicken rotisseries - G6S A
