13520,simple,,,"PITCO GAS FLOOR FRYER 35C+",1,0,visible,"The Pitco 35C+ Gas Floor Fryer is a robust and versatile commercial kitchen appliance designed for high-volume frying, making it an essential addition to any restaurant, foodservice establishment, or catering business. This fryer is known for its reliability, performance, and efficiency.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• GAS FLOOR FRYER Picto Frialator</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cap: 2 basket</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Oil cap: 35 - 40 lbs (15.9 - 18.1 kg)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• The standing pilot and thermostat maintain the temperature\nautomatically at the selected temperature (between 200°F (93°C) and 400°F (190°C-CE))</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Runs on 90,000 BTU's/Hour (26.3 kW)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cooking area: 355.6 x 355.6 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight: 161 lbs. (73.0284 kg)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Legs: 6""""(152 mm) adjustable legs</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 384 x 769 x 1168.4 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Model No. 35C+ /<a href=""https://mariotstore.comold/brand/pitco/"">PITCO</a> / USA made</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,7850,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Fryers",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/PITCO-GAS-FLOOR-FRYER-35C.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Pitco,Brand,Pitco,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,129,index,72,148,0,,"GAS FLOOR FRYER",,"• PITCO GAS FLOOR FRYER 35C+
