automatically at the selected temperature",,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,35C+,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,100110110011101100101001100001100100110010111100,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
13522,simple,,,"PITCO GAS FLOOR FRYER 65C+",1,0,visible,"The Pitco 65C+ Gas Floor Fryer is a powerful and dependable commercial kitchen appliance designed to meet the demands of high-volume frying operations. Whether you're running a busy restaurant, a fast-food establishment, or a catering business, this fryer is an excellent choice for consistent and efficient deep frying.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Picto Frialator</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cap: 2 basket</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Oil cap: 65 - 80 lbs</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Temperature limit automatically shuts off all gas flow if\nthe fryer temperature exceeds 450°F (232°C) ±15°F (±10°C) / 410°F (210°C) for International units</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Runs on 150K BTU/hr</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cooking area: 457.2 x 457.2 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight: 226 lbs. (102.5 kg)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Legs: 6""""(152.4 mm) adjustable legs</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 512 x 875 x 1204 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Model No. 65C+ /<a href=""https://mariotstore.comold/brand/pitco/"">PITCO</a> / USA made</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,12595,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Fryers",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/65c.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Pitco,Brand,Pitco,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,129,index,68,148,0,,"GAS FLOOR FRYER",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,65C+,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011001001001111001111001100100110010011001000111,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
13524,simple,,,"PITCO SOLSTICE GAS FRYER 14 SG14S",1,0,visible,"The Pitco Solstice Gas Fryer 14 (SG14S) is an innovative and energy-efficient commercial fryer designed to provide reliable and consistent frying performance in professional kitchens. This fryer is renowned for its advanced technology and user-friendly features","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• <a href=""https://mariotstore.comold/brand/pitco/"" target=""_blank"" rel=""noopener"">Pitco</a> SG14S tube fryer with the patented Solstice Burner Technology</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• A dependable blower-free atmospheric heating system provides fast recovery to cook a variety of food products</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Solstice gas fryer comes standard with a millivolt thermostat with a thermo-safety pilot</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• High-temperature safety limit switch</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Unique Solstice burner and baffle design increases cooking production lowers flue temperature and improves the working environment</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• dim: 397 x 876 x 1172 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• SG14S / <a href=""https://mariotstore.comold/brand/pitco/"">PITCO</a> /USA made</p>",,,taxable,,0,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,9154,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Fryers",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/SG14S-600x600-removebg-preview.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Pitco,Brand,Pitco,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,129,index,79,148,0,,"GAS FRYER",,"• PITCO SOLSTICE GAS FRYER 14 SG14S
•Solstice gas fryer comes standard with a millivolt thermostat with a thermo-safety pilot",,off,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,SG14S,field_6387359a51f50,yes,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,100111110011101100101001100001100100110010011001,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
13526,simple,,,"Industrial Washing Machine - LM 26 EL IM11",1,0,visible,,"<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Industrial Washing Machine - LM 26 EL IM11</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Load capacity: 26 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Innovative IM11 computer touchscreen makes programming, use &amp; maintenance extremely simple and intuitive</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• IM8 colored touchscreen; Easy, intuitive, unlimited possibilities</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• USB Port on washing machine control panel: easy DATA transfer w/ PC or other washing machines</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• GSM remote assistance: Control, diagnosis, service</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Orgonomic control panel: Optimal visibility</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Motorized door lock: Innovative door lock to grant safety &amp; ergonomy.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Hot &amp; cold usage optimization: mixed during the loading phase.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Outer drum &amp; panels in S/S 304; Avoiding rust &amp; best mechanical performances.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power: 400V/ 3+N+T/ 50hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• net weight 458 kg / gross weight: 473 kg.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• dim: 1220*1060*1470 mm.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• LM 26 EL IM11 / Imesa / Italy made.</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,54560,"LAUNDRY & DISH WASHER, LAUNDRY & DISH WASHER > Laundry Machines",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/LM-26-EL-IM11.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Imesa,Brand,Imesa,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,70,0,0,,"Industrial Washing Machine - LM 26 EL IM11",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"LM 26 EL IM11",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,defa