13530,simple,,,"VEGETABLE PREPARATION MACHINE - CL 20D",1,0,visible,"The CL 20D Vegetable Preparation Machine is a powerful kitchen appliance designed for efficient and quick vegetable processing. With its cutting-edge technology and precision engineering, this machine effortlessly slices, dices, and shreds a variety of vegetables, streamlining your food preparation process. Its user-friendly interface and compact design make it an essential tool for any kitchen, ensuring convenience and consistent results in vegetable preparation. Upgrade your kitchen efficiency with the CL 20D Vegetable Preparation Machine.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• VEGETABLE PREPARATION MACHINE - CL 20D</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Power: 400W-Single Phase speed-1500rpm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Voltage: 230V/ 50/1 UK plug Induction</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Motor: Magnetic safety system &amp; motor brake</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Motor base: Induction motor Large hopper</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Area: 104 cm²</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Cylindrical hopper: 58 mm dia</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Dim: 325x310x570 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Gross Weight: 12 kg, Slicers</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• 2mm &amp; 5mm and Grater 2mm in R301</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Made by Robot Coupe, France</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,4106,4830,"FOOD PROCESSING, Special Offer, FOOD PROCESSING > Vegtable Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/cl20.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,"Robot Coupe",Brand,"Robot Coupe",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,5,0,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"CL 20D",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011000110010010011010110010110011010