13659,simple,,,"Double Electric Crepe Maker – CDE 400",1,0,visible,"The Double Electric Crepe Maker – CDE 400 is a professional-grade appliance designed for high-volume commercial kitchens. This crepe maker features two separate cooking surfaces, allowing you to prepare multiple crepes simultaneously, increasing efficiency and output. Each plate is crafted from durable materials to ensure even heat distribution and perfectly cooked crepes every time. With precise temperature controls and an easy-to-clean design, the CDE 400 is ideal for cafes, restaurants, and catering services that require consistent, high-quality results.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• Double Electric Crepe Maker – CDE 400</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Features: 2 spiral heating elements, 2 commutator-thermostats 0-300 ° C, pilot lights, wooden ""T"" utensil to spread the batter evenly.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Pancakes plate with 6 imprints Ø110 mm each</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• All stainless steel storage case CK 3 for crepe maker: 2 spatulas, 2 ""T"" wooden, 1 grease pad</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• A batch of crepe mix, Roller Grill recipe (10 packs of 1kg)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Power: 7,2 kW or 2 x 3,6 kW (2 cords)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Outside dimensions: 860 x 480 x 240 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Weight: 44 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• volts: 380 V or 230 V mono</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Diameter: 400 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• CDE 400 / Roller Grill / Made in France</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,4522,"COOKING LINE, SNACK MAKER > Crepe Maker, SNACK MAKER",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/CDE-400.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,"Roller Grill",Brand,"Roller Grill",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,71,0,0,,"Double Electric Crepe Maker – CDE 400,صانعة الكريب الكهربائية المزدوجة,صانعة الكريب",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"CDE 400",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595588,011111011001111000001001000001110101101111000010,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
13661,simple,,,"Wok Induction Cooker - PIW30",1,0,visible,"&nbsp;\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• Wok Induction Cooker - PIW30</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Features: curved glass ceramic hob, induction box, ventilator, professional generator, the front panel. Capacitive front panel: On / Off, sound timer and Power cutoff, 20-level power (+/-) selection, digital display of power levels or timer. Robust design and long-life components. Delivered with wok pan.</p>\n<p style=""padding-top: 0"">• Power: 3 Kw</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Outside dimensions: 390 x 430 x 165 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Weight: 7 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• volts: 230-240 V</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• COM_VIRTUEMART_PERSO_DIAMETRE_WOK: 300 mm</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""true"">\n<div id=""tippy-1"" style=""z-index: 100000200;position: absolute;margin: 0px"" data-tippy-root="""">\n<div class=""tippy-box"" style=""max-width: 350px"" role=""mtttooltip"" data-state=""visible"" data-theme=""custom"" data-animation=""fade"" data-placement=""bottom"">\n<div class=""tippy-content"" data-state=""visible""><span dir=""rtl"">• المميزات: موقد سيراميك زجاجي منحني، صندوق تحريض، جهاز تهوية، مولد احترافي، اللوحة الأمامية.</span></div>\n<div class=""tippy-arrow"" style=""position: absolute;left: 0px""></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,8205,"COOKING LINE > Cooker, COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Cooker > Series 600",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/PIW30.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,"Roller Grill",Electric/Gas,Electric,1,1,Series,"Series 60 Table Top",1,1,default,1,1,0,,71,0,0,,"Wok Induction Cooker - PIW30,شواية دوارة,موقد الحث الاحترافي,مقلاة خاصة",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,PIW30,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595673,011110110000111000000110010001111110011010111000,,,,,,,,,,Brand,"Roller Grill",1,1,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
13663,simple,,,"Gas griddle with decarbonized Steel Plate - PSR 900 G",1,0,visible,"&nbsp;\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(13px, 119px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Gas griddle with decarbonized Steel Plate - PSR 900 G</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Features: decarbonized steel plate, 3 star-shaped burners with 6 - 8 branches, Piezo ignition, 3 adjustment buttons with idle position, 3 safety thermocouples.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Outside dimensions: 900 x 475 x 230 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Baking surface: 900 x 400 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight: 46 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• volts: 9,6 kW</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• cooking areas: 3</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• PSR 900 G / Roller Grill / Made in France</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(928px, 84px);"" aria-expanded=""true"">\n<div id=""tippy-1"" style=""z-index: 100000200; visibility: visible; position: absolute; inset: 0px auto auto 0px; margin: 0px; transform: translate(399px, 20px);"" data-tippy-root="""">\n<div class=""tippy-box"" style=""max-width: 350px; transition-duration: 300ms;"" tabindex=""-1"" role=""mtttooltip"" data-state=""visible"" data-theme=""custom"" data-animation=""fade"" data-placement=""bottom"">\n<div class=""tippy-content"" style=""transition-duration: 300ms;"" data-state=""visible""><span dir=""rtl"">• الميزات: لوح فولاذي منزوع الكربون، 3 شعلات على شكل نجمة مع 6 - 8 فروع، إشعال بيزو، 3 أزرار ضبط مع وضع الخمول، 3 مزدوجات حرارية آمنة.</span></div>\n<div class=""tippy-arrow"" style=""position: absolute; left: 0px; transform: translate(92px, 0px);""></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,4050,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Grills, Top Brands",,,https://mariotstor