13671,simple,,,"Electric Waffle Maker - GES 23",1,0,visible,"The Electric Waffle Maker GES 23 is a versatile kitchen appliance designed to make delicious waffles with ease. Its user-friendly design and advanced heating technology ensure consistent and perfectly cooked waffles every time. The GES 23 features a non-stick cooking surface that allows for easy waffle release and hassle-free cleaning. With adjustable temperature settings and indicator lights, achieving your preferred waffle texture is simple. Whether you're a novice cook or a seasoned chef, the Electric Waffle Maker GES 23 offers a convenient way to enjoy homemade waffles for breakfast or dessert, adding a delightful touch to your culinary creations.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(934px, 207px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Electric Waffle Maker - GES 23</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• The professional electric waffle iron GES 23 is equipped with a cast-iron mold, containing four imprints for the cooking of 4 waffles on sticks.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• This professional waffle maker is meant for intensive use.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• The plates of the corn-shaped waffle machine are made of cast iron.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Features: commutator-thermostat 0-300 ° C, control lights. Delivered with a brush (F05054) and a timer.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Stainless steel display stand (P08002Z03) for waffles on sticks.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Batch of 500 special sticks for corn-shaped waffles.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Set of 10 kg waffle mix.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Waffle size: 230 x 60 x 30 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power: 1.6 kW</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Outside dimensions: 305 x 440 x 230 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight: 22 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• volts: 230 V - Monophasé</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• GES 23 / Roller Grill / Made in France.</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(208px, 340px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,3118,"BAKERY LINE","Electric Waffle Maker",,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/GES23-600x600.jpg.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"Roller Grill",Brand,"Roller Grill",1,1,Electric/Gas,Electric,1,1,default,1,1,0,,80,0,0,,"Electric Waffle Maker,صانعة الوافل الكهربائية,اله صنع الوافل",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"GES 23",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595594,110001100100111001100110110100101101100010011001,,,,,,,,,,"Type of Product","Waffle Maker",1,1,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
13673,simple,,,"Professional Gas Stove - GST 14",1,0,visible,"&nbsp;\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(817px, 175px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Professional Gas Stove - GST 14</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• This gas stove is easy to clean: cast iron grids, burner crowns, and stainless steel plates are completely removable.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• The professional gas stove GAR 14 fits into all restaurants, food trucks, kiosks, and bakeries.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Features: double Piezo ignition, adjustment buttons with idle position, cast-iron grids, stainless steel reducer. Mounted in LPG and delivered with injectors for natural gas.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power: 14 kW (2 x 7)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Outside dimensions: 690 x 510 x 195 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight: 24 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• GST 14 / Roller Grill / Made a France</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(925px, 330px);"" aria-expanded=""true"">\n<div id=""tippy-1"" style=""z-index: 100000200; visibility: visible; position: absolute; inset: auto auto 0px 0px; margin: 0px; transform: translate(399px, -20px);"" data-tippy-root="""">\n<div class=""tippy-box"" style=""max-width: 350px; transition-duration: 300ms;"" tabindex=""-1"" role=""mtttooltip"" data-state=""visible"" data-theme=""custom"" data-animation=""fade"" data-placement=""top"">\n<div class=""tippy-content"" style=""transition-duration: 300ms;"" data-state=""visible""><span dir=""rtl"">• GST 14 / الشواية الدوارة / صنعت في فرنسا</span></div>\n<div class=""tippy-arrow"" style=""position: absolute; left: 0px; transform: translate(92px, 0px);""></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,3105,"COOKING LINE > Cooker, COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Cooker > Series 600",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/GST-14.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,"Roller Grill",Brand,"Roller Grill",1,1,Electric/Gas,Gas,1,1,default,1,1,0,,72,0,0,,"Professional Gas Stove - GST 14,موقد غاز,طباخ غاز",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"GST 14",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595599,110101110001010010100011101011010100100101110010,,,,,,,,,,"Type of Product","Gas Cooker",1,1,Series,"Series 60 Table Top",1,1,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
13675,simple,,,"Professional Electric Rotisserie – RBE 120 Q",1,0,visible,"&nbsp;\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(739px, 176px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Professional Electric Rotisserie – RBE 120 Q</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• The English spit B3 is used to cook steaks and pieces of poultry.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• The 100-mm-high feet (CE / UL-NSF) raise your vertical grill to make it easier to clean underneath the rotisserie.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• The support table with wheels and brake system (TS1: 805 x 345 x 710 mm) makes your rotisserie particularly mobile.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• RBE 120 Q / Roller Grill / Made in France</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(371px, 188px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,10989,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Grills",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/RBE-120Q.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,"Roller Grill",Brand,"Roller Grill",1,1,Electric/Gas,Electric,1,1,default,1,1,0,,72,0,0,,"Professional Electric Rotisserie – RBE 120 Q,مشواة فروج كهربائية,مشواة الكهربائية",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"RBE 120 Q",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595599,011111011011111010001001000110001010010000011101,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
13677,simple,,,"Electric Waffle Maker - GES 20",1,0,visible,"The Electric Waffle Maker - GES 20 is a kitchen appliance designed to effortlessly create delicious waffles. With its user-friendly features and sleek design, it allows you to make perfect waffles with ease. The non-stick cooking plates ensure that waffles are cooked evenly and can be easily removed without sticking. The adjustable temperature control lets you customize the level of browning to achieve your preferred crispiness. Whether for a quick breakfast or a delightful dessert, the Electric Waffle Maker - GES 20 offers a convenient way to enjoy homemade waffles anytime.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• Electric Waffle Maker - GES 20</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• The cast-iron plates of this professional waffle iron are fixed.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Features: commutator-thermostat 0-300 ° C, control lights. Delivered with a brush (F05054) and a timer.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Waffle size: 100 x 180 x 26 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Power: 1.6 kW</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Outside dimensions: 305 x 440 x 230 mm</p>\n<p style=""padding-top: 0"">• Weight: 22 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• volts: 230 V</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• GES 20 / Roller Grill / Made in France</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,3041,"BAKERY LINE","Electric Waffle Maker",,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/GES-20.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,"Roller Grill",Brand,"Roller Grill",1,1,Electric/Gas,Electric,1,1,default,1,1,0,,84,0,0,,"Electric Waffle Maker,صانعة الوافل ال