13737,simple,,,"Cheese Grater- 02A",1,0,visible,"Grater-02A is a versatile kitchen tool designed for easily and efficiently grating and shredding ingredients like cheese, vegetables, and fruits. Its sharp stainless steel blades ensure quick and precise results, while its ergonomic handle provides a comfortable grip for effortless use. Whether you're preparing salads, pasta dishes, or baked goods, Grater-02A simplifies the task of creating fine and consistent textures for your culinary creations.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• Grater- 02A (1 standard disc)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Average output: 50kg/hour</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• A wide range of discs is available to grate hard and soft cheese, chocolate, peanuts and dried fruits</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Its new design facilitates cleaning and maintenance (removable housing and disc)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Safety switch: the machine stops when opening the drawer or lever</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Delivered with 1 standard disc with ø 3 mm holes (other discs available on demand)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Power: 220 - 240 V - 50/60 Hz - 230 W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Speed: 1500 rpm (50 Hz) ~ 1800 rpm (60 Hz)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Weight: Net: 14,5 kg (32 lbs) ~ Packed: 15,6 kg (34 lbs)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Dim: 420 x 250 x 350 mm (D x W x H)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Model: 02A / SANTOS / FRANCE</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,3485,"FOOD PROCESSING > Cheese Grater, FOOD PROCESSING, Kitchen Equipment",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/9-1.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/7-2.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/6-3.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/5-1-1.png",,,,,,,,,0,,Santos,Brand,Santos,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,76,0,0,,"Grater,مبشرة الجبن,مبشرة الجبن- 02A",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,02A,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596293,001011011110001101001100011011010000011110011010,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
13742,simple,,,"Bar Blender Grey-33GEA",1,0,visible,"&nbsp;\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(736px, 199px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(212px, 45px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(54px, 53px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Small bar blender to make any kind of preparation with crushed ice: cocktails, smoothies, frozen drinks, fruit juices, milkshakes</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 2 speeds (13 000 rpm and 16 000 rpm), for an easy control of your preparation</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Strong stainless-steel blades</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Easy cleaning: removable bowl, cover, bowl base, blade</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Filler-cap to add ingredients while blending</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Single phase</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 100 - 120 V - 50/60 Hz - 600 W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 220 - 240 V - 50/60 Hz - 600 W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 2 speeds</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 12000 rpm and 16000 rpm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight 3,6 kg (7,9 lbs)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dimensions: 180x180x420</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Made by Santos, France</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(12px, 296px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(324px, 22px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(133px, 50px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,1400,"COFF