13755,simple,,,"Bar Blender Commercial - HBB255‐UK (replaces HBB250R)",1,0,visible,"The <strong data-start=""4"" data-end=""29"">HBB255-UK Bar Blender</strong> is a high-performance commercial blender designed for smooth and efficient blending of cocktails, smoothies, and frozen drinks. Replacing the HBB250R, it features a powerful motor, durable stainless steel blades, and a user-friendly design for consistent results. Ideal for bars, cafés, and restaurants, it ensures fast and reliable operation for high-demand environments.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(39px, 96px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(552px, 12px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;""><strong>Bar Blender Commercial - HBB255‐UK (replaces HBB250R)</strong>\n. (International) Rio® Bar Blender,\n. Two speed motor,\n. 48 oz. (1.36 liter) capacity\n. Stackable co‐polyester container,\n. Hi/low &amp; pulse switches,\n. Wave‐Action® System,\n. Sure Grip™ feet,\n. Stainless steel blades,\n. 1‐3/5 HP, 220‐240V/50/60/1‐ph, 780 watt, 6.5 amp,\nHamilton Beach Model No. HBB255‐UK (replaces\nHBB250R)</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,1400,"COFFEE & BAR LINE > Blenders, COFFEE & BAR LINE, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Bar-Blender-Commercial-HBB255‐UK.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"Hamilton Beach USA",Brand,"Hamilton Beach- USA",1,1,"Type of Product","Blender Mixer",1,1,default,1,1,0,,61,0,0,,"Bar Blender Commercial,Bar Blender Commercial - HBB255‐UK (replaces HBB250R)",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"HBB255‐UK (replaces
