13792,variable,,,"Coffee Grinder - GH 390",1,0,visible,"• High quality hardened steel blades for reliable high grinding performance.\n• Modern technology for the manufacture of grinding blades.\n• Acceptable quiet grinding sound.\n• Modular construction with easy access to projections for fast and comfortable maintenance. • Stylish molding and high-class materials reflect the prestigious GHS standards.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Coffee Grinder - GH 390</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Voltage/Frequency : 220V or 380V / 50-60Hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Motor Power: 1.5 KW</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Average Grinding Capacity: 900 g / min</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Tank Capacity: 1100 g</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Grinding Disk Diameter: 120 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Net Weight: 45 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dimensions (W*D*H)mm : 260*320*650</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Standard Color: Gold-Chrome, Silver-Chrome, Copper, Black, Red</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Coffee Grinder, Kitchen Equipment",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ghs-390.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/9-2.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/8-2.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/7-2-1.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/221-1-scaled.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/GH-395-1-scaled-1.jpg",,,,,,,,,0,,"George Haddad",Brand,"George Haddad",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,5,0,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110011001000110011001100110110011000110011100110,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,