13829,simple,,,"Classic Citrus Juicer - 11ca",1,0,visible,,"<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• Classic Citrus Juicer - 11ca</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Commercial juicer, built to last, with a heavy duty and quiet induction motor</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Easy to clean: removable bowl, grid, and squeezer</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Spout height: 125 mm (5"")</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Average output: 30l/h</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Voltage 220V</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Dimensions: Height 350mm Depth 300mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• 11ca / Santos / Made in France</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,1894,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Juice Maker, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/11ca.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Santos,Brand,Santos,1,1,"Type of Product","Citrus Juicer",1,1,default,1,1,0,,10,0,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,11ca,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596293,100011001111100110101100100001111001100000011101,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
13831,simple,,,"Silent Espresso Coffee Grinder - 40A",1,0,visible,"<strong>SILENT ESPRESSO COFFEE GRINDER - 40A</strong>\nThe 40A Silent Espresso Coffee Grinder combines precision and quiet operation, ideal for professional settings. With adjustable grind settings, durable construction, and efficient performance, it ensures consistent coffee grounds for the perfect espresso experience in cafes and restaurants.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• Silent Espresso Coffee Grinder - 40A</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Precision grinding: Ø 63,5 mm grinding discs which are designed and manufactured by Santos for a high quality grinding, precise and fine.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Constant dose: precise volumetric dispenser. Easy to adjust the dose (from 6.5g to 9g).</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Silent : 63 dB</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Powerful: commercial reliable induction motor.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Hopper capacity: 2.2 Kg.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Average output: 8 kg/h.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Motor Single Phase: 220 -240 V - 50/60 Hz - 360 W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Speed: 1800 rpm (60 Hz)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Net Weight: 13,8 kg (29 lbs)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Gross Weight: 15,3 kg (33 lbs)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Dimensions: D: 390 mm (16"") W: 190 mm (8"") H: 580 mm (23"")</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• 40A / Santos / Made in France</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,3210,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Coffee Grinder, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/40A.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Santos,Brand,Santos,1,1,"Type of Product","Coffee Grinder",1,1,default,1,1,0,,76,0,0,,"Silent Espresso Coffee Grinder,Silent Espresso Coffee Grinder - 40A",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,40A,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,100111100110100110011100011011001100110000111000,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
13833,simple,,,"Automatic Silent Espresso Coffee Grinder - 55BFA",1,0,visible,"<strong>AUTOMATIC SILENT ESPRESSO COFFEE GRINDER - 55BFA</strong>\nThe 55BFA Automatic Silent Espresso Coffee Grinder delivers precision grinding with minimal noise, making it perfect for busy cafes and restaurants. Featuring adjustable grind settings, a robust motor, and user-friendly operation, it ensures consistent coffee grounds for exceptional espresso every time.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• Automatic Silent Espresso Coffee Grinder - 55BFA</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Motor Single phase: 220 - 240 V - 50/60 Hz - 1100 W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Speed: 3500 rpm (60 Hz)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Net Weight : 15 kg (33 lbs)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Gross Weight: 17 kg (37 lbs)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Dimensions: D: 397 mm (16"") W: 198 mm (8"") H: 577 mm (23"")</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• 55BFA / Santos / Made in France</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,4252,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Coffee Grinder, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/55bfa.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Santos,Brand,Santos,1,1,"Type of Product","Coffee Grinder",1,1,default,1,1,0,,79,0,0,,"Automatic Silent Espresso Coffee Grinder,Automatic Silent Espresso Coffee Grinder - 55BFA",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,55BFA,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596293,100101110011011010010011001011001100110010110010,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
13835,simple,,,"Coffee Shop Grinder - 63A",1,0,visible,,"<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• Coffee Shop Grinder - 63A</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Fast, precise and reliable, this coffee grinder will give you a high quality grinding.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• It is adapted to intensive use.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Precision grinding: Equipped with triple cut grinding discs (Ø120 mm) designed and manufactured by Santos. High resistance, long lasting. Can be resharpened.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Perfect to make turkish coffee.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Stepless micrometric grinding adjustments: from extra fine to extra coarse.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Simple direct dispensing of the coffee: fresh ground coffee.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Bag Holder: 400 mm high. Accepts bags from 250gr to 1 kg.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Vibrating plate: for a better distribution of ground coffee into the bag.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Motor Single phase: 220 - 240 V - 50/60 Hz - 1500 W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Speed: 1800 rpm (60 Hz)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Net Weight: 40 kg (88 lbs)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Gross Weight: 49 kg (108 lbs)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Dimensions Net: D: 329 mm (13"") W: 279 mm (11"") H: 677 mm (27"")</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• 63A / Santos / Made in France</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,15214,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Coffee Grinder, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/63A.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Santos,Brand,Santos,1,1,"Type of Product","Coffee Grinder",1,1,default,1,1,0,,5,0,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,63A,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," 