13839,simple,,,"Santos Juicer - 50CA",1,0,visible,"Ready to experience the convenience and quality of the Santos Juicer? Shop now and discover where to buy this premium juicing machine. Start enjoying healthy, homemade juices with the Santos Juicer in your kitchen.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• Santos Juicer - 50CA</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Perfect filtration: a large basket with a very fine sieve (0.5 mm / 0.02'') offering high-quality juice.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Maximum juice extraction: excellent yield.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Extra wide feeding chute (79.5 mm): no need to cut apples, carrots, tomatoes...</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Silent: perfect to make juice in front of the customer.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Safety: Electric cut-off and motor braking stop the basket when opening the handle.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Exclusive Ezy-clean<sup>™</sup> system: Removable bowl, basket, and cover (no tool needed).</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Spout height: 200 mm (8.6""), to make juice in glasses, jugs, and blender jars.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Output: 100 l/h</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• 50CA / Santos / Made in France</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,5956,6600,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Juice Maker, Kitchen Equipment, Special Offer",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/50CA.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Santos,Brand,Santos,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,62,0,0,,"Santos Juicer",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,50CA,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,100111001100000111001100110001100010001111100111,,,,,,,,,salescountdowntimer,,,,,,,,,00:00,00:00,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
13841,simple,,,"Work Top Chiller - S700 S/S TOP",1,0,visible,,"<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Work Top Chiller - S700 S/S TOP</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• AISI 304 18/10 S/S exterior, except rear panel &amp; part of bottom.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• injected polyurethane insulation, CFC free, density: 40 kgs / m3</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cap: 135 ltr</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• w/ 2 shelf &amp; 1 drs.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• working Temp: +2˚ ~ +8° at 32° temp.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power Supply: 230v / 50 Hz / 1Ph.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• fridge power: 168 Watt</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• refrigerant : R134a</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Net Weight: 48 Kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 700 x 700 x 850 mm (WxDxH)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Digital : DIXELL / ITALY MADE .</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• compressor : ASPERA / EMBRACO / ITALY .</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• S700 S/S TOP / mariot made</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• ISO9001, CE&amp;ROHS approved""</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,2521,"REFRIGERATION LINE > Freezer & Chillers, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/24.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Mariot,Brand,Mariot,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,8,0,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"S700 S/S TOP",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,100000111001000111111000111011110001001010110010,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
13843,simple,,,"Work Top Freezer - S700 S/S BT",1,0,visible,"<strong>Work Top Freezer – S700 S/S BT</strong>\nThe S700 S/S BT Work Top Freezer is a durable and efficient addition to any commercial kitchen. Featuring a stainless steel work surface and reliable freezing storage, it provides consistent low temperatures to keep ingredients fresh while optimizing workspace functionality. Perfect for high-performance food preparation environments.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Work Top Freezer - S700 S/S BT</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• AISI 304 18/10 S/S exterior, except rear panel &amp; part of bottom.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• injected polyurethane insulation, CFC free, density: 40 kgs / m3</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cap: 135 ltr</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• w/ 2 shelf &amp; 1 drs.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• working Temp: -18˚ ~ -22° at 32° temp.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power Supply: 230v / 50 Hz / 1Ph.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• fridge power: 296 Watt</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• refrigerant : R404a</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Net Weight: 48 Kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 700 x 700 x 900 mm (WxDxH)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Digital : DIXELL / ITALY MADE</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• compressor : ASPERA / EMBRACO / ITALY.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• S700 S/S BT / mariot made</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• ISO9001, CE&amp;ROHS approved</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,3210,"REFRIGERATION LINE > Freezer & Chillers, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/24.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Inofrigo,Brand,Inofrigo,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,63,0,0,,"Work Top Freezer,Work Top Freezer - S700 S/S BT",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"S700 S/S BT",f