13882,simple,,,"SALADETTE WITH GLASS COVER - S900T",1,0,visible,"The SALADETTE WITH GLASS COVER - S900T is a compact and efficient refrigerated unit designed to store and display fresh salads, sandwiches, and other chilled items. Its glass cover allows customers to easily view the contents while maintaining optimal temperature and hygiene. Ideal for cafes, delis, and small food establishments, this salade tte offers convenience and style to enhance your food presentation.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• SALADETTE WITH GLASS COVER - S900T</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Volume (Liters): 250</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Glass cover , design for GN pans, Hight density insulation for cooling system</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Static or ventilated system are available</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• S/S structure, GN1/1 shelf size for operation</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Europe brand controller &amp; compressor</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cutting board with PP, Round corner hygiene</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Inner bottom use bend line to drain pipe</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Castor &amp; led light is available</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Door easy to change Drawers or Glass door</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Top quality cooper pipe built-in, Adjustable shelving</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Magnetic gasket can be changed without tools</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• temperature range: 2°C~8°C</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Refrigerant: R134a / R290</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Refrigeration type: Static</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Rated power (W): 204</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Net weight (KGS): 99</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Digital : DIXELL / ITALY MADE</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• compressor : ASPERA / EMBRACO / ITALY</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• S900 T / mariot made</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 900*700*850 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• ISO9001, CE&amp;ROHS approved""</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,2739,3221,"REFRIGERATION LINE > Freezer & Chillers, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE, Special Offer",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/SALADETTE-WITH-GLASS-COVER-–-S900T.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Inofrigo,Brand,Inofrigo,1,1,Model,s900t,1,1,default,1,1,0,,5,0,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,S900T,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,15750,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011100110001110000110110101100100001101111100001,,,,,,,,,salescountdowntimer,"Type of Product","SALADETTE WITH GLASS COVER",1,1,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
