13892,simple,,,"PIZZA SALATTE PREPARATION- PS200",1,0,visible,"The PS200 Pizza Salatte Preparation is a versatile and efficient machine designed to simplify the process of preparing pizza salads. With its user-friendly interface and advanced features, it allows for quick and precise slicing, dicing, and mixing of ingredients, ensuring consistent and delicious pizza salads every time. Whether for small pizzerias or large restaurants, the PS200 is a valuable addition to any kitchen, enhancing productivity and delivering high-quality pizza salads to satisfy customers' cravings.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• PIZZA SALATTE PREPARATION- PS200</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• S/S prep area &amp; cooled gastronom pan section that has a lid</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 304 S/S construction interior and exterior</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Static cooling</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• User friendly controls and digital display</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 1 adjustable shelf per door included</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Auto defrost</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Walls and door 35mm thick insulation</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Self closing doors</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Fits 5x 1/6 gastronom pans (not supplied)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Stainless steel worktop area</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Refrigerated temp +2 to +8</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 900 x 700 x 970 mm (WxDxH)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Digital : DIXELL / ITALY MADE</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• compressor : ASPERA / EMBRACO / ITALY</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• PS200 / MARIOT MADE</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• ISO9001, CE&amp;ROHS approved</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,2689,3170,"REFR