13894,simple,,,"PIZZA SALATTE WITH TABLE TOP- PS300",1,0,visible,"The PS300 PIZZA SALATTE WITH TABLE TOP is a top-of-the-line machine designed to streamline the preparation process for pizza salads. Equipped with cutting-edge technology and user-friendly controls, it enables swift and precise slicing, dicing, and mixing of ingredients, ensuring consistently delectable pizza salads. Its robust build and high capacity make it suitable for busy pizzerias and restaurants, saving time and effort in the kitchen while delivering exceptional quality pizza salads to satisfy discerning customers. Upgrade your salad preparation with the PS300 for enhanced efficiency and mouthwatering results.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• PIZZA SALATTE WITH TABLE TOP- PS300</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Volume: 390</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Open for GN1/6，other GN pans is available</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Hight density insulation for cooling system</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Static or ventilated system are available</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Stainless steel structure</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• GN1/1 shelf size for operation</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Europe brand controller &amp; Europe brand compressor</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Round corner hygiene</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Inner bottom use bend line to drain pipe</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Castor is available</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Door easy to change Drawers or Glass door</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Top quality cooper pipe built-in</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Led light is available</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Magnetic gasket can be changed without tools</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• temperature range: 2°C~8°C</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power: 321</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight: 91</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Refrigerant: R134a / R290</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Refrigeration type: static</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 1365*700*980 mm</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,3400,"REFRIGERATION LINE > Freezer & Chillers, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/PIZZA-SALATTE-WITH-TABLE-TOP1-PS300.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Inofrigo,Brand,Inofrigo,1,1,"Type of Product","PIZZA SALATTE WITH TABLE TOP",1,1,default,1,1,0,,81,0,0,,"PIZZA SALATTE WITH TABLE TOP",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,PS300,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,15756,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,010111101001010110100110101110100001001011101000,,,,,,,,,,Model,PS300,1,1,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
13896,simple,,,"WORK TOP FREEZER- S901 S/S BT",1,0,visible,"The WORK TOP FREEZER- S901 S/S BT is a high-quality and efficient freezer designed to meet the freezing needs of businesses and commercial establishments. With its stainless steel construction, it offers durability and a professional appearance. The worktop design provides a convenient surface for food preparation or other tasks, making it a versatile addition to any kitchen. Its reliable freezing capabilities ensure that your perishable goods stay fresh and preserved for extended periods. Upgrade your freezing solution with the S901 S/S BT Work Top Freezer for optimal performance and storage convenience.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• WORK TOP FREEZER- S901 S/S BT</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• AISI 304 18/10 S/S exterior, except rear panel &amp; part of bottom</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• AISI 304 18/10 S/S interior, w/ water line for colecting condensing water. Magnetic gasket</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• injected polyurethane insulation, CFC free, density: 40 kgs / m3</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cap: 250 ltr</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• w/ 2 shelf &amp; 2 drs</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• working Temp: -15˚ ~ -20° at 32° temp</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power Supply: 230v / 50 Hz / 1Ph</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• refrigerant : R404a</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Net Weight: 70 Kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 900 x 700 x 850 mm (WxDxH)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Digital : DIXELL / ITALY MADE</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• compressor : ASPERA / EMBRACO / ITALY</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• S901 S/S BT / mariot made</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• ISO9001, CE&amp;ROHS approved</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,3352,3626,"REFRIG