13901,simple,,,"WORK TOP CHILLER- S903 S/S TOP",1,0,visible,"The WORK TOP CHILLER- S903 S/S TOP is a premium chiller designed to meet the cooling needs of businesses and commercial establishments. Crafted with stainless steel, it offers both durability and a sleek, professional appearance. The worktop design provides a convenient surface for food preparation or other tasks, adding versatility to any kitchen setup. This chiller delivers efficient and reliable cooling performance, ensuring that perishable items stay fresh and ready for use. Upgrade your cooling solution with the S903 S/S Top Work Top Chiller for exceptional performance and convenient storage.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• WORK TOP CHILLER- S903 S/S TOP</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 3 Door Refrigerated Counter w/ S/S Top</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 304 S/S construction interior and exterior</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Famouse brand compressor</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Temperature +2 ~ +8°C</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Static cooling Userfriendly,controls&amp;digital display</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 1 adjustable shelf per door included</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Auto defrost</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Walls and door 35mm thick insulation</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Self closing doors</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dimensions 1400 x 700 x 850mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Digital : DIXELL / ITALY MADE</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• compressor : ASPERA / EMBRACO / ITALY</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• S903 S/S TOP / MARIOT MADE</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• ISO9001, CE&amp;ROHS approved</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,3328,3598,"REFRIGERATION LINE > Freezer & Chillers, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE, Special Of