13909,simple,,,"COUNTER FREEZER- GN1100BT",1,0,visible,"The Counter Freezer GN1100BT offers a versatile freezing solution for commercial and professional environments. Designed to fit seamlessly into counter spaces, this freezer provides efficient and reliable freezing capabilities. With adjustable temperature controls and a spacious interior, it's perfect for preserving a wide range of frozen goods. The sleek design and user-friendly features make it a practical choice for businesses that require precise and accessible freezing options. The GN1100BT is an ideal combination of convenience and performance, catering to the needs of various establishments.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• COUNTER FREEZER- GN1100BT</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Volume (Ltrs): 260</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• S/S structure, ventilated cooling system, high density insulation body</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Easy to clean</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Self-closing door with magnetic gaskets</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• temperature range: -20°C~-15°C</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Refrigerant: Ventilated</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power (W): 588</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Net weight (KGS): 104</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 925*700*850 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• packing size (mm): 985×740×910 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Model No. GN1100BT / CHINA</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,3483,4098,"REFRIGERATION LINE > Freezer & Chillers, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE, Special Offer",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/COUNTER-CHILLER-GN1100TN.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Inofrigo,Brand,Inofrigo,1,1,Model,GN1100BT,1,1,default,1,1,0,,79,0,0,,"COUNTER FREEZER",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,GN1100BT,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387