13910,simple,,,"WORK TOP CHILLER- GN4100TN",1,0,visible,"The Work Top Chiller GN4100TN is a versatile and efficient cooling solution designed for commercial use. Its convenient worktop design provides both a functional workspace and easy access to chilled ingredients. With adjustable temperature controls and a spacious interior, this chiller is perfect for keeping a variety of food items and beverages at the ideal temperature. Its durable construction and user-friendly features make it a reliable choice for businesses that require convenient and accessible cooling options. The GN4100TN work top chiller combines practicality with performance, catering to the needs of professional establishments.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• WORK TOP CHILLER- GN4100TN</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• AISI 304 18/10 S/S interior &amp; exterior w/ sanitary corner except rear panel &amp; part of bottom</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• automatic closing door w/ magnetic gasket, 90° reversible w/ 6 castor wheels</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• injected polyurethane insulation, CFC free, density: 40 kgs / m3</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cap: 540 ltr.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• w/ 4 shelf &amp; 4 drs</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• working Temp: +2˚ ~ +8° at 32° temp</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power Supply: 230v / 50 Hz / 1Ph</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• frige power: 470 Watt</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• refrigerant : R134a</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Net Weight: 134 Kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 2230 x 700 x 850 mm (WxDxH)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Digital : DIXELL / ITALY MADE</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• compressor : ASPERA / EMBRACO / ITALY</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• GN4100TN / mariot made</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• ISO9001, CE&amp;ROHS approved</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,5229,"REFRIGERATION LINE > Freezer & Chillers, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE, Special Offer",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/WORK-TOP-CHILLER-GN4100TN.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Inofrigo,Brand,Inofrigo,1,1,Model,GN4100TN,1,1,default,1,1,0,,65,0,0,,"WORK TOP CHILLER",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,GN4100TN,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011111110000011110000010111010001100010100110101,false,,,,,,,,salescountdowntimer,"Type of Product","Work Top Chiller",1,1,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
