13942,simple,,,"WORK TOP FREEZER WITH DRAWER- UNGN2140BT",1,0,visible,"The UNGN2140BT Work Top Freezer is a versatile freezing solution designed for commercial use. With its convenient worktop surface, it offers a combination of frozen storage and functional workspace in a single unit. This freezer is expertly designed to ensure optimal freezing performance, making it ideal for preserving the quality of frozen items while providing a practical area for food preparation. Its advanced freezing technology maintains consistent low temperatures, ensuring the longevity of stored items. The UNGN2140BT Work Top Freezer seamlessly integrates freezing and workspace, making it an excellent choice for businesses seeking efficiency and convenience in their operations.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• WORK TOP FREEZER WITH DRAWER- UNGN2140BT</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Volume (Ltrs): 200</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Europe brand controller &amp; compressor</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Europe standard GN 1/1 pan designed, s/s structure, ventilated cooling system, high density insulation body</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Smart automatic defrosting</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Interior body with round corner, easy to clean</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Self-closing door with magnetic gaskets</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Adjustable shelving design</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Doors can be easily change to be 2 set-drawers</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• The depth of the counter can be customized to 60cm,65cm,70cm,75cm,80cm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• temperature range: -15~-20</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Refrigerant: Ventilated</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power (W): 210</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Net weight (KGS): 104</p