style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• UNGN3160TN / mariot made</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• ISO9001, CE&amp;ROHS approved""</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,8683,"REFRIGERATION LINE > Freezer & Chillers, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/WORK-TOP-CHILLER-UNGN3160-TN.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Inofrigo,Brand,Inofrigo,1,1,Model,UNGN3160TN,1,1,default,1,1,0,,81,0,0,,"WORK TOP CHILLER",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,UNGN3160TN,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,010101110000010010100011111010010111010000011111,,,,,,,,,,"Type of Product","WORK TOP CHILLER WITH DRAWER",1,1,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
13944,simple,,,"WORK TOP CHILLER WITH DRAWER- UNGN4180TN",1,0,visible,"The UNGN4180TN Work Top Chiller is a versatile refrigeration solution designed for commercial use. With its convenient worktop surface, it offers a combination of cold storage and functional workspace in one unit. This chiller is expertly designed to ensure optimal cooling performance, making it ideal for preserving the freshness of ingredients while providing a practical area for food preparation. Its advanced cooling technology maintains consistent temperatures, guaranteeing the quality of stored items. The UNGN4180TN Work Top Chiller seamlessly blends refrigeration and workspace, making it a perfect choice for businesses seeking efficiency and convenience in their operations.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• WORK TOP CHILLER- UNGN4180TN</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• automatic closing door w/ magnetic gasket, 90° reversible w/ 6 castor wheels</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• injected polyurethane insulation, CFC free, density: 40 kgs / m3</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cap: 360 ltr.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• w/ 6 shelf &amp; 6 drs.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• working Temp: +2˚ ~ +8° at 32° temp.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power Supply: 230v / 50 Hz / 1Ph.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• frige power: 470 Watt</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• refrigerant : R134a</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Net Weight: 160 Kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 2230 x 700 x 650 mm (WxDxH)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Digital : DIXELL / ITALY MADE</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• compressor : ASPERA / EMBRACO / ITALY</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• UNGN4180TN / mariot made</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• ISO9001, CE&amp;ROHS approved</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,