13945,simple,,,"CHEF DRAWER- CDF-BT-1",1,0,visible,"The CDF-BT-1 Chef Drawer is a versatile and efficient storage solution for commercial kitchens. With its compact design, it offers a practical way to organize utensils, tools, and ingredients right at the chef's workstation. This drawer is expertly crafted to withstand the demands of a busy kitchen environment, providing easy access to essential items for seamless food preparation. The CDF-BT-1 Chef Drawer enhances workflow and organization, making it an essential addition to any professional kitchen setting.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• CHEF DRAWER- CDF-BT-1</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Net capacity (L): 78</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Refrigeration and freezing can be switched freely</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• European standard large capacity drawer, which can hold 2/1 copies of pots, with a maximum depth of 150mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• It can be stacked for use, and can be combined with refrigeration and freezing freely- S/S structure</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• High density insulation body w/ magnetic door seal.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Europe brand controller &amp; compressor</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Refrigeration intelligent automatic defrosting</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• It can be stacked up and down.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Door handle design.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cooling holes.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• temperature range: -15~-20</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Refrigerant: Ventilated</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power (W): 255</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Net weight (KGS): 61</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 1100×670×455 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Model No. CDF-BT-1/ CHINA</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,4306,5067,"REFRIGERATION LINE > Freezer & Chillers, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE, Special Offer",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/chef-drawer-cdf.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/chef-drawer-cdf2.png",,,,,,,,,0,,Inofrigo,Brand,Inofrigo,1,1,Model,CDF-BT-1,1,1,default,1,1,0,,81,0,0,,"CHEF DRAWER",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,CDF-BT-1,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596375,011101110011011000100011101000010111000100110110,,,,,,,,,salescountdowntimer,"Type of Product","CHEF DRAWER",1,1,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
13946,simple,,,"Vertical Conveyor Bun Grill Toaster- M-83",1,0,visible,"The Vertical Conveyor Bun Grill Toaster- M-83 is an innovative kitchen appliance designed to efficiently toast burger buns. This toaster features a unique vertical conveyor system that evenly toasts buns from top to bottom, ensuring a consistent and crispy result. Its space-saving design and fast toasting capability make it an ideal choice for commercial kitchens seeking quick and uniform bun toasting.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Vertical Conveyor Bun Grill Toaster - 240V</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Capacity: up to 500 to 800 pieces per hour</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• The M-83 Bun Grill toaster standard grilling cycles of 35 seconds produce 500 to 800 bun halves per hour</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Bun Grill is available with extended superfeeder to allow for high volume production</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Fast heat-up allows your operatbn to react to surges in volume</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Contructed of heavy-duty s/s. Nickel plated steel griddle plate. adjustable legs</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power: 240V, 1600 W, 6.7 Amps</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight: 44 kg (97 lbs)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Overall Dimensions: 508 x 625.4 x 304.8 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 787.4 x 625.4 x 419.1 mm (with superfeeder)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Model No. APW Wyott M-83 / USA</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,12102,"BAKERY LINE, Kitchen Equipment, SNACK MAKER, BAKERY LINE > Toaster",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Toaster-m-3-2.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Toaster-m-3-2-1.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Toaster-m-3-3.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Toaster-m-3-4.png",,,,,,,,