13951,simple,,,"Single Door Upright Chiller- SNACK301TN",1,0,visible,"The Single Door Upright Chiller- SNACK301TN is a versatile refrigeration appliance designed to store and preserve perishable items. With its spacious interior and efficient cooling system, it offers an ideal solution for keeping snacks, beverages, and other products at the desired temperature. The single door design optimizes space usage, making it suitable for various commercial settings such as convenience stores, cafes, and restaurants, where efficient cooling and easy access are essential.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Single Door Upright Chiller- SNACK301TN</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• S/S structure, Ventilated system, High density insulation body, Automatic defrosting</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Volume: 300</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Europe brand digital controller &amp; compressor</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Self-closing door with magnetic gaskets</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Adjustable shelving</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Glass door is available</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Adjustable feet or castor is available</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Led light is available</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Freezer modle are added heating element in doorframe, keep no fog around doorframe</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• temperature range: 2°C~8°C</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power: 340</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight: 98</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Refrigerant: Ventilated</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 498*690*2040 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Model No. SNACK301TN / CHINA</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,3314,3899,"REFRIGERATION LINE > Freezer & Chillers, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE,