13957,simple,,,"Upright Chiller w/Glass Door- GN1410TN/G",1,0,visible,"The Upright Chiller with Glass Door - GN1410TN/G is a sophisticated refrigeration appliance designed to elegantly display and preserve a wide range of perishable items. With its sleek glass door design and efficient cooling system, it provides an attractive showcase for products while maintaining their freshness. The spacious interior and adjustable shelving make it versatile for storing various items at optimal temperatures. Ideal for supermarkets, delis, and convenience stores, this chiller offers easy visibility and access to products, enhancing both aesthetics and functionality.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Upright Chiller w/Glass Door- GN1410TN/G</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• S/s structure AISI 304 interior &amp; exterior</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Material: Stainless Steel</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Door: 2 doors, Double</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Capacity: &gt;300L</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Compressor-- Aspera</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• EBM Motor</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Controller ---Italian Dixell</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Standard: CE STD</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Use: Refrigerator</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power Source: Electricity</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 1480 x 830 x 2010 mm (WxDxH)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Digital : DIXELL / ITALY MADE</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• compressor : ASPERA / EMBRACO / ITALY</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• GN1410TN/G MARIOT MADE</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• ISO9001, CE&amp;ROHS approved</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,6412,"REFRIGERATION LINE > Freezer & Chillers, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE, Special Offer",,,ht