13959,simple,,,"Double Doors Upright Chiller/Freezer-  GN650DT/D",1,0,visible,"The Double Doors Upright Chiller/Freezer - GN650DT/D is a versatile refrigeration solution designed to meet diverse storage needs. With its dual compartments, this appliance offers both chilling and freezing capabilities, making it ideal for businesses requiring flexible temperature zones. The spacious interior, adjustable shelving, and efficient cooling system ensure optimal preservation of a wide range of products. Whether used in restaurants, supermarkets, or catering facilities, this chiller/freezer provides convenient access, efficient organization, and reliable temperature control for perishable items.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Double Doors Upright Chiller/Freezer- GN650DT/D</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• AISI 304 18/10 S/S interior &amp; exterior w/ sanitary corner except rear panel &amp; part of bottom</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• automatic closing door w/ magnetic gasket, 90° reversible</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• injected polyurethane insulation, CFC free, density: 40 kgs / m3</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cap: 580 ltr.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• w/ 3 shelf &amp; 1 drs + 4 castor wheels</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Double temp. Chiller room :+2~+8 degree</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Double temp. Freezer room:-18~-22 degree</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power Supply: 230v / 50 Hz / 1Ph.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• frige power: 520 Watt</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• refrigerant : R404a</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Net Weight: 122 Kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 830 x 740 x 2010mm (WxDxH)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Digital : DIXELL / ITALY MADE</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• compressor : ASPERA / EMBRACO / ITALY</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• GN650DT/D/ MARIOT MADE/ ISO9001, CE&amp;ROHS approved</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,5800,6969,"REFRIGERATION LINE > Freezer & Chillers, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE, Special Offer",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Double-Doors-Upright-Chiller-Freezer.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Inofrigo,Model,GN650DT/D,1,1,"Type of Product","Double Doors Upright Chiller/Freezer",1,1,default,1,1,0,,63,0,0,,"Double Doors Upright Chiller/Freezer",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,GN650DT/D,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011000000111011100111100110110001110011001100001,,,,,,,,,salescountdowntimer,Brand,Inofrigo,1,1,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
