13965,simple,,,"Saladette  Preparation Chiller- SH3000/700TN",1,0,visible,"""Elevate your food preparation with the Saladette Preparation Chiller - Model SH3000/700TN. This compact and efficient unit is designed to keep your ingredients fresh and readily accessible. With its spacious design and convenient worktop, it's perfect for creating salads and sandwiches. The advanced cooling system ensures optimal temperatures, making it an essential addition to any professional kitchen or food establishment.""","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Saladette Preparation Chiller- SH3000/700TN</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• AISI304 S/S framework construction. CFC free</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Electronic control panel with digital display</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Temperature: +2℃--+8</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Refrigerant: R134A Reversible door.Magnetic gaskets. Replaceable without tools</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• AISI 304 S/S adjustable feet. Self closing door designed with S/S handle</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Perforated panel on both sides allows good ventilation for the fresh food</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Standard eqpt: n°1 gn1/1 shelf for each door</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dimensions 1795 x 700 x 1050mm (WxDxH)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Digital : DIXELL / ITALY MADE</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• compressor : ASPERA / EMBRACO / ITALY</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• SH3000/700TN NEW / mariot made</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• ISO9001, CE&amp;ROHS approved</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,6412,"REFRIGERATION LINE > Freezer & Chillers, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE","COUNTER CHILLER WITH DRAWER, GLASS DOOR COUNTER CHILLER, Salad bar, WORK TOP CHILLER",,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Saladette-Pr