13971,simple,,,"LUXURY PIZZA COUNTER- PZ3100TN+VRX",1,0,visible,"""Elevate your pizza experience with the Luxury Pizza Counter - Model PZ3100TN+VRX. This exquisite counter is designed to redefine pizza preparation, seamlessly blending luxury and functionality. With its sophisticated aesthetics and cutting-edge features, it sets a new standard for pizza craftsmanship. Offering ample storage, convenient access, and an integrated workspace, it's a must-have addition for upscale pizzerias and culinary establishments aiming for excellence.""","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• LUXURY PIZZA COUNTER- PZ3100TN+VRX</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Pizza preparation chiller + salad bar.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• granite top: 1460 x 740 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 3 stainless steel doors: 500 x 670 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• temp: +2 ~ +10 °c.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• compressor : aspera, slovakia made (left side)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• refrigeration gas: r 134a.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• adjustable height</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• power: 220~240 v / 50~60 hz / 370 w</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• gross weight: 185 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• dim: 1795 x 700 x 850 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Digital : DIXELL / ITALY MADE</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• compressor : ASPERA / EMBRACO / ITALY</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• PZ3100TN+VRX/ mariot made / uae</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• ISO9001, CE&amp;ROHS approved</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,5853.95,6887,"REFRIGERATION LINE > Freezer & Chillers, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE, Special Offer","COUNTER CHILLER WITH DRAWER, GLASS DOOR COUNTER CHILLER, LUXURY PIZZA COUNTER, WORK TOP CHILLER",,https://mariotstore.com/wp-conte