13973,simple,,,"LUXURY PIZZA COUNTER- PZ2610TN",1,0,visible,"""Elevate your pizza-making game with the Luxury Pizza Counter - Model PZ2610TN. Crafted for perfection, this counter seamlessly blends elegance and functionality. Its sleek design and advanced features enhance the pizza preparation process, while offering ample storage and a dedicated workspace. An essential addition for high-end pizzerias and culinary establishments aiming to create exceptional pizzas.""","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• LUXURY PIZZA COUNTER- PZ2610TN</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Pizza preparation chiller</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• granite top: 1460 x 740 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 3 stainless steel doors: 500 x 670 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• temp: +2 ~ +10 °c</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• compressor : aspera, slovakia made (left side)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• refrigeration gas: r 134a</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• adjustable height</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• power: 220~240 v / 50~60 hz / 370 w</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• gross weight: 185 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• dim: 2025 x 800 x 850 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Digital : DIXELL / ITALY MADE</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• compressor : ASPERA / EMBRACO / ITALY</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• PZ2610TN/ mariot made / uae</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• ISO9001, CE&amp;ROHS approved</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,7837,9221,"REFRIGERATION LINE > Freezer & Chillers, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE, Special Offer","COUNTER CHILLER WITH DRAWER, GLASS DOOR COUNTER CHILLER, LUXURY PIZZA COUNTER, Salad bar, WORK TOP CHILLER",,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/LUXURY-PIZZA-COUNTER-PZ2610TN.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Inofrigo,Brand,Inofrigo