13987,simple,,,"ELECTRIC FRYER FE - 07 V",1,0,visible,"The ELECTRIC FRYER FE - 07 V is a versatile kitchen appliance designed to deliver efficient frying results. With its user-friendly controls and compact design, it's perfect for both professional kitchens and home use. The fryer's adjustable temperature settings and reliable heating element ensure that various foods can be fried to perfection. Its easy-to-clean construction and safety features make it a convenient choice for anyone seeking crispy and delicious fried dishes with ease. Elevate your frying experience with the ELECTRIC FRYER FE - 07 V.","• ELECTRIC FRYER FE - 07 V\n\n• 7-8 liter tank\n\n• basket size: 210x235x100 mm\n\n• Cold zone type\n\n• temperature control between 50 -190°C.\n\n• Special stainless steel heating elements\n\n• ceramic thermostat (working, safety)\n\n• drain outlet 3/4\n\n• External dimensions: 270 x 420 x 370 mm\n\n• Voltage: 230 V, 50 Hz\n\n• Capacity: 3 kW\n\n• Net weight: 7,9 kg\n\n• Gross weight: 8,9 kg\n\n• FE-07V/ RM GASTRO / europe made",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,1813,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Fryers, Kitchen Equipment, Offer",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ELECTRIC-FRYER-FE-07-V.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"RM Gastro",Brand,"RM Gastro",1,1,Electric/Gas,Electric,1,1,default,1,1,0,index,68,0,0,,"ELECTRIC FRYER",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"FE - 07 V",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,010000011010111000011001111100101100110101001011,true,backend,,,,,,,salescountdowntimer,Series,"Table Top",1,1,"Type of Product",Fryer,1,1,10:00,10:00,,,,,,,,,1359.75,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
13989,simple,,,"Electric Waffle Iron for ice cream cones - GES 40",1,0,visible,"The Electric Waffle Iron GES 40 is a specialized kitchen appliance designed for crafting delectable ice cream cones at home. With its user-friendly features and advanced heating technology, you can effortlessly create perfectly textured and crispy cones. The GES 40 comes equipped with a non-stick cooking surface, ensuring easy cone removal and quick cleaning. Its adjustable temperature settings and indicator lights make it simple to achieve the ideal cone crispiness. Whether you're an amateur cook or a culinary enthusiast, the Electric Waffle Iron GES 40 offers a convenient solution to enjoy homemade ice cream cones that perfectly complement your favorite frozen treats.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• Electric Waffle Iron for ice cream cones - GES 40</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Waffle size: 250 x 250 x 4 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Power: 1.6 kW</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Outside dimensions: 305 x 440 x 230 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Weight 22 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• volts 230 V</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• commutator-thermostat 0-300 ° C</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• control lights</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Delivered with a brush (F05054) and a timer</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• GES 40 / Roller Grill / Made in France</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,3041,"BAKERY LINE, Kitchen Equipment","Electric Waffle Iron for ice cream cones - GES 40, Electric Waffle Maker",,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Electric-Waffle-Iron-for-ice-cream-cones-GES-40.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"Roller Grill",Brand,"Roller Grill",1,1,Electric/Gas,Electric,1,1,default,1,1,0,,81,0,0,,"Electric Waffle",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"GES 40",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f