13991,simple,,,"Double Waffle Maker - GED 20",1,0,visible,"The Double Waffle Maker GED 20 is an innovative kitchen appliance designed for crafting two delicious waffles simultaneously. With its advanced features and efficient heating technology, you can effortlessly create evenly cooked and golden-brown waffles every time. The GED 20 is equipped with non-stick cooking surfaces, ensuring easy waffle release and quick cleanup. Adjustable temperature settings and indicator lights make it simple to achieve your preferred waffle texture. Whether you're cooking for a small group or a hungry family, the Double Waffle Maker GED 20 offers a convenient solution for enjoying homemade waffles that satisfy your cravings and elevate your culinary experience.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• Double Waffle Maker - GED 20</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Waffle size 100 x 180 x 26 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Power 3.2 kW</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Outside dimensions 550 x 440 x 230 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Weight 38 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• volts 230 V</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• commutator-thermostats 0-300 ° C</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• control lights</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Delivered with a brush (F05054) and a timer</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• GED 20 / Roller Grill / Made in France</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,5964,"Kitchen Equipment, SNACK MAKER, Top Brands, SNACK MAKER > Waffle Maker","Electric Waffle Iron for ice cream cones - GES 40, Electric Waffle Maker",,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Electric-Waffle-Maker-GED-20.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ICE-CREAM-MACHINE-WITH-STAND-KLS-F626.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ICE-CREAM-MACHINE-WITH-STAND-KLS-F626-1.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Co