14003,simple,,,"Hot - Cold Food Distribution Carts - Emp.med.s.24-1/3",1,0,visible,"This vehicle is specially designed for easy transportation of meals and maintaining them at the required temperature in hospitals, clinics, and similar places. Its unique design offers convenience to the user. The vehicles can be easily arranged side by side or in a row, saving space in businesses. Thanks to its compact structure, it can be easily transported between floors and operate without taking up space on the floors. With handles on both sides, users can easily maneuver and move the vehicle. Additionally, with six wheels on the vehicle, it can easily rotate around itself. At the front of the vehicle, there is a foldable tray table where the user can place trays as needed or seek assistance from it as required.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Hot - Cold Food Distribution Carts - Emp.med.s.24-1/3</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• IP-65 protected USB port</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• IP-65 protected Ethernet port</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Wireless network (Wi-Fi) connectivity</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Ability to collect temperature data while in motion thanks to its built-in battery</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Ability to store 1 year of historical temperature data in its internal memory</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Capability to transfer data to EMPERO MED-SOFT software via USB flash drive or through wired or wireless network</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Display of battery status and date on the screen</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Display of the department label to which the device belongs on the screen</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Temperature adjustment for hot compartment between +50°C and +90°C</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Temperature adjustment for cold compartment between 0°C and +6°C</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Ability to program with 4 adjustable programs for desired temperature and time settings</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Tray Dimensions: 575x325 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Tray Type: GN 1/2 - GN 1/3</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,32000,"Kitchen Equipment, Uncategorized","Hot - Cold Food Distribution Carts",,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/EMP.MED_.S.24-12-EMP.MED_.S.24-13-scaled.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Empero,Brand,Empero,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,68,0,0,,"Hot - Cold Food Distribution Carts",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595951,110010011011010011011001110100100110010001001101,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14005,simple,,,"RICE/GRAIN COOKER - 37560R-UK",1,0,visible,"The RICE/GRAIN COOKER - 37560R-UK is a convenient and versatile kitchen appliance designed to simplify the process of cooking rice and grains. With its user-friendly features and efficient functionality, this cooker is an essential addition to any kitchen","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• RICE/GRAIN COOKER - 37560R-UK</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• (International) Proctor-Silex® Commercial Rice</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cooker/Warmer,</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 60 cup cooked (14 liter) capacity,</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Includes: measuring cup (3.8 cup)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• paddle, moisture cup, lined/heated hinged lid (37560R-CE)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• press button trigger handle</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• button trigger handle</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• cook/warm switch</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• automatic keepwarm feature</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• double wall insulated</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• stainless steel</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 220-240v/50/60/1-ph</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 1950 watts</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Hamilton Beach Model No. 37560R-UK</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,1700,"COOKING LINE, Kitchen Equipment, COOKING LINE > Rice Cooker","RICE/GRAIN COOKER",,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/rice-cooker.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"Hamilton Beach USA",Brand,"Hamilton Beach- USA",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,79,0,0,,"RICE/GRAIN COOKER",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,37560R-UK,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,10001110010000011100