14007,variable,,,"ICE CREAM MAKING MACHINE - KLS-S12",1,0,visible,"The KLS-S12 Ice Cream Making Machine is a state-of-the-art appliance designed to simplify the process of creating delicious, creamy ice cream in various flavors and textures. This machine is a versatile and indispensable addition to any kitchen, whether you're a professional ice cream maker or a home enthusiast looking to craft your frozen treats.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• ICE CREAM MAKING MACHINE - KLS-S12</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Many colors are available.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Touch screen operation panel，Chinese and English screen optional.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Brand compressor, super refrigeration.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Overnight preservation function, pre-cooling preservation and no cleaning.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Magnetic drive cylinder stirrer.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Silent reducer with finely ground steel gears</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• The 4.5L hopper is made of 304 food grade stainless steel.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Efficient evaporator to prevent leakage.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• All copper tube double inlet single outlet condenser.</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,,"REFRIGERATION LINE > Ice Cream Machines, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ICE-CREAM-MAKING-MACHINE-KLS-S12-O-scaled-1.jpg, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ICE-CREAM-MAKING-MACHINE-KLS-S12-OR.jpg, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ICE-CREAM-MAKING-MACHINE-KLS-S12-ORA.jpg, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ICE-CREAM-MAKING-MACHINE-KLS-S12-ORAN.jpg, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ICE-CREAM-MAKING-MACHINE-KLS-S12-YE.jpg, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/20