14018,simple,,,"ROTARY OVEN VENARRO VENARDI DEF-D9",1,0,visible,"The Venarro Venardi DEF-D9 Rotary Oven is a high-quality and versatile baking appliance designed to meet the demanding needs of commercial bakeries and foodservice establishments. This powerful rotary oven offers a range of features and capabilities that make it an indispensable tool for professional bakers:","Rotary part\n\n7 inches with LCD color touch screen and control panel\nLarge capacity, memory program\nProduction information with pictures\nMulti-language menu\nMulti-stage cooking features\nDouble-sided rotating fan and even heat distribution\nAdjustable cooking temperature from 0 to 300°C.\nadjustable cooking time and digital indicator\nManual or automatic humidity function\nSensor door system\nSilicone gasket with tempered glass\nOpen interior glass for easy cleaning\nStainless steel body\n\nProofing cabinet\n\n2.4 inch color LCD control panel\nTouch screen with LED\nAutomatic operation with real time function\nAdjustable lower and higher ground heat temperature\n\nSpecifications\nRotary part capacity 10 x 40x60 cm\nOven operating temperature 0... +300 °C\nFuel type electricity\nThermal power -\nVoltage 380 V\nPower 19 kW\ndimensions 1010x1390x1220 mm\nWeight 277 kg\nCapacity dist. cabinet 10 x 40x60 cm\nVoltage 220 V\nPower 3 kW\nOverall dimensions dist. cabinet 1010x1390x750 mm\nWeight dist. cabinet 106 kg\nStand capacity 7 x 40x60 cm\nDimensions of the stand 1010x1270x830\nStand weight 56 kg\nOverall dimensions of the exhaust hood 1010x1630x210 mm\nHood weight 15 kg",,,taxable,,0,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,27800,"BAKERY LINE, BAKERY LINE > Bakery Oven, Kitchen Equipment, Special Offer",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ROTARY-OVEN-VENARRO-VENARDI-DEF-D9.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Venarro,Brand,Venarro,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,61,0,0,,"ROTARY OVEN",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,DEF-D9,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517