14023,simple,,,"Venarro DEF-MK2 Fermentation Chamber with Carriage",1,0,visible,"The Venarro DEF-MK2 Fermentation Chamber with Carriage is ideal for bakeries, pastry shops, and other food establishments.\nIt streamlines the dough handling process, making it more efficient and effective.\nIts carriage design makes it easy to use and transport.","Venarro DEF-MK2 Fermentation Chamber with Carriage, 20-60x80 Tray Capacity\n\nGeneral Specifications:\n\nOperating Temperature Range: 0/90°C\nThe Venarro DEF-MK2 Fermentation Chamber with Carriage is a single-door unit designed to enhance the efficiency and control of dough fermentation processes. It is crafted to provide ideal temperature and humidity conditions for dough proofing.\nWith its spacious interior, it can easily accommodate trays and containers sized between 20-60x80 cm.\nConstructed from stainless steel, it offers a hygienic and durable surface.\nIts carriage design allows for easy mobility and transportation to desired locations.\nImproving the Proofing Process:\nThe fermentation chamber ensures that the dough proofs under ideal temperature and humidity conditions. This promotes dough rising, achieving a soft texture, and enhancing the quality of the final product.\nBy optimizing the process time, it makes dough preparation more efficient.\nCarriage for Tray Transport:\nThe carriage design allows for easy movement and relocation, contributing to better space management and operational efficiency in your establishment.\n\nTechnical Specifications:\nProduct Code: DEF-MK2\nProduct Dimensions: 850x1280x2120 mm\nPower: 10 KW - 380 V\nCapacity: 20x(60x80)\nWeight: 250 Kg",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,11999,14150,"BAKERY LINE, COOKING LINE, Kitchen Equipment, Special Offer",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Venarro-DEF-MK2-Fermentation-Chamber-with-Carriage-20-60x80-Tray-Capacity.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Venarro-DEF-MK2-Fermentation-Chamber-with-Carriage-20-60x80-Tray-Capacity1.png",,,,,,,,,0,,Venarro,Brand,Venarro,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,76,0,0,,"Venarro DEF-MK2",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,DEF-MK2,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011000100110011001110011010110010100110011100110,,,,,,,,,salescountdowntimer,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14026,simple,,,"Venarro DYK-03 Foldable Rotating Electric Pizza Oven",1,0,visible,"Rotating Base Design: The oven is built on a rotating base, ensuring stable performance. The foldable upper section allows for space-saving storage when the oven is not in use.\nElectric Heating System: The electric heating system rapidly and precisely heats the oven's interior, enabling pizzas to cook quickly.\nSpacious Interior: With a Ø 300 mm oven interior, it has the capacity to cook 6 pizzas simultaneously, making it ideal for serving a high volume of orders efficiently.\nFoldable Upper Section: The oven's upper section has a foldable design, making it easy to lift for storage or cleaning when the oven is not in use.\nSleek Black Design: The oven's exterior is elegantly designed in a sleek black color, adding a modern aesthetic to your kitchen.\nFast Cooking: Thanks to the electric heating system and the Ø 300 mm base, pizza cooking times are significantly reduced, allowing you to provide quick and fresh service to customers.\nAdjustable Temperature Control: You can adjust the oven's temperature setting to suit your needs, providing precise control when cooking different types of pizzas or ingredients.\nHigh-Quality Materials: The oven is constructed using high-quality materials to ensure long-lasting use.\nEasy Cleaning: The oven's interior surface and base are designed for easy cleaning, simplifying maintenance tasks.","The Venarro DYK-03 Foldable Rotating Electric Pizza Oven, Ø 300 mm, 6 Pizzas\n\n7” Color Touch Control Panel\nAdjustable Temperature Setting Displayed on Screen\nAdjustable Conveyor Speed from 0 to 10\nUpper Temperature Set Value and Display\nLower Temperature Set Value and Display\nMaximum Upper and Lower Temperature Setting\nMinimum Upper and Lower Temperature Setting\nAdjustable Cooking Temperature Range and Digital Display from 0°C to 400°C\n450°C Limit Thermostat\nOperating Power: 380 V, 50/60 Hz\n225 mm Oven Interior Height\n575x225 m