14032,variable,,,"Venarro Rotating Base Gas Pizza Oven DYK-08",1,0,visible,"The Venarro Rotating Base Gas Pizza Oven DYK-08 is a high-capacity, professional-grade pizza oven designed to meet the demanding needs of commercial pizzerias and foodservice establishments. With its advanced features and efficient design, it delivers exceptional performance in pizza preparation.","Venarro Rotating Base Gas Pizza Oven 30 cmx9 Pizza Capacity DYK-08 Maestro\n\nGeneral features\n\n7” Color Touch control Panel\nTemperature adjustable from the screen\nTable speed adjustable from the screen (0-10)\nUpper temperature set value and upper temperature display\nLower temperature set value and lower temperature display\nGoing to sleep in oven standby mode\nMaximum lower and upper temperature determination\nMinimum lower and upper temperature determination\nAdjustable cooking temperature and digital display between 0° C – 400° C\n450° C limit thermostat\n220 V. 50/60 Hz. Working Force\nAbility to work with LPG and NG\n450 mm oven interior height\n500x215 mm door size\nThermal stabilization feature that provides fast and efficient cooking\nthermostatic heating\nRotary base that provides homogeneous cooking\nRefractory Baking Stone\nStone Dome Inner Chamber\nTechnicial Specifications\n\nCapacity: Ø 300 mm x 9\nDimensions: 1750x1900x2200 mm\nCooking Size: 1200 mm\nPower: 50 Kw - 230 Vac - 50 Hz\nWeight: 987 Kg",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,,"BAKERY LINE, BAKERY LINE > Bakery Oven, Kitchen Equipment, Special Offer",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Venarro-Rotating-Base-Gas-Pizza-Oven-DYK-08-g.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Venarro-Rotating-Base-Gas-Pizza-Oven-DYK-08.png",,,,,,,,,0,,Venarro,Brand,Venarro,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,73,0,0,,"Venarro Rotating Base Gas Pizza Oven",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,def