14040,variation,,,"Venarro Rotating Base Gas Pizza Oven DYK-08",1,0,visible,,,,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,31365,36900,,,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Venarro-Rotating-Base-Gas-Pizza-Oven-DYK-08-g.png,,,id:14032,,,,,,0,,Venarro,Brand,,,1,,,,,default,,1,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,salescountdowntimer,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14050,variable,,,"SLUSH Mono Allure - 12L",1,0,visible,"<strong>Slush granita and fruit juice dispenser</strong>\n<em>Countertop dispenser designed for the production and distribution of slush, granita, iced coffee, iced cappuccino and similar iced drinks.</em>\n\nMulti-color RGB light source for better display of the beverage. LED illuminated front panel for branding and better appearance. When the slush machine's chamber cover is opened, the mixer function automatically stops for safety (optional). The sugar content of the product mixture should be between 12% and 17%. It is also suitable for use as a cold fruit dispenser. Thanks to the night mode with very low energy consumption, the iced beverage in the chamber can be stored at night without any problems. For perfect cleanliness and hygiene, all parts in contact with the beverage are easily accessible and can be cleaned quickly. The polycarbonate bowl is impact resistant and suitable for food use. It is a suitable solution for small and medium-sized businesses.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• SLUSH Mono Allure- 12L</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Hopper Capacity 12L</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Defrost Mode Mechanical</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weights and Measures Machine Parcel</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight 25.5kg 28kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Width 195mm 225mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Depth 530mm* 510mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Height 770mm 805mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• dropper included</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Flow 1.6A</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Refrigerant GasR404A/R290</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Strength 350W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• cooling power 490W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Supply Voltage 220-240V 50Hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Optional Voltage 208-220V 60Hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Optional Voltage 115V 60Hz</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, Kitchen Equipment, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Slush Machine",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/SLUSH12.YA_.jpg, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/SLUSH12.BA_.jpg, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/SLUSH12-BACK.jpg",,,,,,,,,0,,Samixir,Brand,Samixir,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,2,0,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011000110011010011000110011011001100110001100111,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,"14052,14051",,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14054,simple,,,"SLUSH Twin Allure - 12L + 12L",1,0,visible,"<strong>Slush granita fruit juice dispenser</strong>\n<em>Counter top dispenser developed to produce and dispense Slush, Granita, coffee, ice cappuccino, cream, sherbets and similar frosty beverages.</em>\n\nRGB (multi color) illuminated bowls for better product exhibit. Led illuminated front panel for branding and better appearance. The mixer function stops automatically for better safety when the bowl cover is opened. The sugar ratio of the product mix must be between 12% to 17%. It can be also used as a cold fruit juice dispenser. Bowls can operate independently both cooling and mixing, multiple containers allow to always have some beverage available at any time. Night-mode operation allows storage of the product with very low energy consumption. In order to achieve perfect cleaning and hygiene; all parts which are in contact with the beverage can be easily accessed and quickly cleansed. Polycarbonate bowl is vandal-proof and food grade. It’s compact body makes the machine suitable for food-service outlets with high daily consumption needs. Water level indicator incorporated into the drip tray serves to indicate the time to empty the tray.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• <strong>SLUSH Twin Allure - 12L + 12L</strong></p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Bowl capacity 12L + 12L</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Defrost Mode Mechanical</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weights &amp; Dimensions Machine Package</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight 43,5 kg 46,5 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Width 390 mm 430 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Depth 530 mm* 520 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Height 770 mm 805 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• includes drip tray</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Current 2,31 A</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cooling Gas R404A / R290</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power 510 W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cooling Power 984 W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Supply Voltage 220-240 V 50 Hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Optional Voltage 208-220 V 60 Hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Optional Voltage 115 V 60 Hz</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,4600,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, Kitchen Equipment, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Slush Machine","SLUSH Twin Allure - 12L + 12L",,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/SLUSH24.YA_.jpg, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/SLUSH24.BA_.jpg, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/SLUSH24.IA_.jpg, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/SLUSH24-BACK.jpg",,,,,,,,,0,,Samixir,Brand,Samixir,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,47,0,0,,"SLUSH Twin Allure - 12L + 12L",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011000110011110011011001100010011100110001100011,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
