14067,variation,SLUSH36.IL,,"SLUSH Triple Allure - 12L + 12L + 12L",1,0,visible,,,,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,8053,,,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/SLUSH36.IA_.png,,,id:14061,,,,,,0,,Samixir,Brand,,,1,,,,,default,,1,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14068,variation,SLUSH36.YL,,"SLUSH Triple Allure - 12L + 12L + 12L",1,0,visible,,,,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,7796,,,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/SLUSH36.YA_.png,,,id:14061,,,,,,0,,Samixir,Brand,,,1,,,,,default,,1,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14069,simple,,,"Panoramic M10.AB - 10 Liter",1,0,visible,"<div class=""vc_row wpb_row column-padding-0px"">\n<div class=""vc_row-fluid clr"">\n<div class=""vc_col-sm-12 wpb_column clr column_container "">\n<div class=""wpb_text_column wpb_content_element "">\n<div class=""wpb_wrapper"">\n\nPanoramic mixer cold beverage dispenser\n<strong>Counter top cold beverage dispenser for cooling and dispensing natural fruit juices, ayran and all sorts of cold beverages</strong>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=""vc_row wpb_row column-padding-0px"">\n<div class=""vc_row-fluid clr"">\n<div class=""vc_col-sm-12 wpb_column clr column_container "">\n<div class=""wpb_text_column wpb_content_element "">\n<div class=""wpb_wrapper"">\n\nCounter top cold beverage dispenser; specially equiped with slow agitation system, for cooling and dispensing natural juices with particles, as well as ayran, shalgam, cold coffee, cold tea, milk and all similar cold drinks. Beverages cool faster and equally until the last drop thanks to the large cooling base, it saves energy up to 50% compared classical dispensers. Practical tap system allows easy dispensing of the beverage with single hand. Large diameter tap hose alows constant fluidity and can easily be disassembled and cleansed.\nIt eliminates the risk of leakage to the engine compartment thanks to the magnetic twisted pallet system, hence motor is fully protected. It provides a homogeneous mix thanks to the magnetic and twisted pallet system, this allows the beverage to cool faster. In order to achieve perfect cleaning and hygiene; all parts which are in contact with the beverage can be  easily accessed and quickly cleansed. Polycarbonat bowl is vandal-proof and food grade. It is the right choice for small and mid size food-service outlets. Water level indicator incorporated into the drip tray serves to indicate the time to empty the tray.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Panoramic M10 - 10 Liter</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Bowl capacity 10 Liter</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cooling Gas R134A / R290</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weights &amp; Dimensions Machine Package</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight 16,4 kg 18,4 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Length 250 mm 300 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Depth 390 mm* 335 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Height 700 mm 720 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• includes drip tray</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Optional Voltage 115 V 60 Hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Current 1,1 A</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Temperature Range +3 °C — +10 °C</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Energy Consumption 1,8 kWh/24h</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power 160 W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cooling Power 350 W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Supply Voltage 220-240 V 50 Hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Optional Voltage 208-220 V 60 Hz</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,1996,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Juice Maker, Kitchen Equipment","Panoramic M10",,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/M10.AB_.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/M10.AB-model.png",,,,,,,,,0,,Samixir,Brand,Samixir,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,77,0,0,,"Panoramic M10",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,M10.AB,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596440,011000110010110001110110010100110100110001100111,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14072,simple,,,"Panoramic M22.AB - 22 Liters",1,0,visible,"<strong>The 22 liter capacity of the impact-resistant, food-grade polycarbonate chamber and the compact body of the machine are suitable for small and medium-sized businesses</strong>.\n<strong>22 L panoramic cold drink dispenser with</strong>\n<strong>stirrer Countertop dispenser designed for cooling and dispensing natural fruit juices, ayran and all kinds of cold drinks</strong>\n\nThanks to the slow-working magnetic paddle mixing system; Countertop dispenser designed especially for the cooling and distribution of natural fruit juices with particles, ayran, turnip, cold coffee, ice tea, milk and all kinds of cold drinks. Thanks to the wide cooling base, drinks cool faster and evenly down to the last drop. In this way, it provides energy savings of up to 50% compared to classical products. Practical tap system; It allows you to easily take drinks using one hand. The wide tap hose provides fast filling even for drinks with particles and can be easily disassembled and cleaned. Thanks to the magnetic pallet system, the risk of the beverage in the chamber leaking into the lower engine section is eliminated, thus extending the life of the engine. The screw pallet system provides a homogeneous mixture and faster cooling of the beverage. For perfect cleanliness and hygiene, all parts in contact with the beverage are easily accessible and can be cleaned quickly. The polycarbonate bowl is impact resistant and suitable for food use. It is a suitable solution for small and medium-sized businesses. Thanks to the level indicator on the dropper, it is easy to notice that the waste water needs to be drained before it overflows.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Panoramic M 22 - 22 Liters</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Hopper Capacity 22 Liters</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Refrigerant Gas R134A/R290</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weights and Measures Machine Parcel</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight 20 kg 21.6kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Width 350mm 400mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Depth 405mm* 430mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Height 755mm 795mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• dropper included</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Optional Voltage 115V 60Hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Flow 1.4A</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Temperature Range +3 °C — +10 °C</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Energy consumption 2.8kWh/24h</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Strength 250W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cooling Power 500W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Supply Voltage 220-240V 50Hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Optional Voltage 208-220V 60Hz</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,2506,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Juice Maker, Kitchen Equipment",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Panoramic-M-22.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Panoramic-M-22-models.png",,,,,,,,,0,,Samixir,Brand,Samixir,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,28,0,0,,"Panoramic M 22",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,M22.AB,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596440,011000100111111001100110100100110100100011100110,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14075,simple,,,"Panoramic foamed buttermilk dispenser - KAM22.DW",1,0,visible,"<div class=""vc_row wpb_row column-padding-0px"">\n<div class=""vc_row-fluid clr"">\n<div class=""vc_col-sm-10 wpb_column clr column_container "">\n<div class=""wpb_text_column wpb_content_element "">\n<div class=""wpb_wrapper"">\n\n<strong>22 L panoramic foamed buttermilk dispenser</strong>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=""vc_col-sm-2 wpb_column clr column_container "">\n<div class=""wpb_single_image wpb_content_element clr vc_align_"">\n<div class=""wpb_wrapper"">\n<div class=""vc_single_image-wrapper ""></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=""vc_row wpb_row column-padding-0px"">\n<div class=""vc_row-fluid clr"">\n<div class=""vc_col-sm-12 wpb_column clr column_container "">\n<div class=""wpb_text_column wpb_content_element "">\n<div class=""wpb_wrapper"">\n\nCountertop dispenser developed for cooling and distributing buttermilk, working with a special tap system that produces foamy buttermilk. The only, compact, foamy buttermilk dispenser in its class. Thanks to the special tap system, the ayran is foamed while pouring it into the glass, so the consistency and taste of the ayran does not deteriorate, and it provides fast filling. Thanks to its wide cooling base, drinks cool faster and evenly down to the last drop, thus providing energy savings of up to 50% compared to conventional products. Thanks to the slow-working magnetic paddle mixing system, the consistency and taste of the buttermilk does not change and prevents the formation of foam in the chamber. The screw pallet system provides a homogeneous mixture and faster cooling of the beverage. Thanks to the magnetic pallet system, the risk of the beverage in the chamber leaking into the lower engine section is eliminated, thus extending the life of the engine. For perfect cleanliness and hygiene, all parts in contact with the beverage are easily accessible and can be cleaned quickly. The polycarbonate bowl is impact resistant and suitable for food use. Thanks to the level indicator on the dropper, it is easily noticed that the waste water needs to be drained before it overflows.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Panoramic foamed buttermilk dispenser - KAM22.DW</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Hopper Capacity22 Liters   Flow1.3A</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">•  Refrigerant GasR134A/R290 Weights</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• MeasuresMachineParcel</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Temperature Range+3 °C — +10 °C</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight21.8kg22.9kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Energy consumption2.8kWh/24h</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Width350mm400mm  Strength255W Depth405mm*425mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cooling Power500W Height825mm865mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Supply Voltage 220-240V 50Hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Optional Voltage 208-220V 60Hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Optional Voltage 115V 60Hz</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,3329,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, Kitchen Equipment",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/KAM22.DW_.jpg, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/KAM22.DW1_.jpg",,,,,,,,,0,,Samixir,Brand,Samixir,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,72,0,0,,"Panoramic foamed buttermilk dispenser",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,KAM22.DW,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011001110011110011000100110001100111001001100110,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14078,variable,,,"Classical Mono Classical cold beverage dispenser - 20.SY",1,0,visible,"<strong>20 L classical cold beverage dispenser</strong>\n\n<em>Counter top cold beverage dispenser for cooling and dispensing fruit juices, ayran and all sorts of cold beverages.</em>\n\n<em>Counter top cold beverage dispenser for cooling and dispensing fruit juices, ayran and all sorts of cold beverages.</em>\n\nSpray counter top cold beverage dispenser; equiped with magnetic spray system, for cooling and dispensing specially fruit juices without particules and shalgam. Mixer counter top cold beverage dispenser; specially equiped with slow agitation system, for cooling and dispensing fruit juices with particles, as well as ayran, shalgam, cold coffee, cold tea, milk and all imilar cold drinks. The magnetic spray system in the Spray version and the twisted magnetic pallet system in the Mixer version; eliminate the risk of leakage to the engine compartment, hence the engine is fully insulated. Beverages cool faster and equally until the last drop thanks to the large cooling base, it saves energy up to 50% compared classical dispensers. Spray versions are not suitable for the use of particulate beverages. It offers appetizing look thanks to the spray system. It provides a homogeneous mix thanks to the magnetic and twisted pallet system, this allows the beverage to cool faster. Practical tap system allows easy dispensing of the beverage with single hand. Large diameter tap hose allows fast filling and can easily be disassembled and cleansed. In order to achieve perfect cleaning and hygiene; all parts which are in contact with the beverage can be easily accessed and quickly cleansed. Polycarbonat bowl is vandal-proof and food grade. The compact body makes the machine suitable for food-service outlets with high daily consumption needs.Water level indicator incorporated into the drip tray serves to indicate the time to empty the tray. The desired temperature level is set manually inside the body, concealed thermostat keeps this level constant.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Bowl Capacity 20 Liter</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Current 1,4 A</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cooling Gas R134A / R290</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weights &amp; Dimensions Machine Package</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight 20,5 kg 21,9 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Width 185 mm 225 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Depth 525 mm* 550 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Height 665 mm 690 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• includes drip tray</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Optional Voltage 115 V 60 Hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Temperature Range +5 °C — +10 °C</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Energy Consumption 5,6 kWh/24h</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power 275 W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cooling Power 500 W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Supply Voltage 220-240 V 50 Hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">•Optional Voltage 208-220 V 60 Hz</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Juice Maker, Kitchen Equipment",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20.SY_.jpg, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20.Sb_.jpg.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20.SI_.jpg.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20l-modelpng.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20l-modelp1ng.png",,,,,,,,,0,,Samixir,Color,"Black, Silver, Yellow",1,1,Brand,Samixir,1,1,default,1,1,0,,63,0,0,,"Classical Mono Classical cold beverage dispenser",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,defaul