14092,variable,,,"Classical Triple Classical spray mixer cold beverage - 60.SSY",1,0,visible,"<strong>20 L+20 L+20 L classical spray mixer cold beverage dispenser</strong>\n<em>Counter top cold beverage dispenser for cooling and dispensing fruit juices, ayran and all sorts of cold beverages</em>\n\nSpray counter top cold beverage dispenser; equiped with magnetic spray system, for cooling and dispensing specially fruit juices without particules and shalgam. Mixer counter top cold beverage dispenser; specially equiped with slow agitation system, for cooling and dispensing fruit juices with particles, as well as ayran, shalgam, cold coffee, cold tea, milk and all similar cold drinks. The magnetic spray system in the Spray version and the twisted magnetic pallet system in the Mixer version; eliminate the risk of leakage to the engine compartment, hence the engine is fully insulated. Beverages cool faster and equally until the last drop thanks to the large cooling base, it saves energy up to 50% compared classical dispensers. Spray versions are not suitable for the use of particulate beverages. It offers appetizing look thanks to the spray system. It provides a homogeneous mix thanks to the magnetic, twisted pallet system, this allows the beverage to cool faster. Multiple containers allow to always have some beverage available at any time. Practical tap system allows easy dispensing of the beverage with single hand. Large diameter tap hose allows fast filling and can easily be disassembled and cleansed. In order to achieve perfect cleaning and hygiene; all parts which are in contact with the beverage can be easily accessed and quickly cleansed. Polycarbonat bowl is vandal-proof and food grade. The compact body makes the machine suitable for food-service outlets with high daily consumption needs. Water level indicator incorporated into the drip tray serves to indicate the time to empty the tray. The desired temperature level is set manually inside the body, concealed thermostat keeps this level constant.","<p style="" margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Classical Triple Classical spray mixer cold beverage - 20 L+20 L+20 L</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Hopper Capacity 20L+20L+20L</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Refrigerant Gas R134A/R290</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weights and Measures Machine Parcel</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight	42.3kg 44.5kg</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Width	545mm 575mm</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Depth	525mm* 550mm</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Height	665mm 690mm</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• dropper included</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Optional Voltage 115V 60Hz</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Flow 1.75A</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Temperature Range +5 °C — +10 °C</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Energy consumption 8kWh/24h</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Strength 340W</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cooling Power 1020W</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Supply Voltage 220-240V 50Hz</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Optional Voltage 208-220V 60Hz</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Juice Maker, Kitchen Equipment",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/60-SSY.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/60-SSB.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/60-SSI.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/60-SSY-M.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/60-SSY-M1.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/60-SSY-M2.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/60-SSY-M3.png",,,,,,,,,0,,Samixir,Color,"Black, Silver, Yellow",1,1,Brand,Samixir,1,1,default,1,1,0,,78,0,0,,"Classical Triple Classical spray mixer cold beverage",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596440,011111100101111000001110000111001000011111100000,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,"14094,14095,14093",,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,Black,Samixir
14100,simple,,,"Panoramic Hot Drink Dispenser - SC.05",1,0,visible,"<strong>[<strong>Restock in 20 Days</strong>]</strong>\n\n<strong>5 L panoramic hot drink dispenser</strong>\n\nSC05 Salep is a 5 liter capacity countertop hot beverage dispenser that keeps hot chocolate, tea, coffee, milk and similar hot beverages warm with the ""BAIN-MARIE"" method, mixes and distributes them homogeneously and without lumps. Thanks to the specially designed “BAIN-MARIE” heating system, hot drinks do not condense and do not stick to the bottom of the chamber. All metal parts of our hot drink machine are made of high quality stainless steel. Thanks to the continuous rotation of the mixing palette, the fluid consistency is maintained and no lumps are formed. The water level of the “BAIN-MARIE” system can be observed from outside the hull. Thanks to the closed-circuit ""BAIN-MARIE"" water heating system, there is no loss of water vapor, the water level is maintained for a long time, thus preventing calcification of the resistance. If our Hot Beverage Machine operates without water, the warning light on the outside of the body will turn on, indicating that water needs to be added to the machine. If the solidified beverage becomes difficult to flow from the tap, the problem is solved with the opening pin built into the tap. For perfect cleanliness and hygiene, all parts in contact with the beverage can be easily accessed and cleaned quickly. SC05Thanks to the “BAIN-MARIE” boiler being independent from the outer body, it prevents the user from burning his hand and there is no heat loss. Thanks to the level indicator on the dropper, it is easily noticed that the waste water needs to be drained before it overflows.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Panoramic Hot Drink Dispenser - SC05</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Hopper Capacity 5 Liters</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Thermostat Range 30 – 90°C</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weights and Measures Machine Parcel</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight 6.3kg 7kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Width 275mm 285mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Depth 360mm* 285mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Height 450mm 470mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Flow 3.3A</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Energy consumption10kWh/24h</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Heating Power 700W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Supply Voltage 220-240V 50Hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Optional Voltage 208-220V 60Hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Optional Voltage 115V 60Hz</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,1639,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Food Warmers, Kitchen Equipment","Panoramic Hot Drink Dispenser",,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/SC05.B.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/SC05.I.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/SC05-MODELS.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/SC05-MODEL.png",,,,,,,,,0,,Samixir,Brand,Samixir,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,56,0,0,,"Panoramic Hot Drink Dispenser",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011010110100111000010011011011010011000111100001,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,"14101,14102",,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14107,simple,,,"Panoramic Hot Drink Dispenser - SC.10.I",1,0,visible,"<strong>[<strong>Restock in 20 Days</strong>]</strong>\n\n<strong>10 L panoramic hot drink dispenser</strong>\n\nCountertop hot beverage dispenser with a capacity of 10 liters, which keeps hot drinks such as salep, hot chocolate, tea, coffee, milk and similar hot beverages warm with the ""BAIN-MARIE"" method, mixes and distributes them homogeneously and without lumps. Thanks to the specially designed “BAIN-MARIE” heating system, hot drinks do not condense and do not stick to the bottom of the chamber. All metal parts are made of high quality stainless steel. Thanks to the continuous rotation of the mixing palette, the fluid consistency is maintained and no lumps are formed. The water level of the “BAIN-MARIE” system can be observed from outside the hull. Thanks to the closed-circuit ""BAIN-MARIE"" water heating system, there is no loss of water vapor, the water level is maintained for a long time, thus preventing calcification of the resistance. If it operates without water, the warning light on the outside of the body will turn on, indicating that water needs to be added to the machine. If the solidified beverage becomes difficult to flow from the tap, the problem is solved with the opening pin built into the tap. For perfect cleanliness and hygiene, all parts in contact with the beverage can be easily accessed and cleaned quickly. Thanks to the “BAIN-MARIE” boiler being independent from the outer body, it prevents the user from burning his hand and there is no heat loss. Thanks to the level indicator on the dropper, it is easily noticed that the waste water needs to be drained before it overflows.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Panoramic Hot Drink Dispenser - SC.10.I</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Hopper Capacity 10 Liters</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Thermostat Range 30 – 90°C</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weights and Measures Machine Parcel</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight 6.9kg 7.7kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Width 275mm 290mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Depth 360mm* 290mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Height 535mm 565mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Energy consumption 10kWh/24h</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Heating Power 1200W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Supply Voltage 220-240V 50Hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Optional Voltage 208-220V 60Hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Optional Voltage 115V 60Hz</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,2287,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Food Warmers, Kitchen Equipment","Panoramic Hot Drink Dispenser",,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/SC10.I.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/SC10.B.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/SC05-MODEL.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/SC10.models.png",,,,,,,,,0,,Samixir,Brand,Samixir,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,56,0,0,,"Panoramic Hot Drink Dispenser",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,010011110100111001000010110110011010010011100110,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,"14109,14108",,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
