14146,simple,,,"Blender Drink MachineTwo-Speed - 10011",1,0,visible,"<strong>Reliable, simple and efficient blending.</strong>\nIdeal for blending fresh fruit, liquid smoothie and coffee mixes and ice\nor ice cream.\nPrecision engineering and robust construction allows these blenders\nto homogenise the ingredients. The result is creamier, smoother frozen\ndrinks with ice crystals so fine and so thoroughly blended, that they do\nnot separate or lose their flavour.\nWith a two-speed switch, the operation can be tailored to suit the\nvarious methods used to mix different types of drinks.","<p style="" margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Blender Drink MachineTwo-Speed - 10011</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Reliable robust performer.</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Wet blade, for versatile blending</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Suitable for coffee shops and cafés</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Tamper stick to push dense ingredients down through the blade.</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 1.4 Ltr high-impact stackable container with wet blade.</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• ~2.3 HP (peak output)* motor. </p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Simple 2 - speed operation.</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Motor: ~2.3 HP (peak output)* motor</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Electrical: Standard single phase 10 Amp plug, 230 V, 50/60 Hz, 1000 - 1200 Watts (load dependent)</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Includes: 1.4 litre high-impact, clear/stackable container, complete with Wet blade assembly, lid and base\n</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,3250,"COFFEE & BAR LINE > Blenders, COFFEE & BAR LINE, Kitchen Equipment","Blender Drink MachineTwo-Speed",,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/10011.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Vitamix,Brand,vitamix,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,10,0,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,10011,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,15766,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110011100111110011000110010100101110011001000100,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14148,simple,,,"Blender Drink Machine Advance - 10198",1,0,visible,"<strong>The Ultimate Blender for Every Beverage Program</strong>\nFrom fruit smoothies to thick shakes, the Drink Machine\nAdvance is an essential tool for adding or expanding a\nblended beverage program.","<p style="" margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Blender Drink Machine Advance - 10198</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 6 optimized programs and automatic shut‐off means you can turn it on, walk away, and achieve consistent results</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Pulse control quickly refreshes drinks for efficiency</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Advance® container creates faster, smoother pouringand has a longer blade life resulting in time and cost savings along with improved customer experience</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Advanced motor is designed to resist overheating when blending extra‐thick ingredients resulting in cooler operation and enhanced reliability during peak hours of operation</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Advance Blade</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 0.9 litre high impact clear container</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 6 setting dial switch</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 6 x optimise programs</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Pulse switch</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power Supply: 240V, 50Hz, 10A</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power Output: 750W‐850W</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Motor:  ≈ 2.0HP</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dimensions:   203W x 229D x 449H mm</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight:   5.5kg</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,3900,"COFFEE & BAR LINE > Blenders, COFFEE & BAR LINE, Kitchen Equipment","Blender Drink Machine Advance",,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/10198.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Vitamix,Brand,vitamix,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,5,0,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,10198,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,15767,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595388,110010110001110010110110110100100110011001001100,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14150,simple,,,"Blender Vita-Prep 3 - 10089",1,0,visible,"<strong>Unmatched Performance in Commercial Kitchens</strong>\nBlender Vita-Prep 3 - 10089\nProfessional chefs and culinary schools around the world trust the\nVita-Prep® 3 for exceptional power, versatility and performance.\nFrom chopping delicate ingredients to blending tough purees, the\nVita-Prep® 3 is the only tool that’s durable and capable of perfectly\nchopping, grinding, and blending it all.","<p style="" margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">•  Blender Vita-Prep 3 - 10089</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Powerful ~3 HP (peak output)* motor delivers unmatched performance when pureeing, grinding, chopping and more </p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Advanced cooling fan for optimum reliability during peak hours of operation </p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 2.0 litre high-impact clear container with Wet blade assembly and lid</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Patented Tamper stick allows for control and easy processing of dense ingredients</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Motor: ~3 HP (peak output)* motor</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Electrical: Standard single phase 10 Amp plug, 230 V, 50/60 Hz, 1200 - 1400 Watts (load dependent)</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Includes: 2.0 litre high impact, BPA-free, clear container, complete with Wet blade assembly, lid, Tamper stick and base</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,4420,"COFFEE & BAR LINE > Blenders, COFFEE & BAR LINE, Kitchen Equipment","Blender Vita-Prep 3 - 10089",,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/10089.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Vitamix,Brand,vitamix,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,10,0,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,10089,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,15768,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110011100110101100100110011100110100011001001100,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14152,simple,,,"Blender Touch & Go Advance Bar - 67000",1,0,visible,"<strong>Blender Touch & Go Advance Bar - 67000</strong>\nTouch & Go Advance offers a powerful engine, convenient preset controls and noise reduction for Bars & Kitchens.\nPowerful Motor : 2.3 HP motor mixes frozen drinks easily.\nNoise Reduction : Our twist and lock audio booth features a tool-free design for easy disassembly and cleaning, helping to provide a quiet environment for your clients.\nOptimized Programs : 6 preset buttons and 20 recipe programs provide consistent results for most frequently made drinks.","<p style="" margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Blender Touch & Go Advance Bar - 67000</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Extra cover (provides sound insulation)</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Polycarbonate 1 liter capacity chamber</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dimensions: 457x216x272 mm</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Engine: 2.3 hp</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Electricity: 220-240 V, 50/60 Hz</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power: 1100-1300W</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight: 5.67 kg</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Product features</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Chamber Capacity (Lt): 1</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power (Watt): 1300</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Chamber Material: Polycarbonate</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,5750,6240,"COFFEE & BAR LINE > Blenders, COFFEE & BAR LINE, Kitchen Equipment, Special Offer","Blender Touch & Go Advance Bar - 67000",,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/67000.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Vitamix,Brand,vitamix,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,73,0,0,,"Blender Touch & Go Advance Bar - 67000",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,67000,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,111001110011010011000011000110011000110010110011,,,,,,,,,salescountdowntimer,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14154,simple,,,"Blender On Counter Sound proof - 50031",1,0,visible,"<strong>About the Product and Brand</strong>\nBlender On Counter Sound proof - 50031\n<strong>The Quietest Commercial Blender Available</strong>\n\n<em>The Quiet One® a ground breaking commercial blender with unparalleled sound reduction, exceptional beverage blends, and improved speed of service.</em>\n\n<strong>Smart Product Design</strong>\n\nUp to 4 times quieter due to the advance vibration dampening technology; quality drinks in a more enjoyable atmosphere\nMagnetically secured floating sound enclosure is dramatically easier to clean &amp; disassemble with no screws to damage the enclosure\n6 program buttons with 34 optimised programs for easier, consistent blending\nAdvance® container creates faster, smoother pouring and has a longer blade life\nAir management and powerful ≈3 peak output HP motor reduces noise, improves reliability, and reduces down time","<p style="" margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Blender On Counter Sound proof - 50031</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 1.4 Litre Advance Container</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Unparalleled sound reduction</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Up to 4 times quieter</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Innovative vibration dampening technology</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Exceptional beverage blends</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Improved speed of service</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Magnetically secured floating sound enclosure</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Touch pad</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Variable speed control</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Pulse switch</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 6 program buttons</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 34 optimised programs in memory</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Advance container includes Advance blade assembly & lid</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 3+ Peak HP Motor</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power: 1500 Watts; 10 Amp</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dimensions: 216 x 295 x 457 H</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,7280,"COFFEE & BAR LINE > Blenders, COFFEE & BAR LINE, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/50031.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Vitamix,Brand,vitamix,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,10,0,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,50031,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110011100110011001100110010100110001100100011011,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14156,simple,,,"Blender Variable Speed - 10185 XL",1,0,visible,"<strong>Blender Variable Speed - 10185 XL</strong>\n\n<em><strong>HIGH PRODUCTION FOOD BLENDER</strong></em>\nMaximize your kitchen’s possibilities with the largest capacity,\ncountertop blender. Blend up to 24 (200ml) servings at once! The\nXL is engineered to reduce prep-time, improve staff efficiency, and\nexpand your menu capabilities","<p style="" margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Blender Variable Speed - 10185 XL</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Powerful 4.2 peak output HP motor allows heavy blending from delicate tomatoes to dense meat</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Large 5.6 litre container provides extra blending capacity for both hot and cold ingredients</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Pulse function and variable speed control allow for flexibility and </p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• XL Blade</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 5.6 litre and 2.0 litre high impact clear container </p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Basic Start/stop function</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 1-10 speed settings</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Pulse switch</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Tamper stick</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• DIMENSIONS 216W x 483D x 459H mm</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power Supply: 240V, 50Hz, 10A</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power Output: 1700W-1900W</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Motor: ≈ 4.2HP</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight: 22.7kg</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,11830,"COFFEE & BAR LINE > Blenders, COFFEE & BAR LINE, Kitchen Equipment","Blender Variable Speed - 10185 XL",,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Blender-Variable-Speed-10185-XL.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Vitamix,Brand,vitamix,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,5,0,0,,,,,,,,,,field_