14158,simple,,,"Blender Container High-Impact  - 15506",1,0,visible,"<strong>Blender Container High-Impact - 15506</strong>\nThe Vita-Mix blender is a staple of the kitchen. Because it is used so often, multiple blender containers are necessary to keep up with customer demands that come through. This Vita-Mix 15506 High-Impact Blender 48 ounce Container is made of clear, polycarbonate, that is high-impact to withstand the tough and frozen ingredients that it will encounter. This container fits Touch &amp; Go 2 and Drink Machine blenders. Includes stainless steel ice blade assembly and lid.\n\n<em>This product measures 13.4 inches high, 7.6 inches wide, and 9.1 inches deep.</em>\n<strong>Features</strong>\nHigh impact, BPA free, polycarbonate, 48 ounce container\nIncludes stainless steel ice blade assembly and lid\nFor use with Touch &amp; Go 2 and Drink Machine blenders","Blender Container High-Impact - 15506\nCapacity 48 oz.\nDepth 9.1 in.\nHeight 13.4 in.\nWeight 2 lbs.\nWidth 7.6 in.\nType : Blender Parts &amp; Accessories",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,728,"ACCESSORIES, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Blenders, COFFEE & BAR LINE, Kitchen Equipment","Blender Container High-Impact",,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Blender-Container-High-Impact-15506.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Vitamix,Brand,vitamix,1,1,"Type of Product","Blender Mixer",1,1,default,1,1,0,,12,0,0,,"مطبخ,kitchen equipment",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,15506,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595388,010111100100011010000110111001111110010000110100,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14160,simple,,,"Blender Container w/Wet Blade Assembly and Lid - 05626 (1195)",1,0,visible,"<strong>Blender Container w/Wet Blade Assembly and Lid - 05626 (1195)</strong>\n64 oz. / 2.0L BPA Free Tritan™ Container with wet blade assembly and lid - 1 per standard pack, 3.2 lbs. / 1.45 kg., 0.6 cubic feet / .02 cu.m","<p style="" margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Blender Container w/Wet Blade Assembly and Lid - 05626 (1195)</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 1 per standard pack, 3.2 lbs.</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 1.45 kg., 0.6 cubic feet</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• .02 cu.m</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 64 oz. / 2.0L </p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,728,"ACCESSORIES, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Blenders, COFFEE & BAR LINE, Kitchen Equipment","Blender Container w/Wet Blade Assembly and Lid - 05626 (1195)",,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Blender-Container-High-Impact-05626-1195.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Vitamix,Brand,vitamix,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,10,0,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"05626 (1195)",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595388,110011011001000110111000110110010011001011100100,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14162,simple,,,"Blender Advance Container w/Lid & Blade - 058669 (15978)",1,0,visible,"<strong>Blender Advance Container w/Lid &amp; Blade - 058669 (15978) Description</strong>\n\nThe Vitamix 15978 Advance container has a 48-ounce capacity and can be ordered as a replacement container or an additional container for The Quiet One, T&amp;G2, and Advance series blenders. The unique shape of this container is designed for thorough blending and quick pouring and includes a no-drip spout for efficient and mess-free product delivery. It's constructed of Tritan, a durable, crystal-clear, BPA-free, and dishwasher-safe plastic. This container comes standard with double-sealed bearings and a stainless steel blade assembly to increase the life of your blade, as well as a lid that facilitates the adding of ingredients while the blender is in use.","<p style="" margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Blender Advance Container w/Lid & Blade - 058669 (15978)</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 48-oz. Advance container is compatible with The Quiet One, T&G2, and Advance series blenders</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Unique design enhances blending and pourability</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Built-in, no-drip spout</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cotainer made of high-impact and BPA-free Tritan plastic</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Includes stainless steel blade assembly with double-sealed bearings increases the life of the blade</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Lid allows for additional ingredients to be added during blending</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Overall dimensions: 71/10 in. W x 81/5 in. D x 101/2 in. H</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,806,"ACCESSORIES, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Blenders, COFFEE & BAR LINE, Kitchen Equipment","Blender Advance Container, Blender Advance Container w/Lid & Blade - 058669 (15978)",,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Blender-Container-High-Impact-058669-15978.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Blender-Container-High-Impact-058669-15978-1.png",,,,,,,,,0,,Vitamix,Brand,vitamix,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,5,0,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"058669 (15978)",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595388,011000001111011000011100001110011100110110100110,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14165,simple,,,"Blender Jar complete for Vitamix Blenders - 058667 (15981)",1,0,visible,"<strong>Vitamix 015981 Details</strong>\nReplace a broken blender jar or keep an extra on hand with this Vitamix 15981 Advance 32 oz. clear TRITAN® copolyester deluxe blender jar. This large blender jar is compatible with a variety of Vitamix blenders. It's made of BPA-free Eastman TRITAN® copolyester that will accommodate both hot and cold ingredients. The special triangular shape of the jar is designed for thorough blending. The laser-cut stainless steel wet blade assembly creates an extra fast, smooth blend with a minimum of noise.\n\nThe container is marked with oz. and mL measurements for perfect measuring accuracy. The lid has an easily removable lid plug so you can add and tamp down ingredients as you go. The lid locks into place for safety. This jar's pronounced spout makes pouring easy and prevents spills. Its large handle allows a strong grip. Use this durable blender jar to make delicious purees and vibrant smoothies for years to come! This blender jar is compatible with Vitamix 36019, 36021, 34013, 62824, and 62825.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Blender Jar with Lid and Wet Blade Assembly for Vitamix Blenders - 058667 (15981)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Shipping Weight 2.6 lb.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Width 7 9/16 Inches</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Depth 9 1/16 Inches</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Height 13 3/8 Inches</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Color Clear</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Features Made in America NSF Listed</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,806,"ACCESSORIES, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Blenders, COFFEE & BAR LINE, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Blender-Jar-with-Lid-and-Wet-Blade-Assembly-for-Vitamix-Blenders-058667-15981.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Vitamix,Brand,vitamix,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,3,0,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"058667 (15981)",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011010001111001100011100001110010111000011000111,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14167,simple,,,"Blender Jar complete for XL Vitamix Blenders - 15899",1,0,visible,"<strong>Blender Jar with Lid and Wet Blade Assembly for XL Vitamix Blenders - 15899 Details</strong>\nReplace a broken blender jar or keep an extra on hand with this Vitamix 15899 1.5 gallon clear TRITAN® copolyester blender jar. This large blender jar is compatible with XL Vitamix blenders. It's made of BPA-free Eastman TRITAN® copolyester that will accommodate both hot and cold ingredients. The laser-cut stainless steel wet blade assembly creates an extra fast, smooth blend with a minimum of noise.\n\nThe container is marked with oz., cup, and gallon measurements for perfect measuring accuracy. The lid has an easily removable lid plug so you can add and tamp down ingredients as you go. The lid locks into place for safety. This jar's pronounced spout makes pouring easy and prevents spills. Its large handle allows a strong grip. Use this durable blender jar to make delicious purees and vibrant smoothies for years to come! This blender jar is compatible with Vitamix 5201, 5202, and 5205.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Blender Jar with Lid and Wet Blade Assembly for XL Vitamix Blenders - 15899</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Shipping Weight 7.32 lb.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Width 12 1/16 Inches</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Depth 12 1/16 Inches</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Height 13 1/2 Inches</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Color Clear</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Features Made in America NSF Listed</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Jar Size 1 1/2 Gallons 192 Ounces</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,2210,"ACCESSORIES, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Blenders, COFFEE & BAR LINE, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Blender-Jar-with-Lid-and-Wet-Blade-Assembly-for-XL-Vitamix-Blenders-15899.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Vitamix,Brand,vitamix,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,3,0,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,15899,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110010011010000110011001110100011111000011100101,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14169,simple,,,"Commercial Water boilers 10Liter - SHU111",1,0,visible,"<strong>Commercial Water boilers for Restaurant</strong>, Hotel, Catering,Offices, etc\nstainless steel is the most common steel. The steel contains both chromium and nickel metals as the main non-iron constituents. It is an austenitic stainless steel. It is less electrically and thermally conductive than carbon steel and is essentially non-magnetic.\n\nHigh quality &amp; low maintenance – 304 grade ""18/10"" mirror polished stainless steel body with vented lid.\nConcealed element – quick heating, superior corrosion resistance for effortless cleaning, the element is replaceable on the 10, 20 ,30,40litre models.\nTemperature control – thermostat has variable settings, for greater temperature control. Safety – over temperature protection device turns off the power if the urn boils dry.\nStandard inclusions– Dual indicator lights, on/off switch, heat-resistant knobs, easy-lift safety handles with a notch for Enhanced Safty chrome plated brass non-drip tap,","<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• SAE304 Standard ""18/8"" mirror Polished stainless Steel</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Safety protection to comply with IEC (international electrotechnical commission)norms</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Temperature control by capillary thermostat</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Double Auto boil dry protection for enhanced safety</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Non drip faucet with superior nickel finish 13A fused moulded British Standard Plug</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dual indicator lamp for heat monitoring</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 50/60Hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 220V</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,455,"ACCESSORIES, Kitchen Equipment, SNACK MAKER, SNACK MAKER > Water Boiler",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Commercial-Water-boilers.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Sheffield,Brand,Sheffield,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,7,0,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,SHU111,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110100000000110010111011010100101111001101001101,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14171,simple,,,"Commercial Water boilers 20Liter - SHU222",1,0,visible,"<strong>Commercial Water boilers for Restaurant</strong>, Hotel, Catering,Offices, etc\nstainless steel is the most common steel. The steel contains both chromium and nickel metals as the main non-iron constituents. It is an austenitic stainless steel. It is less electrically and thermally conductive than carbon steel and is essentially non-magnetic.\n\nHigh quality &amp; low maintenance – 304 grade ""18/10"" mirror polished stainless steel body with vented lid.\nConcealed element – quick heating, superior corrosion resistance for effortless cleaning, the element is replaceable on the 10, 20 ,30,40litre models.\nTemperature control – thermostat has variable settings, for greater temperature control. Safety – over temperature protection device turns off the power if the urn boils dry.\nStandard inclusions– Dual indicator lights, on/off switch, heat-resistant knobs, easy-lift safety handles with a notch for Enhanced Safty chrome plated brass non-drip tap,","<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• SAE304 Standard ""18/8"" mirror Polished stainless Steel</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Safety protection to comply with IEC (international electrotechnical commission)norms</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Temperature control by capillary thermostat</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Double Auto boil dry protection for enhanced safety</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Non drip faucet with superior nickel finish 13A fused moulded British Standard Plug</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dual indicator lamp for heat monitoring</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 50/60Hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 220V</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,539,"ACCESSORIES, Kitchen Equipment, SNACK MAKER, SNACK MAKER > Water Boiler",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Commercial-Water-boilers.png,,,,,,,