14174,simple,,,"FRYRITE 40 LITRE MACHINE",1,0,visible,"Fryrite is an oil filter machine that filters &amp; purifies down to 4 microns – dramatic extension of the life &amp; quality of your oil\n\nThe Fryrite Filter Machine purifies down to12 microns – this means a dramatic extension of the life and quality of frying oil. This will save you the cost of the machine within approximately 6 months!\n\nThis cooking oil filter machine is lightweight, compact, safe to use and requires no manual handling of hot oil.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• FRYRITE 40 LITRE MACHINE</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• BATTMOBILE</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Battery operated Fry oil filter machine. No More Leads.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Features:</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 75 minutes of Battery life.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Portable in design</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• BATTMOBILE runs on DC</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• BATTMOBILE offers twice onboard filtration</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Quick to recharge</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• External battery charging system</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Easy to clean &amp; use</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Specifications:</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Primary Materials: Stainless Steel type 304</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Length – 80 cm (fully assembled)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Width – 35 cm (fully assembled)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Depth – 44 cm (fully assembled)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Capacity Tank: 40 litres</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,9800,"ACCESSORIES, COOKING LINE, Kitchen Equipment",FRYRITE,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/FRYRITE-40-LITRE-MACHINE.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/BATTMOBILE.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/machine2.png",,,,,,,,,0,,Falater,Brand,Falater,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,9,0,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,FRFIL40LM,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011111100100011000000011111100011011000010011101,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14178,simple,,,"FRYRITE 40L FILTERS - FRFIL40SH",1,0,visible,"FRYRITE 40L FILTERS: Oil filters are essential components used in various types of machinery and vehicles to remove impurities from the oil circulating within the system. They prevent contaminants such as dirt, debris, and metal particles from causing damage to the equipment and ensure the smooth functioning of the machinery. Consider offering oil filters in different sizes, designs, and filtration efficiencies to accommodate the requirements of different applications.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• FRYRITE 40L FILTERS - FRFIL40SH</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cooking Oil filter paper loaded with magnesium silicate</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Oil filters are essential components used in various types of machinery and vehicles to remove impurities from the oil circulating within the system. They prevent contaminants such as dirt, debris, and metal particles from causing damage to the equipment and ensure the smooth functioning of the machinery. Consider offering oil filters in different sizes, designs, and filtration efficiencies to accommodate the requirements of different applications.</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,490,"ACCESSORIES, Kitchen Equipment","FRYRITE 40L FILTERS",,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/FRYRITE-40L-FILTERS.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Falater,Brand,Falater,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,9,0,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,FRFIL40SH,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,001010110001011000001011111001111101100001111000,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14180,simple,,,"MIRACLE POWDER 100X135G SACHET - MP135SAC",1,0,visible,"MIRACLE POWDER 100X135G SACHET\n<strong>Why is Miracle Fry Oil Powder better than other fry powders?</strong>\n\nMiracle Fry Oil Powder is free flowing and not chemically reactive. It is made of magnesium silicate which absorbs fatty acids and remove impurities that form during the frying process.\n\nThis specially designed powder has been developed to remove minute carbon particles which are a host to bacteria that attacks your oil creating acidity. It is of the highest food grade standard and most major fast food companies use it.\n\n'I already filter my oil with filter paper… why use a oil powder?'\n\nFiltering alone only removes the lumps out of the oil, the gummy sticky residue remains. This residue is made up of a polarised Free Fatty Acids (FFAs)and Oxidised Fatty Acids (OFAs). Miracle Fry Oil Powder absorbs the FFAs and OFAs, changing them into solid particles, which then is removed by the filtering process. Miracle Fry Oil Powder extends the life of your oil significantly.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• MIRACLE POWDER 100X135G SACHET</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Benefits include:</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• food grade filter aid</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• neutralise acidity (FFAs)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• reduces total polar compounds (TMP’s)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• removes carbons</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• improves the colour of fry oil</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• improves food quality</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• free flowing inert white powder</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• significantly extends the life of oil</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• easy to us</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,525,"ACCESSORIES, Kitchen Equipment","MIRACLE POWDER 100X135G SACHET",,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/MIRACLE-POWDER-100X135G-SACHET.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Falater,Brand,Falater,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,7,0,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,MP135SAC,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596219,110101010011010010100011001001011111001000111100,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
