14185,simple,,,"PITCO T2 FILTER 365x520 PAPER - PTCT2P",1,0,visible,"Preserve the freshness and quality of your shortening with PITCO T2 FILTER 365x520 PAPER - PTCT2P heavy-duty envelope style filter paper! Compatible with Pitco’s Solstice filter drawer, this paper filters out impurities, which prolongs your oil’s life. Not only will this save you money on oil costs, but it also improves the taste and quality of your finished product.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• PITCO T2 FILTER 365x520 PAPER - PTCT2P</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 1 pack / 100pcs.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 365x520</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Preserve the freshness and quality of your shortening with PITCO FILTER T24 255x520 - PTCT24P heavy-duty envelope style filter paper! Compatible with Pitco’s Solstice filter drawer, this paper filters out impurities, which prolongs your oil’s life. Not only will this save you money on oil costs, but it also improves the taste and quality of your finished product.</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,693,"ACCESSORIES, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/PITCO-PP10613.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Pitco,Brand,Pitco,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,5,0,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,PTCT2P,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110010100100110011010110110100110110010010110010,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
