14202,simple,,,"Potato Peeler including Stand & Drawer - PPF10M",1,0,visible,"<h5 class=""serp-title""><mark>Potato Peeler including Stand &amp; Drawer - PPF10M</mark></h5>\nThe Potato Peeler with Stand &amp; Drawer, model PPF10M, is a versatile and efficient kitchen tool designed to streamline the process of peeling potatoes. This innovative appliance combines functionality with convenience, making it an essential addition to any kitchen.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Potato Peeler including Stand &amp; Drawer - PPF10M</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">•. Tank Capacity (L.): ± 10 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cap: Production 120 kg/h</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Potato peeling machine. Structure in AISI 304 s/s</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• upper cover in transparent food-grade polycarbonate</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• safety microswitches on the upper cover and on the outlet – product ejection button</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• power: 1.1 kW (1.5 HP)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Packaging volume (m3):  0.326</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Supply: 230V/1N/50Hz -230-400V/3-3N/50Hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• N.weight: 34 Kg /  G.weight: 45 Kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• dimension: 380 x 770 x 1160(h) mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• ackaging dimensions: 830 x 530 x 740(h) mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• PPF10M / fimar/ italy made</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,7935.048,"FOOD PROCESSING > Cutter Mixer, FOOD PROCESSING, Kitchen Equipment, FOOD PROCESSING > Vegtable Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Potato-Peeler-including-Stand-Drawer-PPF10M.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Fimar,Brand,Fimar,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,7,0,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,PPF10M,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d83