14204,simple,,,"Potato Peeler including Stand & Drawer - PPF18M",1,0,visible,"<strong>Potato Peeler including Stand &amp; Drawer </strong>\nThe Potato Peeler with Stand &amp; Drawer, model PPF18M, is a state-of-the-art kitchen appliance that takes the hassle out of potato preparation. Engineered for efficiency and user convenience, this peeler is a must-have for culinary enthusiasts and professional kitchens alike.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Potato Peeler including Stand &amp; Drawer - PPF18M</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Tank Capacity (L.): ± 18 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cap: Production 220 Kg/h</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Potato peeling machine. Structure in AISI 304 s/s</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• upper cover in transparent food-grade polycarbonate</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• safety microswitches on the upper cover and on the outlet – product ejection button</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• power: 1.1 kW (1.5 HP)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Packaging volume (m3): 0.463</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Supply: 230V / 1N / 50Hz - 230-400V / 3-3N / 50Hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• N.weight: 39 Kg / G.weight: 50 Kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• dimension: 380 x 770 x 1230(h) mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Packaging dimensions: 830 x 530 x 950(h) mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• PPF18M / fimar/ italy made</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,8071.272,"FOOD PROCESSING > Cutter Mixer, FOOD PROCESSING, Kitchen Equipment, FOOD PROCESSING > Vegtable Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Potato-Peeler-including-Stand-Drawer-PPF10M.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Fimar,Brand,Fimar,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,7,0,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,PPF18M,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517