14205,simple,,,"Vegetable Cutter with a set of 5 discs - TV2000",1,0,visible,"<strong>Vegetable Cutter with a set of 5 discs</strong>\nThe Vegetable Cutter with a set of 5 discs, model TV2000, is a versatile and efficient kitchen tool that revolutionizes the way you prepare vegetables. Designed for ease of use and a variety of cutting options, this appliance is a valuable addition to any kitchen.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Vegetable Cutter with a set of 5 discs - TV2000</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• D10 , E2 , E10 , H10 , Z4</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• power: 0,37 kW (0,5 HP)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Supply: 230V/1N/50Hz – 230-400V/3/50Hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• N.weight: 22 Kg / G.weight: 24 Kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Mixing speed: 255 rpm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Mouth size: oval mouth ~ 155×75 mm – round mouth size ø 56 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Packaging volume (m3): 0.108</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• dimension: 220 x 610 x 520h (mm)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Packaging dim: (lxwxh mm): 300 x 620 x 580(h) mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• TV2000 / TV2000RNK235M / fimar/ italy made</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,5092.56,"FOOD PROCESSING > Cutter Mixer, FOOD PROCESSING, Kitchen Equipment, FOOD PROCESSING > Vegtable Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Vegetable-Cutter-with-a-set-of-5-discs-TV2000.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Fimar,Brand,Fimar,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,11,0,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"TV2000 / TV2000RNK235M",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011000100110110011010110110001101100011001001110,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14207,simple,,,"Bone Saws machine (PAINTED) - SE1830V",1,0,visible,"<strong>Bone Saws machine (PAINTED) - SE1830V</strong>\nThe Bone Saws machine (PAINTED) - SE1830V is a precision-engineered and expertly crafted tool designed for the efficient and precise cutting of bones in various culinary and food processing applications. Its sleek and durable exterior is enhanced with a high-quality paint finish, not only providing an aesthetic appeal but also adding an extra layer of protection against corrosion and wear.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(83px, 30px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Bone Saws machine (PAINTED) - SE1830V</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Painted aluminum structure with low voltage controls</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Emergency button</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Microswitch on the machine closing cover</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Motor brake - Adjustment of the cutting thickness, height, portioner, work surface, blade guide and meat pusher s/s.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power : 0.75 kW (1 HP)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• SUPPLY 230V / 1N / 50Hz - 230-400V / 3 / 50Hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• N.Weight 39 Kg / G. Weight : 47 Kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• BLADE DEVELOPMENT 1830 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Useful cut dim : 200 x 225h (mm)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Worktop: 410 x 410 (mm)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Packaging volume (m3): 0.286</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dimension: 630 x 450 x 970h (mm)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Packing Dim: 1020 x 560 x 500(h) mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• SE1830V / fimar/ italy made</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(277px, 277px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,7117.704,"FOOD PROCESSING, Kitchen Equipment, FOOD PROCESSING > Meat Slicer & Bone Saw",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Bone-Saws-machine-PAINTED-SE1830V.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Fimar,Brand,Fimar,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,62,0,0,,"Bone Saws machine (PAINTED) - SE1830V,ماكينة منشار العظام (مطلية) – SE1830V,منشار عظام,احسن منشار كهربائي لتقطيع اللحم,منشار كهربائي لتقطيع اللحم",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,SE1830V,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595961,011000110011111000110011100110010010011001100011,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14209,simple,,,"KitchenAid Planetary Mixer White - KA5W230M",1,0,visible,"<strong>KitchenAid Planetary Mixer White - KA5W230M</strong>\nThe KitchenAid Planetary Mixer in White (Model KA5W230M) is a versatile and powerful kitchen appliance designed to meet the demands of both amateur and professional bakers. This stylish and efficient mixer is part of KitchenAid's renowned line of stand mixers, known for their durability and performanc\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(191px, 79px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• KitchenAid Planetary Mixer White - KA5W230M</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Capacity 5 Lt</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• KitchenAid Classic White Planetary Mixer with 5 liter removable stainless steel bowl</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Equipped with 3 enamelled aluminum accessories : spatula, drum and dough hook</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Easy to use and clean, robust and resistant entirely made of metal</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Equipped with a power take-off to apply the numerous</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• KitchenAid accessories available separately</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Planetary Speed: 0 to 10</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power : 250 W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• SUPPLY: 220 - 240V</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight: 12 Kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Speed ​​Rpm: 58 - 220</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• External dimension: 419 x 279 x 414 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• KA5W230M / 5KPM5 / KitchenAid / USA""</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(420px, 166px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,3928.32,"BAKERY LINE, BAKERY LINE > Bakery Mixers, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/KitchenAid-Planetary-Mixer-White-KA5W230M.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"Kitchen Aid",Brand,"Kitchen Aid",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,62,0,0,,"KitchenAid Planetary Mixer White - KA5W230M,كيتشن إيد خلاط كوكبي أبيض – KA5W230M,خلاط كهربائية",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,KA5W230M,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,010010100110110011010110010110001110110011001100,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14211,simple,,,"KitchenAid Planetary Mixer White - KA7W230M",1,0,visible,"<strong>KitchenAid Planetary Mixer White - KA7W230M</strong>\nThe KitchenAid Planetary Mixer in White (Model KA7W230M) represents a pinnacle of culinary excellence, combining timeless design with cutting-edge functionality. Crafted with precision and durability, this stand mixer is an indispensable companion for passionate home cooks and professionals alike.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• KitchenAid Planetary Mixer White - KA7W230M</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Capacity 7 Lt</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• KitchenAid Heavy Duty mixer with silent and powerful motor with direct transmission.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Homogeneous and fast mixing, for perfect results</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Bathtub lifting</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Speed ​​from 0 to 10</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• High efficiency 1.3 HP motor</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power : 500 W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• SUPPLY: 220 - 240V</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight: 12 Kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Speed ​​Rpm: 60/265 min</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• External dimension: 260 x 330 x 410 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• KA7W230M / 5KSM7990 / KitchenAid / USA</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(551px, 164px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(5px, 54px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,0,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,6035.04,"BAKERY LINE, BAKERY LINE > Bakery Mixers, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/KitchenAid-Planetary-Mixer-White-KA7W230M.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"Kitchen Aid",Brand,"Kitchen Aid",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,62,0,0,,"KitchenAid Planetary Mixer White - KA7W230M,كيتشن إيد خلاط كوكبي أبيض – KA7W230M,خلاط كهربائية",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"KA7W230M / 5KSM7990",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110010100110110011100110000111000110010111001100,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14213,simple,,,"Professional electric crepe maker – CSE 400",1,0,visible,"<strong>With the enamelled cast-iron crepe maker CSE 400, the weekly seasoning is over!</strong>\nThe electric crepe maker CSE 400 is equipped with a Ø400 mm enamelled cast-iron plate. The enamelled coating of the plate substantially reduces the seasoning phase. This long and tedious seasoning phase is normally required before the first use and must be renewed every week. With the Roller Grill enamelled cast-iron plate, the electric crepe maker CSE 400 is in operation from the first pancake cooking and is just as easy to use.\n\n<strong>The professional electric crepe maker CSE 400 guarantees perfectly homogeneous cooking</strong>.\nAnother advantage of an enamelled cast-iron plate: the professional electric crepe maker is then perfectly smooth. It ensures an excellent temperature transfer and a real cooking by contact.\n\nThe Incoloy heating element is integrated into the cast-iron plate and maintained by 2 counter plates. This spiral heating element guarantees a constant and precise cooking regulated by thermostat.\n\nJust lightly grease the single crepe machine between each baking to obtain a light and well-golden crepe, perfectly honeycombed, without caramelization or glazing effect.\n\n<strong>The professional crepe maker Roller Grill is more than just cooking crepes!</strong>\nThe professional crepe maker CSE 400 is recognized as the ideal equipment to succeed in also buckwheat pancakes, Indian tampuras, Indonesian chapatis, blinis etc. This electric crepe machine is also meant to cook fried eggs, to simmer vegetables or to grill meat. This enamelled cast-iron crepe maker is also very popular for preparing Peking duck in Asian cuisine.\n\n<strong>Features:</strong> 2 spiral heating elements, 2 commutator-thermostats 0-300 ° C, pilot lights, wooden ""T"" utensil to spread the batter evenly.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• Professional electric crepe maker – CSE 400</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• pancakes plate with 6 imprints Ø110 mm each</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• all stainless steel storage case CK 3 for crepe maker: 2 spatulas, 2 ""T"" wooden, 1 grease pad</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Batch of crepe mix, Roller Grill recipe (10 packs of 1kg)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Power3.6 kW</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Outside dimensions 450 x 480 x 240 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Weight 23 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• volts 230 V</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Diameter 400 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• 100% Made in FRANCE</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,2590,"SNACK MAKER > Crepe Maker, Kitchen Equipment, SNACK MAKER, Top Brands",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/CSE-400.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"Roller Grill",Brand,"Roller Grill",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,72,0,0,,"Professional electric crepe maker – CSE 400,صانعة الكريب الكهربائية الاحترافية – CSE 400,صانعة الكريب الكهربائية",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"CSE 400",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595055,011111001110011010001100011110000100011000010111,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14215,simple,,,"Professional electric waffle iron - GES 10",1,0,visible,"The Professional Electric Waffle Iron - GES 10 is a high-performance appliance designed for both commercial and home use. Featuring a robust stainless steel construction, it ensures durability and longevity. The GES 10 comes with precise temperature control, allowing for perfectly cooked waffles every time. Its non-stick plates make for easy cleanup, while the compact design saves counter space. Ideal for cafes, restaurants, and serious home cooks, this waffle iron delivers consistent results and professional-grade performance.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• Professional electric waffle iron - GES 10</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• <strong>Technical characteristics</strong></p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Waffle size 100 x 170 x 22 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Power 1.6 kW</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Outside dimensions 305 x 440 x 230 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Weight 22 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• volts 230 V</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,3041,"Kitchen Equipment, SNACK MAKER, SNACK MAKER > Waffle Maker",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Professional-electric-waffle-iron-GES-10.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"Roller Grill",Brand,"Roller Grill",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,68,0,0,,"Professional electric waffle iron - GES 10,مكواة الوافل الكهربائية الاحترافية – GES 10,الة الوافل,وافل",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"GES 10",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595599,011000100110111001110110110100100101100010011001,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14217,simple,,,"Professional Pizza Oven Extra Large - PZ 430 2D",1,0,visible,"<strong>Professional Pizza Oven Extra Large - PZ 430 2D </strong>\nThe professional pizza oven PZ 430 2D is particularly innovative in its double regulation.\nThe professional pizza oven PZ 430 2D is equipped with an innovative system of double regulation of the vault and the bottom of the oven:\n\n- A thermostat regulates the oven chamber and the infrared quartz in the upper part\n\n- A power regulator for the bottom, that is to say the firestone and infrared quartz in the lower part.\n\nThanks to its innovative technology, the deck oven PZ 430 2D offers varied and very fast cooking possibilities.\nIn addition to its double regulation system, the deck oven PZ 430 2D is equipped with infrared quartz tubes in the upper part and under the firestone. These infrared quartz spread a radiation of 1050 ° C on the products to be cooked. They ensure fast and thorough cooking of products.\n\nThe combination of these two revolutionary technologies gives exceptional cooking results in the infrared oven PZ 430 2D:\n\n- 2 fresh pizzas Ø32 cm at 350 ° C in 3 minutes!\n\n- 2 frozen pizzas Ø32 cm at 350 ° C in 3'30 minutes!\n\nAdapt your deck oven with firestone ""special pizza""! You can regulate the lower part for all pizzas with thin dough (Tuscan pizza), thicker basis (Neapolitan pizza) or very thick dough (""American pan pizza""). This power control offers you the possibility to cook a wide variety of pancakes, chapatis, flambé tarts, pastries etc. according to their dough.\n\nFeatures: firestone for even cooking, 15-minutes-sound-timer lock position for non-stop use, 2 thermic controls (Thermostat 0-350 ° + power regulator), control lights. Double insulated door with tempered glass.\n\nOption: stainless steel kit KPZ 430 to stack up to 3 Roller Grill pizza ovens.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(1px, 154px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(2px, 144px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Professional Pizza Oven Extra Large - PZ 430 2D</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Capacity Ø 2 x 32 cm or 600x400 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power 5 kW</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Outside dimensions 895 x 580 x270 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight 57 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• volts 380 V ou 230 V mono</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Inside dimensions 660 x 430 x 110 mm</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(729px, 328px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(1px, 253px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(478px, 207px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,5291,"BAKERY LINE, BAKERY LINE > Bakery Oven, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Professional-pizza-oven-extra-large-PZ-430-2D.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"Roller Grill",Brand,"Roller Grill",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,74,0,0,,"Professional Pizza Oven Extra Large - PZ 430 2D,فرن بيتزا احترافي كبير جدًا – PZ 430 2D,فرن بيتزا",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"PZ 430 2D",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595599,011111100101011000000010111001111111000100110000,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14219,simple,,,"Infrared conveyor toaster for breakfast - CT 540 B",1,0,visible,"<strong>Infrared conveyor toaster for breakfast - CT 540 B</strong>\nThe infrared conveyor toaster CT 540 B indispensable for continuous use at breakfast!\nThe infrared conveyor toaster CT 540 B is equipped with 2 ramps of 4 infrared quartz tubes. These infrared quartz spread rays of 1050 ° C on the products. It enables the hotel guest to quickly and continuously toast or heat every kind of bread for breakfast: 300 to 540 toasts per hour according to the type of bread without preheating!\n\nThe infrared quartz on the upper part is protected by a patented cover.\n\nThe quartz grill CT 540 B is extremely flexible in use and maintenance!\nThe quartz grill CT 540 B is a very flexible conveyor toaster thanks to its 2 independent settings:\n\n- A switch selects the quartz ramps on top and bottom\n\n- The speed of the conveyor belt is regulated according to the product to be cooked or to be reheated. The minimum pass through time is 47 seconds. The maximum pass through time of is 2 minutes and 30 seconds.\n\nTwo exits are possible depending on the products:\n\n- The front exit is used for bread, brioche, bagels etc.\n\n- The rear exit is recommended for heavier and more delicate products such as big slices of farmhouse bread (30 cm in diameter), buttered slices, baguettes, pastries, delicacies, quiche etc.\n\nThe top roof keeps breads or pastries ready for use at the hotel's breakfast buffet.\n\nThe conveyor toaster can be cleaned very easy. The carpet is cleaned with a brush supplied with the quartz grill. The top as well as the 2 sliding trays placed at the entrance and exit under the carpet are completely removable.\n\nFeatures: 2 ramps of 4 quartz tubes (1550 W at the top, 1450 W at the bottom), heating selector, variable speed drive, conveyor belt made of flexible stainless steel mesh, 15 cm front and rear trays, pilot lights, ventilated motor, adjustable feet.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• Infrared conveyor toaster for breakfast - CT 540 B</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Inside dimensions 85 mm (hauteur)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Power 2,65 kW</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Outside dimensions 510 x 680 x 455 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Baking surface 330 x 335 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Weight 20 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• volts 230 V</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,5829,"BAKERY LINE, Kitchen Equipment, BAKERY LINE > Toaster",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Infrared-conveyor-toaster-for-breakfast-CT-540-B.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"Roller Grill",Brand,"Roller Grill",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,66,0,0,,"Infrared conveyor toaster for breakfast - CT 540 B,النقل بالأشعة تحت الحمراء محمصة لتناول الإفطار - CT 540 ب,محمصة الإفطار بالأشعة تحت الحمراء",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"CT 540 B",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595594,010101111110010010100100011111000110010111100000,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14221,simple,,,"Professional sausage heater with 11 rollers - RG 11 B",1,0,visible,"<strong>Professional sausage heater with 11 rollers - RG 11 B</strong>\nThe professional sausage heater RG 11 is very efficient and ideal for high-speed service!\nThe professional sausage heater RG 11 is fitted out with 11 rolls and keeps warms 20 pre-cooked sausages at right temperature for 96 hot dogs per hour! This optimal efficiency is ensured by the rotation of the rollers on themselves thanks to an asynchronous motor. Each 3-cm-diameter chrome roller has a power of 125 W. The gap between the rollers is 1.5 cm. This sausage warmer is particularly popular in hot dog concepts or football/rugby stadiums during the rush hours for a prompt service. This double sausage heater is equipped with 2 independent heating zones.\n\nThe sausage roller heater is very compact and can be surmounted by the bun warmer CB 20 to keep warm the hot dog buns too. An ideal package to create your own hot dog concept!\n\nThe sausage heater with 11 rolls is very easy to clean!\nThe chrome rollers of the sausage heater make maintenance very easy and guarantee a long service life. A grease tray is placed under the rollers. This stain less steel tray is completely removable and can be cleaned in a dishwasher.\n\nFeatures: on / off switch, energy regulator, pilot light, high performance motor.\n\nOption: Breath Guard H01077SE (580 x 450 x 250 mm) for any Roller Grill sausage roller heater, with lifting rear door for service.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• Professional sausage heater with 11 rollers - RG 11 B</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Weight 20 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• volts 230 V</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Outside dimensions 545 x 460 x 240 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Power 1,4 kW</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,5132,"SNACK MAKER > Hot Dog Machine, SNACK MAKER > Hotdog Maker, Kitchen Equipment, SNACK MAKER",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Professional-sausage-heater-with-11-rollers-RG-11-B.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"Roller Grill",Brand,"Roller Grill",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,68,0,0,,"Professional sausage heater with 11 rollers - RG 11 B,سخان سجق احترافي مزود بـ 11 بكرة – RG 11 B,سخان سجق",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"RG 11 B",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595673,010111100101111010000110110000000111000010011111,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14223,simple,,,"Professional sausage heater with 7 rollers - RG 7 B",1,0,visible,"<strong>Professional sausage heater with 7 rollers - RG 7 B</strong>\nThe professional sausage heater RG 7 is very efficient and ideal for high-speed service!\nThe professional sausage heater RG 7 is fitted out with 7 rolls and keeps warms 12 pre-cooked sausages at right temperature for 58 hot dogs per hour! This optimal efficiency is ensured by the rotation of the rollers on themselves thanks to an asynchronous motor. Each 3-cm-diameter chrome roller has a power of 125 W. The gap between the rollers is 1.5 cm. This sausage warmer is particularly popular in hot dog concepts or football/rugby stadiums during the rush hours for a prompt service.\n\nThe sausage roller heater is very compact and can be surmounted by the bun warmer CB 20 to keep warm the hot dog buns too. An ideal package to create your own hot dog concept!\n\nThe sausage heater with 7 rolls is very easy to clean!\nThe chrome rollers of the sausage heater make maintenance very easy and guarantee a long service life. A grease tray is placed under the rollers. This stain less steel tray is completely removable and can be cleaned in a dishwasher.\n\nFeatures: on / off switch, energy regulator, pilot light, high performance motor.\n\nOption: Breath Guard H01077SE (580 x 450 x 250 mm) for any Roller Grill sausage roller heater, with lifting rear door for service.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(165px, 37px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Professional sausage heater with 7 rollers - RG 7 B</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight 14 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• volts 230 V</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power 0,9 kW</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Outside dimensions 545 x 320 x 240 mm</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(504px, 15px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,3640,"Kitchen Equipment, Uncategorized",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Professional-sausage-heater-with-7-rollers-RG-7-B.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"Roller Grill",Brand,"Roller Grill",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,68,0,0,,"Professional sausage heater with 7 rollers - RG 7 B,سخان سجق احترافي مزود بـ 7 بكرات – RG 7 B,سخان سجق",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"RG 7 B",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595673,010111100101011100000110100000100111010010011111,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14225,simple,,,"Infrared salamander toaster – 1 cooking level GN 1/1 - TS 1270",1,0,visible,"<strong>Infrared salamander toaster – 1 cooking level GN 1/1 - TS 1270</strong>\nThe infrared salamander toaster TS 1270: the champion of cooking!\nThe infrared salamander toaster TS 1270 is equipped with 2 ramps of 3 infrared quartz tubes. This electric toaster can cook without preheating, without smoke or smell, any type of snacks. The infrared quartz spread a harmless radiation of 1050 ° C on the products to be cooked. They ensure a fast and thorough cooking at core of the products.\n\nThe infrared quartz tubes of this stainless steel toaster are protected by a patented protection grid.\n\nVary your cooking with the professional toaster TS 1270 !\nThe professional toaster TS 1270 can cook up to 200 toasts per hour!\n\nThanks to its Gastronorm GN 1/1 capacity, the infrared salamander toaster TS 1270 makes it possible to vary cooking in big quantities such as :\n\n- to cook and reheat a croque-monsieur, quiche or pizza,\n\n- to brown onion soup, eggs casserole, gratins\n\n- to toast all kinds of bread in long or round slices, thick or thin\n\n- to defrost frozen dishes.\n\nFeatures: selector for infrared quartz ramps, 15-minute-timer with lock position for non-stop use, control lights, patented protection grid for quartz tubes, crumb tray.\n\nOption : Sandwich tong ( F01013 )","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Infrared salamander toaster – 1 cooking level GN 1/1 - TS 1270</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cooking surface 520 X 320 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Capacity 1 x GN 1/1</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power 2.47 kW</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Outside dimensions 640 x 380 x 335 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight 13 kG</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• volts 230 V</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Useful height 85 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 100% Made in FRANCE</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,2925,"COOKING LINE, Kitchen Equipment, COOKING LINE > Salamander",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Photo-dun-toaster-salamandre-a-infrarouge-TS-1270.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"Roller Grill",Brand,"Roller Grill",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,2,0,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"TS 1270",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595599,011111100100111000000110100001111110000010110101,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14227,simple,,,"Infrared salamander toaster – 2 cooking levels GN 1/1 - TS 3270",1,0,visible,"<strong>Infrared salamander toaster – 2 cooking levels GN 1/1 - TS 3270 </strong>\nThe infrared salamander toaster TS 3270: the champion of cooking!\nThe infrared salamander toaster TS 3270 is equipped with 3 ramps of 3 infrared quartz tubes. This electric toaster can cook without preheating, without smoke or smell, any type of snacks. The infrared quartz spread a harmless radiation of 1050 ° C on the products to be cooked. They ensure a fast and thorough cooking at core of the products.\n\nFor a fast service during rush hours, the upper compartment of this double toaster is exclusively equipped with a closed tray-grid with handles.\n\nThe infrared quartz tubes of this stainless steel toaster are protected by a patented protection grid.\n\nVary your cooking with the professional toaster TS 3270 !\nThe professional toaster TS 3270 can cook up to 200 toasts per hour!\n\nThanks to its 2 cooking levels and it Gastronorm GN 2/1 capacity, the infrared salamander toaster TS 3270 makes it possible to vary cooking in large quantities such as :\n\n- to cook and reheat a croque-monsieur, quiche or pizza,\n\n- to brown onion soup, eggs casserole, gratins\n\n- to toast all kinds of bread in long or round slices, thick or thin\n\n- to defrost frozen dishes.\n\nFeatures: selector for infrared quartz ramps, 15-minute-timer with lock position for non-stop use, control lights, patented protection grid for quartz tubes, crumb tray.\n\nOption : Sandwich tong ( F01013 )","<p style="" margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Infrared salamander toaster – 2 cooking levels GN 1/1 - TS 3270 </p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Capacity	1 x GN 1/1</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power	4 kW or 2x2 kW (2 cords)</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Outside dimensions	640 x 380 x475 mm</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Baking surface	2 (520 x 320) mm</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight	19 kg</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• volts	380 V or 230 V mono</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Useful height	85 mm</p>\n<p style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 100% Made in FRANCE</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,3510,"COOKING LINE, Kitchen Equipment, COOKING LINE > Salamander, Top Brands",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Infrared-salamander-toaster-–-2-cooking-levels-GN-1-1-TS-3270.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"Roller Grill",Brand,"Roller Grill",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,2,0,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"TS 3270",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595055,110101100001110010100110100010010110010110010111,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14229,simple,,,"Ventilated negative display cabinet RDN 800",1,0,visible,"<strong>Ventilated negative display cabinet - Glass shelves, large model - RDN 800</strong>\nHighlight your frozen desserts at good temperature in the negative display cabinet with glass shelves!\nPanoramic and equipped with a 4 LED lighting, the ventilated negative display cabinet RDN 800 enhances your ice creams, pastries and frozen pies.\n\nYour pastries and ice cream creations are presented on 5 glass shelves measuring 610 x 510 mm and adjustable on 6 levels.\n\nThe vertical showcase RDN 800 is equipped with a very efficient cold system.\nThe ventilated refrigeration system ensures a uniform temperature of -5 to -20 ° C throughout the vertical showcase.\n\nThe evaporator placed in the upper part guarantees a homogeneous cold throughout the showcase.\n\nThe electronic thermostat allows automatic defrosting every 2 hours.\n\nPerfectly insulated, this vertical showcase with negative cold is equipped with triple glazed walls.\n\nAll refrigerated pastry display cabinets are factory tested at an ambient outside temperature of 29 ° C.\n\nFeatures: electronic thermostat control, 4 LED ramps, magnetic closing door, triple glazing, Tecumseh FRANCE compressor, R290 gas. Tropicalized showcase mounted on 4 double wheels. Available in 3 colors: stainless steel, black or white.\n\nOption: micro-hole glazing for use in the mountains.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Ventilated negative display cabinet - Glass shelves, large model - RDN 800</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Inside dimensions 710 x 560 x 1170 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Capacity 480 l</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power 0,80 kW</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Outside dimensions 800 x 645 x 1850 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight 200 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• volts 230 V</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 100% Made in FRANCE</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,18200,"REFRIGERATION LINE > Display Chiller, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ventilated-negative-display-cabinet-Glass-shelves-large-model-RDN-800-F.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"Roller Grill",Brand,"Roller Grill",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,5,0,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595673,011100110010001100110010010110110100100101100111,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14231,simple,,,"Ventilated positive display cabinet - Glass shelves - RD 600",1,0,visible,"<strong>Ventilated positive display cabinet - Glass shelves - RD 600</strong>\nHighlight your desserts at the right temperature in the refrigerated display cabinet with glass shelves!\nPanoramic and equipped with 4 LED lighting, the refrigerated display cabinet RD 600 sublimates your pastries, your pies and all your desserts with fruit.\n\nYour pastries and culinary creations are presented on 5 glass shelves measuring 465 x 455 mm and adjustable on 6 levels.\n\nThe vertical showcase RD 600 is equipped with a very efficient cold system.\nThe ventilated refrigeration system ensures a uniform temperature of +2 to + 10 ° C throughout the vertical showcase.\n\nThe evaporator placed in the upper part guarantees a homogeneous cold in the whole refrigerated display cabinet.\n\nThe electronic thermostat allows automatic defrosting every 2 hours.\n\nPerfectly insulated, this vertical showcase with positive cold is equipped with double glazed walls.\n\nAll refrigerated pastry display cabinets are factory tested at an ambient outside temperature of 29 ° C.\n\nFeatures: electronic thermostat control, 4 LED ramps, magnetic closing door, double glazing, Tecumseh FRANCE compressor, R290. Tropicalized showcase mounted on 4 double wheels. Available in 3 colors: stainless steel, black or white.\n\nOption: micro-hole glazing for use in the mountains.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• Ventilated positive display cabinet - Glass shelves - RD 600</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Inside dimensions 520 x 580 x 1170 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Capacity 360 l</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Power 0,43 kW</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Outside dimensions 600 X 645 X 1850 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Weight 150 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• volts 230 V</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• 100% Made in FRANCE</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,10074,"REFRIGERATION LINE > Display Chiller, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ventilated-positive-display-cabinet-Glass-shelves-RD-600.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"Roller Grill",Brand,"Roller Grill",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,5,0,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"RD 600",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595673,110010100110010011001110010100110101100011001101,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14233,simple,,,"Ventilated heated display showcase - 3 grids - WD 780 DN",1,0,visible,"<strong>Ventilated heated display showcase - 3 grids - WD 780 DN</strong>\nThe heated showcase WD 780 DN features a unique ventilated firestone heating system!\n- The firestone placed on the Incoloy heating element accumulates, releases and spreads the heat in the showcase. It guarantees a sufficient temperature (72 ° C) of meat-based snacks such as nuggets, meatballs or delicacies.\n\n- The 2 fans spreads the heat evenly throughout the showcase\n\n- The electronic thermostat regulates the temperature from 20 to 90 ° C with a precision to the nearest degree.\n\n- A water drawer allows a humidity control essential to keep moist and delicious the sweet pastries and delicatessen.\n\nThis ventilated heated showcase, equipped with 4 LED ramps, highlights and keeps warm in quantities quiches, pizzas, fondues, meatballs, pastries and so on. The display is supplied with 3 grids (670 x 433 mm each). It can receive Gastronorm GN 1/1 dishes, 400 x 600 mm dishes or 3 American dishes.\n\nThe professional showcase WD 780 DN is very easy to use and to clean.\nThe rear glass doors open at 180 ° C for the loading of the professional showcase and for the service.\n\nThe grids and theirs supports, the stainless steel lower tray, the water drawer and the firestone are completely removable.\n\nThe professional showcase WD 780 is available in stainless steel or black version.\n\nFeatures: electronic thermostat (20-90 ° C), water drawer, on / off switch, switch for ventilation, fans, firestone. Supplied with 3 grids. Additional grids on request. Delivered with no GN tray.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Ventilated heated display showcase - 3 grids - WD 780 DN</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Inside dimensions 750 x 460 x 530 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power 1.8 kW</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Outside dimensions 780 x 490 x 640 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight 35 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• volts 230 V</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Grilles 3 x (670 x 433 mm)</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,0,,,4355,"COOKING LINE, Kitchen Equipment, COOKING LINE > Salamander",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ventilated-heated-display-showcase-3-grids-WD-780-D.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"Roller Grill",Brand,"Roller Grill",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,5,0,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"WD 780 DN",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595673,011111110001011000000110101100001010111000110101,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14235,simple,,,"Meat Smoker Oven - CST290",1,0,visible,"<strong><em>Meat Smoker Oven - CST290</em></strong>\n<strong>SMOKES THE MEAT - KEEPS THE MEAT WARM\nTHE SMOKE CHANGES ACCORDING TO THE COAL OR WOOD USE</strong>\nDiscover the perfect balance of flavor and convenience with our 4-Tray Meat Smoker Oven. Elevate your grilling experience as you infuse your favorite meats with irresistible smokiness. The four spacious trays provide ample space for a variety of culinary creations, while precise temperature control ensures deliciously smoked results every time. Unleash the essence of slow-cooked perfection in the comfort of your kitchen – your journey to flavorful, smoky dishes starts here!","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Meat Smoker Oven - CST290</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight 250 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Trays 4</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Length 70cm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Width 95cm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Height 185cm</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,9499,"BAKERY LINE, BAKERY LINE > Bakery Oven, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/meat-smoker-oven.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Mariot,Brand,Mariot,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,5,0,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,CST290,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595916,011010110011011001011100110110010100110001100100,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14237,simple,,,"Suitable for fryers up to 12 volume -VITO 30",1,0,visible,"The VITO 30 cleans the oil and provides an easy and hygienic filtration in the kitchen. Like every VITO oil filter system the VITO 30 provides a microfiltration up to 5 µm (200µin). As an additional feature no chemicals are needed to clean the oil, which preserves the optimal taste of the fried dishes. The unique design makes sure the VITO can handle temperatures up to 200°C (392°F) and provides highest safety at work, because of avoiding direct contact with the hot oil. After filtration the oil can be immediately used for frying again.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Suitable for fryers up to 12 volume -VITO 30</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• <strong>Benefits:</strong></p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Increases the lifetime of your oil</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Improves taste and quality</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Saves time and labor</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• <strong>Specifications</strong></p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Normal usage Ideal for fryers up to 12 l / 22 lbs</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Filtration power up to 30 l/min</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 66 lbs/min</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Filtration efficiency up to 5 µm / 200µin</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Particle uptake 0,8 kg / 1.8 lbs</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Work cycle 4.5 min</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Suction depth ~ 20 cm / ~ 7.9 in</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight 6,3 kg / 14 lbs</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Temperature max. 200°C / 392°F</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Material Stainless steel 1.4301</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,7900,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Fryers, Kitchen Equipment",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/2738_vito-30-oil-filter-system.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/5426_vito-30-in-fryer.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/9769_vito-gear-detail.jpg",,,,,,,,,0,,"Vito Oil Filter System",Brand,"Vito Oil Filter System",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,6,0,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"VITO 30",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,15770,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,100111011001001100100111001001110001100110011100,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14241,simple,,,"Suitable for fryers up to 20 volume - VITO VM",1,0,visible,"The VITO VM cleans the oil and provides an easy and hygienic filtration in the kitchen. Like every VITO oil filter system the VITO VM provides a microfiltration up to 5 µm (200µin). As an additional feature no chemicals are needed to clean the oil, which preserves the optimal taste of the fried dishes. The unique design makes sure the VITO can handle temperatures up to 200°C (392°F) and provides highest safety at work, because of avoiding direct contact with the hot oil. After filtration the oil can be immediately used for frying again.\nThe integrated VITOconnect software enables seamless documentation of the VITO VM usage and maximum cost control.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Suitable for fryers up to 20 volume - VITO VM</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">•<strong> Benefits:</strong></p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Saves up to 50% of frying oil</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Improves taste and quality</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Saves time and labor</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• <strong>Specifications</strong></p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Normal usage Ideal for fryers up to 20 l / 37 lbs</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Filtration power up to 60 l/min</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 130 lbs/min</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Filtration efficiency up to 5 µm / 200µin</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Particle uptake 1,3 kg / 2.9 lbs</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Work cycle 4.5 min</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Suction depth ~ 35 cm / ~ 13.8 in</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight 7,7 kg / 17 lbs</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Temperature max. 200°C / 392°F</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Material Stainless steel 1.4301</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,11500,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Fryers, Kitchen Equipment",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/1820_vito-vm-oil-filter-system.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/6306_vito-vm-in-fryer.png",,,,,,,,,0,,"Vito Oil Filter System",Brand,"Vito Oil Filter System",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,10,0,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"VITO VM",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,15771,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011000001100010011010011100100110111001110110011,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14244,simple,,,"Suitable for all fryers with heavy sediment - VITO VL",1,0,visible,"The VITO VL cleans the oil and provides an easy and hygienic filtration in the kitchen. Like every VITO oil filter system the VITO VL provides a microfiltration up to 5 µm (200µin). As an additional feature no chemicals are needed to clean the oil, which preserves the optimal taste of the fried dishes. The unique design makes sure the VITO can handle temperatures up to 200°C (392°F) and provides highest safety at work, because of avoiding direct contact with the hot oil. After filtration the oil can be immediately used for frying again.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Suitable for all fryers with heavy sediment - VITO VL</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• <strong>Benefits:</strong></p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Increases the lifetime of your oil</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Improves taste and quality</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Saves time and labor</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• <strong>Specifications:</strong></p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Normal usage Ideal for fryers up to 70 lbs</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Filtration power</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• up to 100l/min /</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 220.5 lbs/min</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Filtration efficiency up to 200µin</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Particle uptake 5.5 lbs</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Work cycle 4.5 min</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Suction depth ~ 17.7 in</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight 19.4 lbs</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Temperature max. 392 °F</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Material Stainless steel 1.4301</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,14200,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Fryers, Kitchen Equipment",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/1681_vito-vl-frying-oil-filter.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/6801_vito-vl-without-drip-pan.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/2488_vito-vl-filtration-process.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/5786_vito-vl-in-fryer.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/1524_vito-vl-in-fryer-with-lorena.png",,,,,,,,,0,,"Vito Oil Filter System",Brand,"Vito Oil Filter System",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,10,0,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"VITO VL",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,15772,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011001100100110011010011001100100110011011100110,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14250,simple,,,"Tank volume 40 - VITO XS",1,0,visible,"The VITO XS cleans the oil, stores it in its 40 l (73lbs) tank and provides an easy and hygienic transport in the kitchen. Because of its innovative vacuum-filtration technology, particles remain in the filter in a dry condition. Like every VITO oil filter system the XS provides a microfiltration up to 5 µm (200µin). The unique design makes sure the XS can handle temperatures up to 200°C (392°F) and provides highest safety at work, because of avoiding direct contact with the hot oil. After filtration the oil can easily be pumped back into the fryer.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Tank volume 40 - VITO XS</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• <strong>Benefits:</strong></p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Increases the lifetime of your oil</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Improves taste and quality</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Saves time and labor</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• <strong>Specifications</strong></p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Normal usage Ideal for catering industry and bakeries or high frying volume</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Filtration power up to 30 l/min</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 66 lbs/min</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Filtration efficiency up to 5µm / 200µin</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Pumping capacity up to 35 l/min</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 77 lbs/min</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Tank Volume 40 l / 73 lbs</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Particle uptake 10,7 kg / 23.6lbs</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight 45 kg / 99 lbs</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Temperature max. 200°C / 392°F</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Material Stainless steel 1.4301</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,28000,"COOKING LINE, Kitchen Equipment",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/8241_vito-xs.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/8356_vito-x-handle.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/7292_vito-x-side-view.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/1773_vito-x-cover-open.png",,,,,,,,,0,,"Vito Oil Filter System",Brand,"Vito Oil Filter System",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,15,0,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"VITO XS",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,15773,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,yes," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011011001111011001001100100110000111000111001100,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14255,simple,,,"Tank volume 75 - VITO XM",1,0,visible,"<strong>Tank volume 75 - VITO XM</strong>\nThe VITO XM cleans the oil, stores it in its 75 l (137 lbs) tank and provides an easy and hygienic transport in the kitchen. Because of its innovative vacuum-filtration technology, particles remain in the filter in a dry condition. Like every VITO oil filter system the XM provides a microfiltration up to 5 µm (200µin). The unique design makes sure the XM can handle temperatures up to 200°C (392°F) and provides highest safety at work, because of avoiding direct contact with the hot oil. After filtration the oil can easily be pumped back into the fryer automatically.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Tank volume 75 - VITO XM</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• <strong>Benefits:</strong></p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Increases the lifetime of your oil</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Improves taste and quality</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Saves time and labor</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• <strong>Specifications</strong></p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Normal usage Ideal for catering industry and bakeries or high frying volume</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Filtration power up to 30 l/min</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 66 lbs/min</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Filtration efficiency up to 5 µm / 200µin</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Pumping capacity up to 35 l/min</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 77 lbs/min</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Tank Volume 75 l / 137lbs</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Particle uptake 10,7 kg / 23.6lbs</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight 55,8 kg / 123 lbs</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Temperature max. 200°C / 392°F</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Material Stainless steel 1.4301</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,30000,"Kitchen Equipment, Uncategorized",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/8582_vito-xm.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/8356_vito-x-handle-1.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/1773_vito-x-cover-open-1.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/7292_vito-x-side-view-1.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/2206_vito-x-cover-handle.png",,,,,,,,,0,,"Vito Oil Filter System",Brand,"Vito Oil Filter System",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,10,0,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"VITO XM",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,15774,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,yes," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110110001010010010001001011100100111101101100110,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14261,simple,,,"Tank volume 120 - VITO XL",1,0,visible,"<strong>Tank volume 120 - VITO XL</strong>\nThe VITO XL cleans the oil, stores it in its 120 l (219 lbs) tank and provides an easy and hygienic transport in the kitchen. Because of its innovative vacuum-filtration technology, particles remain in the filter in a dry condition. Like every VITO oil filter system the XL provides a microfiltration up to 5 µm (200µin). The unique design makes sure the XL can handle temperatures up to 200°C (392°F) and provides highest safety at work, because of avoiding direct contact with the hot oil. After filtration the oil can easily be pumped back into the fryer automatically.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Tank volume 120 - VITO XL</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Benefits:</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Increases the lifetime of your oil</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Improves taste and quality</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Saves time and labor</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Specifications</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Normal usage Ideal for catering industry and bakeries or high frying volume</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Filtration power up to 30 l/min</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 66 lbs/min</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Filtration efficiency up to 5 µm / 200µin</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Pumping capacity up to 35 l/min</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 77 lbs/min</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Tank Volume 120 l / 219 lbs</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Particle uptake 10,7 kg / 23.6 lbs</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight 64 kg / 141 lbs</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Temperature max. 200°C / 392°F</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Material Stainless steel 1.4301</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,32000,"COOKING LINE, Kitchen Equipment",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/4471_vito-xl.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/7292_vito-x-side-view-2.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/8356_vito-x-handle-2.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/1773_vito-x-cover-open-2.png",,,,,,,,,0,,"Vito Oil Filter System",Brand,"Vito Oil Filter System",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,15,0,0,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"VITO XL",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,yes," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110010011001010010010011001100110110010111100110,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14266,simple,,,"Frying oil tester and temperature measurement - VITO FT 440",1,0,visible,"The FT 440 determines the temperature and the quality of your frying oil. Measuring the ""Total Polar Material"" (TPM) content in the oil, the tester gives you an accurate overview of the quality of your frying medium in a percentage value. The FT 440 comes with a top light which works after the traffic light principle and gives clear warning when it is time to dispose your fat. Never change your oil too early or too late again.\n\nThe FT 440 provides easy measurement and saves oil.\n\nMeasure the quality and temperature of your oil\nChange your oil at the right time\nQuick and reliable measuring results\nSupports HACCP quality standards\nErgonomic and sturdy design\nHigh degree of protection (IP67)\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(101px, 119px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Frying oil tester and temperature measurement - VITO FT 440</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Specifications</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dimensions 54 x 22 x 314 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Parameters % TPM, °C/°F</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Resolution 0.5% TMP, 0.1 °C/°F</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Range TPM 0 - 40%</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Range °C/°F 50°C - 200°C / 122°F - 392°F</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Accuracy ±2.0% TPM, ±1°C/°F</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Battery 3V Lithium (CR 2477)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• IP Code IP 67</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Alarm 3-color traffic light function</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(973px, 323px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,2100,"ACCESSORIES, Kitchen Equipment",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/3270_ft-440-frying-oil-tester.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/2261_ft-440-traffic-light-alarm.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/2261_ft-440-traffic-light-alarm1.png",,,,,,,,,0,,"Vito Oil Filter System",Brand,"Vito Oil Filter System",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,71,0,0,,"Frying oil tester and temperature measurement - VITO FT 440,جهاز اختبار زيت القلي وقياس درجة الحرارة",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"VITO FT 440",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011100001111100001111100011110011100110000011000,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14270,simple,,,"Frying oil tester and temperature measurement - VITO oiltester",1,0,visible,"The VITO oiltester determines the temperature and the quality of your frying oil. Measuring the ""Total Polar Material"" (TPM) content in the oil, the tester gives you an accurate overview of the quality of your frying medium in a percentage value. The VITO oiltester comes with a colored display which works after the traffic light principle and gives clear warning when it is time to dispose your fat. Never change your oil too early or too late again.\n\n•Measure the quality and temperature of your oil\n•Change your oil at the right time\n•Quick and reliable measuring results\n•Supports HACCP quality standards\n•Ergonomic and sturdy design\n•High degree of protection (IP65)\n•Clear alarms via colored display using the traffc light principle\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(65px, 48px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(418px, 111px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Frying oil tester and temperature measurement - VITO oiltester</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• <strong>Specifications</strong></p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dimensions 48 x 173 x 298 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Parameters % TPM, °C/°F</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Resolution 0.5% TMP, 0.1 °C/°F</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Range TPM 0 - 40%</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Range °C/°F 40°C - 200°C / 104°F - 392°F</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Accuracy ±2.0% TPM, ±1.5°C/°F</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Battery 2x 1.5V AAA</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• IP Code IP 65</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Alarm 3-color traffic light function</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(744px, 238px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,2200,"ACCESSORIES, Kitchen Equipment",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/1305_oiltester.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/6748_ft-440-and-oiltester-in-use.jpg",,,,,,,,,0,,"Vito Oil Filter System",Brand,"Vito Oil Filter System",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,71,0,0,,"Frying oil tester and temperature measurement - VITO oiltester,جهاز اختبار زيت القلي وقياس درجة الحرارة",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"VITO oiltester",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,15775,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,001011100111001101000010011011001101001111001001,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14273,simple,,,"Cellulose particle filter - 1 box = 100 pcs - VITO 30",1,0,visible,"<strong>Cellulose particle filter - 1 box = 100 pcs - VITO 30 </strong>\nVITO Particle filters\nThe VITO particle filters keep all particles that are filtered out of the oil by the frying oil filter machines.\nThey are placed inside the unit and can be used for several filtration cycles.\nThe filters are made of cellulose and are therefore biodegradable.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(33px, 183px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Cellulose particle filter - 1 box = 100 pcs - VITO 30</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• VITO Particle filters</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• The VITO particle filters keep all particles that are filtered out of the oil by the frying oil filter machines.\nThey are placed inside the unit and can be used for several filtration cycles.\nThe filters are made of cellulose and are therefore biodegradable.</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(756px, 23px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,755,"ACCESSORIES, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/1305_oiltester-1.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"Vito Oil Filter System",Brand,"Vito Oil Filter System",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,73,0,0,,"Cellulose particle filter - 1 box = 100 pcs - VITO 30,فلاتر ورق,ورق فلاتر",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"VITO 30",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596598,100010100110100011010001111001110100111000011101,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14275,simple,,,"IMPERIAL GAS FLOOR FRYER – IFS‐40 - LPG",1,0,visible,"IMPERIAL GAS FLOOR FRYER – IFS‐40 - LPG freestanding tube fired fryer with large heat transfer area heats oil quickly producing a better tasting product with less oil absorption and a fast recovery to desired temperature. It has a large cool zone to capture particles and holds particles out of the fry zone to reduces taste transfer. The robot welding of the fry pots virtually eliminates leaks and ensures a perfect finish every time.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• IMPERIAL GAS FLOOR FRYER – IFS‐40 - LPG</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Capacity 22 litres</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Output 32kgs chips per hour</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Temperature range 93 – 204C</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Nickle basket size 159 x 305 x 133 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 2 Large nickle basket with polyurethane coated handles</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Large cool zone area below tubes</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Very fast heating time for oil</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Full heat shield behind the control panel</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cool zone captures food particles prolonging oil life</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Large heat transfer area rapidly heats oil</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Fine mesh crumb screen</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• No tube fired burners and no air shutter adjustments needed</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• High efficiency cast iron tube-fired burners</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Precision welded on the outside of the frypot.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Welds are robotically welded for consistency</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Millivolt temperature control circuit.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Full heat shield behind control panel</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Stainless steel double panel door</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Recessed bottom for drain accessibility</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Comes with legs, castors optional see below</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Stainless steel exterior, baskets, hanger and frypot</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight 100kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Natural or LPG gas selectable from options below</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Gas 105,000 BTU’s 31kW, 3/4″ BSP</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(573px, 270px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(931px, 1px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,6800,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Fryers, Kitchen Equipment, Limited Sale, Special Offer",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/IMPERIAL-GAS-FLOOR-FRYER-–-IFS‐40-LPG.png,,,,,,,,,0,,IMPERIAL,Brand,IMPERIAL,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,54,0,0,,"IMPERIAL GAS FLOOR FRYER – IFS‐40 - LPG,مقلاة غاز إمبيريال",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"IFS‐40 - LPG",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734597011,011000001100110010011001100110011111001101100110,false,,,,,,,,salescountdowntimer,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14277,simple,,,"Merrychef conneX ® 12e",1,0,visible,"Specification : Triple heating - microwave / hot air heating / hot air jet, cooking speed 12 times faster than ordinary oven; Convected heat, Planar Plumes, impingement air and microwave energy -achieving cook times that are 12x times than conventional ovens,The image menu and touch screen make cooking simple and fast, ideal for coffee shops, front kitchens, convenience stores, bakeries and other placeswhere kitchen space is limited;Ideal for coffee shops, food courts, convenience stores, bakeries etc;.• Dimension (cm): 40.60 x 53.7 x 58.7• Weight (kg): 60.7• Power: 230V/50Hz/1Ph• Manufactured in China• Parts from UKIncluded Accessories:• 1 x Cook plate liner• 1 x Solid Cook Plate• 1 x Guarded Paddle with supporting sidewalls• 1 x Solid Base Basket\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(17px, 146px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<strong>Specifications</strong>\nHigh speed Technology® combines three heat technologies:\n-Microwave\n-Convection\n-Tuned impingement.\nMICROWAVE POWER\n• Microwave setting options: Off and 5-100% in 1% increments.\n• Microwave distribution system uses a rotating active\nantenna to ensure even heating throughout the food.\nCONVECTED HEAT\n• Temperature setting options: Off and 212°F (100°C) to 500°F\n(260°C) in 1°C increments.\n• The Heat distribution system is via Tuned Impingement,\nensuring the most even browning.\nVENTILATION\n• Ventless certification. EPA 202 tested (8 hr).\n• Internal catalytic filtration to limit grease and\nodour emissions.\neasyTouch® 2.0 CONTROL SYSTEM\n• Icon driven, HD colour touch screen control panel with\nunlimited storage for multi-stage cooking profiles.\n• Each cooking profile offers up to six (6) stages with\nprogrammable cooking times, microwave power settings and\nwritten and/or pictorial user instructions for each stage.\n• Self diagnostics capability to monitor components.\n• Easy menu updates or data transfer via USB memory stick\nand KitchenConnect cloud\n\n<strong>Features</strong>\n• The conneX®12e is our versatile entry\nmodel, for high speed cooking with\npre-programmed menus.\n• An all-in-one unit ideally suited to cook,\ntoast, grill and reheat food, eliminating the\nneed for other appliances.\n• Cooking up to 70% faster than other\ncooking methods it can provide hot food\non demand.\n• It has the a large cavity 30.5cm x 30.5cm\n(12” x 12”) to oven width 40.7 cm (16”) ratio,\nand fits on a 600mm worktop, perfect\nwhen space is at a premium.\n• Suitable for front-of-house, operating\nquietly and easy to install due to ventless\ncooking capabilities through a built-in\ncatalytic converter, eliminates the need for\nan extraction fan.\n• Cool to touch exterior makes it safe to\nlocate anywhere with no need to allow\nspace around the unit.\n• Easy to operate with a 7” HD widescreen\ndisplay and new generation easyTouch®2.0,\nicon driven controller, ensuring consistent,\nhigh quality dishes.\n• Easy to clean, with on oven pictorial\ninstructions.\n• Patented easy access front\nmounted monitored air filter.\n• Wi-fi/ethernet connected with\naccess to KitchenConnect cloud\nfor easy menu updates (or, via\na USB memory stick).\n• Available in Matt black only.",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,29000,"COOKING LINE, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/PRODUCT-IMAGE.webp,,,,,,,,,0,,merrychef,Brand,merrychef,1,1,,,,,default,1,2,0,,10,0,0,,"MERRY CHEF OVEN E1S BLACK,فرن ميكروويف,فرن عالي السرع",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"E1S BLACK",field_6387359a51f50,yes,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,yes,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011101000111111010000000110110001011100101001011,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14280,simple,,,"Merrychef conneX ® 12",1,0,visible,"<strong>Merrychef conneX 12</strong>\n \nThe most compact high speed oven, with the fastest speeds.\nThe very latest in high speed ovens, Merrychef conneX® 12 delivers consistent, high quality food, up to 80% faster than conventional cooking methods.\n\nIts compact, and stylish design, with cool-to-touch sides, allows it to fit anywhere. The 12” x 12” cavity sits in a 14” width oven on a standard 600mm worktop. It’s easy to install, with ventless technology, no need for a ventilation hood, and a standard power unit will work off a 13/16 Amp plug.\n\nThe new high definition 7” operating screen, sits in a robust glass surround, and showcases the new easyTouch® 2.0 software. The conneX range delivers the most intuitive operating controller, it works just like a mobile phone, and along with over 100 pre-programmed recipes, operators are very quickly able to deliver consistent, delicious results with every order.\n\nBorn connected, the conneX® range comes with Wi-fi and ethernet connectivity as standard, and offers free subscription for the first 12 months after purchase, to the industry leading Welbilt KitchenConnect® platform enabling the ovens to be monitored and menus to be updated remotely.\n\nLike all Merrychef high speed ovens the new Merrychef conneX® 12 is easy to install, ventless, operates quietly, has cool-to-touch exterior, quick pre-heat and cool down times, low energy usage in standby, providing unbeatable value for money.","<strong>Technical Specifications</strong>\nconneX®12 High Power\nW x D x H	14″ x 251/2” x 243/4“\n35.6cm x 64.8cm x 62.9cm\nWeight	111 lb\n50.3 kg\nPower Output	N/A\nPower Input Type	Electric\nPrimary Power Input	220-240 V x 60 Hz x 1 PH\n230 V x 50 Hz x 1 PH\nCertifications	CEUL\nconneX®12 Standard Power\nW x D x H	14″ x 251/2” x 243/4“\n35.6cm x 64.8cm x 62.9cm\nWeight	111 lb\n50.3 kg\nPower Output	N/A\nPower Input Type	Electric\nPrimary Power Input	220-240 V x 60 Hz x 1 PH\n230 V x 50 Hz x 1 PH\nCertifications	CEUL\n\n<strong>Features</strong>\nMost versatile, high speed oven on the market\nAn all-in-one unit ideally suited to rapidly cook, toast, grill, and reheat fresh or frozen food, eliminating the need for other appliances\nCooking up to 20x faster than other cooking methods\nLargest 30.5cm x 30.5cm (12” cavity with a 14” wide footprint\nFits on a 600mm worktop\nSuitable for front-of-house, operating quietly and easy to install due to ventless cooking capabilities through a built-in catalytic converter, eliminates the need for an extraction fan\nCool to touch exterior makes it safe to locate anywhere with no need to allow space around the unit.\nEasy to operate with a 7” HD widescreen display and new generation easyTouch®2.0, icon driven controller, ensuring consistent, high quality dishes.\nVery easy to clean stainless steel cavity with large rounded corners.\nPatented easy access front mounted air filter.\nWiFi/ethernet connected with access to KitchenConnect cloud for easy menu update (or update via a USB memory stick).\n",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,36499,"COOKING LINE, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/merry-chef.png,,,,,,,,,0,,merrychef,Brand,merrychef,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,13,0,0,,"MERRY CHEF OVEN E2S BLACK,فرن عالي السرع,فرن ميكروويف",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E2S,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110100011010001100001001111100101100110101001011,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14283,simple,,,"MERRYCHEF OVEN CLEANER ENGLISH LABEL",1,0,visible,"The MERRYCHEF OVEN CLEANER ENGLISH LABEL is a specially formulated cleaning solution designed to effortlessly remove grease, grime, and stubborn residues from your Merrychef oven. This powerful cleaner is crafted with precision, ensuring optimal cleanliness without compromising the integrity of your oven's surfaces.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(22px, 47px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• MERRYCHEF OVEN CLEANER ENGLISH LABEL</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Specification : MERRYCHEF OVEN\nCLEANER-ENGLISH LABEL</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(853px, 3px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,165,"ACCESSORIES, Kitchen Equipment",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/MERRYCHEF-OVEN-PROTECTOR_.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/MERRYCHEF-OVEN-PROTECTOR-GB.png",,,,,,,,,0,,merrychef,Brand,merrychef,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,72,0,0,,"MERRYCHEF OVEN CLEANER ENGLISH LABEL,واقي فرن,تنظيف فرن",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"OVEN CLEANER",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596219,011001110011011001100011001110001111001100000110,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14286,simple,,,"MERRYCHEF OVEN PROTECTOR GB  ENGLISH LABEL",1,0,visible,"The MERRYCHEF OVEN PROTECTOR GB ENGLISH LABEL is a high-quality accessory designed to enhance the performance and durability of your Merrychef oven. Crafted with precision, this protector serves as a reliable barrier against spills, stains, and potential damage to your oven's interior.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• MERRYCHEF OVEN PROTECTOR GB ENGLISH LABEL</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Specification : MERRYCHEF OVEN PROTECTOR GB ENGLISH LABEL</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,250,"ACCESSORIES, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/MERRYCHEF-OVEN-PROTECTOR-GB.png,,,,,,,,,0,,merrychef,Brand,merrychef,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,72,0,0,,"MERRYCHEF OVEN PROTECTOR GB ENGLISH LABEL,واقي فرن,تنظيف فرن",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"OVEN PROTECTOR",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596219,011001110010011001100011000110011111001100011001,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14287,simple,,,"MERRYCHEF OVEN PROTECTOR GB  ENGLISH LABEL (Copy)",1,0,visible,"The MERRYCHEF OVEN PROTECTOR GB ENGLISH LABEL is a high-quality accessory designed to enhance the performance and durability of your Merrychef oven. Crafted with precision, this protector serves as a reliable barrier against spills, stains, and potential damage to your oven's interior.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(71px, 58px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• MERRYCHEF OVEN PROTECTOR GB ENGLISH LABEL</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Specification : MERRYCHEF OVEN PROTECTOR GB ENGLISH LABEL</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(1149px, 307px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,167,"ACCESSORIES, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/MERRYCHEF-OVEN-PROTECTOR-GB.png,,,,,,,,,0,,,,,,,,,,,default,1,1,0,,57,0,0,,"MERRYCHEF OVEN PROTECTOR GB ENGLISH LABEL (Copy),واقي فرن,تنضيف فرن",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"OVEN PROTECTOR",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no,,,,,,,,,,,,,1734596219,011001110010011001100011000110011111001100011001,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14294,simple,,,"LAUNDRY DRYERS (Up to 460 Litres) - SR-22 M E",1,0,visible,"SR-22 M E Laundry Dryer: The SR-22 M E is a powerful, high-capacity dryer designed to handle up to 460 liters of laundry. Featuring advanced drying technology and a variety of cycles, it efficiently dries a range of fabric types while preserving their quality. This dryer offers quick and energy-efficient operation, making it ideal for large households or commercial use. With its robust build and intuitive controls, the SR-22 M E ensures ease of use and reliable performance for all your drying needs.","'- LAUNDRY DRYERS (Up to 460 Litres) - SR-22 M E\n- Capaity: 22-24 kg\n- Easy Control """"M"""".\n- All models offer reverse motor rotation. This makes the drying process more efficient and offers greater uniformity in the clothes drying process.\n- The reverse rotation drum system is performed by the inverter.\n- DRUM: Ø Drum: 835 mm / Drum length: 800 mm /\n- Drum volume: 440 l / Ø Door : 574 mm\n- POWER: (Electric / Gas)\n- Installed heating power: 24 kW / Gas power: 105775,6 Btu/hr\n- Installed electrical power: 24,97 KW / Gas Power: 0,97 KW\n- Installed heating power gas: 31 kW\n- Evaporation capacity: 17 l/hr / For Gas : 20 l/hr\n- Hourly output: 34 Kg/h / For Gas : 40 Kg/hr\n- Ø Gas inlet: 1/2'' BSPP ISO 228-1\nSTEAM POWER:\n- Installed heating power steam: 49,2 kW\n- Installed electrical power: 0,97 kW\nVENTILATION: Nominal air flow: 1200 m³/h , Air outlet Ø: 200mm\n- Fan motor power: 0,55 kW\n- Total max heat dissipation: 2,4 kW\n- Front pannel max heat dissipation: 1,68 kW\n- Voltage: 400V 3N 50 Hz\n- Net / Gross weight: 210 / 230 kg\n- Dim: 890 x 1255 x 1812 mm.\nSR-22 M E / FOGOR PROFESSIONAL / Italy made.""",,,taxable,,0,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,20315,"Kitchen Equipment, LAUNDRY & DISH WASHER, LAUNDRY & DISH WASHER > Laundry Machines",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ADVANCE-SR-22-TP2-E-1.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ADVANCE-SR-22-TP2-E.png",,,,,,,,,0,,"Fagor Professional",Brand,Fagor,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,51,0,0,,"LAUNDRY DRYERS,LAUNDRY DRYERS (Up to 460 Litres) - SR-22 M E",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"SR-22 M E",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596801,011010011001110010011001111110000110011001001001,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14297,simple,,,"LAUNDRY WASHING - LBS-27 TP2 E 400V 3N50/60Hz",1,0,visible,"DENOMINATION:\nSanitary barrier washer of 27 kg electric\nDESCRIPTION :\n- Installed between two separate areas, avoids all contact between dirty\n(infectious) linen and the clean linen, and any type of cro\nsscontamination during the process.\n- External steel casing with grey coating (skinplate), stainless steel,\neasy to clean finish.\n- 20 programs pre-set from factory.\n- Telemetry as standard.\n- 8 signals for automatic liquid dosing, programmable in time and delay.\n6 extra signals available optionally.\n- Optimum load. Intelligent weighing system.\n- Possibility of configuring three levels of savings.\n- Central drain.\n- Technical menu. Statistics, alarms, autotest, data recovery for\ntechnicians and maintenance.\n- Motor with variable-frequency drive incorporated.\n- Prepared for Wet cleaning.\n- FagorKonnect - Standard IOT connectivity.\n- TP2 processor with two 7” screens, a touch screen for programming\non the dirty linen loading side, and an information screen on the\nunloading side in the clean zone.\n- 3 water inlets.\n- Automatic drum positioning with motor brake to facilitate the loading\nand unloading operation\n800 mm loading height.\n- Designed for water recovery tanks. Low water consumption.\n- 1-compartment horizontal spin drum.\n- Loading and unloading doors. Door locks with safety opening\n- Electrical part to the left, mechanical to the right, connections at the\ntop.\n- Electric Heating System.Heated by means of stainless steel armoured\nheating elements.\nPOSSIBLE OPTIONS :\n- Voltage options BM\n- Accesories BM\n- Certification BM\n- Maritime wood packaging\n- STAINLESS STEEL CABINET\nPOSSIBLE ACCESSORIES:\n- LAUNDRY ACCESSORIES\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(131px, 83px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","LAUNDRY WASHING - LBS-27 TP2 E 400V 3N50/60Hz\nDIMENSIONS\nX Width 1