14299,simple,,,"LAUNDRY WASHING - LN-18 TP2",1,0,visible,"LN-18 TP2 Laundry Washing Machine: A high-efficiency, top-load washing machine designed for superior cleaning performance. The LN-18 TP2 features advanced washing technology, multiple wash cycles, and a large capacity drum, making it ideal for both small and large loads. Durable and user-friendly, it ensures effective stain removal while being energy and water-efficient, perfect for modern laundry needs.",". LAUNDRY WASHING - LN-18 TP2\n. Load capacity: 18-20 kg\n. VOLUME (L): 180\n. Touch Plus Control (TP2)\n- 7"""" Touch Plus TP2 control.\n- Steam Inlet 1/2"""" inch\n- Water Inlet: 3/4"""" inch\n- Drain 3"""" inch\n- 8 liquid dosing signals.\n- G-force 200.\n- Wash Speed / Spin Speed (r.p.m): 50/714\n- Drum and envelope in AISI-304 stainless steel.\n- Height Door Centre / Base / Diameter: 655 / 348 / 460 mm\n- Power: Motor: 2.2 / Heating Power: 12 KW\n- Total Electrical Power (Electric Mod.) 12.75 KW\n- Electrical Power (Hot Water And Steam Mod.): 2.2 Kw\n- Voltage: 380-415 V 3N 50/60 Hz\n- Net / Gross weight: 281 / 301 kg\n- Volume: 1.3 (m3)\n- Drum Size: 700 x 470 mm\n- Dim: 788 x 840 x 1307 mm.\nLN-18 TP2 / FOGOR PROFESSIONAL / Italy made.""",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,29706,"Kitchen Equipment, LAUNDRY & DISH WASHER",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Fagor-Normal-Spin-WM-LN11-LN14-LN18-TP2.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"Fagor Professional",Brand,Fagor,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,80,0,0,,"LAUNDRY WASHING,LAUNDRY WASHING - LN-18 TP2",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"LN-18 TP2",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596801,110100011000110010010011100100110010011111001011,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14301,simple,,,"LAUNDRY WASHING - LN-22 TP2",1,0,visible,"LN-22 TP2 Laundry Washing Machine: The LN-22 TP2 is a top-of-the-line washing machine, featuring a large capacity and advanced cleaning technology. Designed for maximum efficiency, it offers various wash cycles to accommodate different fabric types and load sizes. With a sleek design and user-friendly controls, this model ensures deep cleaning while being gentle on clothes. Energy and water-efficient, the LN-22 TP2 is perfect for households seeking superior laundry care.",". LAUNDRY WASHING - LN-22 TP2\n. Load capacity: 25/22 kg\n. VOLUME (L): 220\n. Touch Plus Control (TP2)\n- 7"""" Touch Plus TP2 control.\n- Steam Inlet 1/2"""" inch\n- Water Inlet: 3/4"""" inch\n- Drain 3"""" inch\n- 8 liquid dosing signals.\n- G-force 200.\n- Wash Speed / Spin Speed (r.p.m): 50/714\n- Drum and envelope in AISI-304 stainless steel.\n- Height Door Centre / Base / Diameter: 655 / 348 / 460 mm\n- Power: Motor: 2.2 / Heating Power: 12 KW\n- Total Electrical Power (Electric Mod.) 12.75 KW\n- Electrical Power (Hot Water And Steam Mod.): 2.2 Kw\n- Voltage: 380-415 V 3N 50/60 Hz\n- Net / Gross weight: 300 / 320 kg\n- Volume: 1.5 (m3)\n- Drum Size: 700 x 570 mm\n- Dim: 788 x 950 x 1307 mm.\nLN-22 TP2 / FOGOR PROFESSIONAL / Italy made.""",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,30330,"Kitchen Equipment, LAUNDRY & DISH WASHER, LAUNDRY & DISH WASHER > Laundry Machines",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Fagor-Normal-Spin-WM-LN11-LN14-LN18-TP2.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"Fagor Professional",Brand,Fagor,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,76,0,0,,"LAUNDRY WASHING,LAUNDRY WASHING - LN-22 TP2",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"LN-22 TP2",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596801,110100011000110010010011100100110010011111001011,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14302,simple,,,"LAUNDRY IRONING AND FOLDING - PS-35/200 M PLUS GR CE LPG 230/400V 3/3N",1,0,visible,"DENOMINATION:\nWall flatwork ironer with roller diameter 32,5 cm and length 200 gas\nheating\nDESCRIPTION :\nMAINTENANCE CARE\nSimple, reliable and accesible mechanism in which the components\nhave been designed and manufactured with the highest quality and\nprestige.\nINVERTER\nFrequency inverter in all models.\nHIGH-TECH ROLL\nHigh-performance steel roller.\nM ELECTRONIC CONTROL\nIntuitive and easy to use.\n2 selectable operating modes:\n· Manual Mode: selection of speed and temperature.\n· Auto Mode: automatic adjustment of the ironing speed according to\nthe temperature selected.\n- Front insertion and reception of linen.\n- Variable-frequency drive to control ironing speed.\n- Safety protector for hands.\n- Automatic stop on cooling (80 ºC).\n- Unit exterior constructed in sandwich panel and stainless steel.\n- Powerful exhaust extraction system.\n- Insertion and ironing belts in Nomex for easy operation, high quality\nironing and great durability.\n- 7 ironing speeds, adjustable by variablefrequency drive, for selection\nbetween 1.5 and 10 m/ minute, PLUS models up to 12 mts/min.\n- Reverse roll standard.\n- Table height of 990 mm.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(367px, 174px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","LAUNDRY IRONING AND FOLDING - PS-35/200 M PLUS GR CE LPG 230/400V 3/3N\nDIMENSIONS\nX Width 2552 mm X Gross width 2740 mm\nY Depth 685 mm Y Gross depth 770 mm\nZ Height 1112 mm Z Gross height 1400 mm\nNet Weight 438,0 kg Gross Weight 438,0 kg\nNet Volume 1,95 M3 Gross Volume 2,95 M3\nGAS TECHNICAL SPECIFICATIONS\nCau.G30/A.Cal.24 3,130 KGH\nCau.G20/A.Mot.22 4,240 MQH\nRegulated -85999,14 kCal/h\nELECTRICITY TECHNICAL SPECIFICATIONS\nEngine power 0,520 KW\nElectric power 0,520 KW\nAmperage (A) 6A\nVoltage 400V - 3N\nElectric frequency 50/60Hz\nCONNECTIONS TECHNICA