14308,simple,,,"LAUNDRY ACCESSORIES - TROLLEY CFM-2",1,0,visible,"DENOMINATION:\nTrolley for wet laundry with lifting bottom 50 kg\nDESCRIPTION :\n- Trolley for laundry transport and storage\n- Racks and trolleys for handling laundry easier and helping to prevent\nrepetitive stress injuries.\n- Ergonomic laundry trolleys are suitable for laundries, hospitals,\nnursing homes, hotels, spas, etc. Their design ensures that the trolley\nwill be close to the equipment so that the clothing does not end up on\nthe floor.\n- Trolley for wet laundry.\n- Trolley with lifting bottom.\n- Made of light alloy, anodised.\n- Mobile bottom.\n- With springs in the base of the trolley to maintain a constant level.\n- Two fixed wheels and two swivel casters.\n- Wheels diameter: 125 mm.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(829px, 148px);"" aria-expanded=""true"">\n<div id=""tippy-1"" style=""z-index: 100000200; visibility: visible; position: absolute; inset: auto auto 0px 0px; margin: 0px; transform: translate(399px, -20px);"" data-tippy-root="""">\n<div class=""tippy-box"" style=""max-width: 350px; transition-duration: 300ms;"" tabindex=""-1"" role=""mtttooltip"" data-state=""visible"" data-theme=""custom"" data-animation=""fade"" data-placement=""top"">\n<div class=""tippy-content"" style=""transition-duration: 300ms;"" data-state=""visible""><span dir=""rtl"">- رفوف وعربات لتسهيل التعامل مع الغسيل والمساعدة على منعه</span></div>\n<div class=""tippy-arrow"" style=""position: absolute; left: 0px; transform: translate(92px, 0px);""></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(164px, 109px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","LAUNDRY ACCESSORIES - TROLLEY CFM-2\nX Width 100 mm X Gross width 1010 mm\nY Depth 100 mm Y Gross depth 620 mm\nZ Height 100 mm Z Gross height 800 mm\nNet Weight 1,0 kg Gross Weight 60,0 kg\nNet Volume 0,52 M3 Gross Volume 0,50 M3\n<di