14310,simple,,,"Roasting and baking tray - 6013.1003",1,0,visible,"The TriLax aluminum unperforated baking tray by Rational boasts exceptional non-stick properties, ensuring an extended service life and robust performance. With its optimum non-stick coating, this tray facilitates browning and excels at temperatures up to 300°C. Its easy-to-clean design makes it ideal for baking a diverse range of pre-baked products.\n\nFrom succulent poultry and perfectly browned escalopes to flaky pastries and golden roast potatoes, this versatile roasting and baking sheet delivers uniform browning and ensures a juicy, crisp finish across an array of delectable dishes. Elevate your culinary creations with the reliability and efficiency of the TriLax baking tray.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","Dimensions\n\nBakery standard (400 × 600 mm)\n<ul>\n 	<li>Excels at temperatures up to 300°C</li>\n 	<li>Rational TriLax aluminum unperforated baking tray</li>\n 	<li>Optimum non-stick coating</li>\n</ul>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(434px, 99px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,580,"ACCESSORIES, Kitchen Equipment, ACCESSORIES > Tray",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/icombi-pro-accessories-roasting-and-baking-tray-1-1-gn-rational-99036-fix725x370.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Rational,Brand,Rational,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,57,0,0,,"Roasting and baking tray - 6013.1003,صينية التحميص والخبز",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,6013.1003,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011000100111011001010110000100111000110110110110,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
