14315,simple,,,"Roasting and baking tray - 6013.2103",1,0,visible,"The TriLax aluminum unperforated baking tray by Rational boasts exceptional non-stick properties, ensuring an extended service life and robust performance. With its optimum non-stick coating, this tray facilitates browning and excels at temperatures up to 300°C. Its easy-to-clean design makes it ideal for baking a diverse range of pre-baked products.\n\nFrom succulent poultry and perfectly browned escalopes to flaky pastries and golden roast potatoes, this versatile roasting and baking sheet delivers uniform browning and ensures a juicy, crisp finish across an array of delectable dishes. Elevate your culinary creations with the reliability and efficiency of the TriLax baking tray.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(930px, 188px);"" aria-expanded=""true"">\n<div id=""tippy-1"" style=""z-index: 100000200; visibility: visible; position: absolute; inset: auto auto 0px 0px; margin: 0px; transform: translate(399px, -20px);"" data-tippy-root="""">\n<div class=""tippy-box"" style=""max-width: 350px; transition-duration: 300ms;"" tabindex=""-1"" role=""mtttooltip"" data-state=""visible"" data-theme=""custom"" data-animation=""fade"" data-placement=""top"">\n<div class=""tippy-content"" style=""transition-duration: 300ms;"" data-state=""visible""><span dir=""rtl"">من الدواجن النضرة والإسكالوب ذات اللون البني المثالي إلى المعجنات القشرية والبطاطس المشوية الذهبية، توفر صينية التحميص والخبز متعددة الاستخدامات هذه تحميصًا موحدًا وتضمن لمسة نهائية عصيرية ونضرة عبر مجموعة من الأطباق اللذيذة.</span></div>\n<div class=""tippy-arrow"" style=""position: absolute; left: 0px; transform: translate(92px, 0px);""></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","Dimensions\n\n2/1 GN (650 × 530 mm)\n<ul>\n 	<li>Excels at temperatures up to 300°C</li>\n 	<li>Rational TriLax aluminum unperforated baking tray</li>\n 	<li>Optimum non-stick coating</li>\n</ul>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"