14318,simple,,,"AUTOMATIC ORANGE JUICER ZUMEX",1,0,visible,"AUTOMATIC ORANGE JUICER ZUMEX : At Zumex, we believe in a healthier world. That is why, after nearly 35 years of experience in the design of juicing solutions for fruits and vegetables, our goal is to continue improving the well-being of people. Professional equipment for squeezing fruits and vegetables in places such as bars, cafes and bakeries. Small, smart and stylish.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(965px, 38px);"" aria-expanded=""true"">\n<div id=""tippy-1"" style=""z-index: 100000200; visibility: visible; position: absolute; inset: 0px auto auto 0px; margin: 0px; transform: translate(399px, 20px);"" data-tippy-root="""">\n<div class=""tippy-box"" style=""max-width: 350px; transition-duration: 300ms;"" tabindex=""-1"" role=""mtttooltip"" data-state=""visible"" data-theme=""custom"" data-animation=""fade"" data-placement=""bottom"">\n<div class=""tippy-content"" style=""transition-duration: 300ms;"" data-state=""visible""><span dir=""rtl"">عصارة البرتقال الأوتوماتيكية زومكس: في زوميكس، نحن نؤمن بعالم أكثر صحة.</span></div>\n<div class=""tippy-arrow"" style=""position: absolute; left: 0px; transform: translate(92px, 0px);""></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• AUTOMATIC ORANGE JUICER ZUMEX</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cap: Fruits Capacity Per Min: M/S KIT: 18; XS KIT: 36</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Feeder Capacity: 3-6 Oranges / 7-8 Limes</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power: 100W 220-240V, 0.134 HP; Weight 32 kg&lt;/p</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 300X480X537 Mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Brand: Zumex</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Origin: Spain&lt;/p</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(231px, 16px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable