14333,simple,,,"Roasting and baking tray - 6013.1103",1,0,visible,"The TriLax aluminum unperforated baking tray by Rational boasts exceptional non-stick properties, ensuring an extended service life and robust performance. With its optimum non-stick coating, this tray facilitates browning and excels at temperatures up to 300°C. Its easy-to-clean design makes it ideal for baking a diverse range of pre-baked products.\n\nFrom succulent poultry and perfectly browned escalopes to flaky pastries and golden roast potatoes, this versatile roasting and baking sheet delivers uniform browning and ensures a juicy, crisp finish across an array of delectable dishes. Elevate your culinary creations with the reliability and efficiency of the TriLax baking tray.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(196px, 157px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","Dimensions\n\n1/1 GN (325 × 530 mm)\n<ul>\n 	<li>Excels at temperatures up to 300°C</li>\n 	<li>Rational TriLax aluminum unperforated baking tray</li>\n 	<li>Optimum non-stick coating</li>\n</ul>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(1134px, 1px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,520,"ACCESSORIES, Kitchen Equipment, ACCESSORIES > Tray",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/icombi-pro-accessories-roasting-and-baking-tray-1-1-gn-rational-99036-fix725x370.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,,,,,,,,,,default,1,1,0,,57,0,0,,"Roasting and baking tray - 6013.1103,صينية بلاك ستون,صينية التحميص والخبز",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"6013.1103 <span style=""color: red; font-weight: 700; "">10 Qty coming within 45 days</span>",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no,,,,,,,,,,,,,,011000100111011001010110000100111000110110110110,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
