14335,simple,,,"ROBOT COOK - 43001R",1,0,visible,"The Robot Cook 43001R is a cutting-edge kitchen companion designed to revolutionize your cooking experience. This versatile robotic chef is equipped with advanced features, including precision chopping, stirring, and blending capabilities. With a user-friendly interface and customizable settings, it effortlessly handles various culinary tasks, saving you time and effort in the kitchen. Elevate your cooking with the efficiency and innovation of the Robot Cook 43001R.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""true"">\n<div id=""tippy-1"" style=""z-index: 100000200; position: absolute; margin: 0px;"" data-tippy-root="""">\n<div class=""tippy-box"" style=""max-width: 350px;"" role=""mtttooltip"" data-state=""visible"" data-theme=""custom"" data-animation=""fade"" data-placement=""bottom"">\n<div class=""tippy-content"" data-state=""visible""><span dir=""rtl"">يعتبر Robot Cook 43001R رفيق مطبخ متطور مصمم لإحداث ثورة في تجربة الطهي الخاصة بك.</span></div>\n<div class=""tippy-arrow"" style=""position: absolute; left: 0px;""></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• ROBOT COOK - 43001R</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power: 1800W-1Ph</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Induction motor 5 speed function: Variable speed from 100 to 3500 rpm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• High speed; Turbo/ Pulse of 4500 rpm R- mix blend speed from 100 to 500 rpm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Intermittent speed; slow speed blade rotation every 2 seconds</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Pulse; variable speed</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Voltage: 230V/ 50-60/1 UK plug</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• S/s bowl cutter 3.7 L with handle; liquid capacity 2.5 liters Gross weight 15 kg</p>\n<p 