14344,simple,,,"COMBI RANGE – POWER MIXER - MP350 COMBI ULTRA",1,0,visible,"The Robot Coupe MP350 Combi Ultra is a versatile and powerful power mixer designed for professional kitchens. It combines the functionalities of an immersion blender and a whisk, making it ideal for a wide range of food preparation tasks such as blending, pureeing, mixing, and whipping. The MP350 Combi Ultra features a robust 1 HP motor, a variable speed control, and an ergonomic handle for comfortable use. Its stainless steel construction ensures durability and easy cleaning, while the detachable blending arm and whisk attachment provide convenience and flexibility. This power mixer is perfect for chefs and food service professionals who require reliable and efficient equipment for high-volume food preparation.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• COMBI RANGE – POWER MIXER - MP350 COMBI ULTRA</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Self regulating speed system</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• all stainless steel knife</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• bell whisk and tube and foot with removable bell</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• delivered with 1 stainless steel wall support</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight: 7.9 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power: 440 watts 230V / 50 /1</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• UK plug Single phase</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Speed: 1500 to 9000 rpm in mixer function</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Speed: 250 to 1500 rpm in whisk function</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Length with tube 725 mm / with whisk 805 mm Ø 125 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Made by Robot Coupe, France</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,4025,"BAKERY LINE, BAKERY LINE > Bakery Mixers, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Blenders, COF