14352,simple,,,"DOUGH KNEADING MACHINE - HY.15",1,0,visible,"The HY.15 Dough Kneading Machine is a robust and efficient appliance designed to handle heavy-duty dough kneading tasks in commercial settings. With its powerful motor and large capacity, it effortlessly mixes and kneads large batches of dough with precision and consistency. Its durable construction and user-friendly interface make it an essential tool for bakeries, pizzerias, and other foodservice establishments. The HY.15 ensures reliable performance, saving time and effort while consistently delivering high-quality dough for a variety of culinary creations.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• DOUGH KNEADING MACHINE - HY.15</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Capacity: 20 Kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power: 0.37 kW - 0.5 Hp - 220 V - 50 HZ</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Stainless Bowl</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Stainless dough fork</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Easy to use and clean</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 760 x 500 x 730 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Model No. HY.15 / Mestro Horeca / Make in Turkey</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(631px, 163px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,1980,"BAKERY LINE, BAKERY LINE > Bakery Mixers, Kitchen Equipment",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/6-4.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/5-3.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/4-4-scaled.png",,,,,,,,,0,,Capinox,Brand,Capinox,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,71,0,,,"DOUGH KNEADING MACHINE - HY.15,الة عجن العجينة,آلة عجن العجين",,,,,,0,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,HY.15,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_65701746799