14360,simple,,,"DOUGH KNEADING MACHINE - HY.35",1,0,visible,"The HY.35 Dough Kneading Machine is a heavy-duty appliance designed for large-scale dough preparation in industrial settings. With its high-capacity bowl and powerful motor, it effortlessly mixes and kneads substantial quantities of dough with precision and consistency. Engineered for durability and efficiency, it offers advanced features and controls to tailor the kneading process to specific recipes and dough types. The HY.35 is the ultimate solution for bakeries, food production facilities, and other commercial enterprises seeking reliable performance and exceptional dough quality on a massive scale.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(21px, 131px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(560px, 203px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Capacity: 45 Kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power: 0.55 kW - 220 V - 50 HZ</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Stainless Bowl</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Stainless dough fork</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Easy to use and clean.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 960 x 640 x 900 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Model No. HY.35 / Mestro Horeca / Make in Turkey</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(638px, 333px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(1147px, 130px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,2750,3233,"BAKERY LINE, BAKERY LINE > Bakery Mixers, Kitchen Equipment, Special Offer",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/11-4.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/12-2.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/10-2.png