14364,simple,,,"La Marzocco Strada AV 3 Group Coffee Machine - AV 3",1,0,visible,"The La Marzocco Strada AV 3 Group Coffee Machine (AV 3) is a top-of-the-line espresso machine crafted for professional baristas and coffee enthusiasts. With its advanced technology and precision engineering, it delivers exceptional espresso quality and consistency. Featuring three group heads, it allows simultaneous brewing, maximizing efficiency during peak hours. The automatic volumetric dosing system ensures precise shot volumes, while customizable pre-infusion and brewing parameters offer control over extraction. The sleek design and robust construction make the Strada AV 3 a standout addition to any upscale cafe or coffee bar, offering unparalleled performance and reliability.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(581px, 74px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(709px, 199px);"" aria-expanded=""true"">\n<div id=""tippy-1"" style=""z-index: 100000200; visibility: visible; position: absolute; inset: auto auto 0px 0px; margin: 0px; transform: translate(399px, -20px);"" data-tippy-root="""">\n<div class=""tippy-box"" style=""max-width: 350px; transition-duration: 300ms;"" tabindex=""-1"" role=""mtttooltip"" data-state=""visible"" data-theme=""custom"" data-animation=""fade"" data-placement=""top"">\n<div class=""tippy-content"" style=""transition-duration: 300ms;"" data-state=""visible""><span dir=""rtl"">يضمن نظام الجرعات الحجمي الأوتوماتيكي الحصول على كميات دقيقة من الجرعات، في حين توفر معلمات التسريب المسبق والتخمير القابلة للتخصيص التحكم في عملية الاستخلاص.</span></div>\n<div class=""tippy-arrow"" style=""position: absolute; left: 0px; transform: translate(92px, 0px);""></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(257px, 44px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• La Marzocco Strada AV 3 Group Coffee Machine - AV 3</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 3-Group espresso machine.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Auto-volumetric programmable dosing.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Exposed saturated groups for increased temperature stability, ergonomics and workspace visibility.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dual PID allows you to electronically control coffee and steam boiler temperature.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Independent insulated boilers for each group head (x3) and dispensing steam.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Includes: Stainless steel portafilters, precision basket, and tamper.</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(940px, 250px);"" aria-expanded=""true"">\n<div id=""tippy-1"" style=""z-index: 100000200; visibility: visible; position: absolute; inset: auto auto 0px 0px; margin: 0px; transform: translate(399px, -20px);"" data-tippy-root="""">\n<div class=""tippy-box"" style=""max-width: 350px; transition-duration: 300ms;"" tabindex=""-1"" role=""mtttooltip"" data-state=""visible"" data-theme=""custom"" data-animation=""fade"" data-placement=""top"">\n<div class=""tippy-content"" style=""transition-duration: 300ms;"" data-state=""visible""><span dir=""rtl"">• يشتمل على: فلاتر القهوة المصنوعة من الفولاذ المقاوم للصدأ، وسلة دقيقة، ومكبس.</span></div>\n<div class=""tippy-arrow"" style=""position: absolute; left: 0px; transform: translate(92px, 0px);""></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(381px, 217px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(1235px, 92px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" styl