14366,simple,,,"La Marzocco Strada AV 2 Group Coffee Machine - AV 2",1,0,visible,"The La Marzocco Strada AV 2 Group Coffee Machine (AV 2) is a premium espresso machine designed for professional use in cafes and specialty coffee shops. Renowned for its precision engineering and advanced technology, it delivers exceptional espresso quality with consistency. Featuring two group heads, it enables simultaneous brewing for increased efficiency during busy periods. The automatic volumetric dosing system ensures precise shot volumes, while customizable pre-infusion and brewing parameters allow baristas to fine-tune their espresso extraction. With its sleek design and durable construction, the Strada AV 2 is a standout choice for establishments seeking high-performance espresso equipment.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(35px, 201px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• La Marzocco Strada AV 2 Group Coffee Machine - AV 2</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 2-Group Espresso Machine.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Exposed saturated groups for increased temperature stability, ergonomics and workspace visibility.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Auto-volumetric programmable dosing.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Independent Insulated boilers for each group head (X2) and dispensing steam.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Includes: Stainless steel portafilters, precision basket, and tamper.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Capacity: Steam boiler - 8.2L, Coffee Boiler - 1.3L.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 4600W three phase.</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(640px, 146px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(698px, 284px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,64500,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Coffee Machines, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/La-Marzocco-Strada-AV-2-Group-Coffee-Machine.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"La Marzocco",Brand,"La Marzocco",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,71,0,,,"La Marzocco Strada AV 2 Group Coffee Machine - AV 2,ماكينة اسبريسو,ماكينة الإسبريسو التقليدية",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"AV 2",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595055,111100100010010000110101001101001001101100111101,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14370,simple,,,"Mahlkonig EK43S Coffee Grinder Matte Black - EK43S",1,0,visible,"The Mahlkonig EK43S Coffee Grinder in Matte Black (EK43S) is a high-performance grinder designed for specialty coffee shops and discerning home baristas. Renowned for its precision and versatility, it features 98 mm flat burrs that deliver consistent particle size distribution for exceptional espresso and filter coffee extraction. The compact design of the EK43S makes it suitable for smaller spaces without compromising on performance. With stepless grind adjustment and a powerful motor, it offers unparalleled control and efficiency. The Matte Black finish adds a sleek and modern aesthetic to any coffee setup, making the Mahlkonig EK43S a standout choice for coffee enthusiasts seeking premium quality and style.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Mahlkonig EK43S Coffee Grinder Matte Black - EK43S</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Compact version of iconic EK43 coffee grinder, ideal for smaller cafes.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Burr type: 98mm Steel Flat.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Grinding Capacity: 19-21 grams of coffee per second.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Precise stepless grind adjustment.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Suitable for filter, espresso, or even Turkish-fine coffee grinding.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Capacity: Beans Hopper - 0.8 kg.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Color: Matte Black.</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(804px, 302px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,12390,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Coffee Grinder, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Mahlkonig-EK43S-Coffee-Grinder-Matte-Black.png,,,,,,,,,0,,MAHLKÖNIG,Brand,MAHLKÖNIG,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,12,0,,,"La Marzocco Mahlkonig EK43S Coffee Grinder Matte Black - EK43S,مطحنة القهوة,مطحنة قهوة",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,EK43S,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011001100110010011000110011001110001100111001101,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14372,simple,,,"La Marzocco Smart Water Filter 35 (Filter Head +  Cartridge - BWT)",1,0,visible,"The BWT Bestmax Smart Water Filter 35 is a comprehensive water filtration system designed to optimize water quality for coffee and espresso machines. This all-in-one solution combines a filter head and cartridge to effectively reduce scale buildup, chlorine, and other impurities that can affect the taste and performance of beverages. The Smart technology ensures precise water mineralization, enhancing the flavor and aroma of coffee while prolonging the lifespan of equipment. Easy to install and maintain, the BWT Bestmax Smart Water Filter 35 is an essential accessory for coffee professionals and enthusiasts seeking consistent and exceptional brewing results.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• BWT Bestmax Smart Water Filter 35 (Filter Head + Cartridge - BWT</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Special water filter system for cafes.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Features the new High-​Efficiency-​Technology (HET) ensures better water optimisation.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Provides protection against limescale and off-flavour components.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Space-​saving design that is very easy to handle.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Ideal for the production of both hot and cold beverages.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Flexibility of horizontal or vertical installation.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Includes both filter head and cartridge.</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(1180px, 332px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,950,"ACCESSORIES, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/BWT-Bestmax-Smart-Water-Filter-35-Filter-Head-.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"La Marzocco",Brand,"La Marzocco",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,12,0,,,"La Marzocco BWT Bestmax Smart Water Filter 35 (Filter Head + Cartridge - BWT,فلتر مياه المزورة,فلتر مياه",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,BWT,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110110100100111000010110110100111000010011100011,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14374,simple,,,"BLAST CHILLER/FREEZER - BC-15T-40",1,0,visible,"Your Ultimate Solution for Rapidly Chilling and Freezing Foods. This innovative appliance ensures food safety and preserves freshness by swiftly bringing temperatures down, enhancing efficiency and extending shelf life. With its compact design and advanced features, the BC-15T-40 is ideal for commercial kitchens, catering services, and food establishments aiming for optimal food preservation and quality.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(1117px, 206px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• BLAST CHILLER/FREEZER - BC-15T-40</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cap: 280 ltr.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• S/S structure</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Ventilated cooling system</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• High density insulation body</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Europe brand digital controller，Dixell</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Smart automatic defrosting</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Interior body with round corner, easy to clean</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Self-closing door with magnetic gaskets</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Let the temperature in the cabinet drops from the normal temperature to -40℃ in just 30 minutes</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• It can hold the versatile GN1/1 pans and 400x600 mm bakery trays, 65mm deep.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Net Weight: 165 Kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Temp: +30 ~ -40 (℃)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Related Power: 1950 W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Refrigeration type: Ventilated</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 800 * 800 * 1980 mm (WxDxH)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Digital : DIXELL / ITALY MADE .</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• compressor : ASPERA / EMBRACO/ EU made</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• BC-15T-40 / Inofrigo made/ Italian Technology</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• ISO9001, CE&amp;ROHS approved""</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(531px, 362px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,19926,22914,"REFRIGERATION LINE > Freezer & Chillers, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE, Special Offer",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/BLAST-CHILLER-FREEZER-BC-15T-40.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Inofrigo,Brand,Inofrigo,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,69,0,,,"BLAST CHILLER/FREEZER - BC-15T-40,مبرد الانفجار / الفريزر,معدات التبريد التجارية ذات التهوية مبرد الانفجار,مبرد الانفجار",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,BC-15T-40,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596801,110010100110011000010110010100110101100111001101,,,,,,,,,salescountdowntimer,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14376,simple,,,"LOWER HANGING MEAT CABINET - GN1410/MDG",1,0,visible,"Discover the GN1410/MDG Lower Hanging Meat Cabinet: Your Reliable Solution for Meat Preservation and Display. This specialized cabinet offers ample space and optimal conditions for storing and showcasing fresh meats, ensuring their quality and prolonging shelf life. With its sleek design and customizable features, the GN1410/MDG is perfect for butcher shops, delis, and supermarkets seeking to enhance product presentation while maintaining freshness and hygiene standards.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(271px, 35px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• LOWER HANGING MEAT CABINET - GN1410/MDG</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cap: 1225 ltr.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• S/S structure</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Ventilated system (no wind)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• High density insulation body</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Self-closing door with magnetic gaskets</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Adjustable feet or castor is available</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Refrigeration unit lower</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Including T-shaped hanging rod- LED lighting</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Front and rear visual glass</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Optional double side evaporator and upper evaporator</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Temp: -5～+5</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power: 412 W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Refrigerant: R134a/R290</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Refrigeration type: Ventilated</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Net Weight: 212 Kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 1480 × 830 × 2040 mm (WxDxH)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Digital : DIXELL / ITALY MADE</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• compressor : ASPERA / EMBRACO/ EU made</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• GN1410/MDG / Inofrigo made/ Italian Technology</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• ISO9001, CE&amp;ROHS approved""</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(560px, 265px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,7898,9082,"REFRIGERATION LINE > Display Chiller, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE, Special Offer",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/LOWER-HANGING-MEAT-CABINET-GN1410-MDG.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Inofrigo,Brand,Inofrigo,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,71,0,,,"LOWER HANGING MEAT CABINET - GN1410/MDG,سعر ثلاجة عرض لحوم,ثلاجة عرض لحوم",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,GN1410/MDG,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595985,110101110010010110100011011100100010010101011001,,,,,,,,,salescountdowntimer,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14378,simple,,,"Single door ICE STORGE FREEZER VENTILATED  - ICE300 VENTILATED",1,0,visible,"The ICE300 Ventilated Single-Door Ice Storage Freezer is a cutting-edge appliance designed to meet the demanding storage needs of businesses and individuals alike. With its innovative ventilation system, this freezer ensures efficient airflow, maintaining optimal temperatures for your stored items.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(446px, 36px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Single door ICE STORGE FREEZER VENTILATED - ICE300 VENTILATED</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Capacity (Ltrs): 300</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• S/S structure, ventilated cooling system, high density insulation body, Smart automatic defrosting</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Interior body with round corner, Easy to clean</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Europe brand controller &amp; compressor</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Large capacity ice storage</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Adjustable shelving design</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• LED lighting.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Built in temperature sensor</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• temperature range: -10 ~ -15 °C</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power (W):</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Net weight (KGS):</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Door size: 640 × 1150 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 915 × 765 × 2065 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Model: ICE300 VENTILATED / Inofrigo made/Italian Technology</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(764px, 201px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,5483,6415,"REFRIGERATION LINE > Freezer & Chillers, Kitchen E