14380,simple,,,"Single door ICE STORGE FREEZER STATIC - ICE300 STATIC",1,0,visible,"The Single Door ICE STORAGE FREEZER STATIC - ICE300 STATIC is a durable and efficient freezer designed for storing ice in commercial or industrial settings. With a single door design, it offers convenient access to the freezer's contents while optimizing space utilization.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(93px, 8px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Single door ICE STORGE FREEZER STATIC - ICE300 STATIC</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Capacity (Ltrs): 300</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• S/S structure, ventilated cooling system, high density insulation body, Smart automatic defrosting</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Interior body with round corner, Easy to clean</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Europe brand controller &amp; compressor</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Large capacity ice storage</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Adjustable shelving design</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• LED lighting.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Built in temperature sensor</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• temperature range: -10 ~ -15 °C</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power (W):</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Net weight (KGS):</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Door size: 640 × 1150 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 915 × 765 × 2065 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Model: ICE300 STATIC / Inofrigo made/Italian Technology</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(270px, 247px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,5085,5949,"REFRIGERATION LINE > Freezer & Chillers, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE, Special Offer",,,ht