14381,simple,,,"Counter Freezer  with evaporator in the middle - PA1100BT-700",1,0,visible,"The Counter Freezer with evaporator in the middle - PA1100BT-700 is a versatile and space-saving freezing solution ideal for commercial kitchens, bars, or any food service establishment. With its innovative design featuring the evaporator placed in the middle, it optimizes storage capacity while ensuring efficient cooling performance.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(734px, 62px);"" aria-expanded=""true"">\n<div id=""tippy-1"" style=""z-index: 100000200; visibility: visible; position: absolute; inset: auto auto 0px 0px; margin: 0px; transform: translate(399px, -20px);"" data-tippy-root="""">\n<div class=""tippy-box"" style=""max-width: 350px; transition-duration: 300ms;"" tabindex=""-1"" role=""mtttooltip"" data-state=""visible"" data-theme=""custom"" data-animation=""fade"" data-placement=""top"">\n<div class=""tippy-content"" style=""transition-duration: 300ms;"" data-state=""visible""><span dir=""rtl"">يعد الفريزر المضاد المزود بمبخر في المنتصف - PA1100BT-700 حل تجميد متعدد الاستخدامات وموفر للمساحة ومثالي للمطابخ التجارية أو الحانات أو أي مؤسسة لخدمات الطعام.</span></div>\n<div class=""tippy-arrow"" style=""position: absolute; left: 0px; transform: translate(92px, 0px);""></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Counter Freezer with evaporator in the middle - PA1100BT-700</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Volume (Ltrs): 250</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• S/S structure, ventilated cooling system, high density insulation body, Smart automatic defrosting</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Europe standard 600*400mm tray designed &amp; door handle</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Interior body with round corner, Easy to clean</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Self-closing door with magnetic gaskets</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Freezer mordels are added heating element in doorframe, keep no fog around doorframe</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Europe brand controller &amp; compressor</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Adjustable shelving design, Adjustable feet or castor is available</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• temperature range: -15 ~ -18 °C</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Refrigerant: Ventilated</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power (W): 588</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Net weight (KGS): 96</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 1200 * 700 * 850 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• packing size (mm): 1260×740×910 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Model: PA1100BT-700/ Inofrigo made/Italian Technology</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(1242px, 74px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,4555,5329,"REFRIGERATION LINE > Freezer & Chillers, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE, Special Offer",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Counter-Freezer-with-evaporator-in-the-middle-PA1100BT-700.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Inofrigo,Brand,Inofrigo,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,73,0,,,"Counter Freezer with evaporator in the middle - PA1100BT-700,ثلاجة طاولة,عداد فريزر مع مبخر في المنتصف",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,PA1100BT-700,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011111110000011100000010111110100000110110100101,,,,,,,,,salescountdowntimer,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14383,simple,,,"Counter Chiller  with evaporator in the middle - PA1100TN-700",1,0,visible,"he Counter Chiller with evaporator in the middle - PA1100TN-700 is a sophisticated cooling solution tailored for commercial food service environments. Its innovative design features the evaporator strategically positioned in the middle, optimizing storage space and ensuring uniform cooling across the unit.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(1040px, 202px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Counter Chiller with evaporator in the middle - PA1100TN-700</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Volume (Ltrs): 250</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• S/S structure, ventilated cooling system, high density insulation body, Smart automatic defrosting</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Europe standard 600*400mm tray designed &amp; door handle</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Interior body with round corner, Easy to clean</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Self-closing door with magnetic gaskets</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Europe brand controller &amp; compressor</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Adjustable shelving design, Adjustable feet or castor is available</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• temperature range: 2°C~8°C</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Refrigerant: Ventilated</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power (W): 350</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Net weight (KGS): 92</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 1200 * 700 * 850 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• packing size (mm): 1260×740×910 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Model: PA1100TN-700/ Inofrigo made/Italian Technology</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(585px, 166px);"" aria-expanded=