14384,simple,,,"Upright Chiller - BACK SIDE GLASS - GN1410TN/G + BACKGLASS",1,0,visible,"The Upright Chiller - BACK SIDE GLASS - GN1410TN/G + BACKGLASS is a modern and versatile refrigeration unit tailored for commercial use, particularly in food service establishments. Notably, its unique design incorporates a glass panel on the back side, offering a sleek and attractive display while ensuring optimal functionality.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(868px, 207px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Upright Chiller - BACK SIDE GLASS - GN1410TN/G + BACKGLASS</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• AISI 304 18/10 S/S interior &amp; exterior w/ sanitary corner except rear panel &amp; part of bottom.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• automatic closing door w/ magnetic gasket, 90° reversible w/ 4 castor wheels.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• injected polyurethane insulation, CFC free, density: 40 kgs / m3</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cap: 1285 ltr.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• w/ 3+3 shelf &amp; 2 drs.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Temp: +2˚ ~ +8° at 32° C.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power Supply: 230v / 50-60 Hz / 1Ph.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• frige power: 1130 Watt</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Type : R290</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Net Weight: 197 Kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 1480*830*2040 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Digital : DIXELL / ITALY MADE</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• compressor : ASPERA / EMBRACO/ EU made</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Model: GN1410TN/G + BACKGLASS / Inofrigo made/Italian Technology</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• ISO9001, CE&amp;ROHS approved""</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(771px, 79px);"" aria-expanded=""true"">\n<div id=""tippy-1"" style=""z-index: 100000200; visibility: visible; position: absolute; inset: 0px auto auto 0px; margin: 0px; transform: translate(399px, 20px);"" data-tippy-root="""">\n<div class=""tippy-box"" style=""max-width: 350px; transition-duration: 300ms;"" tabindex=""-1"" role=""mtttooltip"" data-state=""visible"" data-theme=""custom"" data-animation=""fade"" data-placement=""bottom"">\n<div class=""tippy-content"" style=""transition-duration: 300ms;"" data-state=""visible""><span dir=""rtl"">• AISI 304 18/10 S/S داخلي وخارجي مع زاوية صحية باستثناء اللوحة الخلفية وجزء من الأسفل.</span></div>\n<div class=""tippy-arrow"" style=""position: absolute; left: 0px; transform: translate(92px, 0px);""></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,8057,9426,"REFRIGERATION LINE > Display Chiller, REFRIGERATION LINE > Freezer & Chillers, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE, Special Offer",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Upright-Chiller-BACK-SIDE-GLASS-GN1410TN-G-BACKGLASS.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Inofrigo,Brand,Inofrigo,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,70,0,,,"Upright Chiller - BACK SIDE GLASS - GN1410TN/G + BACKGLASS,مبرد عمودي زجاج خلفي",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"GN1410TN/G + BACKGLASS",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,101101101100010100001001011101001000011111001011,,,,,,,,,salescountdowntimer,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
