14406,simple,,,"TABLE TOP ICE CREAM SHOWCASE -  WDONE T3",1,0,visible,"The WDONE T3 Tabletop Ice Cream Showcase is a compact and efficient display unit designed to showcase and merchandise a variety of ice cream flavors or frozen desserts. With its sleek and modern design, it adds an attractive aesthetic to any countertop or tabletop space, making it ideal for cafes, restaurants, ice cream parlors, and other foodservice establishments.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• TABLE TOP ICE CREAM SHOWCASE - WDONE T3</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Internal configuration GN1/3 pan designed, S/S structure.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Static cooling system, high density insulation body.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Europe brand controller &amp; European brand compressor</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Can be inserted into the bar, glass door can be customized front or back opening</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• The cabinet is equipped with LED lights around the top to make the cabinet fresh and bright and equipped with a large area of heat dissipation hole, effective heat dissipation, the unit can be used for a longer time</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• temperature: -10~-20</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power/ Voltage: 500 W / 220V / 50 Hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 880*600*390mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Model: WDONE T3 / Inofrigo made/Italian Technology</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(206px, 145px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,5500,5722,"REFRIGERATION LINE > Ice Cream Display, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE, Special Offer",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/TABLE-TOP-ICE-CREAM-SHOWCASE-WDONE-T3.png,,,,,