14412,simple,,,"ICE CREAM FREEZER DISPLAY - ICFD14X1-4",1,0,visible,"The ICE CREAM FREEZER DISPLAY (Model: ICFD14X1-4) is a state-of-the-art commercial refrigeration unit designed to elegantly showcase a variety of delicious frozen treats. With its sleek design and ample display space, this freezer is perfect for ice cream parlors, convenience stores, supermarkets, and other retail environments.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• ICE CREAM FREEZER DISPLAY - ICFD14X1-4</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 14 X GN 1/3</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Europe brand controller &amp; compressor.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• All copper tube manufacturing.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Strong refrigeration, air cooling and frost free.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Heating wire, degree film, hot gas demisting.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• High quality marble base, Universal caster, LED lighting</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Impact resistant double layer explosion-proof glass.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Internal configuration GN1/3 pan designed.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Internal temperature display, Glass movable door with handle.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Thickened explosion-proof glass.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• temperature: -16 ~ -20</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 1431 * 900 * 1250 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Model: ICFD14X1-4 / Inofrigo made/Italian Technology</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(590px, 86px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,13854,16209,"REFRIGERATION LINE > Ice Cream Display, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE, Special Offer",,,https:/