14416,simple,,,"ICE CREAM FREEZER DISPLAY - ICFD6X1-3",1,0,visible,"The ICE CREAM FREEZER DISPLAY (Model: ICFD6X1-3) is an advanced refrigeration unit meticulously engineered to showcase frozen treats with elegance and efficiency. Designed to meet the needs of various retail environments, from ice cream parlors to grocery stores, this freezer combines functionality with sleek aesthetics to attract customers and enhance product visibility.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• ICE CREAM FREEZER DISPLAY - ICFD6X1-3</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 6 X GN 1/3</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Europe brand controller &amp; compressor.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• All copper tube manufacturing.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Strong refrigeration, air cooling and frost free.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Heating wire, degree film, hot gas demisting.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• High quality marble base, Universal caster, LED lighting</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Impact resistant double layer explosion-proof glass.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Internal configuration GN1/3 pan designed.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Internal temperature display, Glass movable door with handle.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Thickened explosion-proof glass.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• temperature: -16 ~ -20</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 1253 * 725 * 1250 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Model: ICFD6X1-3 / Inofrigo made/Italian Technology</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(836px, 24px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,9453,11060,"REFRIGERATION LINE > Ice Cream Display, Kitchen Equipment, REFR