14417,simple,,,"ICE CREAM FREEZER DISPLAY - ICFD5X1-3",1,0,visible,"The ICE CREAM FREEZER DISPLAY (Model: ICFD5X1-3) is a sophisticated refrigeration unit tailored to beautifully exhibit a variety of frozen treats while optimizing space and energy efficiency. Crafted to meet the demands of modern retail settings such as ice cream parlors, cafes, and convenience stores, this freezer seamlessly integrates functionality with an attractive design.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(793px, 204px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• ICE CREAM FREEZER DISPLAY - ICFD5X1-3</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 5 X GN 1/3</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Europe brand controller &amp; compressor.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• All copper tube manufacturing.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Strong refrigeration, air cooling and frost free.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Heating wire, degree film, hot gas demisting.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• High quality marble base, Universal caster, LED lighting</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Impact resistant double layer explosion-proof glass.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Internal configuration GN1/3 pan designed.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Internal temperature display, Glass movable door with handle.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Thickened explosion-proof glass.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• temperature: -16 ~ -20</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 1075 * 725 * 1250 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Model: ICFD5X1-3 / Inofrigo made/Italian Technology</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(590px, 305px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,8930,10448,"REFRIGERATI