14418,simple,,,"COOLING WELLS - TD-2124EC",1,0,visible,"The Cooling Wells TD-2124EC is a cutting-edge refrigeration system engineered to maintain optimal temperatures for food and beverage items. It's specifically designed for use in commercial settings such as restaurants, catering services, and banquet facilities where precise temperature control is crucial.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• COOLING WELLS - TD-2124EC</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Gastronorm Pans: 6 x GN 1/1</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Net capacity: 200 - 220 L</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Embedded on the table for use.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Offset design of the unit to maximize the use of space under the platform.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Designed according to GN 1/1 batch size</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• S/S structure and Ventilated cooling system</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• High density insulation body</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cooling wells are designed to be build into a counter.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Europe brand controller &amp; compressor</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• temperature range: +2~+8</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Refrigeration type: Ventilated</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Refrigerant Type: R134a</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Related Power (W): 235</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Net / gross weight (KGS): 54 / 70</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 2124 × 688 × 636 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Model: TD-2124EC / Inofrigo made/Italian Technology</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(489px, 227px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,3759,4398,"REFRIGERATION LINE > Freezer & Chillers, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE, Special Offer",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/COOLING-WELLS-TD-2124EC.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Inofrigo,Brand,Inofrigo,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,71,0,,,"COOLING WELLS - TD-2124EC,آبار تبريد,بئر تبريد,وحدة تبريد",,,,,,,https://mariotstore.comold/ar/shop/refrigeration-line/freezer-chillers/cooling...,field_60befc9fc0fb7,TD-2124EC,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110111100100111010000110110000101100110100110100,,,,,,,,,salescountdowntimer,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14420,simple,,,"COOLING WELLS - TD-1790EC",1,0,visible,"I couldn't find specific information on a product named ""TD-1790EC"" as a cooling well. It's possible that it's a proprietary model number from a particular manufacturer or a less widely known product. However, typically, cooling wells are used in commercial food service settings to keep cold foods at safe serving temperatures. They are commonly found in salad bars, buffet lines, and catering events.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• COOLING WELLS - TD-1790EC</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Gastronorm Pans: 5 x GN 1/1</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Net capacity: 183 L</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Embedded on the table for use.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Offset design of the unit to maximize the use of space under the platform.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Designed according to GN 1/1 batch size</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• S/S structure and Ventilated cooling system</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• High density insulation body</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cooling wells are designed to be build into a counter.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Europe brand controller &amp; compressor</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• temperature range: +2~+8</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Refrigeration type: Ventilated</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Refrigerant Type: R134a</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Related Power (W): 235</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Net / gross weight (KGS): 50 / 64</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 1790 × 688 × 636 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Model: TD-1790EC / Inofrigo made/Italian Technology</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(107px, 415px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,3952,4623,"REFRIGERATION LINE > Freezer & Chillers, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE, Special Offer",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/COOLING-WELLS-TD-2124EC.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Inofrigo,Brand,Inofrigo,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,71,0,,,"COOLING WELLS - TD-1790EC,آبار تبريد,بئر تبريد,وحدة تبريد",,,,,,,https://mariotstore.comold/ar/shop/refrigeration-line/freezer-chillers/cooling...,field_60befc9fc0fb7,TD-1790EC,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110111100100111010000110110000101100110100110100,,,,,,,,,salescountdowntimer,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14421,simple,,,"COOLING WELLS  - TD-1456EC",1,0,visible,"The TD-1456EC Cooling Wells is an advanced refrigeration system designed to maintain optimal temperatures for food and beverage items in commercial settings. Ideal for use in restaurants, catering services, and banquet facilities, this cooling well ensures efficient cooling and preservation of perishable items.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• COOLING WELLS - TD-1456EC</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Gastronorm Pans: 4 x GN 1/1</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Net capacity: 146 L</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Embedded on the table for use.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Offset design of the unit to maximize the use of space under the platform.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Designed according to GN 1/1 batch size</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• S/S structure and Ventilated cooling system</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• High density insulation body</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cooling wells are designed to be build into a counter.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Europe brand controller &amp; compressor</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• temperature range: +2~+8</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Refrigeration type: Ventilated</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Refrigerant Type: R134a</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Related Power (W): 235</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Net / gross weight (KGS): 46 / 58</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 1456 × 688 × 636 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Model: TD-1456EC / Inofrigo made/Italian Technology</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,3508,4104,"REFRIGERATION LINE > Freezer & Chillers, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE, Special Offer",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/COOLING-WELLS-TD-