14427,simple,,,"Cake Showcase - CCS100R3M BLACK",1,0,visible,"The Cake Showcase CCS100R3M BLACK is a sleek and sophisticated display unit designed specifically for showcasing cakes. With its stylish black exterior, it adds a touch of elegance to any bakery or confectionery setup. Featuring ample display space and adjustable shelves, it allows for versatile presentation options while ensuring optimal visibility for your delicious creations. Its efficient cooling system maintains the perfect temperature to preserve the freshness and taste of your cakes. Ideal for both professional bakers and dessert enthusiasts, the Cake Showcase CCS100R3M BLACK is the perfect blend of functionality and aesthetics.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(7px, 84px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Cake Showcase - CCS100R3M BLACK</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Curved glass with LED light</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• S/S BLACK MIRROR base; Auto defrosting;</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Rear sliding door, with 3 shelves;</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Temperature:+2～+8℃；220V/ 50-60 Hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Embraco / SECOP compressor; Dixell / Carol controller</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• dim: 1000 * 685 * 1300 mm.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• CCS100R3M BLACK / Inofrigo made/Italian Technology""</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(913px, 63px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,4459,"BAKERY LINE > Bakery Display, BAKERY LINE, REFRIGERATION LINE > Display Chiller, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/CAKE-SHOWCASE-black.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Inofrigo,Brand,Inofrigo,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,71,0,,,"Cake Showcase - CCS100R3M BLACK,ثلاجة عرض حلويات صغ