14440,simple,,,"Cake Showcase - CCS200R3M BRONZE",1,0,visible,"The Cake Showcase CCS200R3M BRONZE combines functionality with elegance, providing an exquisite display solution for bakeries, patisseries, and cafes. Its bronze exterior exudes warmth and sophistication, adding a touch of luxury to any setting. This showcase is designed to effectively highlight your cakes and desserts, enticing customers with their tempting presentation. With generous storage capacity and advanced cooling technology, it ensures optimal freshness and preservation of your baked goods. Whether showcasing signature cakes or artisan pastries, the CCS200R3M BRONZE offers a stylish and practical solution for displaying your culinary creations with flair.\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" style=""transform: translate(653px, 129px);"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Cake Showcase - CCS200R3M BRONZE</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Curved glass with LED light</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• S/S BRONZE Mirror base; Auto defrosting;</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Rear sliding door, with 3 shelves;</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Temperature:+2～+8℃；220V/ 50-60 Hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Embraco / SECOP compressor; Dixell / Carol controller</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• dim: 2000 * 685 * 1300 mm.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• CCS200R3M BRONZE / Inofrigo made/Italian Technology""</p>\n\n<div id=""mttContainer"" class=""notranslate"" aria-expanded=""false""></div>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,7898,"BAKERY LINE > Bakery Display, BAKERY LINE, REFRIGERATION LINE > Display Chiller, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/CAKE-SHOWCASE-BRONZE.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Inofrigo,Brand,Inofrigo,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,71,0,,,"Cake Showcase - CCS200R3M BRONZE,ثلاجة عرض كيك,ثلاجة عرض ل