14499,simple,,,"SINGLE DOOR UPRIGHT CHILLER - PBM7",1,0,visible,"The SINGLE DOOR UPRIGHT CHILLER - PBM7 is a compact and efficient refrigeration unit designed for commercial use. With its sleek design and single door configuration, it offers convenient storage for perishable goods while maximizing space. Ideal for small businesses, cafes, or convenience stores, it ensures reliable cooling to preserve food freshness and quality.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• SINGLE DOOR UPRIGHT CHILLER</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Capacity Lt : 700 - Nos. of shelves: 3</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Constructed with Stainless Steel interior &amp; exterior.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• FRONTPANEL: Embossed front panel, hinged to facilitate the routine maintenance.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Monoblock refrigeration system</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cord and plug included</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Adjustable stainless steel legs</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Electronic digital controller.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Gas/ Charge: R290 / 0,065 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Casters &amp; Lock option.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Temp. °C: -2° , 8° C</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Absorb. Power: 280 W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight: 125 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Voltage: 220V/50Hz/1ph - Plug: Schuko 16A</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Amps: 1,5</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim [mm]: 720 x 798 x 2120</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Packing Dim [mm]: 780 x 860 x 2280</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Model No. PBM7 / DESMON / ITALY</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,5600,7172,"REFRIGERATION LINE > Freezer & Chillers, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LIN