14504,simple,,,"SINGLE DOOR UPRIGHT FREEZER - PBB7",1,0,visible,"The SINGLE DOOR UPRIGHT FREEZER - PBB7 is a versatile and dependable freezing solution for commercial environments. Featuring a single door design, it optimizes space while providing ample storage for frozen goods. With its efficient cooling system, it maintains consistent temperatures to preserve food quality over extended periods. Ideal for restaurants, supermarkets, or foodservice operations, it offers reliable performance to meet the demands of busy kitchens.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• SINGLE DOOR UPRIGHT FREEZER</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Capacity Lt : 700 - Nos. of shelves: 3</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Constructed with Stainless Steel interior &amp; exterior.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• FRONTPANEL: Embossed front panel, hinged to facilitate the routine maintenance.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Monoblock refrigeration system</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cord and plug included</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 3 epoxy coated wire shelve standard, installed per full door section.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Adjustable stainless steel legs</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Electronic digital controller.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Gas/ Charge: R290 / 0,070 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Casters &amp; Lock option.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Temp. °C: -25° , -10° C</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Absorb. Power: 500 W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight: 125 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Voltage: 220V/50Hz/1ph - Plug: Schuko 16A</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Amps: 2,5A</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim [mm]: 720 x 798 x 2120</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Packing Dim