14505,simple,,,"2-DOOR UPRIGHT REFRIGERATOR - PBM14",1,0,visible,"The 2-DOOR UPRIGHT REFRIGERATOR - PBM14 is a spacious and efficient refrigeration unit designed for commercial use. With its double-door configuration, it offers ample storage capacity while maximizing accessibility to stored items. Ideal for restaurants, supermarkets, or foodservice establishments, it ensures reliable cooling to preserve food freshness and quality. Its durable construction and advanced cooling technology make it a dependable choice for businesses with high refrigeration needs.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• 2-DOOR UPRIGHT REFRIGERATOR</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Capacity Lt : 1400 - Nos. of shelves: 6</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Constructed with Stainless Steel interior &amp; exterior.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• FRONTPANEL: Embossed front panel, hinged to facilitate the routine maintenance.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Monoblock refrigeration system</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cord and plug included</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Adjustable stainless steel legs</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Electronic digital controller.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Gas/ Charge: R290 / 0,062 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Casters &amp; Lock option.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Temp. °C: -2° , 8° C</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Absorb. Power: 400 W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight: 185 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Voltage: 220V/50Hz/1ph - Plug: Schuko 16A</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Amps: 2,2 A</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim [mm]: 1440 x 798 x 2120</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Packing Dim [mm]: 1480 x 860 x 2280</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Model No. PBM14 / DESMON / ITALY</p>",,,taxable,,0,,,0,0,,,,,1,,8395,10494,"REFRIGERATION LINE > Freezer & Chillers, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE, Special Offer",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/double-door.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Desmon,Brand,Desmon,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,79,0,,,"2-DOOR UPRIGHT REFRIGERATOR",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,PBM14,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595134,010111010011110110000110111100101011010001001000,,,,,,,,,salescountdowntimer,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14506,simple,,,"2-DOOR UPRIGHT FREEZER - PBB14",1,0,visible,"The 2-DOOR UPRIGHT FREEZER - PBB14 is a versatile and high-capacity freezing solution designed for commercial applications. Featuring a double-door design, it provides ample storage space for frozen goods while allowing convenient access to stored items. Ideal for supermarkets, restaurants, or foodservice establishments, it ensures reliable freezing to preserve food quality and freshness over extended periods. With its robust construction and advanced cooling system, it offers dependable performance to meet the demands of busy commercial kitchens.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• 2-DOOR UPRIGHT FREEZER</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Capacity Lt : 1400 - Nos. of shelves: 6</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Constructed with Stainless Steel interior &amp; exterior.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• FRONTPANEL: Embossed front panel, hinged to facilitate the routine maintenance.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Monoblock refrigeration system</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cord and plug included</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Adjustable stainless steel legs</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Electronic digital controller.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Gas/ Charge: R290 / 0,095 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Casters &amp; Lock option.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Temp. °C: -25° , -10° C</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Absorb. Power: 700 W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight: 185 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Voltage: 220V/50Hz/1ph - Plug: Schuko 16A</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Amps: 3,8 A</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim [mm]: 1440 x 798 x 2120</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Packing Dim [mm]: 1480 x 860 x 2280</p>\n<p styl