14508,simple,,,"3 DOOR REFRIGERATOR COUNTER - PTBM3",1,0,visible,"The 3 DOOR REFRIGERATOR COUNTER - PTBM3 is a versatile refrigeration unit designed for countertop placement in commercial environments. Featuring three refrigerator doors, it offers ample storage space while maximizing accessibility to stored items. Ideal for cafes, delis, or small foodservice establishments, it ensures reliable cooling to preserve the freshness and quality of perishable goods. With its compact footprint and durable construction, it provides a practical solution for businesses looking to optimize space while maintaining efficient refrigeration capabilities.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• 3 DOOR REFRIGERATOR COUNTER</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Capacity Lt : 363 - Nos. of shelves: 3</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Constructed with Stainless Steel interior &amp; exterior.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• FRONTPANEL: Embossed front panel, hinged to facilitate the routine maintenance.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Traditional cooling system with interior airventilated evaporators</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cord and plug included</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Adjustable stainless steel legs</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Electronic digital controller.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Gas/ Charge: R290 / 0,060 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Casters &amp; Lock option.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Temp. °C: -2° , 8° C</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Absorb. Power: 270 W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight: 160 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Voltage: 220V/50Hz/1ph - Plug: Schuko 16A</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Amps: 1,7 A</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim [mm]: 1779 x 700 x 865</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; p