14509,simple,,,"2 DOOR FREEZER COUNTER - PTSB2",1,0,visible,"The 2 DOOR FREEZER COUNTER - PTSB2 is a compact and efficient freezing unit designed for countertop placement in commercial settings. With its two-door configuration, it offers convenient access to frozen items while optimizing space usage. Ideal for cafes, delis, or small foodservice operations, it ensures reliable freezing to preserve the quality and integrity of frozen goods. Its durable construction and advanced freezing technology make it a practical choice for businesses with limited space or those in need of a versatile freezing solution.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• 2 DOOR FREEZER COUNTER</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Capacity Lt : 240 - Nos. of shelves: 2</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Constructed with Stainless Steel interior &amp; exterior.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Environmentally friendly R290 (Propane).</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cord and plug supplied</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Adjustable plastic feet</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Electronic digital controller.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Nr. 1 epoxy coated wire shelf standard, installed per full door section.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Gas: R290</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Casters &amp; Lock option.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Temp. °C: -10° , -25° C</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Absorb. Power: 560 W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cooling Power: 560 W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight: 120 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Voltage: 230/50/1 - Shuko : 1</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Amps: 2,5</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim [mm]: 1315 x 700 x 865</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Packing Dim [mm]: 1350