14514,simple,,,"8+8 Liter Fryer With Electric - RS046",1,0,visible,"The 8+8 Liter Fryer with Electric (model RS046) is a high-capacity fryer designed for commercial use. With a total capacity of 16 liters, it offers ample space for frying a variety of foods. Its electric operation ensures efficient cooking, while its compact design makes it suitable for kitchens with limited space. Ideal for restaurants, cafes, and food service establishments, this fryer is a reliable choice for crispy and delicious fried dishes.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• 8+8 Liter Fryer With Electric</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Capacity: 8 + 8 ltr</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Voltage: 220-230V / 50-60 Hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power: 6.4 kW</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight: 17 Kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 660 x 450 x 300 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• RS046/Turkey made</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,800,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Fryers, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/88-Liter-Fryer-With-Electric-–-RS046.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Mariot,Brand,Mariot,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,66,0,,,"8+8 Liter Fryer With Electric",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,RS046,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596914,110111010100111000000010110100111011001100110100,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14517,simple,,,"HOT PLATE LP GAS COUNTERTOP 24 wide NO. OF BURNERS: 4",1,0,visible,"Efficient and versatile, our 24-inch wide LP gas countertop hot plate features four burners, perfect for busy kitchens where space is a premium. Whether you're cooking up a storm or need extra burners for your culinary creations, this hot plate delivers reliable performance with ease.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• HOT PLATE LP GAS COUNTERTOP 24 wide NO. OF BURNERS: 4</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Stainless steel front, sides and front top ledge.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Full width front crumb trays.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 13"""" cooking height on 4"""" adjustable legs.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 25,000 BTU/hr. open burners with lift-off heads.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Total BTU/hr: 100,000</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cast iron top grates.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• One infinite heat control valve for each burner.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Standing pilot ignition system.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• ¾"""" rear gas connection and convertible gas pressure regulator for LP service.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Constructed standard for natural gas service. LP conversion kit supplied with unit.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight: 93 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• dim: 610 x 746 x 340 mm.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Model: VCRH24 / VULCAN</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,3564,"COOKING LINE > Cooker, COOKING LINE, Kitchen Equipment, COOKING LINE > Cooker > Series 600",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/HOT-PLATE.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Vulcan,Brand,Vulcan,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,81,0,,,"HOT PLATE",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,VCRH24,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,