14528,simple,,,"CHARBROILER LP GAS COUNTERTOP 36 wide NO. OF BURNERS: 6 - VCRB36",1,0,visible,"Experience superior grilling with our VCRB36 LP gas countertop charbroiler. At 36 inches wide and equipped with six burners, it offers ample space and power for all your grilling needs. Perfect for achieving restaurant-quality results, this charbroiler delivers exceptional flavor and even cooking every time.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• CHARBROILER LP GAS COUNTERTOP 36 wide NO. OF BURNERS: 6 - VCRB36</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Stainless steel front, sides and front top ledge.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Full width front grease drawers.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 13"""" cooking height on 4"""" adjustable legs.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Heavy duty cast iron char-radiants.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 51⁄4"""" wide cast iron grates are reversible for level or inclined broiling positions.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• One 14,500 BTU/hr. cast iron burner for each broiler grate.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• One infinite heat control valve for each burner.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Standing pilot ignition system.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Total BTU/hr: 87,000</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 3⁄4"""" rear gas connection and convertible gas pressure regulator for LP service.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Constructed standard for natural gas service. LP conversion kit supplied with unit.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight: 167 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• dim: 915 x 686 x 330 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Model: VCRB36 / VULCAN</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,5542,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Grills, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/CHARBOILER1.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Vulcan,Brand,Vulcan,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,76,0,,,CHARBROILER,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,VCRB36,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596598,011111001010011000001101001001110100101110010110,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14529,simple,,,"CHARBROILER LP GAS COUNTERTOP 47 wide NO. OF BURNERS: 8 - VCRB47",1,0,visible,"Elevate your grilling experience with the VCRB47 LP gas countertop charbroiler. With an impressive 47-inch width and eight burners, this unit offers expansive cooking space and powerful performance. Perfect for high-volume kitchens, it ensures consistent, delicious results with every use, making it ideal for achieving professional-quality grilling","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• CHARBROILER LP GAS COUNTERTOP 47 wide NO. OF BURNERS: 8</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Stainless steel front, sides and front top ledge.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Full width front grease drawers.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 13"""" cooking height on 4"""" adjustable legs.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Heavy duty cast iron char-radiants.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 51⁄4"""" wide cast iron grates are reversible for level or inclined broiling positions.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• One 14,500 BTU/hr. cast iron burner for each broiler grate.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• One infinite heat control valve for each burner.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Standing pilot ignition system.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Total BTU/hr: 116,000</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 3⁄4"""" rear gas connection and convertible gas pressure regulator for LP service.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Constructed standard for natural gas service. LP conversion kit supplied with unit</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight: 203 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• dim: 1194 x 686 x 330 mm.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Model: VCRB47 / VULCAN</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,7230,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Grills, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/CHARBOILER2.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Vulcan,Brand,Vulcan,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,76,0,,,CHARBROILER,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,VCRB47,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596598,010111011010011000001001011001111100101011110000,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14530,simple,,,"GRIDDLE LP GAS COUNTERTOP 24 wide NO. OF BURNERS: 2 - VCRG24-M",1,0,visible,"VCRG24-M LP gas countertop griddle, perfect for versatile cooking in compact spaces. With a 24-inch width and two burners, this griddle offers efficient cooking power for a variety of dishes. Whether you're making breakfast, lunch, or dinner, enjoy even heat distribution and delicious results every time.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• GRIDDLE LP GAS COUNTERTOP 24 wide NO. OF BURNERS: 2 - VCRG24-M</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Equipped with a natural gas connection but can be field converted to liquid propane with a conversion kit supplied with the unit.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cooking surface of 24 by 20.5 inches.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 1-inch thick polished steel griddle plate.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• A 3.25-inch back guard and tapered side guards minimize hot oil and grease splatter on your walls and other appliances.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 50,000 BTU/hr of power.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• It features one manual heat control valve per burner and uses a standing pilot ignition system to start up.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• With 4-inch adjustable legs.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• The griddle is constructed from a completely welded stainless and aluminized steel. Easy to use and clean.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• The unit offers a comfortable 12.5-inch working height. All these features, plus a 4.5-quart removable grease can, add to its convenience.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight: 111 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• dim: 610 x 686 x 406 mm.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Model: VCRG24-M/ VULCAN</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,5043,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Grills, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/GRIDLLE.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Vulcan,Brand,Vulcan,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,79,0,,,GRIDDLE,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,VCRG24-M,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011111011010110010101001000111000010010101110001,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14531,simple,,,"GRIDDLE LP GAS COUNTERTOP 36 wide NO. OF BURNERS: 3 - VCRG36-M",1,0,visible,"Meet the VCRG36-M LP gas countertop griddle, your versatile cooking companion with a 36-inch width and three burners. Whether you're cooking up breakfast, lunch, or dinner, this griddle offers ample space and power for even heat distribution and delicious results. Perfect for any kitchen, it's designed to make cooking a breeze.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• GRIDDLE, LP GAS, COUNTERTOP 36"""" wide\nNO. OF BURNERS: 3 - VCRG36-M</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Equipped with a natural gas connection but can be field converted to liquid propane with a conversion kit supplied with the unit.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cooking surface of 36 by 20.5 inches.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 1-inch thick polished steel griddle plate.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• A 3.25-inch back guard and tapered side guards minimize hot oil and grease splatter on your walls and other appliances.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 75,000 BTU/hr of power.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• It features one manual heat control valve per burner and uses a standing pilot ignition system to start up.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• With 4-inch adjustable legs.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• The griddle is constructed from a completely welded stainless and aluminized steel. Easy to use and clean.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• The unit offers a comfortable 12.5-inch working height. All these features, plus a 4.5-quart removable grease can, add to its convenience.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight: 155 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• dim: 915 x 686 x 406 mm.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Model: VCRG36-M/ VULCAN</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,5671,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Grills, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/GRIDLLE1.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Vulcan,Brand,Vulcan,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,79,0,,,GRIDDLE,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,VCRG36-M,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011111011001111000101001000010000101001010011111,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14532,simple,,,"GRIDDLE LP GAS COUNTERTOP 48 wide NO. OF BURNERS: 4 - VCRG48-M",1,0,visible,"Experience the ultimate cooking flexibility with the VCRG48-M LP gas countertop griddle. With its expansive 48-inch width and four burners, this griddle provides ample space and power for any culinary task. Whether you're cooking breakfast, lunch, or dinner, enjoy even heat distribution and precise control for delicious results every time.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• GRIDDLE LP GAS COUNTERTOP 48 wide NO. OF BURNERS: 4 - VCRG48-M</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Equipped with a natural gas connection but can be field converted to liquid propane with a conversion kit supplied with the unit.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cooking surface of 48 by 20.5 inches.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 1-inch thick polished steel griddle plate.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• A 3.25-inch back guard and tapered side guards minimize hot oil and grease splatter on your walls and other appliances.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 100,000 BTU/hr of power.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• It features one manual heat control valve per burner and uses a standing pilot ignition system to start up.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• With 4-inch adjustable legs.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• The griddle is constructed from a completely welded stainless and aluminized steel. Easy to use and clean.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• The unit offers a comfortable 12.5-inch working height. All these features, plus a 4.5-quart removable grease can, add to its convenience.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight: 185 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• dim: 1220 x 686 x 406 mm.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Model: VCRG48-M/ VULCAN</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,9300,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Grills, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/GRIDLLE2.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Vulcan,Brand,Vulcan,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,71,0,0,,GRIDDLE,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,VCRG48-M,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,000111011110111000001000010011110100000110011111,,,9139134372841951,yes,yes,,product,no,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14533,simple,,,"Natural Gas 6-Burner Range With Standard Oven SX36-6B SX Series",1,0,visible,"Upgrade your kitchen with the SX36-6B SX Series natural gas 6-burner range, featuring a standard oven and one rack. With six burners, this range provides ample cooking space and power for your culinary needs. Whether you're cooking for a crowd or preparing multiple dishes simultaneously, enjoy reliable performance and even cooking with this versatile appliance.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Natural Gas 6-Burner Range With Standard Oven NO. OF BURNERS: 6 - No. of Racks: 1 - SX36-6B SX Series</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• It is highly efficient and features six 28,000 BTU/hr open top burners and a 30,000 BTU/hr oven.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Total BTU: 198,000</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Four 6” stainless steel adjustable legs.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• A porcelain door liner and oven floor also make it easy to maintain a clean oven.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• A shrouded flash tube pilot system is used to ignite the burners and with one pilot light to operate two burners.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• The oven measures 26.75” x 26"""" x 13.75” and comes with an oven rack that can be placed at four different heights giving you plenty of space to bake or broil a variety of dishes.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Oven Temperature Range: 250°F - 500°F (121°C - 260°C)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight: 207 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Oven Dim: 680 x 660 x 349 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 915 x 813 x 1474 (w/legs) mm.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Model: SX36-6B SX Series/ VULCAN</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,7525,"COOKING LINE > Cooker, COOKING LINE, Kitchen Equipment, COOKING LINE > Cooker > Series 900",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/NATURAL-GAS-6.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Vulcan,Brand,Vulcan,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,76,0,,,"Natural Gas 6-Burner",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"SX36-6B SX Series",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,010111011000011000001001111100111100111101100000,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14534,simple,,,"Natural Gas Floor Fryer Capacity: 35-40 lb 18 to 20 ltr - LG300 Series",1,0,visible,"Elevate your frying experience with the LG300 Series natural gas floor fryer, offering a capacity of 35-40 lbs (18 to 20 liters). Perfect for commercial kitchens, this fryer ensures consistent and crispy results every time. With its reliable performance and large capacity, it's ideal for meeting the demands of high-volume frying.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Natural Gas Floor Fryer Capacity: 35-40 lb 18 to 20 ltr - LG300 Series</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• A 355 x 355 mm tank size and twin fryer baskets.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• A thermostat controls temperatures between 200° and 400°F (93°-204°C).</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Stainless steel constructed fry tank</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Easily removable stainless steel basket hanger for cleaning.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 90,000 BTU of power.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Easily removable stainless steel basket hanger for cleaning.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight: 95 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 394 x 749 x 1210 (w/legs) mm.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Model: LG300 Series/ VULCAN</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,4727,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Fryers, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/NATURAL-GAS-FLOR-FRYER.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Vulcan,Brand,Vulcan,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,80,0,,,"Natural Gas Floor Fryer",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"LG300 Series",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011000001101110010010011000110011111000111001110,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14535,simple,,,"Prince castle 8 channel merlin II timer, 220 volts,  (Horizantal) - 741 T88 CE",1,0,visible,"Series Single Function Timers\nIdeal for many kitchen applications, including monitoring frying,\ngrilling and prep stations, and tracking coffee-making and\nemployee handwashing. Quite simply, if a kitchen task needs to be\ntimed or monitored, Prince Castle timers can help manage these\ntasks.\nThese simple-to-use timers countdown in hours and minutes,\nor minutes and seconds. Up and down scan buttons make each\nchannel easy to program. Each channel is activated with a push of\na button. A digital channel display shows the active channel.\nLED channel indicators change colors during the timing cycle\ndepending on the stage of the countdown: the light is green\nduring the first 70% of the cycle, then turns yellow during the next\n20% of the cycle, and finally turns red during the last 10% of the\ncycle. A dual tone volume alarm and flashing channel indicator\nalert the operator when timing is complete.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Prince castle 8 channel merlin II timer, 220 volts, (Horizantal) - 741 T88 CE</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Product Features</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Digital channel display shows the active channel.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• New multi-colored LED channel indicators show the\nstatus of the timing cycle and provide early warning as\nthe countdown expires.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Lightweight ultra-slim 2.5 inch (6.4 cm) thick design and\n6 foot (1.8 m) line cord allow these units to be mounted\nvirtually anywhere.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Each channel can be programmed independently, and all\nchannels can be used simultaneously.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• The two-tone alarm is adjustable for either high or low\nsound levels.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Includes menu labels to identify channels: Burgers,\nSteak, Chicken, Fish, Fries, and blank stickers.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Includes set of 3-1/2 inch (8.9 cm) mounting brackets. For\nincreased mounting flexibility, flush mount brackets are\navailable.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• One year warranty.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Timers operate on any voltage worldwide</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,7700,"Kitchen Equipment, Uncategorized",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Untitled-2-1.png,,,,,,,,,0,,PrinceCastle,Brand,PrinceCastle,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,73,0,,,"Prince castle 8",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"741 T88 CE",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,15777,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110101001110111010001100000001011100111011100100,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14537,simple,,,"Traditional coffee machine Automatic - AURELIA II 2Gr V",1,0,visible,"The Traditional coffee machine Two Group Automatic - AURELIA II 2Gr V (MAUREIIVOL02000007) is a professional-grade espresso machine designed for commercial use. It features automatic brewing functionality and two brewing groups, making it capable of handling high volumes of coffee production. With its traditional design and advanced features, it delivers consistent and high-quality espresso drinks, making it ideal for cafes, restaurants, and other hospitality businesses.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Traditional coffee machine Two Group Automatic - AURELIA II 2Gr V (MAUREIIVOL02000007</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 2 Stainless steel steam wands with Push &amp;Pull command</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• MATT BLACK</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Code :MAUREIIVOL02000007</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Capacity : 14Ltr</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dimensions : 815 x 565 x 565 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power : 230V / 1Ph / 50-60Hz, 4.5kW</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Brand : NUOVA SIMONELLI</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Make : ITALY</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Model : AURELIA II 2Gr V (MAUREIIVOL02000007)</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,19620,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Coffee Machines, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/TRADITIONAL-COFFEE.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"Nuova Simonelli",Brand,"Nuova Simonelli",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,79,0,,,"Traditional coffee machine",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"AURELIA II 2Gr V (MAUREIIVOL02000007",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595055,010110011000011010101001101111000001111000001111,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14539,simple,,,"ROBOT COUPE R5 TABLE TOP CUTTER MIXER - R5 2V",1,0,visible,"The must for pastry and kitchen chefs!\nWith its bowl-base twin-blade assembly – a Robot-Coupe innovation – it is the ideal assistant in your kitchen. All preparations can be made by simply pressing a button: emulsions and sauces; mince meat and fish; chop onions, herbs and spices; grind nuts, chocolate or praline; knead dough.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• ROBOT COUPE R5 TABLE TOP CUTTER MIXER - R5 2V</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Product details</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Brand\nRobot Coupe</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Induction motor\nYes</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Wattage\n1500 W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Voltage\nThree phase</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Speed(s)\n1500 – 3000 rpm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Timer\nYes</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Motor base\nMetal</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Effective throughput (kg/h)\n150</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Bowl\n5.9 L stainless steel bowl with handle</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Blade(s)\nStainless steel smooth blade – Included</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Net weight\n22 KG</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Gross weight\n24 KG</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Dimensions (L x W x H)\n280 x 365 x 510 MM</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Pulse\nYes</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,10035,11805,"FOOD PROCESSING > Cutter Mixer, FOOD PROCESSING, Kitchen Equipment, Special Offer, Top Brands, FOOD PROCESSING > Vegtable Equipment",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/r5-2V-scaled.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/r5-2V-1-scaled.png",,,,,,,,,0,,"Robot Coupe",Brand,"Robot Coupe",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,71,0,,,"ROBOT COUPE R5 TABLE TOP CUTTER MIXER",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"R5 2V",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no,,,,,,,,,,,,,1734595055,110010110000110011001001100100101111010011001011,,,,,,,,,salescountdowntimer,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14542,simple,,,"Robot Coupe 4.5 Qt. Combination Food Processor- R402 A",1,0,visible,"The Robot Coupe R 402 A is both a cutter bowl and a vegetable preparation machine -- all on the same sturdy motor base. It has a powerful 2 horsepower motor, with two speeds of 600 and 1800 RPM (plus a pulse switch) and it comes with one smooth blade, one slicing disc (4mm), and one grating disc (2mm), and with a stainless steel bowl. This combination food processor can be used as either a continuous feed machine or as a batch bowl machine -- and it's capable of dicing and french fries with an optional dicing kit.\n\nThis machine has been designed to produce between 20 to 100 meals per service: in other words, for each service -- breakfast, lunch, and dinner -- you'll be able to process enough fruit and vegetables for up to 100 meals (so up to 300 meals per day). And because there are 28 compatible discs for this machine, you're going to be able to slice, julienne, ripple cut, grate, or dice.\n\nThe Robot-Coupe R402 is similar to the Robot Coupe R401, with a couple difference: the R401 has a 1.5 horsepower motor, and the R402 Ahas a 2 HP motor. The R402 is capable of dicing and french fries (if you purchase an optional dicing kit). And the R401 A is a single speed machine, whereas the R402 is a two speed machine.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Robot Coupe R402 A - 4.5 Qt. Combination Food Processor - 2 HP - R402 A</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 2 discs and 1 ""S"" blade included</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 28 optional discs available (including dicing and french fries)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 2 speed - 600 and 1800 RPM (with a pulse switch)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 2 horsepower</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 4.5 quart capacity</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 120v, 1 phase</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Perfect for long or bulky vegetables, and can function both as a cutter or vegetable prep machine. Many possible uses with its 28 optional discs, including dicing and french fries (with optional dicing discs)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Specs\nModel R 402\nPower 2 HP\nVoltage 120, 1 Phase\nSpeeds Two speeds - 600 and 1800 RPM\nCutter Bowl Capacity 4.5 Qt.\nAvailable Discs 28\nNumber of Covers Recommended for 20 to 100 meals\nDimensions (HLW) 17.5"" x 12"" x 9""\nShip Weight 49 lb\nNEMA# 5-15P\nCertifications ETL electrical sanitation Listed / cETL Canada</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,11510,"FOOD PROCESSING, Kitchen Equipment, Special Offer, Top Brands, FOOD PROCESSING > Vegtable Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Robot-Coupe-4.5-Qt.-Combination-Food-Processor-R402-A.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"Robot Coupe",Brand,"Robot Coupe",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,10,0,,,"Robot Coupe R402 A",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"R402 A",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595055,011110101111110010010100000111000010101100100011,true,backend,,,,,,,salescountdowntimer,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14544,simple,,,"BONE SAWS SO-SM 1550 ECO",1,0,visible,"A complete range of bone saws consisting of 2 models (small mod. 1550, large mod. 1830)\n\nTYPE OF USE: Butcher’s shops, fishmongers, catering, canteens, frozen fish and meat industries.\nHYGIENIC, ROBUST AND EASY TO USE: Machines comply with international hygiene standards. Nitro painted or anodised cast metal machine body. Stainless-steel work table, adjustable blade tensioner, incorporated cut portioner.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• BONE SAWS SO-SM 1550 ECO / SO-SM 1830 ECO</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• BONE SAW SO-SM 1550 ECO</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Blade length 1550 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Cutting height 250 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Work table 330 x 330 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Motor 1.1 kW – 1.00 hp 230V – 50 Hz / 230-400 V – 50 Hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Electrical system 24 V Low-voltage board</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Weight Kg 32</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Dimensions 44 x 37 x 81 cm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Package dimensions 90 x 52 x 40 cm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Optional Stainless-steel table (75 x 50 x 35 cm) Anodized or painted version</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Useful cutting height 150 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Cutting width 170 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• ø Pulley Ø 190</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,4642,"FOOD PROCESSING > fimar Meat Slicer & Bone Saw, FOOD PROCESSING, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/BONE-SAWS-SO-SM-1550-ECO-SO-SM-1830-ECO.png,,,,,,,,,0,,SAP,Brand,SAP,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,77,0,,,"BONE SAWS SO-SM 1550 ECO",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"SM 1550 ECO",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,fiel