14546,simple,,,"BONE SAWS SO-SM 1830 ECO",1,0,visible,"A complete range of bone saws consisting of 2 models (small mod. 1550, large mod. 1830)\n\nTYPE OF USE: Butcher’s shops, fishmongers, catering, canteens, frozen fish and meat industries.\nHYGIENIC, ROBUST AND EASY TO USE: Machines comply with international hygiene standards. Nitro painted or anodised cast metal machine body. Stainless-steel work table, adjustable blade tensioner, incorporated cut portioner.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• BONE SAWS SO-SM 1830 ECO</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Blade length 1830 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Cutting height 320 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Work table 410 x 410 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Motor 1.1 kW – 1.00 hp 230V – 50 Hz / 230-400 V – 50 Hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Electrical system 24 V Low-voltage board</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Weight Kg 36</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Dimensions 53 x 42 x 91 cm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Package dimensions 100 x 53 x 40 cm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Optional Stainless-steel table (75 x 50 x 35 cm) Anodized or painted version</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Useful cutting height 225 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Cutting width 200 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• ø Pulley Ø 200</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,4937,"FOOD PROCESSING > fimar Meat Slicer & Bone Saw, FOOD PROCESSING, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/BONE-SAWS-SO-SM-1550-ECO-SO-SM-1830-ECO.png,,,,,,,,,0,,SAP,Brand,SAP,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,77,0,,,"BONE SAWS SO-SM 1830 ECO",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"SM 1830 ECO",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,d