14547,simple,,,"MEAT MINCER - TC12P",1,0,visible,"The TC12P/CE and TC22P/CE meat mincers consist of a stainless steel case, mincing unit, tray and hopper.\nThe machines are equipped with a reverse switch and a 24 V electronic board.\nEasy to use and clean, as the mincing unit can be easily removed and all the parts cleaned using a damp cloth.\n\nThe ideal machine for general meat mincing. It can be supplied, with sausage filling funnels, on request.\nThe TC12 P/ CE e TC 22 P/CE machines comply with the strictest EC safety standards.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• MEAT MINCER TC12P</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Steel Mouth Ø 70</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Inlet Neck Ø 52</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Hourly Output Kg 100</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Weight Kg 21</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Power kW 0.75 – hp 1</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Standard plate holes 4.5 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Dimensions 42 x 26 x 48 cm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Package dimensions 60 x 34 x 55 cm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Optional Funnel set for sausage filling</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,3970,"FOOD PROCESSING, Kitchen Equipment, FOOD PROCESSING > Meat Mincer",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/MEAT-MINCER-TC12P-–-TC22P.png,,,,,,,,,0,,SAP,Brand,SAP,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,39,0,,,"MEAT MINCER TC12P",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,TC12P,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595653,111101100111011000100100001100101101101001101000,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14549,simple,,,"MEAT MINCER – TC22P",1,0,visible,"The TC12P/CE and TC22P/CE meat mincers consist of a stainless steel case, mincing unit, tray and hopper.\nThe machines are equipped with a reverse switch and a 24 V electronic board.\nEasy to use and clean, as the mincing unit can be easily removed and all the parts cleaned using a damp cloth.\n\nThe ideal machine for general meat mincing. It can be supplied, with sausage filling funnels, on request.\nThe TC12 P/ CE e TC 22 P/CE machines comply with the strictest EC safety standards.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• MEAT MINCER – TC22P</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Steel moutho Ø 82</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Inlet neck Ø 52</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Hourly output Kg 250</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Weight Kg 32</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Power kW 1.1- hp 1.5</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Standard plate holes 4.5 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Dimensions 46 x 28 x 52 cm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Package dimensions 60 x 34 x 55 cm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Optional Funnel set for sausage filling</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,4399,"FOOD PROCESSING, Kitchen Equipment, FOOD PROCESSING > Meat Mincer",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/MEAT-MINCER-TC12P-–-TC22P.png,,,,,,,,,0,,SAP,Brand,SAP,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,76,0,,,"MEAT MINCER – TC22P",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,TC22P,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595653,111101100111011000100100001100101101101001101000,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14550,simple,,,"MEAT MINCER-TC22",1,0,visible,"HYGIENIC, ROBUST, EASY TO CLEAN AND USE::\nCast alloy structure, covered entirely with stainless steel. Self-ventilated motors. Gear motor consisting of 4 hardened steel gears enclosed in a leak-proof oil bath gearbox.\nStainless steel hopper and meat collection tray. The mincing unit can be disengaged by simply turning a lever. All machine parts can be easily cleaned using a damp cloth.\nSAFETY: The machines comply with European and international standards. Motor and controls have IP 45 ingress protection, equipped with reverse switches and EC regulation compliant meat inlet mouth.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• MEAT MINCER-TC22</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Steel mouth Ø 22 (82 UNGER)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Inlet neck Ø 52</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Hourly output Kg. 300</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Motor 1.1 kW – 1.5 hp single phase</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Electrical system 24 V Low-voltage board</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Net weight kg 39</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Dimensions 45 x 30 x 36 cm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Package dimensions 60 x 34 x 55 cm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Hopper dimensions 39 x 29 x 7 cm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Optional HOPPER with microswitch – neck Ø 76</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Optional AISI 304 stainless-steel UNGER mouth with 3 plates (0 mm – 4.5 mm – 8 mm) and 2 blades</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,5098,"FOOD PROCESSING, Kitchen Equipment, FOOD PROCESSING > Meat Mincer",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/MEAT-MINCER-TC22-TC32.png,,,,,,,,,0,,SAP,Brand,SAP,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,81,0,,,"MEAT MINCER-TC22",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,TC22,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011100011110111000010110111100111000100101100000,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14552,simple,,,"MEAT MINCER Three Phase-TC32",1,0,visible,"HYGIENIC, ROBUST, EASY TO CLEAN AND USE::\nCast alloy structure, covered entirely with stainless steel. Self-ventilated motors. Gear motor consisting of 4 hardened steel gears enclosed in a leak-proof oil bath gearbox.\nStainless steel hopper and meat collection tray. The mincing unit can be disengaged by simply turning a lever. All machine parts can be easily cleaned using a damp cloth.\nSAFETY: The machines comply with European and international standards. Motor and controls have IP 45 ingress protection, equipped with reverse switches and EC regulation compliant meat inlet mouth.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• MEAT MINCER Three Phase-TC32</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Steel mouth Ø 32 (98 UNGER)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Inlet neck Ø 52</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Hourly output Kg. 600</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Motor 1.85 kW – 2.2 hp Three phase</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Electrical system 24 V Low-voltage board</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Net weight kg 43</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Dimensions 47 x 30 x 45 cm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Package dimensionsllo 60 x 34 x 55 cm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Optional Stainless steel AISI 304 UNGER mouth with three plates (0 mm – 4.5 mm – 8 mm) and two blades HOPPER with microswitch – neck Ø 76 Funnel set for sausage filling</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Package dimensions 39 x 29 x 7 cm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Made by SAP / Italy</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,5635,"FOOD PROCESSING, Kitchen Equipment, FOOD PROCESSING > Meat Mincer",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/MEAT-MINCER-TC22-TC32.png,,,,,,,,,0,,SAP,Brand,SAP,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,77,0,,,"MEAT MINCER Three Phase-TC32",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"Three Phase-TC32",