14553,simple,,,"MEAT MINCER Single Phase-TC32",1,0,visible,"HYGIENIC, ROBUST, EASY TO CLEAN AND USE::\nCast alloy structure, covered entirely with stainless steel. Self-ventilated motors. Gear motor consisting of 4 hardened steel gears enclosed in a leak-proof oil bath gearbox.\nStainless steel hopper and meat collection tray. The mincing unit can be disengaged by simply turning a lever. All machine parts can be easily cleaned using a damp cloth.\nSAFETY: The machines comply with European and international standards. Motor and controls have IP 45 ingress protection, equipped with reverse switches and EC regulation compliant meat inlet mouth.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• MEAT MINCER Single Phase-TC32</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Steel mouth Ø 32 (98 UNGER)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Inlet neck Ø 52</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Hourly output Kg. 600</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Motor 1.85 kW – 2.2 hp single phase</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Electrical system 24 V Low-voltage board</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Net weight kg 45</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Dimensions 47 x 30 x 45 cm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Package dimensionsllo 60 x 34 x 55 cm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Optional Stainless steel AISI 304 UNGER mouth with three plates (0 mm – 4.5 mm – 8 mm) and two blades HOPPER with microswitch – neck Ø 76 Funnel set for sausage filling</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Package dimensions 39 x 29 x 7 cm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Made by SAP / Italy</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,5635,"FOOD PROCESSING, Kitchen Equipment, FOOD PROCESSING > Meat Mincer",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/MEAT-MINCER-TC22-TC32.png,,,,,,,,,0,,SAP,Brand,SAP,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,77,0,,,"MEAT MINCER Single Phase-TC32",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"Single Phase-TC32",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595653,011100011110111000010110111100111000100101100000,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14554,simple,,,"VERTICAL CUTTER MIXERS R30 A",1,0,visible,"This top of the range floor-standing cutter is a must for manufacturers or pastry and kitchen chefs processing large volumes!\nWith its bowl-base twin-blade assembly - a Robot-Coupe innovation - it is the ideal assistant in your kitchen. All preparations can be made by simply pressing a button: emulsions and sauces; mince meat and fish; chop onions, herbs and spices; grind nuts, chocolate or praline; knead dough.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• VERTICAL CUTTER MIXERS R30 A</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• motor Yes</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power 7 HP</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Voltage 3 phase 208 - 240 V</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Speeds 1800 - 3600 rpm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Pulse Yes</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• IP65 control panel with digital timer Yes</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Bowl 28 L stainless steel bowl</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Lid wiper Yes</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Blade(s) 3 adjustable stainless steel smooth ""S"" blade assembly - Included</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Three retractable wheels Yes</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Gross weight (Lbs) 310</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dimensions\n(W × L × H) 31.5"" x 27.5"" x 58.5""</p>",,,taxable,,0,,,0,0,,,,,1,,51000,60000,"FOOD PROCESSING > Cutter Mixer, FOOD PROCESSING, Kitchen Equipment, Special Offer",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/VERTICAL-CUTTER-MIXERS-R30-A.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/VERTICAL-CUTTER-MIXERS-R30-A1.png",,,,,,,,,0,,"Robot Coupe",Brand,"Robot Coupe",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,79,0,,,"VERTICAL CUTTER MIXERS R30 A",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"R30 A",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no,,,,,,,,,,,,,,011000001100011000110011011110011010011011100110,,,,,,,,,salescountdowntimer,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14557,simple,,,"Robot Coupe R60 Vertical Cutter Mixer",1,0,visible,"Made in France\nDimensions: W: 810 x D: 600 x H: 1400mm\nWeight: 187 Kg\n\nPower: 3 phase (supplied without plug)\nThis top of the range floor-standing cutter is a must for manufacturers or pastry and kitchen chefs processing large volumes!\nWith its bowl-base twin-blade assembly - a Robot-Coupe innovation - it is the ideal assistant in your kitchen. All preparations can be made by simply pressing a button: emulsions and sauces; mince meat and fish; chop onions, herbs and spices; grind nuts, chocolate or praline; knead dough.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• Robot Coupe R60 Vertical Cutter Mixer</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• 11,000W Induction motor</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Speed: 1500 - 3000 rpm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• IP65 control panel with digital timer</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Timer: From 0-15 minutes for consistency. Automatically repeats the previously set time</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Stainless steel control buttons: flush with the casing for easy cleaning and durability</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Indicator lights for user safety</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Pulse control for precision processing</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Polycarbonate see-through lid</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">•Lid wiper allows you to monitor your preparation from start to finish</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Opening in the lid centre to add liquids or dry ingredients during processing</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Lid is designed to direct liquid back into the bowl when opened</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Lid rubber seal prevents liquid overflow</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Quick and easy to remove for cleaning</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Lid is dishwasher-safe</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• 60L stainless steel bowl with handles</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Tilting mechanism, at more than 90°, for effortless empyting of your preparation</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Removable, exclusive to Robot Coupe, for easy cleaning</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Smooth blade: 100% stainless-steel Bowl-base blade assembly for working small and large quantities. Dismountable and adjustable</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Frame: All Stainless steel construction:</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• 3 sturdy legs for stability and safety</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Compact footprint</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Easy to clean</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Wheels: 3 retractable wheels making it easier to move and allow cleaning of your production area</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,92588,108927,"FOOD PROCESSING > Cutter Mixer, FOOD PROCESSING, Kitchen Equipment, Special Offer",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/VERTICAL-CUTTER-MIXERS-R30-A.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/VERTICAL-CUTTER-MIXERS-R30-A1.png",,,,,,,,,0,,"Robot Coupe",Brand,"Robot Coupe",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,72,0,,,"Robot Coupe R60 Vertical Cutter Mixer",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,R60,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595733,011000001100011000110011011110011010011011100110,,,,,,,,,salescountdowntimer,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14558,simple,,,"Glo-Ray Aluminum Infrared Strip Heater (GRAH-24)",1,0,visible,"The Glo-Ray Aluminum Infrared Strip Heater (GRAH-24) is a durable and efficient heating solution designed for commercial kitchens. Measuring 24 inches, it features an aluminum housing that enhances its durability and heat conduction. The infrared technology ensures even heat distribution, keeping food at optimal serving temperatures without drying it out. Ideal for pass-through stations, buffet lines, and other food service applications, this strip heater is both reliable and energy-efficient.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Glo-Ray Aluminum Infrared Strip Heater (GRAH-24)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Tubular metal heater rod.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Single heater rod housing.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Aluminum construction.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Built‐in toggle control.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• High wattage.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Elec. Rating: 240v/50/1‐ph/500w/2.1A.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dimensions: 610 x 153 x 64 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Gross weight: 3.6Kg.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• GRAH-24/ HATCO/ USA</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,1592,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Food Warmers, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Glo-Ray-Aluminum-Infrared-Strip-Heater-GRAH-24.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Hatco,Brand,Hatco,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,66,0,,,"Glo-Ray Aluminum Infrared Strip Heater (GRAH-24)",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,GRAH-24,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011111010000111000001001110001111001100011100101,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14560,simple,,,"Glo-Ray Infrared Strip Heater with Lights (GRAHL‐24)",1,0,visible,"The Glo-Ray Infrared Strip Heater with Lights (GRAHL-24) is a versatile and efficient heating solution for commercial food service environments. This 24-inch strip heater features built-in lights that illuminate the food holding area, enhancing visibility and presentation. Its infrared heating technology ensures consistent and even heat distribution, maintaining food at optimal serving temperatures. The durable aluminum construction provides excellent heat conduction and long-lasting performance, making it ideal for use in pass-through stations, buffet lines, and other food service applications.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Glo-Ray Infrared Strip Heater with Lights (GRAHL‐24)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Tubular metalheater rod with lights.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Single heater rod housing.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Aluminum construction.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Built‐in toggle control.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• High wattage.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Elec. Rating: 240v/50/1‐ph/620w/2.6A.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dimensions: 610 x 229 x 64 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Gross weight: 4.5Kg.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• GRAHL‐24/ HATCO/ USA</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,2535,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Food Warmers, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Glo-Ray-Infrared-Strip-Heater-with-Lights-GRAHL‐24.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Hatco,Brand,Hatco,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,64,0,,,"Glo-Ray Infrared Strip Heater with Lights (GRAHL‐24)",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,GRAHL‐24,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596053,110101101001010010001110100011110100011110010010,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14562,simple,,,"Glo-Ray Infrared Strip Heater with Lights (GRAHL‐36)",1,0,visible,"The Glo-Ray Infrared Strip Heater with Lights (GRAHL-36) is a robust and efficient heating solution tailored for commercial food service settings. This 36-inch model combines infrared heating technology with integrated lights to ensure even heat distribution while illuminating the food holding area for enhanced visibility and presentation. Its sturdy aluminum construction guarantees excellent heat conduction and long-lasting durability. Perfect for use in pass-through stations, buffet lines, and other food service applications, the GRAHL-36 helps maintain food at optimal serving temperatures efficiently and effectively.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Glo-Ray Infrared Strip Heater with Lights (GRAHL‐36)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Tubular metalheater rod with lights.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Single heater rod housing.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Aluminum construction.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Built‐in toggle control.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• High wattage.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Elec. Rating: 240v/50/1‐ph/980w/4.1A.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dimensions: 914 x 229 x 64 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Gross weight: 6Kg.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• GRAHL‐36/ HATCO/ USA</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,3055,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Food Warmers, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Glo-Ray-Infrared-Strip-Heater-with-Lights-GRAHL‐24.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Hatco,Brand,Hatco,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,64,0,,,"Glo-Ray Infrared Strip Heater with Lights (GRAHL‐36)",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,GRAHL‐36,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,d