14565,simple,,,"High Volume – Open Fryer PFE 590/8000 Electric",1,0,visible,"<strong>High Volume – Open Fryer PFE 590/8000 Electric</strong>\nThe PFE 590/8000 Electric Open Fryer is a high-capacity, commercial-grade fryer designed for busy kitchens. It features a robust stainless steel construction for durability and easy cleaning. With its large frying area, it accommodates high volumes of food, making it ideal for restaurants and food service establishments with heavy demand. The precise temperature control ensures consistent cooking results, while the user-friendly interface allows for efficient operation. Safety features include over-temperature protection and an automatic shut-off system. This fryer combines efficiency, reliability, and high performance to meet the demands of high-volume frying operations.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• High Volume – Open Fryer PFE 590/8000 Electric</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 10.9 kg product</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• capacity (8-head chicken)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 45 Kg shortening capacity</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• computerized control systems and counter balanced lid\nlift system with loading rack and baskets in place</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• cooks up to 11 kg, 17 kW, 480V/50Hz/3Ph.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 648 x 1040 x 1549 mm (H)</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,133500,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Fryers, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/High-Volume-Open-Fryer-PFE-590-8000-Electric.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"Henny Penny",Brand,"Henny Penny",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,54,0,,,"High Volume – Open Fryer PFE 590/8000 Electric",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"PFE 590/8000",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,