14567,simple,,,"High Volume – Open Fryer PFG 690/8000 Gas",1,0,visible,"<strong>High Volume – Open Fryer PFG 590/8000 Gas</strong>\nThe PFG 590/8000 Gas Open Fryer is a high-capacity, commercial-grade fryer designed for high-demand kitchens. It boasts a durable stainless steel construction for longevity and ease of maintenance. With a spacious frying area, it efficiently handles large volumes of food, making it perfect for restaurants and food service establishments with heavy traffic. The fryer features precise temperature controls for consistent cooking results and a user-friendly interface for easy operation. Enhanced safety measures include over-temperature protection and an automatic shut-off system. Combining efficiency, reliability, and top-notch performance, this gas fryer is ideal for any high-volume frying operation.","[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text css=""""]\n<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• High Volume – Open Fryer PFG 690/8000 Gas</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Henny Penny stainless steel high volume gas pressure\nfryer, computerized control systems</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• built-in filter</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 10.9 kg product capacity</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• shortening capacity 59 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 4 casters (2 locking) 100,000 BTU/hr (29 kW)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 240V/50Hz/1Ph. LPG.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dim: 648 x 1062 x 1595 mm (H)</p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,159500,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Fryers, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/High-Volume-Open-Fryer-PFE-590-8000-Electric.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"Henny Penny",Brand,"Henny Penny",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,17,0,,,"High Volume – Open Fryer PFG 590/8000 Gas",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"PFG 690/8000",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110010100110110010010110110110001101110001001100,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14568,simple,,,"BLIXER 3D Single phase - 3D",1,0,visible,"<strong>BLIXER 3D Single phase</strong> The Blixer®, especially designed for the healthcare sector, turns raw products into texture modified foods.\nAll foods, whether raw or cooked, sweet or savoury, whether entrees or mains, dessert or cheese, can be eaten by everyone at the table, even the most elderly.\nIdeal for processing 2-10 portions","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• BLIXER 3D Single phase - 3D</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Induction</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• motor Yes</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Wattage 750 W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Voltage Single phase</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Speed(s) 3000 rpm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Pulse Yes</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Motor base Composite material</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Bowl 3.7 L stainless steel with Soft touch handle</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Lid Watertight</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">•Blade(s) Stainless steel fine serrated blade - Included Stainless steel fine serrated blade</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Equipped with Blixer® arm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Number of 200 g portions 2 to 10</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Net weight (kg) 12</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Gross weight (kg) 13</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Dimensions (L x W x H) mm 240 x 305 x 445</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,8585,"FOOD PROCESSING > Cutter Mixer, FOOD PROCESSING, Kitchen Equipment",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/1-5-1.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/3-5-1.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/2-5-1.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/4-5.png",,,,,,,,,0,,"Robot Coupe",Brand,"Robot Coupe",1,1,,,,,default,1,