14573,simple,,,"Ice cream machine WITH STAND - MK618CBPA",1,0,visible,"The Ice Cream Machine WITH STAND - MK618CBPA is a professional-grade appliance designed for commercial use in ice cream parlors, cafes, and restaurants. This machine comes equipped with a sturdy stand for stable positioning and convenient operation. The MK618CBPA model features robust construction and user-friendly controls, ensuring reliable performance and easy operation. Its advanced freezing technology allows for the rapid production of high-quality ice cream, making it a valuable asset for businesses looking to offer a wide range of frozen desserts.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Ice cream machine WITH STAND - MK618CBPA</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Capacity: 18 L/H</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Compressor: EMBRACO / ASPERA</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Voltage : 220-240v / 50hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power : 1600w / UK PLUG</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Refrigerant : R404A/ 550g / R134A/ 120g</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Noise: 48db</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Double puffed air pump; make the ice cream well formed and taste delicate.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Features a night mode program.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power: 1600W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight N/ G: 105 / 115 Kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Ice cream temperature up to -7 to -8 degrees Celsius</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• DIM: 480*560*1260 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• MK618CBPA / MKE-MATIC</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,5359,"REFRIGERATION LINE > Ice Cream Machines, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/MK618-ice-cream-machine.png,,,,,,,,,0,,MKE-MATIC,Brand,"MKE MATIC",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,7