14586,simple,,,"HARD ICE CREAM MACHINE - YKF-7218",1,0,visible,"The HARD ICE CREAM MACHINE YKF-7218 is a powerful and efficient appliance designed specifically for producing high-quality hard ice cream. It features a robust compressor for rapid freezing, a durable stainless steel build, and an intuitive control panel for precise adjustments. Ideal for both commercial and home use, the YKF-7218 ensures consistent, creamy results and easy operation, making it perfect for ice cream enthusiasts and professionals alike.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• HARD ICE CREAM MACHINE - YKF-7218</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Capacity: 18-24 L/H</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Mix hopper: 6L</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Refrigerant: R404a</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power: 220V~ 50Hz 2000W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Stainless Steel body</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Compressor: Embraco</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight: 95 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• dim: 500 x 795 x 790 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Model: YKF-7218 / MKE-MATIC / CHINA</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,5713,"REFRIGERATION LINE > Ice Cream Machines, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/HARD-ICE-CREAM-MACHINE-YKF-7218.png,,,,,,,,,0,,MKE-MATIC,Brand,"MKE MATIC",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,64,0,,,"HARD ICE CREAM MACHINE - YKF-7218",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,YKF-7218,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110101011001111010011001110100001010001101001010,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14588,simple,,,"JUICE DISPENSER - KK18PL-1",1,0,visible,"The JUICE DISPENSER KK18PL-1 is a sleek and efficient appliance designed for serving a variety of chilled beverages. Featuring a single-tank design with a large capacity, it is perfect for both commercial and home use. The dispenser includes a transparent tank for easy visibility of the contents, a user-friendly control panel, and a powerful cooling system to ensure beverages are served at the optimal temperature. Its durable construction and easy-to-clean components make the KK18PL-1 a reliable choice for any setting.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• JUICE DISPENSER - KK18PL-1</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Volume: 18 L</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Colour Black</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Spraying type/ cold drink</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power: 220V~ 50Hz 200W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight: 15 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• dim: 210 x 442 x 675 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Model: KK18PL-1 / MKE-MATIC / CHINA</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,1341,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Juice Maker, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/JUICE-DISPENSER-KK18PL-1.png,,,,,,,,,0,,MKE-MATIC,Brand,"MKE MATIC",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,64,0,,,"JUICE DISPENSER - KK18PL",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,KK18PL-1,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110010110011101100110011000111001100100101000101,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14590,simple,,,"JUICE DISPENSER - KK18PL-2",1,0,visible,"The JUICE DISPENSER KK18PL-2 is a high-capacity, dual-tank appliance designed for serving a variety of chilled beverages efficiently. It features two transparent tanks for easy monitoring of beverage levels, an intuitive control panel for precise temperature settings, and a powerful cooling system to maintain optimal drink temperatures. Ideal for both commercial and home environments, the KK18PL-2 combines durability, ease of use, and easy maintenance, making it a reliable and convenient solution for dispensing cold drinks.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• JUICE DISPENSER - KK18PL-2</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Volume: 18 x 2 L</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Colour Black</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Spraying type/ cold drink</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power: 220V~ 50Hz 250W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight: 25 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• dim: 402 x 442 x 675 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Model: KK18PL-2 / MKE-MATIC / CHINA</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,1548,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Juice Maker, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/JUICE-DISPENSER-KK18PL-2.png,,,,,,,,,0,,MKE-MATIC,Brand,"MKE MATIC",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,64,0,,,"JUICE DISPENSER - KK18PL-2",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,KK18PL-2,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110110110000101100000011110011000111001111001001,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14592,simple,,,"JUICE DISPENSER - KK18PL-3",1,0,visible,"The JUICE DISPENSER KK18PL-3 is a versatile and efficient appliance designed for dispensing multiple chilled beverages. It features three transparent tanks, allowing for a variety of drinks to be served simultaneously, each with independent temperature controls. The powerful cooling system ensures beverages are kept at the perfect serving temperature, while the user-friendly control panel simplifies operation. Ideal for both commercial and home use, the KK18PL-3 combines durability, convenience, and easy maintenance, making it an excellent choice for any beverage service need.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• JUICE DISPENSER - KK18PL-3</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Volume: 18 x 3 L</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Colour Black</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Spraying type/ cold drink</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power: 220V~ 50Hz 380W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight: 36 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• dim: 610 x 442 x 675 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Model: KK18PL-3 / MKE-MATIC / CHINA</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,1960,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Juice Maker, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/JUICE-DISPENSER-KK18PL-3.png,,,,,,,,,0,,MKE-MATIC,Brand,"MKE MATIC",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,64,0,,,"JUICE DISPENSER - KK18PL-3",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,KK18PL-3,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110101111100001110100000111001100001101011001010,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14594,simple,,,"JUICE DISPENSER - KK18JL-1",1,0,visible,"The JUICE DISPENSER KK18JL-1 is a high-performance appliance designed to efficiently serve chilled beverages. It features a single large-capacity tank with a transparent design for easy monitoring of juice levels. The powerful cooling system ensures drinks are kept at the ideal temperature, while the user-friendly control panel allows for precise adjustments. With its durable construction and easy-to-clean components, the KK18JL-1 is perfect for both commercial and home use, providing a reliable and convenient solution for dispensing a variety of cold beverages.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• JUICE DISPENSER - KK18JL-1</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Volume: 18 L</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Colour Black</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Stirring type/ cold drink</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power: 220V~ 50Hz 200W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight: 15 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• dim: 210 x 442 x 675 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Model: KK18JL-1 / MKE-MATIC / CHINA</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,1341,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Juice Maker, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/JUICE-DISPENSER-KK18PL-1.png,,,,,,,,,0,,MKE-MATIC,Brand,"MKE MATIC",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,64,0,,,"JUICE DISPENSER - KK18JL-1",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,KK18JL-1,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110010110011101100110011000111001100100101000101,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14595,simple,,,"JUICE DISPENSER -KK18JL-2",1,0,visible,"The JUICE DISPENSER KK18JL-2 is a robust and efficient appliance designed for dispensing two varieties of chilled beverages simultaneously. It features two transparent tanks for easy monitoring of beverage levels, each with independent temperature controls. The powerful cooling system ensures optimal serving temperatures, while the intuitive control panel allows for precise adjustments. Perfect for both commercial and home use, the KK18JL-2 combines durability, ease of use, and easy maintenance, making it a reliable choice for serving cold drinks.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• JUICE DISPENSER -KK18JL-2</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Volume: 18 x 2 L</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Colour Black</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Stirring type/ cold drink</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power: 220V~ 50Hz 250W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight: 25 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• dim: 402 x 442 x 675 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Model: KK18JL-2 / MKE-MATIC / CHINA</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,1548,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Juice Maker, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/JUICE-DISPENSER-KK18PL-2.png,,,,,,,,,0,,MKE-MATIC,Brand,"MKE MATIC",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,64,0,,,"JUICE DISPENSER -KK18JL-2",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,KK18JL-2,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110110110000101100000011110011000111001111001001,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14596,simple,,,"JUICE DISPENSER - KK18JL-3",1,0,visible,"The JUICE DISPENSER KK18JL-3 is a versatile and reliable appliance tailored for dispensing three different chilled beverages simultaneously. Featuring three transparent tanks, it allows for easy monitoring of beverage levels and offers independent temperature controls for each tank. With its powerful cooling system, the KK18JL-3 ensures that drinks are served at optimal temperatures. Designed for both commercial and home use, this dispenser combines durability, user-friendliness, and easy maintenance, making it an ideal solution for various beverage-serving needs.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• JUICE DISPENSER - KK18JL-3</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Volume: 18 x 3 L</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Colour Black</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Stirring type/ cold drink</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power: 220V~ 50Hz 380W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight: 36 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• dim: 610 x 442 x 675 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Model: KK18JL-3 / MKE-MATIC / CHINA</p>",,,taxable,,0,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,1960,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Juice Maker, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/JUICE-DISPENSER-KK18PL-3.png,,,,,,,,,0,,MKE-MATIC,Brand,"MKE MATIC",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,52,0,,,"JUICE DISPENSER - KK18JL-3",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,KK18JL-3,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110101111100001110100000111001100001101011001010,false,,,,,,,,salescountdowntimer,,,,,,,,,00:00,00:00,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14597,simple,,,"Frymaster 3 (three) - FPRE317CSE",1,0,visible,"The Frymaster FPRE317CSE is a high-performance, electric triple-battery fryer designed for commercial kitchens. It features three 17-liter fry pots, each with its own temperature control, providing efficient and precise frying for a variety of foods. The unit includes advanced safety features, such as automatic shut-off and high-limit protection, ensuring safe operation. Its durable stainless steel construction and easy-to-clean design make it a reliable choice for busy foodservice establishments.","Frymaster 3 (three) well electric operated fryer with\nstainless steel pot, door and cabinet, foot print filtration,\ncomputerized controls, 22 –28 litre shortening capacity\nper fryer, 3 x 2 twin baskets, casters, 3 x 17 KW,\n380V/50Hz/3Ph,\nDim: 1188 x 767 x 1156 mm (H)",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,82400,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Fryers, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/FPRE317CSE-Frymaster-3.gif,,,,,,,,,0,,Frymaster,Brand,Frymaster,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,79,0,,,"Frymaster 3",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,FPRE317CSE,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110111011010110010101001000110001011010111100000,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14599,simple,,,"Direct Gas Fired Conveyor Oven - PS640G-1",1,0,visible,"Direct Gas Fired Conveyor Oven - PS640G-1\nDirect Gas Fired Conveyor Oven - Middleby Marshall PS Series conveyor ovens bake both\nfaster and at a lower temperature than other ovens. All PS640\nWOW! ovens are designed to cook 30% faster than other\nconveyor ovens. The Hearth Bake Belt produces a “deck\noven” bake. The pizza is placed directly on the tightly meshed\nbelt and cooks with impingement and conduction heat. This\nsurpasses the use of screens and gives the user a superior\nadvantage over other conveyor ovens. Operationally, the\nconversion from a deck oven to this system is seamless.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Direct Gas Fired Conveyor Oven - PS640G-1</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Standard Features\n• Impingement PLUS! low oven profile and dual air\nreturn\n• Patented EMS energy Management System\nreduces gas consumption and increases cooking\nefficiency\n• 40-1/2” (1029mm) long cooking chamber\n• 33-1/2” (851mm) wide, 76-1/2” (1943mm) long\nconveyor belt</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Speed\n• Advanced technology air delivery system bakes up\nto 30% faster than standard conveyor ovens</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Energy Management System\nThe PS640 WOW! TM oven features an Energy\nManagement System (EMS) that automatically\nreduces gas consumption. Touch Screen Control can\nbe programmed in one energy saving mode.\nAutomatic “energy eye” saves gas when no pizzas are\nin the oven</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Optional Features\n• Hearth Bake Belt* for a deck oven crust\n• Split belt - two 15” (381mm) belts with individually\nadjustable speed settings</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cleanability\nPS640 Ovens are designed for easy cleaning. Removable\nparts include: crumb pans, end panels, air fingers, and a\nfolding conveyor belt assembly.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Easily Serviced\nControl compartment is designed for quick and easy\naccess.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Warranty\nAll PS640 models have a one year parts and labor warranty.\nOven start-up is included at no additional charge (USA\nOnly). Factory demo available at additional charge</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Ventilation\nFor installation under a ventilation hood only.</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,64341,71490,"Kitchen Equipment, Special Offer, Uncategorized",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/PS640G-WOW-Conveyor-Oven.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"Middleby Marshall",Brand,"Middleby Marshall",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,76,0,,,"Direct Gas Fired Conveyor Oven",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,PS640HG-1,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,15778,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595498,111100011110110000001000010001001001111010111101,,,,,,,,,salescountdowntimer,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14601,simple,,,"Cutter Mixer - BLIXER 4VVA 33221",1,0,visible,"The Cutter Mixer BLIXER 4VVA 33221 is a versatile and efficient kitchen appliance designed for professional use. It combines the functions of a cutter and mixer, enabling the preparation of various textures and consistencies of food. Ideal for healthcare facilities and catering services, it features a robust stainless steel bowl, variable speed control, and a powerful motor to handle a wide range of ingredients, from raw vegetables to cooked meats. The BLIXER 4VVA 33221 ensures smooth, homogenous, and consistent results, making it an essential tool for chefs and food service professionals.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• Cutter Mixer - BLIXER 4VVA 33221</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• BLIXER® 4 V.V. Single phase</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Bowl 4.5 L stainless steel with</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Soft touch handle</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Wattage 1100w, Speed(s) 300 to</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• 3500 rpm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Electric data 230V /50Hz /1ph</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• 4.8A – plug supplied</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Dim: 240 x 330 x 480 mm,</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Weight 15 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Made by Robot Coupe, France</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,9390,"FOOD PROCESSING > Cutter Mixer, FOOD PROCESSING, Kitchen Equipment",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Cutter-Mixer-BLIXER-4VVA-33221.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Cutter-Mixer-BLIXER-4VVA-33221-blade.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Cutter-Mixer1-BLIXER-4VVA-33221.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Cutter-Mixer2-BLIXER-4VVA-33221.png",,,,,,,,,0,,"Robot Coupe",Brand,"Robot Coupe",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,71,0,,,"Cutter Mixer - BLIXER 4VVA",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"BLIXER 4VVA 33221",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595733,001101001110001100101100011011100001110010110011,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14606,simple,,,"TABLE TOP CUTTER MIXER - R7A (24658)",1,0,visible,"TABLE TOP CUTTER MIXER - R7A The must for pastry and kitchen chefs!\nWith its bowl-base twin-blade assembly - a Robot-Coupe innovation - it is the ideal assistant in your kitchen. All preparations can be made by simply pressing a button: emulsions and sauces; mince meat and fish; chop onions, herbs and spices; grind nuts, chocolate or praline; knead dough.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• TABLE TOP CUTTER MIXER - R7A (24658)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cap: 7.5 Liter</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Input power: 1500W/400V/3N/50Hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Speed: 1500-3000 rpm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dimensions: 280x365x540mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Gross Weight: 23/25 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Made by Robot Coupe, France</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,13500,"FOOD PROCESSING > Cutter Mixer, FOOD PROCESSING, Kitchen Equipment",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/TABLE-TOP-CUTTER-MIXER.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/TABLE-TOP-CUTTER-MIXER1.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/TABLE-TOP-CUTTER-MIXER2.png",,,,,,,,,0,,"Robot Coupe",Brand,"Robot Coupe",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,66,0,,,"TABLE TOP CUTTER MIXER - R7A",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"R7A (24658)",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595733,101111001111001101001001010001101001111000011000,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14610,simple,,,"FOOD PROCESSOR CUTTER &amp;  VEGETABLE SLICER - R502G / 2382",1,0,visible,"FOOD PROCESSOR CUTTER &amp; VEGETABLE SLICER - R502G - A multi-function machine designed for vegetable preparation and all round use. Cutter to chop, emulsify, knead, grind and prepare sauces. Vegetable slicer to easily handle your daily preparation, including slicing, grating, ripple cut, julienne, French Fry and dicing.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• FOOD PROCESSOR CUTTER &amp; VEGETABLE SLICER - R502G / 2382</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Cap: 5.9 Liter with stainless steel</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• bowl</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• stainless steel smooth blade knife</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Power: 900W-3 phase, 400/50/3</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Speed 750rpm – 1500 rpm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Dimensions 280x350x480 Net</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Weight: 30/32 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">•Made by Robot Coupe, France</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,14757,"FOOD PROCESSING > Cutter Mixer, FOOD PROCESSING, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/FOOD-PROCESSOR-CUTTER-VEGETABLE-SLICER-R502G-2382.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"Robot Coupe",Brand,"Robot Coupe",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,61,0,,,"FOOD PROCESSOR CUTTER & VEGETABLE SLICER - R502G",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"R502G / 2382",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595316,001110101010111001100001011101100101000011110100,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14612,simple,,,"FOOD PROCESSORS : CUTTER  AND VEGETABLE SLICER -  R301UD / 2678",1,0,visible,"FOOD PROCESSORS : CUTTER AND VEGETABLE SLICER - R301UD\nA multi-function compact table-top model, easy to clean and simple to store - even in the tiniest of kitchens.\n\n- Cutter to chop, emulsify, knead, grind and prepare sauces.\n\n- Vegetable preparation: slice, grate and julienne for salads, sandwich filling and general daily food preparation.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• FOOD PROCESSORS : CUTTER AND VEGETABLE SLICER - R301UD / 2678</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Cap: 3.7 Liters s/s bowl and handle</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Stainless steel smooth blade – included</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Power: 650W-1Ph-230V-1500rpm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• pulse control</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• 2mm &amp; 4mm slicer, 2mm grater,</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• 4×4 julienne – included</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Dim: 355x305x570 mm Weight: 19/20 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Made by Robot Coupe, France</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,8049,"FOOD PROCESSING > Cutter Mixer, FOOD PROCESSING, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/FOOD-PROCESSORS-CUTTER-R301UD-2678.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"Robot Coupe",Brand,"Robot Coupe",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,73,0,,,"FOOD PROCESSORS : CUTTER AND VEGETABLE SLICER - R301UD",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"R301UD / 2678",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595733,011100100101011001000111101100001001101111000011,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14614,simple,,,"LARGE RANGE – POWER MIXER - MP600 ULTRA",1,0,visible,"LARGE RANGE – POWER MIXER - MP600 ULTRA - Even better performance and ergonomics!\nFor intensive use, Institutions and caterers.\nWith a maximum batch capacity of 300L, the MP 600 Ultra can mix, blend and emulsify in no time at all.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• LARGE RANGE – POWER MIXER - MP600 ULTRA</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Power: 850 watts; One Speed: 9500 rpm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Voltage:230V/50/1 UK plug</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Net Weight: 7.4 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Dim:Tube length: 580 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Total length 970 mm Ø 125 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Made by Robot Coupe, France</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,5205,"BAKERY LINE, BAKERY LINE > Bakery Mixers, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Blenders, COFFEE & BAR LINE, Kitchen Equipment",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/LARGE-RANGE-–-POWER-MIXER-MP600-ULTRA.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/LARGE-RANGE-–-POWER-MIXER-MP600-ULTRA3.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/LARGE-RANGE-–-POWER-MIXER-MP600-ULTRA2.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/LARGE-RANGE-–-POWER-MIXER-MP600-ULTRA1.png",,,,,,,,,0,,"Robot Coupe",Brand,"Robot Coupe",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,66,0,,,"LARGE RANGE – POWER MIXER - MP600 ULTRA",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"MP600 ULTRA",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595581,001100110011001100110110011011001110011001001100,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14619,simple,,,"Robot Coupe Blixer 5 Plus Food Processor - BLIXER 5G/BLIXER 5A plus",1,0,visible,"The Blixer 5 Plus can turn cooked or raw ingredients into texture-modified meals (soft, pureed or liquid) in next to no time. Blixers are quick, efficient, simple to use and robust. Add to this a guarantee of a perfectly finished-end product that contains all the goodness and flavour of the pre-liquidised food. Robot Coupe has a range of Blixers, from 3 to 60 litres, accommodating the smallest of aged-care facilities to the largest of hospitals. Blixers are quick, efficient, simple to use and robust. They can process cooked or raw food, without the need to add liquid, meaning none of the nutritional value is lost","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0px"">• Robot Coupe Blixer 5 Plus Food Processor - BLIXER 5G/BLIXER 5A plus</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• BLIXER 5- 2V; Cap: 5.9 Liter</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Stainless steel fine serrated</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• blade with removable cap</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Power: 1500W; Two speed -1500-3000rpm- three phase</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Power: 400V/50/3, Pulse Function,</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Net / Gross Weight: 21/24 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Dim: 280x365x540 mm, Packing</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Dim: 490x390x650 mm ( LDH)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0;padding-top: 0"">• Made by Robot Coupe, France</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,13334,"FOOD PROCESSING > Cutter Mixer, FOOD PROCESSING, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Robot-Coupe-Blixer-5-Plus-Food-Processor.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"Robot Coupe",Brand,"Robot Coupe",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,79,0,,,"Robot Coupe Blixer 5 Plus Food Processor",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"BLIXER 5G/BLIXER 5A plus",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,