14636,simple,,,"MANUAL BAGGING MACHINE - ZLIMB2",1,0,visible,"The Manual Bagging Machine (Model ZLIMB2) is a reliable and efficient solution for garment bagging in commercial laundry and dry-cleaning operations. Designed for ease of use, this machine allows for quick and precise bagging of various garment types, ensuring protection and presentation quality. The ZLIMB2 features a sturdy construction and user-friendly controls, making it simple to operate and maintain. Its compact design allows it to fit seamlessly into any workspace, enhancing productivity and workflow. The Manual Bagging Machine ZLIMB2 is an essential tool for ensuring garments are neatly and securely packaged for storage or delivery.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• MANUAL BAGGING MACHINE - ZLIMB2</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• ROTONDI (ITALY)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• WALL MOUNTED BAGGING MACHINE</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• MODEL: ZLIMB2</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• MANUAL OPERATED</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• VOLTAGE: 220V/50HZ/1PH</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,5264,"ACCESSORIES, Kitchen Equipment, LAUNDRY & DISH WASHER, LAUNDRY & DISH WASHER > Laundry Machines",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/MANUAL-BAGGING-MACHINE.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/MANUAL-BAGGING-MACHINE1.png",,,,,,,,,0,,"Rotondi Group",Brand,"Rotondi Group",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,64,0,,,"MANUAL BAGGING MACHINE - ZLIMB2",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,ZLIMB2,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,15783,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,100111101101011010000100111101001010010100100101,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14639,simple,,,"COMPACT RANGE POWER MIXER - CMP300VV 34231A",1,0,visible,"The COMPACT RANGE POWER MIXER CMP300VV 34231A is a versatile and powerful kitchen appliance designed for efficient mixing, blending, and whipping. With adjustable speed settings, it provides precise control for various culinary tasks, ensuring consistent and professional results. Its compact design allows for easy storage and handling, making it a perfect addition to any kitchen, whether for home cooks or professional chefs.","COMPACT RANGE POWER MIXER\nPower: 350 watts\nVariable Speed: 2300-9600rpm\nVoltage 230V/50/T UK plug\nNet Weight: 3.9kg\nDim: Tube length: 300 mm\nTotal length 660 min 0.94 mm\nMade by Robot Coupe, France",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,2442,"COFFEE & BAR LINE > Blenders, COFFEE & BAR LINE, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/R420.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"Robot Coupe",Brand,"Robot Coupe",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,57,0,,,"COMPACT RANGE POWER MIXER - CMP300VV 34231A",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"CMP300VV 34231A",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595581,011001011001111001101100110001100100110011001100,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14641,simple,,,"La Marzocco Strada S 2G - Coffee Machine",1,0,visible,"Represented in the La Marzocco Strada S is cutting-edge espresso technology, decades of engineering and design and feedback from the top coffee professionals in the world. The Strada has seen multiple iterations over the years, now culminated into the most advanced and refined espresso machine to date. The Strada S exists for the busiest and more discerning cafes who need a machine that can produce drinks at high volume, and who want complete and precise control over every shot of espresso, especially in terms of brew temperature and yield, and statistics tracking.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• La Marzocco Strada S 2G - Coffee Machine</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Specifications 2 groups</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Height (cm/in) 50 / 19,7</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Width (cm/in) 83 / 32,7</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Depth (cm/in) 69 / 27,2</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight (kg/lbs) 77 / 169,4</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Voltage 200V Single Phase</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 220V Single / 3 Phase</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 380V 3 Phase</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Wattage (min) 4330</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Wattage (max) 5666</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Coffee Boiler Capacity (liters) 2,6</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Steam Boiler Capacity (liters) 8,2</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,78000,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Coffee Machines, Kitchen Equipment",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/La-Marzocco-Strada-S-2G-Coffee.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/2-S-abr-2g.DX_.webp, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/4-S-abr-2gr.SX_.webp, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/3-S-abr-2gr.-back.webp",,,,,,,,,0,,"La Marzocco",Brand,"La Marzocco",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,71,0,,,"La Marzocco Strada S 2G - Coffee Machine",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"S 2G",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595055,101010000101000101011110101001111111000011001010,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14646,simple,,,"La Marzocco Strada S 3G - Coffee Machine",1,0,visible,"The La Marzocco Strada S 3G is a premium commercial espresso machine designed for high performance and precision. Featuring three groups, it offers baristas exceptional control with programmable volumetric dosing and advanced temperature stability, thanks to its dual boiler system. The machine boasts a sleek, durable design with a stainless steel exterior, making it a reliable and stylish addition to any café or coffee shop. Its intuitive interface and customizable settings ensure consistent, high-quality espresso shots, catering to the needs of professional baristas and coffee enthusiasts alike.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• La Marzocco Strada S 3G - Coffee Machine</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Specifications 3 groups</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Height (cm/in) 50 / 19,7</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Width (cm/in) 103 / 40,6</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Depth (cm/in) 69 / 27,2</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight (kg/lbs) 94 / 206.4</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Voltage 200V Single Phase</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 220V Single / 3 Phase</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 380V 3 Phase</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Wattage (min) 5830</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Wattage (max) 7783</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Coffee Boiler Capacity (liters) 3,9</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Steam Boiler Capacity (liters) 11,8</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,88000,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Coffee Machines, Kitchen Equipment",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/La-Marzocco-Strada-S-3G-Coffee-Machine.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/6-S-abr-3gr.-DX.webp, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/7-S-abr-3gr.back_.webp",