14652,simple,,,"Blendtec Connoisseur 825 Professional Commercial Blender",1,0,visible,"The Blendtec Connoisseur 825 Quiet Professional Commercial Blender boasts industry-leading power with features designed for Restaurants, Bars &amp; Coffee Shops. The Connoisseur 825 has 30 preprogrammed cycles and is a durable workhorse for high-volume F&amp;B outlets, delivering speed, consistency and quality.","Blendtec Connoisseur 825 Professional Commercial Blender- Including, 2 x 1L Jars with Lid:\n\nThe Connoisseur 825 boasts industry-leading power and a wide range of state-of-the-art features designed to ensure speed, consistency, and quality with each and every order.\n\nDurable High-speed Motor\n\nPerfect for high-volume shops, the Connoisseur 825 is a workhorse built with longevity in mind. The 3.8 peak horsepower motor easily powers through the toughest ingredients, like ice and frozen fruit, without skipping a beat.\n\nPreprogrammed Cycles\n\nThe Connoisseur 825 includes 30 preprogrammed cycles that can blend your most popular recipes with perfect consistency. Each cycle shuts off automatically, freeing up operators for other tasks.\n\nSound Enclosure\n\nFor shops where noise is a consideration, the sound enclosure cuts down on blender noise, helping ensure an undisrupted atmosphere.\n\nFeatures include:\n\nMotor: 3.8 peak horsepower, 1825 watts, 15 amps\nRecommended daily blends: 150+\nProgram cycles: 30 preprogrammed cycles + Pulse\nCountertop or In-Counter\nColors: Black\nHigh Volume, Low Noise\nDimensions\n\nH: 18.7” (47.5 cm)\nD: 9.0” (22.9 cm)\nW: 9.0” (22.9 cm)\n\nWeight : 16.8 lbs (7.6 kg)",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,4850,"COFFEE & BAR LINE > Blenders, COFFEE & BAR LINE, Kitchen Equipment",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Blendtec-Connoisseur-825-Professional-Commercial-Blender.jpg, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Blendtec-Connoisseur-825-Professional-Commercial-Blender-new-1.jpg, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Blendtec-Connoisseur-825-Professional-Commercial-Blender-new-4.jpg",,,,,,,,,0,,Blendec,Brand,Blendec,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,57,0,,,"Blendtec Connoisseur 825 Professional Commercial Blender",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"Connoisseur 825",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596370,010010110000111001010011110100110110010011100110,false,,,,,,,,salescountdowntimer,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14656,simple,,,"Middleby Marshall PS640G-2 GAS Conveyor Oven",1,0,visible,"The Middleby Marshall PS640G-2 Gas Conveyor Oven is a high-performance commercial oven designed for efficiency and versatility. Featuring a continuous conveyor belt, it allows for consistent, even cooking of pizzas, baked goods, and other menu items. Its gas-powered operation offers rapid heat-up and precise temperature control, while the compact design is ideal for busy kitchens with limited space. With robust construction and advanced technology, the PS640G-2 is built to handle high-volume cooking demands while delivering superior results.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Middleby Marshall PS640G-2 GAS Conveyor Oven</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Patented Energy Management System [EMS] Energy consumption and increases</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• cooking efficiency</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Impingement PLUS! low oven profile and dual air return</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Digital controls</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Microprocessor-controlled bake time/conveyor speed</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Stainless steel front, sides, top and interior</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Designed for easy cleaning with removable parts</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Reversible conveyor direction</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 15”(381mm) wide front window</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Cool exterior</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Stackable up to three [3] units high</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,167000,"BAKERY LINE, BAKERY LINE > Bakery Oven, Kitchen Equipment, Special Offer",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Middleby-Marshall-PS640-2-Electric-Conveyor-Oven.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"Middleby Marshall",Brand,"Middleby Marshall",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,54,0,,,"Middleby Marshall PS640G-2 GAS Conveyor Oven",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,PS640G-2,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,15784,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595916,111101011110110000101010000100000110110111100100,true,backend,,,,,,,salescountdowntimer,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14658,simple,,,"HIGH EFFICIENCY GAS FRYER - THEGF 50‐2C",1,0,visible,"The High Efficiency Gas Fryer THEGF 50‐2C is a top-tier commercial fryer designed for optimal performance and energy savings. It features a high-efficiency gas burner system that provides rapid heating and consistent frying results while minimizing fuel consumption. The fryer’s robust construction and advanced filtration system extend oil life and reduce maintenance needs. With precise temperature control and a user-friendly interface, the THEGF 50‐2C ensures perfect, crispy results for a wide variety of fried foods. Ideal for high-volume kitchens, it combines durability with efficiency for reliable, high-quality performance.","HIGH EFFICIENCY GAS FRYER - THEGF 50‐2C\nMPC Model No. THEGF 50‐2C\nTHEGF 50‐2C ‐ TOASTMASTER ‐ PHIL\n50‐2C SPLIT, SINGLE VAT\n■ High efficiency burner 80,000 BTU\n(20,000 BTU / burner).\n■ Programmable 18 channels computerized\ncontroller.\n■ Automatic ignition with flame loss safety\nshut‐off.\n■ High temperature safety limit switch.\n■ 1 1/4” drain valve.\n■ 4” Caster wheels with brakes and with out brakes.\nStainless Steel\nLENGHT x WIDTH x HEIGHT\n403 x 937 x 1145 mm\nCooking Area\n■ 179 L x 356 W x 100 H /VAT\n■ Oil capacity: 20 LBS /VAT4\n240V / 1 Phase / 1200 watts / 5 amps",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,16599,18443,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Fryers, Kitchen Equipment, Special Offer",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Gas-Fryer-THEGF-50‐2C.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Toastmaster,Brand,Toastmaster,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,71,0,,,"HIGH EFFICIENCY GAS FRYER - THEGF 50‐2C",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"THEGF 50‐2C",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110100011011011000101001110100110000110111100001,,,,,,,,,salescountdowntimer,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14660,simple,,,"Toastmaster GRIDDLE - THEG‐24",1,0,visible,"The Toastmaster THEG‐24 Griddle is a durable and efficient countertop appliance designed for commercial kitchens. This gas-powered griddle features a 24-inch cooking surface, perfect for preparing a variety of foods such as pancakes, eggs, burgers, and more. Its robust stainless steel construction ensures longevity, while the precise temperature controls allow for consistent cooking results. The THEG‐24 is equipped with easy-to-clean surfaces and grease management systems, making it an ideal choice for busy food service establishments seeking reliability and performance.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Toastmaster GRIDDLE - THEG‐24</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• GRIDDLE</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Toastmaster (Middleby) Model No. THEG‐24</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• HIGH EFFICIENCY GAS GRIDDLE</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• STANDARD FEATURES (HEG) :STANDARD FEATURES (MEG):\n• Stainless steel front, sides with aluminized rear bottom\n• Infrared ceramic atmospheric burner - no air blowers\n• Solid state temperature controller for each heating zone\n• Full automatic pilot ignition with flame loss detection\n• 1 inch-thick polish rolled steel plate\n• Side grease can at left and right\n• 3/4"" gas connection\n• Rests on 6"" caster wheels\n• Stainless steel front and sides with aluminized rear and bottom\n• Heavy-duty heating elements covering each heating zones\n• Solid state temperature controller for each heating zone\n• Mercury-free heat relay\n• 1 inch-thick polished rolled plate\n• Side grease can at left and right\n• Rests on 6"" caster wheels\n• Includes egg cooker hanger at rear splasher</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,16158,17954,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Grills, Kitchen Equipment, Special Offer",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/GRIDDLE-Toastmaster-Middleby-Model-No.-THEG‐24-HIGH-EFFICIENCY-GAS-GRIDDLE1.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Toastmaster,Brand,Toastmaster,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,68,0,,,"Toastmaster GRIDDLE - THEG‐24",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,THEG‐24,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,15785,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011111000000011000001110110011110011101101000011,,,,,,,,,salescountdowntimer,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14662,simple,,,"FILTERING MACHINE - TMFS‐65",1,0,visible,"The TMFS-65 Filtering Machine is a high-efficiency, compact unit designed for optimal filtration processes. It features advanced technology to effectively remove impurities from liquids, ensuring a cleaner output. Ideal for various industrial applications, this machine is built for durability and ease of maintenance, offering consistent performance and reliable operation.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• FILTERING MACHINE - TMFS‐65</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Toastmaster (Middleby) Model No. TMFS‐65 FILTERING MACHINE</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• STANDARD FEATURES:</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• MODELTMFS-45 LENGTH 468(18.4) WIDTH728(28.6) HEIGHT 543(21.3) KW SHIP WEIGHT (Kilos) 0.4 44</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• MODELTMFS-65 LENGTH 510(20.0) WIDTH808(31.8) HEIGHT 604(23.7) KW SHIP WEIGHT (Kilos) 0.4 51</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• All stainless steel lo-profile construction</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• ON/OFF switch and quick disconnect hose fittings</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Stainless steel filter framing, stainless filter grate and strainer</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Equipped with a 5-feet flush hose assembly</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Rests on 2"" caster wheels, two (2) with brakes</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Includes 10 pieces filter media</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,6462,7181,"COOKING LINE, Kitchen Equipment, Special Offer",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Toastmaster-Middleby-Model-No.-TMFS‐65.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Toastmaster,Brand,Toastmaster,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,76,0,,,"FILTERING MACHINE - TMFS‐65",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,TMFS‐65,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,defa