14666,simple,,,"FRYER FILTER - P14",1,0,visible,"The P14 Fryer Filter is an essential tool for maintaining oil quality and extending the life of your fryer. Designed for efficiency and ease of use, it effectively removes food particles and impurities from frying oil, resulting in better-tasting food and cost savings on oil consumption. The P14 is built with durable materials, ensuring long-lasting performance and minimal maintenance. Ideal for both commercial and industrial kitchen settings.","FRYER FILTER, MOBILE\nPitco Frialator (Middleby) Model No. P14\nFryer Filter, mobile, 55 lb. oil capacity, 18 gauge stainless steel lift‐\ncover, low‐profile design, with pump &amp; hose assembly, stainless\nsteel, for use with all 7, 12 (floor), &amp; 14 size fryers, CSA, NSF, UL,\nCE (Ships within 1‐2 days)\n9 ea 220/240v/50/1‐ph, 4.0 amps, (5.6 GPM) contact factory",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,13672,15191,"ACCESSORIES, COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Fryers, Kitchen Equipment, Special Offer",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/FRYER-FILTER-MOBILE-Model-No.-P14.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Pitco,Brand,Pitco,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,62,0,,,"FRYER FILTER - P14",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,P14,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011111100101111000000111100100001111100001001100,,,,,,,,,salescountdowntimer,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14668,simple,,,"PITCO FRYER SE14-C-2FD",1,0,visible,"The PITCO FRYER SE14-C-2/FD is a high-efficiency, electric commercial deep fryer designed for fast food and restaurant use. It features a stainless steel tank and cabinet for durability, a solid-state thermostat for precise temperature control, and an automatic filtration system to prolong oil life. This model is known for its energy efficiency and consistent performance, making it ideal for high-volume frying operations.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• PITCO FRYER SE14-C-2/FD</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Solstice™ Prepackaged Fryer System with Solstice™ Filter Drawer System</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• High Power</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• electric</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• (2) 50 lb. oil capacity full tanks</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• solid state controls</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• boil out, drain valve interlock</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• melt cycle</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• stainless steel tank</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• front &amp; sides</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• under‐fryer drawer filtration</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• total 34.0kW (‐FF)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• ENERGY STAR®</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• cULus, NSF, CE, GS (2) 380/220v/50/3‐ph, ""Y"", 22 kW</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• DIRECT (contact factory) Computer Controller P6072145 Basket</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• (2) oblong/twin size</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 13‐1/2"" x 6‐1/2"" x 5‐3/4"" deep</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• long handle</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• regular mesh (shipped std (n/c) with models\n""T"" SG14, SG14R, SSH55, SE14, SE14X, SE14B, SG14T, 35+, 45+, fryer\nbatteries shipped with (1) per fryer\n9"" legs, standard</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,76912,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Fryers, Kitchen Equipment, Special Offer",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/PITCO-FRYER-SE14-C-2-FD.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Pitco,Brand,Pitco,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,33,0,,,"PITCO FRYER SE14-C-2/FD",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,SE14-C-2FD,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110100101001110010101000011110100101101010100101,true,backend,,,,,,,salescountdowntimer,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14670,simple,,,"ELECTRIC FLOOR FRYER - SE14C",1,0,visible,"The PITCO SE14C Electric Floor Fryer is a commercial-grade deep fryer designed for high-efficiency frying in restaurants and fast food establishments. It features a stainless steel tank and cabinet for durability, a precise solid-state thermostat for temperature control, and an easy-to-use manual control system. This model is renowned for its reliability and energy efficiency, making it a preferred choice for establishments needing consistent frying performance.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• ELECTRIC FLOOR FRYER - SE14C</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Pitco Frialator Model No. SE14C Solstice™ Fryer</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• electric</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• floor model</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• full frypot</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 40 ‐ 50 lb. oil capacity</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• solid state controls</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• melt cycle</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• boil out capacity</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• drain valve interlock switch</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• stainless steel tank</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• front &amp; sides</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 17.0kW</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• ENERGY STAR®, cULus, NSF, CE, GS\n380/220v/50/60/3‐ph, 17 kW, ""Y"", DIRECT, (contact factory)\nComputer Controller</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• P6072145 Basket, (2) oblong/twin size, 13‐1/2"" x 6‐1/2"" x 5‐3/4""\ndeep, long handle, regular mesh (shipped std (n/c) with models\n""T"" SG14, SG14R, SSH55, SE14, SE14X, SE14B, SG14T, 35+, 45+, fryer\nbatteries shipped with (1) per fryer\n9"" legs, standard</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,28704,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Fryers, Kitchen Equipment, Special Offer",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ELECTRIC-FLOOR-FRYER-SE14C-1.webp,,,,,,,,,0,,Pitco,Brand,Pitco,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,56,0,,,"ELECTRIC FLOOR FRYER - SE14C",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,SE14C,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011000001110011000110110011100110111011010011000,true,backend,,,,,,,salescountdowntimer,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14672,simple,,,"GAS FRYER - SGH50TC",1,0,visible,"The PITCO SGH50TC Gas Fryer is a high-performance, commercial-grade fryer designed for efficient and reliable frying in restaurant and food service environments. It features a stainless steel tank and cabinet for enhanced durability, and a tube-type heat exchanger system that ensures even heat distribution and optimal cooking performance. The fryer is equipped with a thermostat for precise temperature control and a user-friendly interface for easy operation. Its high capacity and energy efficiency make it an excellent choice for busy kitchens.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• GAS FRYER - SGH50TC</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Pitco Frialator (Middleby) Model No. SGH50TC</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• High Efficiency Gas Frying System</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• The PITCO SGH50TC Gas Fryer is a high-performance, commercial-grade fryer designed for efficient and reliable frying in restaurant and food service environments. It features a stainless steel tank and cabinet for enhanced durability, and a tube-type heat exchanger system that ensures even heat distribution and optimal cooking performance. The fryer is equipped with a thermostat for precise temperature control and a user-friendly interface for easy operation. Its high capacity and energy efficiency make it an excellent choice for busy kitchens.</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,28667,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Fryers, Kitchen Equipment, Special Offer",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/GAS-FRYER-–-SGH50TC-3.webp,,,,,,,,,0,,Pitco,Brand,Pitco,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,60,0,,,"GAS FRYER - SGH50TC",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,SGH50TC,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,111001001100010010011100100110011011001100110011,true,backend