14674,simple,,,"FRYER BATTERY, GAS - SSH55C‐3FD",1,0,visible,"The PITCO SSH55C-3FD Fryer Battery is a high-efficiency, gas-powered commercial fryer setup designed for heavy-duty frying operations in restaurants and fast food establishments. This model consists of three fryer units combined into one cohesive system, allowing for simultaneous frying of multiple food items. Each fryer features a stainless steel tank and cabinet for durability, an advanced burner design for optimal heat transfer, and precise temperature control for consistent cooking results. The integrated filtration system helps extend oil life and maintain food quality. The SSH55C-3FD is known for its reliability, energy efficiency, and high frying capacity, making it ideal for high-volume kitchens.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• FRYER BATTERY, GAS - SSH55C‐3FD</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Pitco Frialator (Middleby) Model No. SSH55C‐3FD</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Solstice Supreme™ High Efficiency Prepackaged Fryer System with Solstice™ Filter Drawer System</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• gas</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• (3) 40‐50 lb. oil capacity full tanks</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• solid state controls</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• boil out &amp; melt cycle</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• drain valve interlock</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• matchless ignition</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• self‐clean burner</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• downdraft protection</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• stainless steel tank</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• front &amp; sides</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• under‐fryer drawer filtration</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• total 240,000 BTU (‐FFF)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• ENERGY STAR®</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• CSA Flame</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• CSAStar, NSF, CE LP gas</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Computer Controller</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 220‐240v/50/1‐ph</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• P6072145 Basket</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• (2) oblong/twin size</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 13‐1/2"" x 6‐1/2"" x 5‐3/4"" deep</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• long handle</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• regular mesh (shipped std (n/c) with models\n""T"" SG14, SG14R, SSH55, SE14, SE14X, SE14B, SG14T, 35+, 45+, fryer\nbatteries shipped with (1) per fryer\n9"" legs, standard</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,74854,83172,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Fryers, Kitchen Equipment, Special Offer",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/FRYER-BATTERY-GAS-SSH55C‐3FD.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Pitco,Brand,Pitco,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,81,0,,,"FRYER BATTERY,GAS - SSH55C‐3FD",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,SSH55C‐3FD,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011111011010010000101001001110100001110110100101,,,,,,,,,salescountdowntimer,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14676,simple,,,"ELECTRIC FLOOR FRYER - SE14TC",1,0,visible,"The PITCO SE14TC Electric Floor Fryer is a commercial-grade deep fryer designed for high-volume frying tasks. It features a durable stainless steel tank and cabinet, providing both longevity and ease of maintenance. The fryer is equipped with a precise solid-state thermostat for accurate temperature control and an efficient heating element for consistent cooking results. Its high-capacity design is ideal for busy kitchens, allowing for large quantities of food to be fried simultaneously.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• ELECTRIC FLOOR FRYER - . SE14TC</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Pitco Frialator (Middleby) Model No. SE14TC</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Solstice™ Fryer, electric, floor model, split frypot</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• (2) 20 ‐ 25 lb. oil capacity tanks</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• solid state controls</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• melt cycle</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• boil out capacity</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• drain valve interlock switch</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• stainless steel tanks</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• front &amp; sides</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• total (2) 8.5kW, cULus, NSF, CE, GS</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 380/220v/50/60/3‐ph, 17 kW, ""Y"", DIRECT</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• (contact factory) (C) Intellifry Computer Controller P6072145 Basket</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• (2) oblong/twin size, 13‐1/2"" x 6‐1/2"" x 5‐3/4"" deep</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• long handle</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• regular mesh (shipped std (n/c) with models\n""T"" SG14, SG14R, SSH55, SE14, SE14X, SE14B, SG14T, 35+, 45+, fryer\nbatteries shipped with (1) per fryer\n9"" legs, standard</p