14678,simple,,,"FRYER BATTERY, ELECTRIC, DUAL TANK - SF‐SE14C",1,0,visible,"The PITCO SF-SE14C Electric Fryer Battery is a versatile, high-capacity commercial fryer system featuring dual tanks for increased frying efficiency. This setup allows for simultaneous cooking of different items or larger quantities of food, making it ideal for high-demand kitchens. Each tank is constructed from durable stainless steel, ensuring longevity and ease of cleaning. The fryer battery is equipped with solid-state thermostats for precise temperature control, and the advanced heating elements provide consistent and reliable performance. Its efficient design helps streamline operations and maximize productivity in busy food service environments.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• FRYER BATTERY, ELECTRIC, DUAL TANK - SF‐SE14C</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• FRYER BATTERY, ELECTRIC, DUAL TANK $37,435.15</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Pitco Frialator (Middleby) Model No. SF‐SE14C</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Solstice™ Prepackaged Fryer System with Solstice™ Solo Filter System</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• electric</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• twin tanks</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 20‐25 lb. oil capacity per tank</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• melt cycle</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• solid state controls</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• boil out capacity</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• drain valve interlock switch</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• stainless steel tank front</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• sides, under‐fryer drawer\nfiltration, total 17.0kW, ENERGY STAR®, UL, NSF, CE\n380/220v/50/3‐ph, ""Y"", 26.0 amps, 17 kW, DIRECT (contact factory)\n(C) Intellifry Computer Controller\nP6072145 Basket, (2) oblong/twin size, 13‐1/2"" x 6‐1/2"" x 5‐3/4""\ndeep, long 