14681,simple,,,"GRIDDLE, GAS, COUNTERTOP - 824TA",1,0,visible,"The 824TA Gas Countertop Griddle is a commercial-grade cooking appliance designed for efficient and versatile grilling in a compact form. It features a durable, stainless steel construction for easy maintenance and long-lasting performance. The griddle is equipped with powerful burners for rapid heating and even heat distribution, ensuring consistent cooking results. Its countertop design makes it suitable for kitchens with limited space, while the adjustable thermostat allows for precise temperature control. Ideal for cooking a variety of foods, from pancakes and eggs to burgers and sandwiches, the 824TA enhances kitchen efficiency and flexibility.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• GRIDDLE, GAS, COUNTERTOP - 824TA</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Star (Middleby) Model No. 824TA</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Ultra‐Max® Griddle</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• countertop gas</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 24"" W x 24"" D cooking surface</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 1"" thick steel griddle plate</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 150° ‐ 550° F embedded mechanical snap‐action thermostat every 12"", 4‐3/8"" tapered wrap‐around splash guard, 3‐1/2"" front grease trough</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• heavy‐duty metal knobs</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• standing pilot</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• welded steel frame with stainless steel exterior 4</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• stainless steel legs with 1‐3/8"" adjustment, 60,000 BTU, cULus, UL EPH Classified, Made in USA 3 ea (824TA‐LP) L.P. gas, 60,000 BTU (Specify elevation over 2,000 ft.) (Not available as Quick Ship</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,18508,20565,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Grills, Kitchen Equipment, Special Offer",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2