14683,simple,,,"GRIDDLE, GAS, COUNTERTOP - 848TA",1,0,visible,"The 848TA Gas Countertop Griddle is a high-performance commercial appliance designed for versatile cooking in a compact space. It features a durable stainless steel construction for long-lasting use and easy cleaning. Equipped with powerful, evenly distributed burners, the griddle ensures consistent cooking results. The adjustable thermostat allows for precise temperature control, making it suitable for a variety of foods, from breakfast items like pancakes and eggs to burgers and sandwiches. Its countertop design makes it an excellent choice for kitchens with limited space while maximizing cooking efficiency.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• GRIDDLE, GAS, COUNTERTOP - 848TA</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Star Model No. 848TA</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Ultra‐Max® Griddle</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• countertop gas</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 48"" W x 24"" D cooking surface</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 1"" thick steel griddle plate,</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 150° ‐ 550° F embedded mechanical snap‐action thermostat every 12</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 4‐3/8"" tapered wrap‐around splash guard</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 3‐1/2"" front grease trough</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• heavy‐duty metal knobs</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• standing pilot</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">•welded steel frame with stainless steel exterior, 4</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• stainless steel legs with 1‐3/8"" adjustment, 120,000 BTU, cULus, UL\nEPH Classified, Made in USA\n4 ea (848TA‐LP) L.P. gas, 120,000 BTU (Specify elevation over 2,000 ft.)</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,20565,22850,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Grills, Kitchen Equipment, Special Offer",,,https://mariotstore.com/w