14685,simple,,,"GRIDDLE, GAS, COUNTERTOP - 860TA",1,0,visible,"The 860TA Gas Countertop Griddle is a commercial-grade cooking appliance designed for high efficiency and durability. It features a robust stainless steel construction, ensuring long-term use and easy maintenance. The griddle is equipped with powerful, evenly distributed burners for consistent heat across the cooking surface, allowing for versatile cooking of various foods. With an adjustable thermostat, it provides precise temperature control, making it suitable for items ranging from breakfast foods to grilled sandwiches and burgers. Its countertop design makes it a practical choice for kitchens with limited space.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• GRIDDLE, GAS, COUNTERTOP - 860TA</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Star (Middleby) Model No. 860TA</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Ultra‐Max® Griddle</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• countertop gas</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 60"" W x 24"" D cooking surface</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• 1"" thick steel griddle plate, 150° ‐ 550° F embedded mechanical\nsnap‐action thermostat every 12"", 4‐3/8"" tapered wrap‐around\nsplash guard, 3‐1/2"" front grease trough, heavy‐duty metal knobs,\nstanding pilot, welded steel frame with stainless steel exterior, 4""\nstainless steel legs with 1‐3/8"" adjustment, 150,000 BTU, cULus, UL\nEPH Classified, Made in USA\n3 ea (860TA‐LP) L.P. gas, 150,000 BTU (Specify elevation over 2,000 ft.)</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,26294,29216,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Grills, Kitchen Equipment, Special Offer",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/GRIDDLE-GAS-COUNTERTOP-860TA.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"Star Manufacturing USA",Brand,"Star Manufacturing USA",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,74,0,,,"GRIDDLE,GAS,COUNTERTOP - 860TA",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,860TA,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517f