14687,simple,,,"Commercial Nachos Warmer 39 * 31 * 57 cm",1,0,visible,"The Commercial Nachos Warmer, with dimensions of 39 x 31 x 57 cm, is designed to keep nachos and similar foods at the ideal serving temperature in a busy food service environment. It features a durable construction, often stainless steel, for easy cleaning and long-lasting use. The unit typically includes adjustable temperature controls to ensure the cheese and toppings remain warm and ready to serve. Its compact size makes it suitable for countertops or other limited spaces, enhancing convenience and efficiency in serving nachos and other heated snacks.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Commercial Nachos Warmer 39 * 31 * 57 cm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Product Name: Chips warming showcase/ nachos warmer</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Application: Snack Bar, Restaurant</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• The Commercial Nachos Warmer, with dimensions of 39 x 31 x 57 cm, is designed to keep nachos and similar foods at the ideal serving temperature in a busy food service environment. It features a durable construction, often stainless steel, for easy cleaning and long-lasting use. The unit typically includes adjustable temperature controls to ensure the cheese and toppings remain warm and ready to serve. Its compact size makes it suitable for countertops or other limited spaces, enhancing convenience and efficiency in serving nachos and other heated snacks.</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,950,"COOKING LINE, FOOD PROCESSING, Kitchen Equipment, SNACK MAKER",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Commercial-Nachos-Warmer1.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Commercial-Nachos-Warmer.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Commercial-Nachos-Warme1r.png",,,,,,,,,0,,Mariot,Brand,Mariot,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,68,0,,,"Commercial Nachos Warmer 39 * 31 * 57 cm",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"39 * 31 * 57 cm",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595813,010110011001111011001100110110000010011011101000,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14691,simple,,,"HALO HEAT TRIPLE WARMING DRAWERS - 500-3D",1,0,visible,"Designed for durability and deliciousness, the 500-3D can fit any kitchen layout where food needs to be held and within arm's reach. Using Halo Heat® technology, prepared food is kept hot and fresh without the use of added water or harsh heating elements. Flexible configurations available. Build into cabinets or counters, or stack to maximize space.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• HALO HEAT TRIPLE WARMING DRAWERS - 500-3D</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• <strong>Key Features</strong></p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Consistent, even heat. Halo Heat® technology provides a controlled, uniform heat source that maintains precise temperatures throughout the holding process.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Place anywhere. No oven hood or outside venting required. Save up to $30 per day in hood operating costs. Portable and stackable configurations available to maximize space.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Unique thermal cabling surrounds the cavity with gentle, precise heat to evenly warm food and retain moisture. No fans. No harsh heating elements. No added humidity.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Maintain precise temperatures. Digital control senses temperature drops faster, providing quick heat and improving recovery time.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Waterless design. Reduce installation and operating costs with no plumbing, drains, filtration or associated maintenance.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Reduce prep time and labor costs. Prepare food hours before serving, and hold it at the optimal temperature for the best quality and taste in time for service.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• <strong>Product Details</strong></p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• CAPACITY\nPer Compartment</p>\n1 Full-Size Steam Table Pan (6"")\n1 GN 1/1 Pan (152mm)\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• DIMENSIONS H X W X D\n26 1/8""” x 24 5/8” x 25 7/8”\n(664mm x 624mm x 657mm)</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,75,,,,1,,,16595,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Food Warmers, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Holding_500-3D_Front.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"Alto Shaam",Brand,"Alto Shaam",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,55,0,,,"HALO HEAT TRIPLE WARMING DRAWERS",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,500-3D,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596054,000000111110001111011001000011110110000100111101,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14693,simple,,,"HALO HEAT DOUBLE WARMING DRAWERS - 500-2D",1,0,visible,"Designed for durability and deliciousness, the 500-2D can fit any kitchen layout where food needs to be held and within arm's reach. Using Halo Heat® technology, prepared food is kept hot and fresh without the use of added water or harsh heating elements. Flexible configurations available. Build into cabinets or counters, or stack to maximize space.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• HALO HEAT DOUBLE WARMING DRAWERS - 500-2D</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• <strong>Key Features</strong></p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• - Sealed, static holding environment traps natural flavor and juices, reducing shrink, improving food quality and extending hold life.</p>\n- Maintain food quality. Keep product at its perfect serving temperature and hold for hours without overcooking or drying out.\n\n- Easy to operate. Adjustable, electronic thermostat with digital display monitors the inside temperature to ensure food is being held at safe and precise temperatures.\n\n- Easy to clean. Simply remove shelves and wipe clean.\n\n- Greater yields and less food waste with Halo Heat technology. Minimize food costs with less overcooking and shrinkage compared to conventional holding.\n\n- Expand menus. Reduce prep time and labor costs. Prepare food hours before serving, and hold it at the optimal temperature for the best quality and taste at time of service.\n\n- Vented drawers available for operations holiding cripier food items.\n\n- Drawers can be mounted on casters for easy mobility.\n\n- Build onto cabinets or counters or stack to further mazimize space.\n\n- Made in the USA with a commitment to quality.\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• CAPACITY\nPer Compartment</p>\n1 Full-Size Steam Table Pan (6"")\n1 GN 1/1 Pan (152mm)\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• DIMENSIONS H X W X D\n18 15/16” x 24 5/8” x 25 7/8”\n(481mm x 624mm x 657mm)</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,52,,,,1,,,13504,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Food Warmers, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Holding_500-2D_Front.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"Alto Shaam",Brand,"Alto Shaam",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,52,0,,,"HALO HEAT DOUBLE WARMING DRAWERS",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,500-2D,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596053,100010011111100111011000010001011110000000011111,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14695,simple,,,"SINGLE LAMP HOT CARVING STATION - CS-100",1,0,visible,"While many carving stations rely solely on old-fashioned heat lamps, Alto-Shaam’s Heated Carving Stations keep food warmed from below and above. Soft, gentle Halo Heat® radiates from the carving shelf surface, while ambient surface lamps effectively maintain temperature from above, without cooking or drying out the food.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• SINGLE LAMP HOT CARVING STATION - CS-100</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• <strong>Key Features</strong></p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Optional breath guard. Decorative clear glass breath guard provides for a more upscale food display and is easily removed for cleaning.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Quality cutting board. The NSF- and USDA-listed cutting board has an integrated gravy lane and is completely removable for easy cleanup. The cutting board remains pliable when heated, providing more consistent heat transfer for greater food safety and longer shelf life.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Radiant temperature control. Radiant Halo Heat technology, combined with attractive ambient lighting, maintains food temperatures over time effectively without overcooking or drying food out.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Portable. Heated Carving Stations are designed to fit as a mobile or stationary service station when placed on top of a 500 Series Cook &amp; Hold Oven or Heated Holding Cabinet.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• <strong>CS-100 PRODUCT DETAILS</strong></p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• CAPACITY\n35 lbs (16kg)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• DIMENSIONS (H X W X D)\n31-3/16"" x 18-3/16"" x 24-5/8""\n792mm x 463mm x 626mm</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,23,,,,1,,,11801,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Food Warmers, Kitchen Equipment",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/CS-100_fd_hr.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/CS-100-S_hr.png",,,,,,,,,0,,"Alto Shaam",Brand,"Alto Shaam",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,57,0,,,"SINGLE LAMP HOT CARVING STATION,SINGLE LAMP HOT CARVING STATION - CS-100",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,CS-100,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596127,001000011110110011010010010011011110100100111100,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14698,simple,,,"DOUBLE LAMP HOT CARVING STATION - CS-200",1,0,visible,"While many carving stations rely solely on old-fashioned heat lamps, Alto-Shaam’s Heated Carving Stations keep food warmed from below and above. Soft, gentle Halo Heat® radiates from the carving shelf surface, while ambient surface lamps effectively maintain temperature from above, without cooking or drying out the food.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• DOUBLE LAMP HOT CARVING STATION - CS-200</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• <strong>Key Features</strong></p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Optional breath guard. Decorative clear glass breath guard provides for a more upscale food display and is easily removed for cleaning.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Quality cutting board. The NSF- and USDA-listed cutting board has an integrated gravy lane and is completely removable for easy cleanup. The cutting board remains pliable when heated, providing more consistent heat transfer for greater food safety and longer shelf life.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Radiant temperature control. Radiant Halo Heat technology, combined with attractive ambient lighting, maintains food temperatures over time effectively without overcooking or drying food out.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Portable. Heated Carving Stations are designed to fit as a mobile or stationary service station when placed on top of a 500 Series Cook &amp; Hold Oven or Heated Holding Cabinet.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• <strong>CS-200 PRODUCT DETAILS</strong></p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• CAPACITY\n70 lbs (32 kgs)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• DIMENSIONS (H X W X D)\n33-3/16"" x 25-3/4"" x 29-5/16""\n842mm x 654mm x 744mm</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,68,,,,1,,,13771,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Food Warmers, Kitchen Equipment",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/CS-200_noBreathGuard_hr.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/CS-200-S_hr.png",,,,,,,,,0,,"Alto Shaam",Brand,"Alto Shaam",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,58,0,,,"DOUBLE LAMP HOT CARVING STATION",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,CS-200,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596931,101001000001111100100111101011010001111000011100,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14701,simple,,,"HIGH VOLUME DOUBLE COMPARTMENT HOLDING CABINET - 1200-UP",1,0,visible,"Double the volume and precision. With two individually-controlled cabinets, the 1200-UP is designed to help you hold more, with less effort while reducing footprint in the kitchen. Precision controls and SureTemp™ technology ensure that food is held at exactly the right temperature until it’s time to be served.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• HIGH VOLUME DOUBLE COMPARTMENT HOLDING CABINET - 1200-UP</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• <strong>Key Features</strong></p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Consistent, even heat. Halo Heat® technology provides a controlled, uniform heat source that maintains precise temperatures throughout the holding process.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Place anywhere. No oven hood or outside venting required. Save up to $30 per day in hood operating costs. Portable and stackable configurations available to maximize space.</p>\np style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;""&gt;• Unique thermal cabling surrounds the cavity with gentle, precise heat to evenly warm food and retain moisture. No fans. No harsh heating elements. No added humidity.\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Maintain precise temperatures. Digital control senses temperature drops faster, providing quick heat and improving recovery time.</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Waterless design. Reduce installation and operating costs with no plumbing, drains, filtration or associated maintenance.</p>\np style="" margin: 0; padding-top: 0;""&gt;• Reduce prep time and labor costs. Prepare food hours before serving, and hold it at the optimal temperature for the best quality and taste in time for service.\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• <strong>1200-UP PRODUCT DETAILS</strong></p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• CAPACITY\nPer Compartment</p>\n8 Full-Size Hotel Pans (4”)\n16 Full-Size Hotel Pans (2-1/2"")\n16 Full-Size Sheet Pans (1"")\n\n8 GN 1/1 Pans (100mm)\n16 GN 1/1 Pans (65mm)\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• DIMENSIONS H X W X D\n75-13/16” x 26-7/16” x 32-3/16”\n(1924mm x 671mm x 817mm)</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,151,,,,1,,,32736,"ACCESSORIES, COOKING LINE, Kitchen Equipment",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Holding_1200-UP_Front.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Holding_1200-UP_Door-Open-Universal.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Holding_1200-UP_Door-Open-SR.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Holding_1200-UP_Door-Open.png",,,,,,,,,0,,"Alto Shaam",Brand,"Alto Shaam",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,55,0,,,"HIGH VOLUME DOUBLE COMPARTMENT HOLDING CABINE",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,1200-UP,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,100111110011100110101001100001101011011000011000,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14706,simple,,,"Ubermilk Machine - Ubermilk",1,0,visible,"The Ubermilk Machine is a state-of-the-art automated milk frother designed for high-demand cafes and coffee shops. It delivers consistently perfect steamed milk and microfoam for various beverages at the touch of a button, improving efficiency and ensuring top-quality drinks every time. The machine's intuitive interface and customizable settings make it a versatile and essential tool for baristas seeking to enhance their service speed and beverage quality.","<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• <strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Perfect and consistent milk foam anytime</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Infinity mode for your peak periods- reducing queues</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Individual quantities keep food costs down - economical and waste reducing</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• High resolution one touch display</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Hygienic milk frothing from the first cup to the last</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Simple semi-automatic cleaning</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• More time for customer interaction</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Helps any barista to achieve latte art skills</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• <strong>Product designation</strong></p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Width x height x depth 180 mm x 540 mm x 485 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Weight 25 kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Voltage 220-240 V</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power consumption 3100 W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Frequency 50/60 Hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Ambient temperature +10°C to +40°C</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Temperature setting Limited from 55°C - 68°C (recommended 65°C)</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Length of the milk hose Max. 2 m</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Diameter of the milk hose 6 mm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Milk throughput 1,3 liters per minute / 250 drinks per hour</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Important note on the installation of the Übermilk The line for the device should be fused separately!</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,39000,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Coffee Machines, Kitchen Equipment",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ubermilk-Machine1.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ubermilk-Machine.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ubermilk-Machine2.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ubermilk-Machine3.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ubermilk-Machine4.png",,,,,,,,,0,,ubermilk,Brand,ubermilk,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,68,0,,,"Ubermilk Machine",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,Ubermilk,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,15786,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595055,110000011100010011011100110100100101101101100011,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14712,simple,,,"Commercial Snowflake ice machine - ZB-XBJ60F",1,0,visible,"The Commercial Snowflake Ice Machine - ZB-XBJ60F is a high-efficiency appliance designed for producing premium snowflake ice. Ideal for bars, restaurants, and cafes, this machine ensures a consistent output of finely textured ice perfect for cocktails and cold displays. With its durable stainless steel construction, user-friendly controls, and reliable performance, the ZB-XBJ60F is an essential addition to any commercial kitchen aiming to enhance its beverage and food presentation.","<p style=""margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0px;"">• Commercial Snowflake ice machine - ZB-XBJ60F</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Snowflake Ice Shaved Machine Milk Snow Ice Machine Bingsu Maker for Snack Bar Ice Cream Shop</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Frequency - 50/60Hz</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Power - 360W</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Dimension - 29*48.5*34cm</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• N.W - 18.5kg</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Refrigerant - R290</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Amount of Refrigerant - 100g</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Manufacture- Jun 12 2024</p>\n<p style=""margin: 0; padding-top: 0;"">• Manufacturing No - A-XBJ202406120007</p>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,2500,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, Kitchen Equipment, Special Offer",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/snow-maker5.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/snow-maker4.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/snow-maker3.png",,,,,,,,,0,,Mariot,Brand,Mariot,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,79,0,,,"Commercial Snowflake ice machine,Commercial Snowflake ice machine - ZB-XBJ60F",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,ZB-XBJ60F,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,