14726,simple,,,"LA MINERVA MEAT MINCER - C/42",1,0,visible,"The MEAT MINCER - C/42 is a high-capacity, heavy-duty meat grinder designed for industrial and commercial use. Equipped with a robust motor and superior cutting blades, this mincer ensures efficient and uniform meat processing, making it ideal for large-scale operations such as butcher shops, meat processing plants, and commercial kitchens. Its durable construction guarantees long-term reliability and performance, enabling the production of finely ground meat, sausages, and other meat products with ease and precision.","• MEAT MINCER 42\n• Output: kg/h (kg/min): 800 (13,3)\n• Casing and feed pan in stainless steel\n• Internal stainless steel head equipped with:\n• Enterprise: 1 plate and 1 self-sharpening knife in stainless steel\n• Removable mincing group for an easy and fast cleaning\n• Forced ventilation motor\n• Forward run, stop and reverse controls\n• Meat mincer power: kW (HP): 3 (4)\n• Weight : 50 kg\n• Power Supply: 400V/3 / 50 Hz\n• Dim: 373 x 629 x 565 / 710 mm\n• C/42 | MINERVA | ITALY""",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,11888,13209,"FOOD PROCESSING, Kitchen Equipment, FOOD PROCESSING > Meat Mincer, Special Offer",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/mEAT-MINCER-A42L.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"LA MINERVA",Brand,"LA MINERVA",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,74,0,,,"MEAT MINCER,MEAT MINCER - C/42",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,C/42,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595653,011100001110011000010110110000111111001101100010,,,,,,,,,salescountdowntimer,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14728,simple,,,"OMEGA MEAT MINCER - TE 22 A",1,0,visible,"The MEAT MINCER - TE 22 A is a versatile and efficient meat grinding machine suitable for both commercial and home use. Featuring a powerful motor and high-quality blades, this mincer ensures consistent and precise meat processing. Its durable construction and user-friendly design make it ideal for producing ground meat, sausages, and other meat products with ease. The TE 22 A model offers reliability and performance, making it an essential tool for butchers, chefs, and cooking enthusiasts.","• MEAT MINCER 22\n• Output: kg/h (kg/min): 270\n• Body of aluminium alloy polished and anodised.\n• A sturdy, reliable machine.\n• Easy to clean.\n• Space-saving design.\n• For retail, small supermarkets and collective catering.\n• Barrel, worm, locking ring and meat receiving tray (optional) made of stainless steel .\n• Removable feed pan.\n• Enterprise version: 1 stainless steel holeplate and 1 self-sharpening knife, 1 extractor.\n• Start, stop and reverse (optional) with N.V.R. device.\n• Motor TPH kW (HP): 0,75 (1)\n• Motor SPH kW (HP): 1,1 (1,5)\n• Net weight TPH (SPH)kg: 32 (35)\n• Power Supply: 220V / 1 / 50 Hz\n• Dim: 185 x 260 / 420 x 500 mm\n• TE 22 A | SILVER | OMEGA | ITALY""",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,7144,7938,"FOOD PROCESSING, Kitchen Equipment, FOOD PROCESSING > Meat Mincer, Special Offer",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/mEAT-MINCER-TE22A.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"OMEGA FOOD TECH",Brand,"OMEGA FOOD TECH",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,62,0,,,"MEAT MINCER,MEAT MINCER - TE 22 A",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"TE 22 A",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734597027,110010100111110010110011100011010000111001001001,true,backend,,,,,,,salescountdowntimer,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
