14738,simple,,,"OMEGA MEAT MINCER 380V- TA 32 V",1,0,visible,"The MEAT MINCER 380V - TA 32 V is a high-capacity, industrial-grade meat grinder designed for heavy-duty commercial use. Featuring a powerful 380V motor and precision-engineered blades, this mincer ensures efficient and consistent meat processing, making it ideal for large-scale meat processing operations, such as butcher shops and meat processing facilities. Its robust construction ensures durability and long-term performance, while its user-friendly design enhances ease of use. The TA 32 V model is perfect for producing ground meat, sausages, and other meat products with precision and reliability.","• MEAT MINCER 32\n• Output: kg/h (kg/min): 500\n• Body of aluminium alloy polished and anodised.\n• A sturdy, reliable machine.\n• Easy to clean.\n• Space-saving design.\n• For retail, small supermarkets and collective catering.\n• Barrel, worm, locking ring and meat receiving tray (optional) made of stainless steel .\n• Removable feed pan.\n• Enterprise version: 1 stainless steel holeplate and 1 self-sharpening knife, 1 extractor.\n• Start, stop and reverse (optional) with N.V.R. device.\n• Motor TPH kW (HP): 2,20 (3,00)\n• Motor SPH kW (HP): 1,8 (2,5)\n• Net weight TPH (SPH)kg: 60 (63)\n• Power Supply: 380V / 2 / 50 Hz\n• Dim: 220 x 260 / 560 x 590 mm\n• TA 32 V | RED | OMEGA | ITALY""",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,10924,12138,"FOOD PROCESSING, Kitchen Equipment, FOOD PROCESSING > Meat Mincer, Special Offer",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/mEAT-MINCER-TA22V.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"OMEGA FOOD TECH",Brand,"OMEGA FOOD TECH",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,78,0,,,"MEAT MINCER,MEAT MINCER 380V- TA 32 V",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"TA 32 V",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734597028,110001100111010011100011001110011001100001001011,,,,,,,,,sale