14742,simple,,,"Rancilio Specialty Coffee Machine - RS1",1,0,visible,"Automatic | Multi-Boiler\nThe RS1 helps coffee professionals offer a better coffee experience by providing cutting-edge brewing technology combined with Rancilio expertise and unique workflow design, resulting in an easy to use espresso machine with great value.\n\nInnovative brewing\nUnmatched temperature control during the extraction allows the barista to fine-tune every shot, resulting in a better cup profile.\n\nADVANCED TEMPERATURE PROFILING\nBy accurately controlling the temperature profile of the espresso extraction, baristas are given a precise tool to unlock the flavor potential of each single-origin coffee or blend.\n\nEach stainless steel group contains a micro-boiler and two heating elements, maximizing accuracy and thermal stability for both the water temperature and group body.\n\nINNOVATIVE BREW GROUP HYDRAULICS\nThe RS1 features an innovative brewing group that maximizes efficiency and can introduce freshwater into the group head micro-boiler with every shot.\n\nALL AROUND FLEXIBILITY\nAll stainless steel body panels can be easily removed, customized, powder-coated or branded to meet customer needs.\n\nVARIABLE STEAM LEVER\nSteam pressure delivery features a purge function and two programmable positions per side, perfect for switching between various pitcher sizes and different types of milk.","3 GROUPHEADS\nW X D X H\n1084 x 600 x 463 mm\n42.67 x 23.62 x 18.23 in\n\nWEIGHT\n110 kg / 242.5 lb\n\nBOILER\n16 l / 3.5 gal UK / 4.2 gal US\n\nMICRO-BOILER\n3x150 ml (300 W)\n\nPOWER SUPPLY\n220-240 V~ / 380-415V3N~\n50-60 Hz\n6750 W\nWATER SUPPLY\n\nWater mains connection\nNOISE LEVEL DURING USE\n&lt; 70 dB\n\n2 GROUPHEAD\nW X D X H\n840 x 600 x 463 mm\n33.07 x 23.62 x 18.23 in\n\nWEIGHT\n95 kg / 209.4 lb\n\nBOILER\n11 l / 2.4 gal UK / 2.9 gal US\n\nMICRO-BOILER\n2x150 ml (300 W)\n\nPOWER SUPPLY\n220-240 V~ / 380-415V3N~\n50-60 Hz\n5600 W\n\nWATER SUPPLY\nWater mains connection\nNOISE LEVEL DURING USE\n&lt; 70 dB\n\nGENERAL SPECIFICATIONS\nWORKSURFACE DEPTH 180 MM / 7.0 IN\n\nUNDER MACHINE HEIGHT 90 MM / 3,5 IN\n\nHEIGHT OF THE DRIP TRAY 80*-100-120 MM / 3*-4-5 IN\n\nVOLTAGE 220-240 V / 380-415 V (3N)\n\nFREQUENCY50/60 HZ",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,55700,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Coffee Machines, Kitchen Equipment",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Rancilio-Specialty-RS1.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Rancilio-Specialty-back-RS1.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Rancilio-Specialty-back-1-RS1.png",,,,,,,,,0,,rancilio,Brand,rancilio,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,62,0,,,"Rancilio Specialty,Rancilio Specialty RS1",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,RS1,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595055,100010011110100111011001111100101001101001100000,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14746,simple,,,"Coffee Grinder - MarKibar IZAGA KEY",1,0,visible,"High consistency in each cup of coffee\n\nThe new IZAGA coffee grinder combines innovation, advanced technology and a modern aesthetic to offer a professional and precise automatic grinder that responds to the requirements of a high coffee consumption customers.","ASSURED COFFEE QUALITY:\n\nCoffee always freshly ground.\nInstant delivery of 1 and 2 coffee doses, independently programmable.\nGrinding chamber separated from the motor, with intelligent ventilation for a cooler grinding.\nElectronically controlled doses.\nEASE OF USE:\n\nHigh precision grinding point control with bi-directional locking system for regulation without errors.\nAutomatic 1 or 2 coffee holder detection.\nTwo operating modes: Pre-ground or Grinding on Demand.\nHigh visibility alphanumeric Oled screen.\nDESIGN:\n\nNew design. High quality materials.\nCustomizable hopper for your Coffee Brand.\nBacklight front panel for advertising.\nEASE OF MAINTENANCE:\n\nA simple and very reliable design.\nConvenience and speed of service.\nOn-line management of your coffee grinder park (optional).",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,8450,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Coffee Grinder, Kitchen Equipment",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/MarKibar-IZAGA-KEY-blcack.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/MarKibar-IZAGA-KEY.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/MarKibar-IZAGA-KEY-84603542_540x.webp, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/MarKibar-IZAGA-KEY-84603452_540x.webp",,,,,,,,,0,,rancilio,Brand,rancilio,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,76,0,,,"Coffee Grinder,Coffee Grinder - MarKibar IZAGA KEY",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"MarKibar IZAGA KEY",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110011100100111001100011000110011001100101001101,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14751,simple,,'-352,"LAUNDRY WASHING – LN-35C TP2",1,0,visible,"LN-35C TP2 Laundry Washing Machine: The LN-35C TP2 is a premium top-load washing machine with an extra-large capacity and cutting-edge technology for exceptional cleaning. Engineered for efficiency and convenience, it features multiple wash cycles and settings to handle various fabrics and stains. Its robust design and intuitive controls make it easy to use, providing thorough cleaning while conserving energy and water. Ideal for busy households, the LN-35C TP2 ensures high performance and gentle care for all laundry needs.",". LAUNDRY WASHING – LN-35C TP2\n. Load capacity: 39/35 kg\n. VOLUME (L): 350\n. Touch Plus Control (TP2)\n- 7"""" Touch Plus TP2 control.\n- Steam Inlet 3/4"""" inch\n- Water Inlet: 3/4"""" inch\n- Drain 3"""" inch\n- 8 liquid dosing signals.\n- G-force 200.\n- Wash Speed / Spin Speed (r.p.m): 45/644\n- Drum and envelope in AISI-304 stainless steel.\n- Height Door Centre / Base / Diameter: 735 / 440 / 560 mm\n- Power: Motor: 4KW / Heating Power: 21 KW\n- Total Electrical Power (Electric Mod.) 22 KW\n- Electrical Power (Hot Water And Steam Mod.): 4 Kw\n- Voltage: 380-415 V 3N 50/60 Hz\n- Net / Gross weight: 473 / 503 kg\n- Volume: 2.1 (m3)\n- Drum Size: 860 x 602 mm\n- Dim: 979 x 1066 x 1411 mm.\nLN-35C TP2 / FOGOR PROFESSIONAL / Italy made.""",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,52329,"Kitchen Equipment, LAUNDRY & DISH WASHER, LAUNDRY & DISH WASHER > Laundry Machines",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/LAUNDRY-WASHING-–-LN-35C-TP2.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"Fagor Professional",Brand,Fagor,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,64,0,,,"LAUNDRY WASHING,LAUNDRY WASHING – LN-35C TP2",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"LN-35C TP2",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596801,110100011001110010110000100100110010011111001011,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,