14753,simple,,,"LAUNDRY WASHING – LN-45C TP2",1,0,visible,"LN-45C TP2 Laundry Washing Machine: The LN-45C TP2 is a high-capacity, top-load washing machine engineered for superior performance and efficiency. It features advanced washing technology with a wide range of cycles and settings to handle diverse fabrics and heavy-duty loads. Its robust construction and user-friendly interface ensure optimal cleaning results while minimizing energy and water consumption. Ideal for large households, the LN-45C TP2 offers reliable, deep cleaning and gentle fabric care for all your laundry needs.","""Washer\n. Load capacity: 49/45 kg\n. VOLUME (L): 450\n. Touch Plus Control (TP2)\n- 7"""" Touch Plus TP2 control.\n- Steam Inlet 3/4"""" inch\n- Water Inlet: 3/4"""" inch\n- Drain 3"""" inch\n- 8 liquid dosing signals.\n- G-force 200.\n- Wash Speed / Spin Speed (r.p.m): 45/644\n- Drum and envelope in AISI-304 stainless steel.\n- Height Door Centre / Base / Diameter: 735 / 440 / 560 mm\n- Power: Motor: 6 KW / Heating Power: 21 KW\n- Total Electrical Power (Electric Mod.) 22 KW\n- Electrical Power (Hot Water And Steam Mod.): 4 Kw\n- Voltage: 380-415 V 3N 50/60 Hz\n- Net / Gross weight: 600 / 670 kg\n- Volume: 2.5 (m3)\n- Drum Size: 860 x 720 mm\n- Dim: 979 x 1255 x 1411 mm.\nLN-45C TP2 / FOGOR PROFESSIONAL / Italy made.""",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,57986,"Kitchen Equipment, LAUNDRY & DISH WASHER, LAUNDRY & DISH WASHER > Laundry Machines",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/LAUNDRY-WASHING-–-LN-35C-TP2.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"Fagor Professional",Brand,Fagor,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,68,0,,,"LAUNDRY WASHING,LAUNDRY WASHING – LN-45C TP2",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"LN-45C TP2",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110100011001110010110000100100110010011111001011,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,