14754,simple,,,"LAUNDRY DRYERS (Up to 460 Litres) - SR-18 M E",1,0,visible,"SR-18 M E Laundry Dryer: The SR-18 M E is a high-capacity dryer capable of handling up to 460 liters, designed to deliver efficient and thorough drying. With multiple drying cycles and settings, this dryer can accommodate various fabric types and drying needs. Its advanced technology ensures quick drying while conserving energy. Built with a durable construction and a user-friendly interface, the SR-18 M E provides consistent performance and ease of use, making it ideal for households requiring large-scale drying solutions.","'-LAUNDRY DRYERS (Up to 460 Litres) - SR-18 M E\n- Capaity: 17-18 kg\n- Easy Control """"M"""".\n- All models offer reverse motor rotation. This makes the drying process more efficient and offers greater uniformity in the clothes drying process.\n- The reverse rotation drum system is performed by the inverter.\n- DRUM: Ø Drum: 750 mm / Drum length: 746 mm /\n- Drum volume: 330 l / Ø Door : 574 mm\nPOWER: (Electric / Gas)\n- Installed heating power: 18 kW / Gas power: 70000 Btu/hr\n- Installed electrical power: 18.97 KW / Gas Power: 0,67 KW\n- Installed heating power gas: 20,51 kW\n- Evaporation capacity: 14,10 l/hr / For Gas : 16,3 l/hr\n- Hourly output: 28,3 Kg/h / For Gas : 31,9 Kg/hr\n- Ø Gas inlet: 1/2'' BSPP ISO 228-1\nSTEAM POWER:\n- Installed heating power steam: 30 kW\n- Installed electrical power: 0,67 kW\n- VENTILATION : Nominal air flow: 850 m³/h , Air outlet Ø: 200 mm\n- Fan motor power: 0,25 kW\n- Total max heat dissipation: 1,8 kW\n- Front pannel max heat dissipation: 1,26 kW\n- Voltage: 400V 3N 50 Hz\n- Net / Gross weight: 187 / 200 kg\n- Dim: 785 x 1125 x 1694 mm.\nSR-18 M E / FOGOR PROFESSIONAL / Italy made.""",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,18382,"Kitchen Equipment, LAUNDRY & DISH WASHER, LAUNDRY & DISH WASHER > Laundry Machines",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/LAUNDRY-DRYERS-Up-to-460-Litres-–-SR-18-M-E.png,,,,