14756,simple,,,"LAUNDRY DRYERS (Up to 660 Litres) - SR-28 M E",1,0,visible,"SR-28 M E Laundry Dryer: The SR-28 M E is an ultra-capacity dryer capable of handling up to 660 liters of laundry, ideal for large households or commercial applications. Equipped with advanced drying technology and a wide array of customizable cycles, it efficiently dries different fabrics while ensuring their longevity. This dryer offers quick, energy-efficient operation and features a robust design with easy-to-use controls for optimal performance and convenience. The SR-28 M E is the perfect solution for managing substantial drying loads with reliability and ease.","""LAUNDRY DRYERS (Up to 660 Litres)\n- Capaity: 27-31 kg\n- Easy Control """"M"""".\n- All models offer reverse motor rotation. This makes the drying process more efficient and offers greater uniformity in the clothes drying process.\n- The reverse rotation drum system is performed by the inverter.\nDRUM: Ø Drum: 947 mm / Drum length: 780 mm /\nDrum volume: 550 l / Ø Door : 802 mm\nPOWER: (Electric / Gas)\n- Installed heating power: 30 kW / Gas power: 35276 kW\n- Installed electrical power: 31,15 KW / Gas Power: 1,15 KW\n- Installed heating power gas: 41 Btu/h\n- Evaporation capacity: 26,1 l/hr / For Gas : 26,1 l/hr\n- Hourly output: 48,4 Kg/h / For Gas : 59,3 Kg/hr\n- Ø Gas inlet: 1/2'' BSPP ISO 228-1\nSTEAM POWER:\n- Installed heating power steam: 50,1 kW\n- Installed electrical power: 1,15 kW\nVENTILATION: Nominal air flow: 1200 m³/h , Air outlet Ø: 200 mm\n- Fan motor power: 0,55 kW\n- Total max heat dissipation: 3 kW\n- Front pannel max heat dissipation: 2,1 kW\n- Voltage: 400V 3N 50 Hz\n- Net / Gross weight: 230 / 260 kg\n- Dim: 985 x 1054 x 1975 mm.\nSR-28 M E / FOGOR PROFESSIONAL / Italy made.""",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,22827,"Kitchen Equipment, LAUNDRY & DISH WASHER, LAUNDRY & DISH WASHER > Laundry Machines",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/LAUNDRY-DRYERS-Up-to-460-Litres-–-SR-18-M-E.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"Fagor Professional",Brand,Fagor,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,71,0,,,"LAUNDRY DRYERS,LAUNDRY DRYERS (Up to 660 Litres) - SR-28 M E",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"SR-28 M E",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596801,110000011001110010011001011110100110011001101001,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14757,simple,,,"LAUNDRY DRYERS (Up to 660 Litres) - SR-35 M E",1,0,visible,"SR-35 M E Laundry Dryer: The SR-35 M E is a high-capacity dryer designed to handle up to 660 liters, perfect for large households or commercial settings. Featuring cutting-edge drying technology and an extensive selection of drying cycles, it efficiently manages a variety of fabric types and load sizes. This dryer ensures rapid, energy-efficient drying while maintaining fabric quality. Built with a sturdy construction and user-friendly controls, the SR-35 M E delivers dependable performance and convenience for all your drying needs.","'- LAUNDRY DRYERS (Up to 660 Litres) - SR-35 M E\n- Capaity: 33-37 kg\n- Easy Control """"M"""".\n- All models offer reverse motor rotation. This makes the drying process more efficient and offers greater uniformity in the clothes drying process.\n- The reverse rotation drum system is performed by the inverter.\n- DRUM: Ø Drum: 947 mm / Drum length: 936 mm /\n- Drum volume: 660 l / Ø Door : 802 mm\n- POWER: (Electric / Gas)\n- Installed heating power: 36 kW / Gas power: 35276 kW\n- Installed electrical power: 37,15 KW / Gas Power: 1,15 KW\n- Installed heating power gas: 41 Btu/h\n- Evaporation capacity: 31,1 l/hr / For Gas : 32,1 l/hr\n- Hourly output: 60 Kg/h / For Gas : 63,9 Kg/hr\n- Ø Gas inlet: 1/2'' BSPP ISO 228-1\nSTEAM POWER:\n- Installed heating power steam: 50,1 kW\n- Installed electrical power: 1,15 kW\nVENTILATION: Nominal air flow: 1200 m³/h , Air outlet Ø: 200 mm\n- Fan motor power: 0,55 kW\n- Total max heat dissipation: 3,6 kW\n- Front pannel max heat dissipation: 2,52 kW\n- Voltage: 400V 3N 50 Hz\n- Net / Gross weight: 260 / 285 kg\n- Dim: 985 x 1210 x 1975 mm.\n- SR-35 M E / FOGOR PROFESSIONAL / Italy made.""",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,27657,"Kitchen Equipment, LAUNDRY & DISH WASHER, LAUNDRY & DISH WASHER > Laundry Machines",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/LAUNDRY-DRYERS-Up-to-460-Litres-–-SR-18-M-E.