14758,simple,,,"GAS RANGE 4 BURNERS ON GAS OVEN - G4SF65",1,0,visible,"G4SF65 Gas Range: The G4SF65 Gas Range is a versatile cooking appliance featuring four high-performance gas burners and a spacious gas oven. Designed for efficiency and precision, the burners provide even heat distribution for various cooking styles, from simmering to searing. The gas oven offers consistent baking and roasting results with easy-to-adjust temperature controls. With its durable construction and sleek design, the G4SF65 is perfect for both home kitchens and professional culinary environments, ensuring a reliable and enjoyable cooking experience.","GAS RANGE 4 BURNERS ON GAS OVEN\nThe worktop is made of 304 stainless steel with a thickness of 1 mm, deep-drawn and watertight to avoid dirt infiltration, also thanks to the rounded edges and the molded recess which guarantees the containment of liquid and overflows.\n. Oven with glass door, enamelled walls, cap. 4 grids 44x37. External dimensions - WxDxH (cm): 60 x 65 x 85\n. Nr. burners 3.5 kW 2-6 kW * 2\nGas oven (kW):2\nTotal power (kW): 21\nOven dimensions: 460 x 420 x 320 (mm)\nVoltage: 230V 1N 50-60Hz\nWeight (kg):63\nVolume (m3): 0.6\nDim: 600 x 650 x 850 mm\nG4SF65 / MBM / Italy made.\nINCLUDE ISO9001",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,7198.7256,"COOKING LINE > Cooker, COOKING LINE, Kitchen Equipment, COOKING LINE > Cooker > Series 700",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/GAS-RANGE-4-BURNERS-ON-GAS-OVEN.png,,,,,,,,,0,,MBM,Brand,MBM,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,58,0,,,"GAS RANGE 4 BURNERS ON GAS OVEN,GAS RANGE 4 BURNERS ON GAS OVEN - G4SF65",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,G4SF65,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595498,011100001101110010010110011100100111000011100101,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14760,simple,,,"JUICER ELECTRIC - HJE960-UK",1,0,visible,"he Juicer Electric HJE960-UK is a powerful, UK-designed appliance that effortlessly extracts juice from fruits and vegetables. Featuring durable construction and a user-friendly design, it ensures maximum juice yield with minimal effort, making it an essential tool for any health-conscious kitchen.","• JUICER, ELECTRIC\n• Otto™ Centrifugal Juice Extractor, electric, countertop, manual feed,\n• 3"" dia. feed chute,\n• Brushless induction motor with dual cooling fans,\n• 304 stainless steel bowl,\n• Polished stainless steel strainer basket,\n• Aluminum base, includes Tritan™™ food pusher,\n• 12 qt. pulp bin &amp; cleaning brush,\n• 220-240v/50/60/1-ph, 8.5 amps\n• Hamilton Beach Model No. HJE960-UK",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,10500,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Juice Maker, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/JUICER-ELECTRIC.png,,,,,,,,,0,,"Hamilton Beach USA",Brand,"Hamilton Beach- USA",1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,71,0,,,"JUICER ELECTRIC,JUICER ELECTRIC - HJE960-UK",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,HJE960-UK,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110100110000010010110011000110011110011111100100,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14762,simple,,,"Gas Mandi oven",1,0,visible,"The Gas Mandi Oven is a robust and efficient cooking appliance designed for preparing traditional Mandi dishes. It delivers consistent heat distribution, ensuring perfectly cooked meals with authentic flavors. Ideal for commercial kitchens, this oven combines durability with high performance, making it a must-have for restaurants specializing in Middle Eastern cuisine.","•Gas Mandi oven made of S/S grade 304, 3pc. S/S net tray per oven,\n•Dim: 90x90x160 cm.\n•Chicken cooking capacity: 250 pcs approximately\n•Lam cooking capacity: 9 pcs approximately Cooking time (approximately): 00:50 checken 1:30\n•Lam Number of trays Space: 3"" trays weight: 275 kg approximately. 2- Lam timing from 1 hour to 1:20 hour.\n•Features: Low pressure Gas (2.8 kPa),\n•Full stainless steel exterior &amp; interior,\n•Safety door handles,\n•Dual dynamic safety pressure valves,\n•Heavy duty wheels with breaks,,\n•Exhaust heat pipe,,\n•Temperature insulated LM oven walls,\n•mariot made/uae.",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,6000,"COOKING LINE > Cooker, COOKING LINE, Kitchen Equipment, COOKING LINE > Cooker > Series 900",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Gas-Mandi-oven.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Mariot,Brand,Mariot,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,86,0,,,"Gas Mandi oven",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,90x90x160,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734597090,011110110011111000110011100100100100100101100001,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
14764,simple,,,"Bain Marie - HHBWF-120",1,0,visible,"The Bain Marie HHBWF-120 is a high-quality food warmer designed for commercial kitchens, ensuring consistent temperature control to keep dishes warm and ready to serve. Its durable stainless steel construction and user-friendly controls make it ideal for buffets, catering, and food service establishments. With multiple compartments, it offers efficient and versatile food storage, maintaining the freshness and flavor of various dishes.","""Bain Marie new style\n. Cap : 4-6 pans\n. w/ top glass &amp; under shelf.\n. 4 adjustable legs.\n. Dish warmer with pans with mechanical control.\n. Good quality heater.\n. temperature: 30 ~ 85 °c.\n. Power : 3.5 kw.\n. Voltage(v)/Frequency(Hz):220-240/50\n. Dim: 1200 x 700+300 x 850+500 mm.\nHHBWF-120""",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,5066,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Food Warmers, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Bain-Marie.png,,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,Brand,Stilco,1,1,,,,,default,1,1,0,,81,0,,,"Bain Marie",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,HHBWF-120,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596931,110111100111010000100110101100110101000011001100,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
