14768,simple,,,"CAN SEALER MACHINE- MX-01",1,0,visible,"<strong>CAN SEALER MACHINE - MX-01</strong>\n\nThe MX-01 Can Sealer Machine is a robust and reliable solution designed for sealing a wide range of cans with precision and efficiency. Built with high-quality materials and advanced sealing technology, this machine ensures airtight and leak-proof seals, preserving the freshness and quality of your products. Ideal for small to medium-scale production, the MX-01 is easy to operate, maintain, and adjust for various can sizes. Whether you're in the food, beverage, or industrial sector, the MX-01 delivers consistent performance, making it an essential tool for your packaging needs.\n\n<strong>Key Features:</strong>\n<ul>\n 	<li><strong>High Efficiency:</strong> Seals cans quickly and accurately, increasing production speed.</li>\n 	<li><strong>Versatility:</strong> Compatible with various can sizes and types.</li>\n 	<li><strong>Durability:</strong> Constructed with premium-grade materials for long-lasting use.</li>\n 	<li><strong>User-Friendly:</strong> Simple controls and easy maintenance for hassle-free operation.</li>\n 	<li><strong>Compact Design:</strong> Space-saving design, perfect for any production environment.</li>\n</ul>","•CAN SEALER MACHINE- MX-01\n•MODEL: MX-01\n•VOLTAGE: 220V\n•POWER: 370W\n•CAN INNER DIAMETER: 52MM\n•CAN OUTER DIAMETER: 55MM\n•CAN CAPACITY: 500ML-650ML\n•PRODUCT SIZE: 255*455*608MM",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,5500,"ACCESSORIES, COFFEE & BAR LINE, Kitchen Equipment",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/CAN-SEALER-MACHINE.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/CAN-SEALER-MACHINE1.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/CAN-SEALER-MACHINE2.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/CAN-SEALER-MACHINE3.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/CAN-SEALER-MACHINE4.png, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/CAN-SEALER-MACHINE5.png",,,,