16957,simple,,,"Coffee Machine La Cimbali - M200 DT/2 GT1 4P 2VAP. BLACK",1,0,visible,"<div class=""flex max-w-full flex-col flex-grow"">\n<div class=""min-h-8 text-message flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 whitespace-normal break-words [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5"" dir=""auto"" data-message-author-role=""assistant"" data-message-id=""6b751ece-6ebd-47ec-8009-1bcc335f06b5"" data-message-model-slug=""gpt-4o"">\n<div class=""flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"">\n<div class=""markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert dark"">\n\n<strong>La Cimbali M200 DT/2 GT1 Coffee Machine</strong>\n\nExperience exceptional coffee brewing with the La Cimbali M200 DT/2 GT1. Featuring 4 programmable profiles, dual steam wands, and sleek black design, it’s perfect for high-performance cafes and baristas.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","<strong> Coffee Machine La Cimbali - M200 DT/2 GT1 4P 2VAP. BLACK</strong>\nSpecification : La Cimbali has a new\nflagship: M200. Designed to steal\nthe show. A design icon that defines\na space’s status. A newly designed\nproject that combines passion for\nhigh-quality coffee with the\nrationale of functional and smart\nergonomics.\n• GT1 System\n•Adjustable water temperature\n•Steam wand Cold Touch\n• PGS\n•Smart Boiler• Mixed water\n•Bluetooth\n• Green Machine\n• USBPort\n• WiFi connectivity embedded\n•New stainless steel portafilters\n•Cold Touch steam wands: 2\n• Hot water wand: 1\n• Hot water selections:3\n• Service boiler capacity (Litres): 7\n•Independent coffee boilers: 2\n•Independent coffee boilers capacity(cc): 600\n• Coffee boiler heater (W):800\n• Electrical cup warmer (3 temperature settings)\n• Dimension (mm): W887 x D649 x H516\n• Weight(kg): 70\n• Power at 380-415V3N~50/60Hz (W): 6000-7000W",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,38500,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Coffee Machines, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PRODUCT-IMAGE-news-2.webp,,,,,,,,,0,,LaCimbali,Brand,LaCimbali,1,1,,,,,,1,1,0,,62,0,,,"Coffee Machin,Coffee Machine La Cimbal",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"M200 DT/2 GT1 4P 2VAP. BLACK",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595055,001010110101001101010010101100101101110101010010,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
16964,simple,,,"Coffee Machine La Cimbali - M100RE DT/2 GTI 3P VA BLACK",1,0,visible,"La Cimbali M100RE DT/2 GTI Coffee Machine\n\nThe La Cimbali M100RE DT/2 GTI delivers precision and performance with 3 programmable profiles, advanced GTI technology, and a sophisticated black finish—ideal for professional coffee brewing.","<strong>Coffee Machine La Cimbali - M100RE DT/2 GTI 3P VA BLACK</strong>\nSpecification : M100 Attiva range,\nwith its new thermal system GTA,\ninterfaces, design, ergonomics\nfeatures and accessories guarantee\nmaximum flexibility and has been\ndesigned to rewrite the rules of an\nentire category and to pave the way\nfor a new generation of professional\nmachinesGTA System.\nAdjustable water temperature.\nSteam wand cold touch.\nPGS.\nSmart Boiler.\nMixed waterBluetooth.\nGreen machineUSBPort.\nCold Touch Steam wands: 2Hot water\nwand: 1Hot water\nselections: 3Service boiler\ncapacity (Litres): 10Independent\ncoffee boilers: 2Independent coffee boilers\ncapacity (cc): 400Coffee boiler\nheater (W): 800Electrical cup warmer (3 temperature settings)\nWidth x Depth x Height (mm): 832X567X582Weight (kg): 89",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,36800,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Coffee Machines, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PRODUCT-IMAGE-news-1.webp,,,,,,,,,0,,LaCimbali,Brand,LaCimbali,1,1,,,,,,1,1,0,,65,0,,,"Coffee Machine,Coffee Machine La Cimbali - M100RE DT/2 GTI 3P VA BLACK",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"M100RE DT/2 GTI 3P VA BLACK",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595055,111101010010110000101001010100101001110000110111,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
16968,simple,,,"Coffee Machine La Cimbali – M40 DT2 BLACK",1,0,visible,"<strong>La Cimbali M100RE DT/2 GTI Coffee Machine</strong>\n\nThe La Cimbali M100RE DT/2 GTI offers precision and performance with 3 programmable profiles, advanced GTI technology, and a stylish black finish, designed for professional baristas and premium coffee experiences.","<strong>Coffee Machine La Cimbali – M40 DT2 BLACK</strong>\nSpecification : A completely\nredesigned and innovative interface.\nA tempered glass panel and a highly\ntechnological full-touch capacitive\nkeypad that offers flexibility, speed,\nand ease of use, all to enhance the\nuser experience.\nHot water only where and when needed: coffee boiler and service boiler are separate.\nA single coffee boiler connects to the coffee groups, always maintained at the correct service temperature.\nThis way, energy and water consumption are reduced, while the flexibility of using the various groups is increased, keeping dispensing constant.\n• Power at 380-415 V3N 50- 60 Hz\n• Installed Power: 7.2-8.6kW\n• Dimension (mm): L768 x H531 x D592\n• Weight (kg): 65",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,32000,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Coffee Machines, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/PRODUCT-IMAGE-news-3.webp,,,,,,,,,0,,LaCimbali,Brand,LaCimbali,1,1,,,,,,1,1,0,,65,0,,,"Coffee Machine,Coffee Machine La Cimbali – M40 DT2 BLACK",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"M40 DT2 BLACK",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595055,001000011110101101111001010100100001101010011101,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
17102,simple,,,"Commercial induction cooker - DC34",1,0,visible,"Commercial Induction Cooker - DC34:\nExperience efficiency and precision with the DC34 Commercial Induction Cooker. Designed for professional kitchens, it delivers rapid heating, energy savings, and consistent performance. Its durable build, user-friendly controls, and safety features make it the perfect solution for fast-paced cooking environments.","""Commercial induction cooker\n- #201 Stainless Steel ; IEC Standard.\n- Portable /Table top.\n- 2 pieces cooling fans.\n- Controller type: Sensor touch control.\n- Cooker surface: A grade black crystal glass.\n- Power &amp; Temperature Level: 10 level.\n- Heating coil material: Pure copper coil.\n- Display: 4 digital LED display.\n- Rated voltage/ Electric phase: 220-240V, 50/60Hz / 1 Ph\n- Display power: 3200W (Power Tolerance -10%)\n- Actual Power: 2800W.\n- Dimension: Glass size: 300 x 300mm\n- Product size: 440 x 355 x 110 mm\nDC34 / AILIPU """,,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,795,"DRY STORE > Insect Killer, Kitchen Equipment, Limited Sale",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/DC34-600x600.png.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Ailipu,Brand,Ailipu,1,1,,,,,,1,1,0,,65,0,,,"Commercial induction cooker,Commercial induction cooker - DC34",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,DC34,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011101011001111000001001100001111101100001111000,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
17104,simple,,,"Commercial induction cooker - CX002",1,0,visible,"Commercial Induction Cooker - CX002:\nThe CX002 Commercial Induction Cooker combines cutting-edge technology with robust performance. Perfect for high-demand kitchens, it offers fast, energy-efficient cooking with precise temperature control. Built with a sleek, durable design and safety-focused features, the CX002 is an essential tool for modern culinary professionals.","""Commercial induction cooker\n- #201 Stainless Steel ; IEC Standard.\n- Portable /Table top.\n- 4 pieces cooling fans.\n- Controller type: Sensor touch control.\n- Cooker surface: A grade black crystal glass.\n- Power &amp; Temperature Level: 10 level.\n- Heating coil material: Pure copper coil.\n- Display: 4 digital LED display.\n- Rated voltage/ Electric phase: 220-240V, 50/60Hz / 1 Ph\n- Display power: 3500W+3500W (Power Tolerance -10%)\n- Actual Power: 3200W+3200W.\n- Dimension: Glass diameter: 280 x 280mm, 2pcs\n- Product size: 750 x 430 x 145mm\nCX002 / AILIPU """,,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,1562,"COOKING LINE > Cooker, COOKING LINE, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/post_12530_577.webp,,,,,,,,,0,,Ailipu,Brand,Ailipu,1,1,,,,,,1,1,0,,60,0,,,"Commercial induction cooker,Commercial induction cooker - CX002",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,CX002,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595813,111101011010010000101000011011110101111000010100,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
17107,simple,,,"Commercial induction cooker - CX008",1,0,visible,"Commercial Induction Cooker - CX008:\nElevate your kitchen's efficiency with the CX008 Commercial Induction Cooker. Engineered for precision and speed, it features advanced temperature control, energy-saving technology, and a sturdy design built for heavy-duty use. Ideal for professional kitchens, the CX008 ensures reliable and safe operation for all your culinary needs.","""Commercial induction cooker\n- #201 Stainless Steel ; IEC Standard.\n- Portable /Table top.\n- 4 pieces cooling fans.\n- Controller type: Sensor touch control.\n- Cooker surface: A grade black crystal glass.\n- Power &amp; Temperature Level: 10 level.\n- Heating coil material: Pure copper coil.\n- Display: 4 digital LED display.\n- Rated voltage/ Electric phase: 220-240V, 50/60Hz / 1 Ph\n- Display power: 3500W+3500W (Power Tolerance -10%)\n- Actual Power: 3200W+3200W.\n- Dimension: Glass diameter: 328 x 569mm\n- Product size: 390 x 720 x 110 mm\nCX008 / AILIPU """,,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,1320,1754,"COOKING LINE > Cooker, COOKING LINE, Kitchen Equipment, sale 11.11",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/CX008.webp,,,,,,,,,0,,Ailipu,Brand,Ailipu,1,1,,,,,,1,1,0,,62,0,,,"Commercial Induction Cooker,Commercial induction cooker - CX008",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,CX008,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595813,110011011010011000011001011100111011100000011001,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
17137,simple,,,"Full Automatic Line Arabic Bread - BIMATIC / LEBANON",1,0,visible,"<strong>Full Automatic Line for Arabic Bread - BIMATIC / Lebanon</strong>\nEfficient and reliable, BIMATIC's Full Automatic Line for Arabic Bread offers seamless production with advanced technology. Designed in Lebanon, this system ensures consistent quality, high capacity, and minimal labor requirements, making it ideal for modern bakeries.","""Full Automatic Line Arabic Bread\n- It is a fully automatic line for producing the Arabic Lebanese Bread.\n- It can be a single, double, triple, and quadrupled , octa output to satisfy any customer need concerning both productive capacity and size.\n- It can produce a range between 500 Loaves up to 20000 Loaves per hour with a diameter between 15 cm to 38 cm.\n- These lines are adopted for supermarkets, big restaurants and bakeries. Space needed for line installation varies from 70-240 m².\nFull Automatic Line Arabic Bread Composed of:\n- Dough Divider\n- Primary Proofer\n- Dough Flattener\n- Final Proofer\n- Tunnel Oven\n- Cooling Conveyor\nBIMATIC / LEBANON """,,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,350075,"BAKERY LINE, BAKERY LINE > Bread Maker, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/855.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Bimatic,Brand,Bimatic,1,1,,,,,,1,1,0,,63,0,,,"Full Automatic Line Arabic Bread,Full Automatic Line Arabic Bread - BIMATIC / LEBANON",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"BIMATIC / LEBANON",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596944,001010101101001101010100101100101110010110010110,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
17140,simple,,,"Dough Divider - PDD-S",1,0,visible,"<strong>Dough Divider - PDD-S</strong>\nThe PDD-S Dough Divider ensures precise and consistent dough portioning for optimal baking results. Engineered for efficiency and durability, it is perfect for high-volume bakeries, delivering uniform pieces with minimal waste and easy operation.","""Dough Divider PDD-S\nDough Weight (grams): 50-150\n- Pies dough divider is used to divide dough into dough balls.\n- The dough weight ranges due to purpose and demand.\n- It consists of aluminum extruding spiral shaft that is compatible with food grade policy.\n- It is relatively silent in-operation.\n- It is a mobilized unit that can be moved from one location to another.\nWeight: 125 kg\nDim: 120 x 85 x 83 cm\nModel: PDD-S / BIMATIC / LEBANON """,,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,10281,"BAKERY LINE, FOOD PROCESSING, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/800.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Bimatic,Brand,Bimatic,1,1,,,,,,1,1,0,,62,0,,,"Dough Divider,Dough Divider - PDD-S",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,PDD-S,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595316,101001110000001101100001011001101101101110010011,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
17147,simple,,,"Dough Flattener - PDF-IN",1,0,visible,"<strong>Dough Flattener - PDF-IN</strong>\nThe PDF-IN Dough Flattener is designed for perfect dough sheet preparation with precision and ease. Ideal for bakeries, it delivers uniform thickness, enhancing efficiency and ensuring consistent quality for a wide range of baked products.","""Dough Flattener PDF-IN\n- Pies dough flattener is used to flatten the divided dough into circular dough plates. \n- It flattens from 10-30 cm or 10-40cm with a thickness that ranges from 2-7 mm. \n- It consists of hard chromate cylinders that are compatible with food grade policy. \n- It is relatively silent in-operation. \n- It is a mobilized unit that can be moved from one location to another. \nWeight (Kg) : 110\nDim: 150 x 60 x 120 cm\nModel: PDF-IN / BIMATIC / LEBANON """,,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,8954,"BAKERY LINE, Kitchen Equipment",,,,,,,,,,,,0,,Bimatic,Brand,Bimatic,1,1,,,,,,1,1,0,,77,0,,,"Dough Flattener,Dough Flattener - PDF-IN",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,PDF-IN,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,,1734596944,100010110000101101010010110000111110110110011100,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
17149,simple,,,"Circular Pies Oven PO-125",1,0,visible,"<strong>Circular Pies Oven - PO-125</strong>\nThe PO-125 Circular Pies Oven combines efficiency and reliability for baking perfectly golden pies. Designed for even heat distribution, it ensures consistent results with every batch, making it a must-have for bakeries and food establishments.","""Circular Pies Oven PO-125\nCapacity (pcs): 12\n• Fixed or Motorized Baking Floor due to demand ( controlled via inverter system)\n• Circular Baking Fire to distribute the heat inside the oven equally.\n• Functions via liquid gas LPG or natural gas\n• Marble Top Working Shelf\n• Horizontal Curtained Door\n• Internal Construction Brick\n• Perfectly Isolated\n• Baking Floor can be steel or brick due to demand\n• Specialized for bread and Manakich\n• Stainless Steel External Covers\n• Damper for controlling open/ close of exhaust.\nWeight: 200 kg\nDim: 125 x 125\nModel: Circular Pies Oven PO-125 / BIMATIC / LEBANON",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,11276,"BAKERY LINE, BAKERY LINE > Bakery Oven, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/765.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Bimatic,Brand,Bimatic,1,1,,,,,,1,1,0,,54,0,,,"Circular Pies Oven,Circular Pies Oven PO-125",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,PO-125,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595826,100011110110001101010101101001011010010100011010,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
17151,simple,,,"Electric with Stand - SAJ-74-S",1,0,visible,"<strong>Electric Saj Maker with Stand - SAJ-74-S (BIMATIC / Lebanon)</strong>\nThe SAJ-74-S Electric Saj Maker is a high-quality stainless steel device designed for crafting authentic Saj bread. Built with food-grade materials, it ensures safe and reliable operation. Ideal for snacks, restaurants, and home use, it effortlessly prepares delicious Saj sandwiches like labneh, jebneh, and zaatar. Compact with dimensions of 65 x 65 cm, this electric model by BIMATIC is perfect for versatile, efficient baking.","""SAJ-74-S/ Electric with stand\n- Saj is used for making dough for bread which is known as SAJ.\n- The device is made up of stainless steel and everything that in touch with food is compatible with food grade.\n- It is used by snack, restaurants, home to make saj sandwiches such as lebneh, jebneh , zaatar, etc…\n- Dim: 65 x 65 cm\nModel: SAJ-74-S/ Electric / BIMATIC / LEBANON """,,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,2542,"BAKERY LINE, BAKERY LINE > Bread Maker, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/848.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Bimatic,Brand,Bimatic,1,1,,,,,,1,1,0,,54,0,,,"Electric with Stand,Electric with Stand - SAJ-74-S",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,SAJ-74-S,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596944,001011100101111011000110100011010001101010101100,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
17153,simple,,,"Gas with Stand - SAJ-74-S",1,0,visible,"<strong>Gas Saj Maker with Stand - SAJ-74-S</strong>\nThe SAJ-74-S Gas Saj Maker is a stainless steel device designed for crafting traditional Saj bread. Made with food-grade materials, it ensures safe and high-quality preparation. Perfect for snacks, restaurants, and homes, it creates delicious Saj sandwiches such as labneh, jebneh, and zaatar. Compact and efficient with dimensions of 65 x 65 cm, it is a versatile addition to any kitchen.","""SAJ-74-S/ Gas with stand\n- Saj is used for making dough for bread which is known as SAJ.\n- The device is made up of stainless steel and everything that in touch with food is compatible with food grade.\n- It is used by snack, restaurants, home to make saj sandwiches such as lebneh, jebneh , zaatar, etc…\n- Dim: 65 x 65 cm",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,2542,"BAKERY LINE, BAKERY LINE > Bakery Oven, BAKERY LINE > Bread Maker, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/868.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Bimatic,Brand,Bimatic,1,1,,,,,,1,1,0,,60,0,,,"Gas with Stand,Gas with Stand - SAJ-74-S",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,SAJ-74-S,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734595916,001011100101111011000110100011010001101010101100,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
17154,simple,,,"Electric (Table Top) - SAJ-54-TT",1,0,visible,"<strong>Electric Saj Maker (Table Top) - SAJ-54-TT (BIMATIC / Lebanon)</strong>\nThe SAJ-54-TT Electric Saj Maker is a compact, table-top stainless steel device designed for making traditional Saj bread. Crafted with food-grade materials, it ensures safety and quality. Perfect for snacks, restaurants, and home kitchens, it effortlessly prepares Saj sandwiches such as labneh, jebneh, and zaatar. With dimensions of 65 x 65 cm, this BIMATIC model from Lebanon combines portability and efficiency for versatile baking needs.","<strong>Electric (Table Top) - SAJ-54-TT</strong>\n- Saj is used for making dough for bread which is known as SAJ.\n- The device is made up of stainless steel and everything that in touch with food is compatible with food grade.\n- It is used by snack, restaurants, home to make saj sandwiches such as lebneh, jebneh , zaatar, etc…\n- Dim: 65 x 65 cm\nModel: SAJ-54-TT/ Electric/ BIMATIC / LEBANON """,,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,2100,"BAKERY LINE, BAKERY LINE > Bread Maker, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/824.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Bimatic,Brand,Bimatic,1,1,,,,,,1,1,0,,58,0,,,"Electric (Table Top),Electric (Table Top) - SAJ-54-TT",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,SAJ-54-TT,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,1734596944,101000010011101101111011000101100001101011100001,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
