18318,simple,,,"Blast Chiller - AT20ISO",1,0,visible,"<div class=""flex-1 overflow-hidden @container/thread"">\n<div class=""h-full"">\n<div class=""react-scroll-to-bottom--css-izsid-79elbk h-full"">\n<div class=""react-scroll-to-bottom--css-izsid-1n7m0yu"">\n<div class=""flex flex-col text-sm md:pb-9""><article class=""w-full scroll-mb-[var(--thread-trailing-height,150px)] text-token-text-primary focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-[-4px]"" dir=""auto"" data-testid=""conversation-turn-59"" data-scroll-anchor=""true"">\n<div class=""m-auto text-base py-[18px] px-3 md:px-4 w-full md:px-5 lg:px-4 xl:px-5"">\n<div class=""mx-auto flex flex-1 gap-4 text-base md:gap-5 lg:gap-6 md:max-w-3xl lg:max-w-[40rem] xl:max-w-[48rem]"">\n<div class=""group/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"">\n<div class=""flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3"">\n<div class=""flex max-w-full flex-col flex-grow"">\n<div class=""min-h-8 text-message flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 whitespace-normal break-words text-start [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5"" dir=""auto"" data-message-author-role=""assistant"" data-message-id=""0628d40b-b15a-4f86-8d93-e2ef68177f47"" data-message-model-slug=""gpt-4o"">\n<div class=""flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"">\n<div class=""markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert dark"">\n\n<strong>Blast Chiller - AT20ISO</strong>\nThe AT20ISO Blast Chiller rapidly reduces food temperature to preserve freshness, flavor, and quality. Designed for commercial kitchens, it ensures food safety with precise cooling technology. Its robust build and energy-efficient operation make it a reliable choice for high-demand environments.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</article></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","Blast Chiller - AT20ISO\nMODEL: AT20ISO\n(ATT20)\nBlast Chiller 20 Trays\nCapacity: 20 GN 1/1 (600x400mm)\nPower: 2040 W 440V/3PH/50HZ\nDim: 750X740X2080 mm\nG. Weight: 195 kg\nMade by Tecnodom, Italy",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,34250,"REFRIGERATION LINE > Freezer & Chillers, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Blast-Chiller-AT20ISO.webp,,,,,,,,,0,,Tecnodom,,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,60,0,0,,"Blast Chiller,Blast Chiller - AT20ISO",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,AT20ISO,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110100100111010010110001110100101101100101001001,true,backend,29184372207828397,yes,yes,,product,no,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,29184371747828443,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
18751,simple,,,"CHOCOLATE BEVERAGE DISPENSER - 10L",1,0,visible,"<strong>Chocolate Beverage Dispenser - 10L</strong>:\nEffortlessly serve hot, creamy chocolate drinks with this 10-liter dispenser. Featuring a sleek design, precise temperature control, and easy-to-clean parts, it’s perfect for cafes, restaurants, and events. Keep beverages warm and ready to pour, ensuring a delightful experience for your customers.","<h1 class=""a-size-base-plus a-text-bold"">About this item</h1>\n<strong>CHOCOLATE BEVERAGE DISPENSER - 10L</strong>\n<ul class=""a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-mini"">\n 	<li class=""a-spacing-mini""><span class=""a-list-item"">*CHOCOLATE BEVERAGE DISPENSER: This machines ten liter capacity will be more than enough to satisfy your entire family</span></li>\n 	<li class=""a-spacing-mini""><span class=""a-list-item"">*TEMPERATURE CONTROL: The temperature of the beverage can be set between 30°C and 90°C; For best results, it is best to keep the temperature set at 60°C.When the temperature has been set, you can turn the heating and mixing on.Once the beverage has reached the set temperature, the heating function will automatically turn off.</span></li>\n 	<li class=""a-spacing-mini""><span class=""a-list-item"">*DIGITAL DISPLAY: It's easy to read digital display will help you to set the precise temperature for your hot chocolate; The display will also give you a temperature readout while your hot chocolate is heating up</span></li>\n 	<li class=""a-spacing-mini""><span class=""a-list-item"">*EASY TO CLEAN: The entire machine disassembles to make for easy cleaning; This machine is meant to be hand washed only; Do NOT put in the dishwasher.</span></li>\n 	<li class=""a-spacing-mini""><span class=""a-list-item"">*It is widely used in hotels, restaurants, shopping malls, bakeries, cafes, chocolate shops, chocolate fountains, etc, to melt chocolate chips.</span></li>\n</ul>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,1200,1500,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, Kitchen Equipment",,,,,,,,,,,,0,,Mariot,,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,62,0,0,,"Chocolate Beverage Dispenser,CHOCOLATE BEVERAGE DISPENSER - 10L",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"CHOCOLATE BEVERAGE DISPENSER - 10L",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011000110010101100010011010110010111001101100110,,,9003144769732669,yes,yes,,product,no,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,9003144506399362,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
19379,simple,,,"COFFEE ESPRESSO MACHINE Single Group Automatic - APPIA LIFE - V",1,0,visible,"The <strong>Appia Life Single Group Automatic Espresso Machine</strong> offers a perfect blend of efficiency and elegance. Designed for small to medium-sized coffee shops or cafes, this machine delivers consistent espresso shots with its advanced automatic features. Built with durable materials, it ensures long-lasting performance and is easy to operate, making it a reliable choice for baristas looking to craft high-quality espresso drinks. Its sleek design and user-friendly interface add a touch of modern sophistication to any coffee station.","<strong>COFFEE ESPRESSO MACHINE - APPIA LIFE - V</strong>\n\nNuova Simonelli\nMade in Italy\nModel : APPIA LIFE - V\nSingle Group - Automatic\nVolumetric Dosage\nBoiler Tank Capacity : 5 Ltr\nStainless Steel Steam Wands With Push &amp; Pull\nCommand\nWith Soft Infusion System - SIS System Makes\nMore Efficient Extraction\nDim : 404 x 545 x 498 mm\nWithout Water Softner\n230 Volt / 50 - 60 Hz / 1 Ph / 1900 Watts",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,9218,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Coffee Machines, Kitchen Equipment",,,,,,,,,,,,0,,"Nuova Simonelli",,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,62,0,,,"COFFEE ESPRESSO MACHINE",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"APPIA LIFE - V Single Group - Automatic",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,,,011110100101111000101100001110100101100101100010,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
19384,simple,,,"COFFEE ESPRESSO MACHINE Two Group Semi Automatic - APPIA LIFE - S",1,0,visible,"The <strong>Appia Life Two Group Semi-Automatic Espresso Machine</strong> is designed for baristas who value control and precision. Ideal for medium to high-volume coffee shops, it features a robust build, energy-saving technology, and an ergonomic design for effortless operation. With two group heads, it allows for simultaneous brewing, ensuring efficiency during peak hours. Combining reliability and performance, this machine delivers consistently rich and flavorful espresso shots while maintaining ease of use and durability.","<strong>COFFEE ESPRESSO MACHINE Two Group Semi Automatic - APPIA LIFE - S</strong>\n\nNuova Simonelli\nMade in Italy\nModel : APPIA LIFE - S\nTwo Group - Semi Automatic\nBoiler Tank Capacity : 11 Ltr\nTwo Stainless Steel Steam Wands With Push &amp;\nPull Command\nWith Soft Infusion System - SIS System Makes\nMore Efficient Extraction\nDim : 784 x 544 x 500 mm\nWithout Water Softner\n230 Volt / 50 - 60 Hz / 1 Ph / 3350 Watts",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,11406,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Coffee Machines, Kitchen Equipment",,,,,,,,,,,,0,,"Nuova Simonelli",,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,66,0,,,"COFFEE ESPRESSO MACHINE Two Group Semi Automatic,COFFEE ESPRESSO MACHINE",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"APPIA LIFE - S Two Group Semi Automatic",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,,,111111110101010000101001001110000001111000011010,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
19393,simple,,,"COFFEE ESPRESSO MACHINE Two Group Automatic - Aurellia II - V",1,0,visible,"<div class=""flex-shrink-0 flex flex-col relative items-end"">\n<div>\n<div class=""pt-0"">\n<div class=""gizmo-bot-avatar flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-full"">\n<div class=""relative p-1 rounded-sm flex items-center justify-center bg-token-main-surface-primary text-token-text-primary h-8 w-8""></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=""group/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"">\n<div class=""flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3"">\n<div class=""flex max-w-full flex-col flex-grow"">\n<div class=""min-h-8 text-message flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 whitespace-normal break-words text-start [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5"" dir=""auto"" data-message-author-role=""assistant"" data-message-id=""159a2d97-b4da-47e1-b9bf-19f79bb5c2ee"" data-message-model-slug=""gpt-4o"">\n<div class=""flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"">\n<div class=""markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert dark"">\n\nThe <strong>Aurelia II Two Group Automatic Espresso Machine</strong> is a high-performance choice for busy coffee shops and professional baristas. Featuring advanced volumetric controls, it ensures consistent espresso extraction with minimal effort. Designed for efficiency, it allows simultaneous brewing with two group heads, making it perfect for high-volume operations. With its sleek design, user-friendly interface, and precision temperature control, the Aurelia II delivers exceptional espresso quality while enhancing workflow and barista comfort.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","<strong>COFFEE ESPRESSO MACHINE Two Group Automatic - Aurellia II - V</strong>\nNuova Simonelli\nMade in Italy\nModel : Aurellia II - V\nTwo Group - Automatic\nVolumetric Dosage\nBoiler Capacity : 14 Ltr\nDim : 815 x 565 x 565 mm\nAutomatic Cleaning System\nWith Soft Infusion System - SIS System Makes\nMore Efficient Extraction\n2 Stainless Steel Steam Wand With Push &amp; Pull\nCommand\nWith USB Slot Facility\nWithout Water Softner\nCode : MAURE18VOL02\n230 Volt / 50 - 60 Hz /1Ph",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,20437,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Coffee Machines, Kitchen Equipment",,,,,,,,,,,,0,,"Nuova Simonelli",,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,60,0,,,"COFFEE ESPRESSO MACHINE Two Group Automatic,COFFEE ESPRESSO MACHINE",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"Aurellia II - V",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011111001001111000001101000101111000001110110001,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
19413,simple,,,"COFFEE ESPRESSO MACHINE Two Group  Digital - Aurellia II - Digital",1,0,visible,"<div class=""flex max-w-full flex-col flex-grow"">\n<div class=""min-h-8 text-message flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 whitespace-normal break-words text-start [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5"" dir=""auto"" data-message-author-role=""assistant"" data-message-id=""017fb784-e896-49d9-bb7d-6888ade99243"" data-message-model-slug=""gpt-4o"">\n<div class=""flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"">\n<div class=""markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert dark"">\n\nThe <strong>Aurelia II Two Group Digital Espresso Machine</strong> is a state-of-the-art solution for professional baristas and high-volume coffee shops. Equipped with advanced digital controls, precise temperature regulation, and programmable settings, it ensures consistent and high-quality espresso extraction. Its two-group design allows for simultaneous brewing, increasing efficiency during peak hours. With an intuitive interface and ergonomic features, the Aurelia II Digital offers superior performance, reliability, and ease of use, making it a top choice for specialty coffee establishments.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=""mb-2 flex gap-3 empty:hidden -ml-2"">\n<div class=""items-center justify-start rounded-xl p-1 flex"">\n<div class=""flex items-center""></div>\n</div>\n</div>","<strong>COFFEE ESPRESSO MACHINE Two Group  Digital - Aurellia II - Digital</strong>\nNuova Simonelli\nMade in Italy\nModel : Aurellia II - Digital\nTwo Group - Digital\nBoiler Capacity : 14 Ltr\nDim : 815 x 565 x 565 mm\nMultifungtion Graphic Display With Rotary\nSwitch &amp; Insulated Boilers\nElectronic PID Temperature Control\nSIS Brewing System &amp; Reverse Mirror\n2 Stainless Steel Steam Wand With Push &amp; Pull\nCommand\nPossibility To Add Electronic Easy cream\nSystem for both steam Nozzles\n1 Hot Water Wand With Economizer\nAutomatic Washing System\nWith USB Slot Facility\nWithout Water Softner\nCode : MAURTFTVT303\n230 Volt / 50 - 60 Hz /1Ph",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,58.4,83.8,58.4,1,,,27062,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Coffee Machines, Kitchen Equipment",,,,,,,,,,,,0,,"Nuova Simonelli",,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,55,0,,,"COFFEE ESPRESSO MACHINE Two Group Digital",,,"COFFEE ESPRESSO MACHINE Two Group Digital",,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"Aurellia II - Digital Two Group",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,010111011000011010101001101111000000111000001111,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,0.1948,field_67a4631e7c12d
19418,simple,,,"COFFEE ESPRESSO MACHINE Two Group  Digital - Aurellia I8 Wave T 32 GV",1,0,visible,"<div class=""flex max-w-full flex-col flex-grow"">\n<div class=""min-h-8 text-message flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 whitespace-normal break-words text-start [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5"" dir=""auto"" data-message-author-role=""assistant"" data-message-id=""a7bd868e-7c27-4cdf-b40c-f24af7883fe2"" data-message-model-slug=""gpt-4o"">\n<div class=""flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"">\n<div class=""markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert dark"">\n\nThe <strong>Aurelia Wave T3 32 GV Two Group Digital Espresso Machine</strong> is a top-tier choice for specialty coffee shops and high-demand environments. Featuring T3 technology, it offers precise multi-boiler temperature control for optimal espresso extraction. Its digital interface provides programmable settings, ensuring consistency and efficiency. With two group heads for simultaneous brewing, ergonomic design, and energy-saving features, the Aurelia Wave T3 enhances workflow while delivering exceptional coffee quality with every shot.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","<strong>COFFEE ESPRESSO MACHINE Two Group  Digital - Aurellia I8 Wave T 32 GV</strong>\nNuova Simonelli\nMade in Italy\nModel : Aurellia I8 Wave T 32 GV\nTwo Group - Digital\nBoiler Capacity : 14 Ltr\nDim : 802 x 605 x 537 mm\nMultifungtion Graphic Display With Rotary\nSwitch &amp; Insulated Boilers\nElectronic PID Temperature Control\nSIS Brewing System &amp; Reverse Mirror\n2 Stainless Steel Steam Wand With Push &amp; Pull\nCommand\nPossibility To Add Electronic Easy cream\nSystem for both steam Nozzles\n1 Hot Water Wand With Economizer\nAutomatic Washing System\nWith USB Slot Facility\nWithout Water Softner\n230 Volt / 50 - 60 Hz /1Ph\n1 AED 30,250.00 AED 30,250.00",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,37812,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Coffee Machines, Kitchen Equipment",,,,,,,,,,,,0,,"Nuova Simonelli",,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,62,0,,,"COFFEE ESPRESSO MACHINE Two Group Digital",,,"COFFEE ESPRESSO MACHINE Two Group Digital ",,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"Aurellia I8 Wave T 32 GV",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,,,011111010000011010101001111110000001100000011111,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
19425,simple,,,"COFFEE GRINDER - MDXS - Core On Demand",1,0,visible,"<div class=""flex max-w-full flex-col flex-grow"">\n<div class=""min-h-8 text-message flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 whitespace-normal break-words text-start [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5"" dir=""auto"" data-message-author-role=""assistant"" data-message-id=""5f11dec2-f44f-4294-8e78-bce46a0d0922"" data-message-model-slug=""gpt-4o"">\n<div class=""flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"">\n<div class=""markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert dark"">\n\nThe <strong>MDXS Core On-Demand Coffee Grinder</strong> is a professional-grade grinder designed for precision and efficiency. Ideal for medium to high-volume coffee shops, it features on-demand grinding for fresh, consistent espresso shots. Equipped with silent technology, micrometric grind adjustment, and durable stainless-steel burrs, it ensures uniform particle size and optimal extraction. Its user-friendly interface and sleek design make it a reliable and stylish addition to any coffee setup.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","<strong>COFFEE GRINDER - MDXS - Core On Demand</strong>\nNuova Simonelli\nMade in Italy\nModel : MDXS - Core On Demand\nBean Hoper Capacity : 1.6 Kg\nDim : 212 x 290 x 585 mm\nLCD Multifunction Display\nWithout Touch Screen\nPre Set Modes &amp; Doses Available\nMicrometric Grinding Regulation\nAdjustable Grinding Dosage\n220-240 Volt / 50-60 Hz / 1 Ph / 500 Watts",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,2750,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Coffee Grinder, Kitchen Equipment",,,,,,,,,,,,0,,"Nuova Simonelli",,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,67,0,,,"COFFEE GRINDER,COFFEE GRINDER - MDXS - Core On Demand",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"MDXS - Core On Demand",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,,,110011100111010011000011000110011000100111001101,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
19429,simple,,,"COFFEE GRINDER- MDXS - On Demand",1,0,visible,"The <strong>MDXS On-Demand Coffee Grinder</strong> is a high-performance grinder designed for baristas who prioritize precision and efficiency. Featuring silent technology, stepless micrometric grind adjustment, and durable stainless-steel burrs, it ensures consistent and fresh espresso grinding. Its on-demand functionality allows for precise dosing, reducing waste while maintaining flavor quality. Ideal for medium to high-volume coffee shops, the MDXS offers reliability, ease of use, and a sleek, modern design.","<strong>COFFEE GRINDER- MDXS - On Demand</strong>\nNuova Simonelli\nMade in Italy\nModel : MDXS - On Demand\nBean Hoper Capacity : 1.6 Kg\nDim : 212 x 290 x 585 mm\nLCD Multifunction Display\nWith Touch Screen\nPre Set Modes &amp; Doses Available\nMicrometric Grinding Regulation\nAdjustable Grinding Dosage\n220-240 Volt / 50-60 Hz / 1 Ph / 500 Watts",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,3200,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Coffee Grinder, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Commercial-Grinder.webp,,,,,,,,,0,,"Nuova Simonelli",,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,65,0,,,"COFFEE GRINDER,COFFEE GRINDER- MDXS - On Demand",,,"COFFEE GRINDER- MDXS - On Demand",,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"MDXS - On Demand",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110011100110110011000100110100110010001101000111,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
19433,simple,,,"COFFEE GRINDER - GX85V",1,0,visible,"<div class=""flex max-w-full flex-col flex-grow"">\n<div class=""min-h-8 text-message flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 whitespace-normal break-words text-start [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5"" dir=""auto"" data-message-author-role=""assistant"" data-message-id=""fb81431a-503b-4371-a555-c2356d0c3f6a"" data-message-model-slug=""gpt-4o"">\n<div class=""flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"">\n<div class=""markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert dark"">\n\nThe <strong>GX85V Coffee Grinder</strong> is a high-performance grinder designed for precision and efficiency. Featuring durable stainless-steel burrs and stepless micrometric grind adjustment, it ensures consistent and uniform grinding for optimal espresso extraction. With its powerful motor and on-demand grinding capability, the GX85V is ideal for high-volume coffee shops looking for reliability, speed, and superior coffee quality. Its sleek design and user-friendly controls make it a valuable addition to any professional coffee setup.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","<strong>COFFEE GRINDER - GX85V</strong>\nNuova Simonelli\nMade in Italy\nModel : GX85V\nBean Hoper Capacity : 2 Kg\nProduction Capacity : 12 Kg / Day\nDim : 202 x 416 x 519 mm\nWith Variable Speed Function\nLong Life Burrs Diameter 85 mm\nTouch Display &amp; Barista Function\nMicro Metric Grinding Regulation\n230 Volt / 50 - 60 Hz / 1 Ph/ 500 Watts",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,10750,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Coffee Grinder, Kitchen Equipment",,,,,,,,,,,,0,,"Nuova Simonelli",,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,70,0,,,"COFFEE GRINDER,COFFEE GRINDER - GX85V",,,"COFFEE GRINDER - GX85V ",,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,GX85V,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,,,011001100011011001111001101100011000001101000111,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
19437,simple,,,"COFFEE GRINDER - GX85W",1,0,visible,"The <strong>GX85W Coffee Grinder</strong> is a professional-grade grinder designed for precision and efficiency. Featuring high-quality stainless-steel burrs and stepless micrometric grind adjustment, it ensures consistent and uniform grinding for the perfect espresso extraction. Its powerful motor and on-demand grinding functionality make it ideal for high-volume coffee shops, delivering speed, reliability, and exceptional coffee quality. With a sleek, modern design and user-friendly controls, the GX85W is a must-have for any professional coffee setup.","<strong>COFFEE GRINDER - GX85W</strong>\nNuova Simonelli\nMade in Italy\nModel : GX85W\nBean Hoper Capacity : 2 Kg\nProduction Capacity : 12 Kg / Day\nDim : 202 x 416 x 519 mm\nVariable Speed &amp; Gravimetric Technology\nLong Life Burrs Diameter 85 mm\nTouch Display &amp; Barista Function\nMicro Metric Grinding Regulation\n230 Volt / 50 - 60 Hz / 1 Ph/ 500 Watts",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,11968,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Coffee Grinder, Kitchen Equipment",,,,,,,,,,,,0,,"Nuova Simonelli",,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,62,0,,,"COFFEE GRINDER",,,"COFFEE GRINDER - GX85W ",,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,,,011001100011011001111001101100011000001101000111,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
19439,simple,,,"WATER SOFTNER 8 Ltr Nuova Simonelli",1,0,visible,"<div class=""flex-shrink-0 flex flex-col relative items-end"">\n<div>\n<div class=""pt-0"">\n<div class=""gizmo-bot-avatar flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-full"">\n<div class=""relative p-1 rounded-sm flex items-center justify-center bg-token-main-surface-primary text-token-text-primary h-8 w-8""></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=""group/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"">\n<div class=""flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3"">\n<div class=""flex max-w-full flex-col flex-grow"">\n<div class=""min-h-8 text-message flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 whitespace-normal break-words text-start [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5"" dir=""auto"" data-message-author-role=""assistant"" data-message-id=""aaafb6d9-3973-47d8-81af-b6a3d25177e5"" data-message-model-slug=""gpt-4o-mini"">\n<div class=""flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"">\n<div class=""markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert dark"">\n\nThe <strong>Nuova Simonelli 8L Water Softener</strong> is designed to protect your coffee equipment by ensuring the water quality is optimal for brewing. With an 8-liter capacity, it efficiently removes minerals and impurities, preventing scale buildup and prolonging the lifespan of your espresso machines. Easy to install and maintain, this water softener helps enhance the performance of your coffee machines while ensuring consistent taste and quality in every cup. Ideal for coffee shops and establishments with hard water, the Nuova Simonelli water softener is a reliable and essential tool for maintaining equipment and quality.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","WATER SOFTNER\nNuova Simonelli\nMade in Italy\nCapacity : 8 Ltr",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,562,"ACCESSORIES, Kitchen Equipment",,,,,,,,,,,,0,,"Nuova Simonelli",,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,70,0,,,"WATER SOFTNER,WATER SOFTNER 8 Ltr Nuova Simonelli",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"WATER SOFTNER 8 Ltr",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,,,011001110011111000111001100110001100110001001100,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
19477,simple,,,"American style 12 Gas cooker - E-RQB-2",1,0,visible,"<div class=""flex max-w-full flex-col flex-grow"">\n<div class=""min-h-8 text-message flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 whitespace-normal break-words text-start [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5"" dir=""auto"" data-message-author-role=""assistant"" data-message-id=""7dc0f8cc-e050-4254-999b-82d309d5ddd0"" data-message-model-slug=""gpt-4o-mini"">\n<div class=""flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"">\n<div class=""markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert dark"">\n\nThe American Style 12 Gas Cooker - E-RQB-2 is a high-performance kitchen appliance designed for efficiency and durability. It features 12 burners, offering ample cooking space for large meals, making it ideal for both residential and commercial kitchens. The cooker’s sleek design and robust construction ensure long-lasting use, while its advanced gas technology provides precise heat control for consistent cooking results. Perfect for high-demand kitchens, it combines functionality with style, making meal preparation effortless.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","<table width=""402"">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width=""402""><strong>American style 12"" Gas cooker-E-RQB-2</strong>\n2 range table top.\n. Stainless steel 430\n. 2 low pressure valves.\n. power:  7.3 kw*2 = 14.6 kw.\n. Net weight: 144 kg.\n. dimension: 308 x 834 x 320 mm.\n<strong>E-RQB-2</strong></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,1120,"COOKING LINE > Cooker, COOKING LINE, Kitchen Equipment, sale 11.11, COOKING LINE > Cooker > Series 600",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/RQB-2-1.webp,,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,57,0,,,"Gas cooker,American style 12 Gas cooker,American style 12 Gas cooker - E-RQB-2",,,"American style 12 Gas cooker - E-RQB-2",,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E-RQB-2,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,,,111011011000111001001000010100100110001111001011,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
19482,simple,,,"German style exhaust hood - DSYZ-1590",1,0,visible,"The <strong>German Style Exhaust Hood - DSYZ-1590</strong> is a premium ventilation solution designed for professional kitchens. Engineered for superior smoke and odor extraction, it features a sleek, durable stainless steel body with an efficient filtration system. Its powerful suction ensures a clean and comfortable cooking environment, while the modern German design enhances both functionality and aesthetics. Ideal for high-performance kitchens, the DSYZ-1590 combines reliability, efficiency, and style.","<table width=""402"">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width=""402""><strong>German style exhaust hood - DSYZ-1590</strong>\n. With motor and electric control\n. Features: good quality motor and lights\n. construction scotch bright finish 18/10 aisi 304.\n. dim: 1500*900*450 mm.\nDSYZ-1590</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,3759,"ACCESSORIES, Fabrication, Fabrication > Hood, Kitchen Equipment, stainless steel",,,,,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,63,0,,,"German style exhaust hood,German style exhaust hood - DSYZ-1590",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,DSYZ-1590,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,010101011010011110001001011100001110111000010101,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
19485,simple,,,"Electric fryer - E-DZ-12L-2",1,0,visible,"The <strong>Electric Fryer - E-DZ-12L-2</strong> is a high-performance double-tank fryer designed for commercial and heavy-duty kitchen use. With a <strong>12L capacity per tank</strong>, it allows for efficient frying of large batches, making it perfect for restaurants, cafés, and catering businesses. Featuring <strong>precise temperature control</strong>, rapid heating, and a durable stainless steel body, it ensures consistent and crispy results. Its user-friendly design, safety features, and easy-to-clean components make frying effortless and efficient.","<table width=""402"">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width=""402""><strong>Electric fryer - E-DZ-12L-2</strong>\n. capacity: 12 + 12 ltr.\n. temp: 0 ~ 180 °C\n. power: 3.25 kw * 2\n. Voltage: 220-240V / 50 hz.\n. net weight: 110 kg / gross weight: 120 kg.\n. Dim: 580 x 440 x 410 mm.\nall stainless steel body w/ heavy duty element and temperature control function.\nE-DZ-12L-2</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,1575,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Fryers, Kitchen Equipment",,,,,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,70,0,,,"Electric fryer,Electric fryer - E-DZ-12L-2",,,"%title% %page% %sep% %sitename%",,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E-DZ-12L-2,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,,,110101011100010010101000111100011001101000011101,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
19488,simple,,,"Electric Grill - E-DP-820",1,0,visible,"The <strong>Electric Grill - E-DP-820</strong> is a powerful and versatile grilling solution designed for commercial and professional kitchens. Featuring a <strong>high-performance heating system</strong>, it ensures even heat distribution for perfectly grilled meats, seafood, and vegetables. Its <strong>durable stainless steel construction</strong> guarantees long-lasting use, while the <strong>adjustable temperature control</strong> provides precision cooking. With a <strong>spacious grilling surface</strong> and easy-to-clean design, the E-DP-820 is ideal for restaurants, cafés, and catering businesses seeking efficiency and quality.","<table width=""402"">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width=""402""><strong>Electric Grill - E-DP-820</strong>\n. smooth plate\n. Griddle Dim:  728 x 400 x 10 mm.\n. Power:  4.4 kw.\n. Voltage:  220V-240V / 50hz.\n. Dim:  730 x 500 x 230 mm.\n. All S/S body w/ iron griddle, heavy duty heating element &amp; temp. control function.\nE-DP-820</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,1194,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Grills, Kitchen Equipment",,,,,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,66,0,,,"Electric Grill,Electric Grill - E-DP-820",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,E-DP-820,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,,,111111000100010100000110111010100111010100010110,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
19523,simple,,,"Hoshizaki Self-Contained Cuber (IM-30CNE-HC)– 30 kg/Day, 11.5 kg -  IM‐30CNE‐HC  (M062",1,0,visible,"<a id=""t44_95d4f334-8ea7-4cd2-b609-2373b1e848b8"" class=""t4s-tab__title t4s-fwm t4s-ch"" href=""https://mariotstore.com/"" data-t4s-tab-item="""" data-no-instant=""""><span class=""t4s-tab__text"">Product Features</span></a>\n<div id=""t4s-tab-destemplate--23798762438967__main"" class=""t4s-rte t4s-tab-content t4s-active"" data-t4s-tab-content="""">\n<div class=""main-collection-block-tab"">\n<ul>\n 	<li><strong>High Production Capacity:</strong> Produces 30 kg of crystal-clear ice daily to meet commercial needs.</li>\n 	<li><strong>Compact Design:</strong> Space-saving, stainless steel construction for easy maintenance and durability.</li>\n 	<li><strong>Energy Efficient: </strong>Low power consumption (0.23 kW) with environmentally friendly R290 refrigerant.</li>\n 	<li><strong>Ample Storage: </strong>Comes with an 11.5 kg ice bin for sufficient supply during peak hours.</li>\n 	<li><strong>Clean Ice Quality:</strong> Closed-cell system ensures pure ice by using fresh water each cycle.</li>\n 	<li><strong>Easy Maintenance:</strong> Convenient air filter that’s simple to clean and maintain.&amp;nbsp;\nReliable Performance: Separate electronics system to ensure stable operation.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=""main-overview-block-tab"">\n<h2>Product Description</h2>\n<div class=""metafield-rich_text_field"">\n\nDesigned for high-demand environments, the Hoshizaki IM-30CNE-HC Ice Maker delivers up to 30 kg of clear, fresh L cube standard ice daily, making it ideal for cafes, bars, restaurants, and other commercial establishments.\n\nIts 11.5 kg self-contained bin provides ample space to meet demands during busy periods. The exterior is made from stainless steel to give the product durability, and it can also be easily cleaned to maintain long-lasting hygiene. This single-phase unit operates at 50 Hz, ensuring optimal performance in commercial settings.\n\nWith a frequency of 0.23 kW and 1/220–240V/50Hz input voltage, it comes with an environmentally friendly R290 refrigerant. The unit has dimensions of (W x D x H) 398 x 451 x 695, weighs 39 kg, and features height-adjustable legs. The closed cell system creates ice with purified water in each cycle, maintaining the water's purity and taste. The air-cooled system ensures efficient cooling of the ice. For any business seeking reliability, quality, and sustainability in ice production, the Hoshizaki IM-30CNE-HC Ice Maker is the right choice.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","Hoshizaki Self-Contained Cuber (IM-30CNE-HC)– 30 kg/Day, 11.5 kg - IM‐30CNE‐HC (M062\n<strong>Specifications</strong>\nItem Number: M062\nProduct Title: Cuber / Self Contained\nRefrigerant: R290\nMaterial: Stainless steel\nInstallation Type: Ready to Use\nColling Style: Air Cooled\nProduction Capacity (kg/24h): 30\nStorage bin capacity (kg) approx.: 11.5\nProduct configuration: Self Contained\nIce Type: L Cube – standard\nElectric connection Load (kW): 0.23 kW\nInput Voltage: 1/220 – 240V/50Hz\nPhase: Single Phase\nHertz: 50 Hz\nFuel Type: Electricity\nNet weight (kg): 34 Kg\nGross Weight Packed (kg): 39 Kg\nDimensions W x D x H (mm): 398 x 451 x 695",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,8768,"REFRIGERATION LINE > ICE MAKER & FLAKES, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/IM-30CNE-HC-CUBER-SELF-CONTAINED.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Hoshizaki,,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,62,0,,,"Hoshizaki Self-Contained Cuber (IM-30CNE-HC)– 30 kg/Day",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"IM‐30CNE‐HC (M062",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110110110010110010010011100110001100110101001001,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
19551,simple,,,"Ice Cube Maker With Bin, Ice Capacity 46 kg/Day, 0.28 kW - IM‐45CNE‐HC (M065)",1,0,visible,"<span class=""t4s-tab__text"">Product Features</span>\n<h5 class=""serp-title"">Ice Cube Maker With Bin</h5>\n<div id=""t4s-tab-destemplate--23798762438967__main"" class=""t4s-rte t4s-tab-content t4s-active"" data-t4s-tab-content="""">\n<div class=""main-collection-block-tab"">\n<ul>\n 	<li>Features a durable stainless steel exterior for enhanced hygiene and longevity.</li>\n 	<li>Measuring W 63.3, D 51.1, H 69 cm, with adjustable legs for a perfect height.</li>\n 	<li>Highly energy efficient operation because of 0.28 kW power rating.</li>\n 	<li>Operates at single phase, 220 – 240V/50Hz.</li>\n 	<li>Capable of producing up to 46 kg of ice per day, meeting high-demand needs efficiently.</li>\n 	<li>Offers a 15 kg self-contained bin for ample ice storage.</li>\n 	<li>Includes an automatic rinse cycle to maintain ice purity and hygiene.</li>\n 	<li>Composed of closed cell system with fresh water for every new ice batch.</li>\n 	<li>Easy-to-clean air filter prolongs product life and reduces maintenance costs.</li>\n 	<li>Utilizes an air cooling system for efficient heat removal.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=""main-overview-block-tab"">\n<h2>Product Description</h2>\n<div class=""metafield-rich_text_field"">\n\nThe Hoshizaki IM-45CNE-HC Ice Cube Maker With Bin, Ice Capacity 46 kg/Day, 0.28 kW is a top-tier solution for commercial ice needs, delivering outstanding performance and reliability. Designed for efficiency, it produces an impressive 46 kg of high-quality ice per 24 hours, making it ideal for busy environments such as restaurants, bars, and cafes.\nIt features an 15 kg self-contained bin, providing ample storage to keep up with high-demand situations. Each ice cube measures 2.8 x 2.8 x 3.2 cm, ensuring a consistent and professional presentation that enhances the customer experience. The stainless steel construction not only offers a sleek, modern appearance but also ensures durability and easy maintenance.\nThe air cooling system is its standout feature paired with R290 refrigerant, known for its energy efficiency and eco-friendly benefits. The machine’s closed cell system uses fresh water for each new batch of ice, significantly reducing the risk of contamination and maintaining the purity of the ice. Additionally, the magnetic water pump eliminates direct coupling, which prevents leaks and adds to the machine’s reliability.\nThe electronically controlled system adjusts to varying conditions, ensuring a consistent ice-making process without the need for manual adjustments. Routine maintenance is simplified with the easily cleanable air filter, which extends the machine's lifespan and reduces maintenance costs.\nWith its compact dimensions (W 63.3, D 51.1, H 69 cm) and adjustable legs, it fits seamlessly into various spaces. Weighing 45 kg and consuming just 0.28 kW of power, it combines durable performance with energy efficiency. For businesses seeking a reliable, high-capacity ice maker, this is the perfect choice.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","<strong>Ice Cube Maker With Bin, Ice Capacity 46 kg/Day, 0.28 kW - IM‐45CNE‐HC (M065)</strong>\n<strong>Specifications</strong>\nItem Number: IM‐45CNE‐HC (M065)\nProduct Title:Cuber / Self Contained\nRefrigerant:R290\nMaterial:Stainless steel\nInstallation Type:Ready to Use\nColling Style:Air Cooled\nProduction Capacity (kg/24h):39\nStorage bin capacity (kg) approx.:15\nProduct configuration:Self Contained\nIce Type:L Cube – standard\nElectric connection Load (kW):0.275 kW\nInput Voltage:1/220 – 240V/50Hz\nPhase:Single Phase\nHertz:50 Hz\nFuel Type:Electricity\nNet weight (kg);34 Kg\nGross Weight Packed (kg);39 Kg\nDimensions W x D x H (mm):633 x 511 x 690",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,10518,"REFRIGERATION LINE > ICE MAKER & FLAKES, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Hoshizaki-IM-45CNE-HC.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Hoshizaki,,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,61,0,,,"Ice Cube Maker With Bin,Ice Capacity 46 kg/Day",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"IM‐45CNE‐HC (M065)",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110100110110110010110010011100110100100100011100,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
19553,simple,,,"Ice Cube Maker With Bin, – 35 kg/hr Ice Production, 62 kgs kg Storage Bin - IM‐65NE‐HC  ( M066)  (G015)",1,0,visible,"<span class=""t4s-tab__text"">Product Features</span>\n<h5 class=""serp-title""><mark>Ice Cube Maker With Bin</mark></h5>\n<div id=""t4s-tab-destemplate--23798762438967__main"" class=""t4s-rte t4s-tab-content t4s-active"" data-t4s-tab-content="""">\n<div class=""main-collection-block-tab"">\n<ul>\n 	<li>Production Capacity: 35 kg of ice per hour, ideal for high-demand environments</li>\n 	<li>Storage Capacity: 62 kg bin for continuous ice supply</li>\n 	<li>Eco-Friendly Refrigerant: Uses R290 for energy efficiency and reduced environmental impact</li>\n 	<li>Energy Efficiency: Consumes only 0.93 kW, minimizing operational costs</li>\n 	<li>Compact Design: Dimensions of 633 x 506 x 860 mm (legs add 90-125 mm), fitting into tight spaces</li>\n 	<li>Durable Construction: Stainless steel build for long-lasting performance and easy cleaning</li>\n 	<li>Self-Contained: No external refrigeration required</li>\n 	<li>Net Weight: 51 kg for stability and reliability in commercial settings</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=""main-overview-block-tab"">\n<h2>Product Description</h2>\n<div class=""metafield-rich_text_field"">\n\nThe Hoshizaki IM-65NE-HC Self-Contained Cuber is a high-performance ice maker perfect for commercial use. It can create up to 35 kg of L cube ice per hour and has a storage capacity of 62 kg. It has a 62 kg storage capacity and can produce up to 35 kg of L cube ice per hour. This energy-efficient cuber uses just 0.93 kW of electricity and works on R290 refrigerant. Its air-cooled, stainless steel structure guarantees enduring performance and ease of maintenance. The product has an installation kit for simple setup, adjustable legs, and a scoop. With compact dimensions (633 (W) x 506 (D)x 860 (H) mm) and weighing 51 kg, it runs on a 1/220-240V/50Hz single-phase power supply, offering an energy-efficient and reliable solution for businesses.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","<strong>Ice Cube Maker With Bin, – 35 kg/hr Ice Production, 62 kgs kg Storage Bin - IM‐65NE‐HC ( M066) (G015)</strong>\n<strong>Product Features</strong>\nSpecifications:\nItem Number:IM‐65NE‐HC ( M066) (G015)\nProduct Title:\nRefrigerant:\nMaterial:\nInstallation Type:\nColling Style:\nProduction Capacity (kg/24h):\nStorage bin capacity (kg) approx.:\nProduct configuration:\nIce Type:\nElectric connection Load (kW):\nInput Voltage:\nPhase:\nHertz:\nFuel Type:\nNet weight (kg):\nGross Weight Packed (kg):\nDimensions W x D x H (mm):\n\nCuber / Self Contained\nR290\nStainless steel\nReady to Use\nAir Cooled\n35\n26\nSelf Contained\nL Cube – standard\n0.93 kW\n1/220 – 240V/50Hz\nSingle Phase\n50 Hz\nElectricity\n51 Kg\n61 Kg\n633 x 506 x 860",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,12415,"REFRIGERATION LINE > ICE MAKER & FLAKES, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/IM-65NE_kt8KIHLofu1bpNzXr5xj.webp,,,,,,,,,0,,Hoshizaki,,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,61,0,,,"Ice Cube Maker With Bin,– 35 kg/hr Ice Production",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"IM‐65NE‐HC  ( M066)  (G015)",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110100110010010010110011001110011001110111001000,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
19560,simple,,,"Top Kit Hoshizaki - TK‐18D",1,0,visible,"The Top Kit Hoshizaki TK-18D is a high-performance, under-counter refrigeration unit designed for commercial use. It offers superior cooling efficiency and durable construction, making it ideal for businesses like restaurants, bars, and cafes. With a spacious interior, adjustable shelves, and user-friendly controls, the TK-18D ensures optimal storage conditions for perishable items, contributing to better food safety and longer shelf life.","<strong>FEATURES</strong> For 762mm head to ﬁt B801 bin. For 559mm head to ﬁt B801 bin add 8D\nWidth 575mm\nDepth 490mm\nHeight 45mm\nPacked Weight 712mm+L21:N21",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,1118,"ACCESSORIES, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/imgprod_196_204_1706085314.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Hoshizaki,,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,70,0,,,"Top Kit,Top Kit Hoshizaki - TK‐18D",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,TK‐18D,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110101001011110010101101000100101001010111001010,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
19565,simple,,,"Top Kit Hoshizaki - TK‐8D",1,0,visible,"<strong>Top Kit Hoshizaki - TK‐8D</strong> is a high-quality stainless steel top cover designed for Hoshizaki refrigeration units. It enhances durability, provides a sleek finish, and ensures optimal hygiene in commercial kitchen environments.","<strong>Top Kit Hoshizaki TK‐8D</strong>\nFEATURES: For 559mm head to ﬁt 762mm B501 bin\nWidth 580mm\nDepth 240mm\nHeight 42mm\nPacked Weight 2kg",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,1118,"ACCESSORIES, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/imgprod_197_548_1706084904.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Hoshizaki,,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,59,0,,,"Top Kit Hoshizaki - TK‐8D,Top Kit Hoshizaki",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,TK‐8D,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110101011010110010001001010010111100100010110101,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
19569,simple,,,"Ice Cube Maker Self-Contained Hoshizaki - 105kg/Day - IM‐100CNE‐HC  (M068)",1,0,visible,"<strong>Product Features</strong>\n<strong>Ice Cube Maker Self-Contained Hoshizaki - 105kg/Day - IM‐100CNE‐HC (M068)</strong>\n100 kg/day Ice Production: Large capacity ideal for commercial settings like cafes, restaurants, and hotels.\nEnergy-Efficient: Power rating of 0.5kW, reducing energy consumption\nEco-Friendly Refrigerant: Uses R290 refrigerant for environmental benefits.\nBuilt-in Ice Bin: 38 kg storage capacity for convenience.\nCompact Design: Dimensions (W X D X H) 1004 x 600 x 800 and net weight 77 Kg fits into tight spaces with ease.\nDurable Construction: Stainless steel exterior for easy cleaning and longevity.\nL-Shaped Ice Cubes: Good for slow-melt\nHeat Rejection: at 32˚C, WT 21˚C) 1150W\nWater Pressure: 0.7-8bar (0,07-0.8MPa) and water temperature is 5 - 35°C.\nAir-Cooled System: Easy to install since it does not require a water connection.\nProduct Description\nThe Hoshizaki IM-100CNE is an excellent solution for businesses that require high-volume ice manufacturing, making up to 105 kg ice (28 x 28 x 32 mm) per day. With a storage bin capacity of 38 kg, it can store a sufficient amount of ice for daily usage. Designed to generate clear, firm, L cube standard ice cube, it's ideal for high-traffic pubs, restaurants, and hotels. With dimensions of (W X D X H) 1004 x 600 x 800 and net weight of 77 Kg, this unit readily fits into narrow places and delivers great performance. The built-in bin ensures a constant ice supply, and the automatic cleaning feature makes maintenance hassle-free.\n\nWith 0.5 kW electric connection load, 0.63 kW electric connection load, and input voltage of 1/220-240V/50 Hz, this single-phase unit can produce 1.8 KG / 80 PCS per cycle. This modular, stackable designed unit works on R290 refrigerant and is made of tough stainless-steel exterior is sturdy and easy to clean, and the air-cooled condenser assures effective performance even in high ambient temperature of 1 - 40°C. The Hoshizaki IM- IM-100CNE is ideal for large commercial applications, providing the reliability and capacity required to fulfill high ice demand.","<strong>Ice Cube Maker Self-Contained Hoshizaki - 105kg/Day - IM‐100CNE‐HC (M068)</strong>\n<strong>Specifications</strong>\nProduct Title:Self-contained\nRefrigerant:R290\nMaterial:Stainless steel\nInstallation Type:Ready to Use\nColling Style:Air Cooled\nProduction Capacity (kg/24h):105\nStorage bin capacity (kg) approx.:38 kg\nProduct configuration:Self Contained\nHeat Rejection:(AT 32˚C - WT 21˚C) 1150W\nAmbient Temperature:1 - 40°C\nWater Supply Pressure:0.7-8bar (0.07-0.8MPa)\nWater Supply Temperature:5 - 35°C\nIce Production (PER CYCLE):1.8 KG / 80 PCS\nCube Dimension:28 x 28 x 32 mm\nElectric connection Load (kW):0.63 kW\nInput Voltage:1/220-240V/50 Hz\nPhase:Single Phase\nHertz:50 Hz\nContains:Scoop and Installation Kit\nFuel Type:Electricity\nNet weight (kg):77 Kg\nGross Weight Packed (kg):88kg\nDimensions W x D x H (mm):1004 x 600 x 800 (Legs add 100 mm)\nPackaging Dimensions:W 1110 X D 600 X H 840",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,16093,"REFRIGERATION LINE > ICE MAKER & FLAKES, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Hoshizaki-IM-100CNE-HC.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Hoshizaki,,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,56,0,,,"Ice Cube Maker,Ice Cube Maker Self-Contained Hoshizaki - 105kg/Day",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"IM‐100CNE‐HC  (M068)",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110101101101010110000100110100100001101111100010,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
19573,simple,,,"Ice Maker Modular & Stackable Cube ‐ (210Kgs/24h) Hoshizaki- IM‐240XNE‐HC  (M071‐D101 )",1,0,visible,"<strong>Ice Maker Modular &amp; Stackable Cube ‐ (210Kgs/24h) Hoshizaki- IM‐240XNE‐HC (M071‐D101 )</strong>\nThe Hoshizaki IM-240XNE is a cube ice maker that can be stacked, capable of producing an impressive 205 kg of premium cube ice within a 24-hour timeframe.\n\nEach Cuber model comes with an integrated electronic control system, guaranteeing an efficient ice production process even when conditions change. With this automated system in place, our Cubers consistently generate substantial quantities of high-grade ice cubes without the need for additional manual intervention or adjustments.","<strong>Ice Maker Modular &amp; Stackable Cube ‐ (210Kgs/24h) Hoshizaki- IM‐240XNE‐HC (M071‐D101 )</strong>\nProduction Capacity per 24hours Approx. 205kg @ 21°C Air temp; 15°C Water\nApprox. 160kg @ 32°C Air temp; 21°C Water\nMax Storage Capacity Select Bin &amp; Kit\nFreeze Cycle Time Approx. 19 Min\nIce Production Per cycle Approx. 3.2kg/140pcs\nWidth 1084mm\nDepth 700mm\nHeight 500mm\nWeight Net 84kg\nPacked Weight 98kg\nCooling Air\nAC Supply Voltage 1 PHASE 220-240V 50Hz/ 10 AMP Plug\nAmperage Running: 6.6A\nRefrigerant Charge R404A / 480g\nOperating Conditions Ambient Temp.: 1-40°C\nWater Supply Temp.: 5-35°C\nWater Supply Pressure: 0.07-0.8MPa (0.7-8bar) Voltage\nRange: Rated Voltage ±6%\n\n<strong>FEATURES</strong>\nNew intelligent control circuit dedicated to saving power and water consumption.\nProduces individually made cubes which are crystal-clear and slow melting.\nUnique closed cell water circuit for ultimate contamination protection.\nAuto rinse and flush cycle.\nMicro computer controller controls ice making process to work at peak performance in any conditions.\nEasily removable and cleanable air filters on front panel.\nInbuilt safety features – freeze cycle back up timer, defrost back up, low voltage and high amp protector.\nDurable stainless-steel exterior.\nCan be stacked and combined with modular bins and bases\nSmart plug-and-play design comes complete with ice chute for an easy and quick setup",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,22610,"REFRIGERATION LINE > ICE MAKER & FLAKES, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/M071‐D101.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Hoshizaki,,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,53,0,,,"Ice Maker Modular & Stackable Cube",,,"Ice Maker Modular &amp; Stackable Cube",,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"IM‐240XNE‐HC  (M071‐D101 )",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110010011001010011011001101100101101100100110010,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
19576,simple,,,"Self Contained Hydrocarbon Ice Flaker (85kg/24hr) Hoshizaki - FM‐80KE‐HC (F114)",1,0,visible,"This Hoshizaki FM-80KE-HC is a self contained flake ice maker producing up to 85 kg of high-quality flake ice per 24 hours.\n\nHoshizaki ice makers generate quality granular ice, such as Flake ice. The light texture of granular ice has a quick cooling effect, creating an environment of uniform temperatures, without causing unpleasant freezer burn. This is why Hoshizaki Flake ice is highly popular and considered the ideal material to prepare and layer attractive food displays. For flake ice, the extruding head is equipped with wide channels and multi-blade cutters.","<strong>Self Contained Hydrocarbon Ice Flaker (85kg/24hr) Hoshizaki - FM‐80KE‐HC (F114)</strong>\nConsists of 70% ice &amp; 30% water\nIdeal for cooling purposes such as to cool, transport &amp; hold fish\nProduction capacity: 85kg/24hr\nStorage capacity: 26 KG\nDimensions: 640(W) x 600(D) x 800(H)mm - (Legs 89 mm)\nElectrical supply: 230V\nElectrical capacity: 0.270 KW\nRefrigerant: R290\nWeight: 65 KG\nPlease note this machine uses a gravity drain\nAll Stands are 605mm high except the STIM-240M which is 355mm\n4HC-H offer filtration and scale reduction\nScalesticks offer scale reduction only\n4HC-H filters are recommended for general use. Capacity: 79,485 litres per cartridge\nCondensate pumps are supplied with 3 amp fused plug (not fitted) &amp; 2 metre reinforced drain hose",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,16898,"REFRIGERATION LINE > ICE MAKER & FLAKES, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/imgprod_540_730_1720858857.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Hoshizaki,,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,57,0,,,"Self Contained Hydrocarbon Ice Flaker",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"FM‐80KE‐HC (F114)",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,111100110000111000100011100110001100111000011110,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
19580,simple,,,"Ice Flaker Self Contained Hydrocarbon  (125kg/24hr) Hoshizaki FM‐120KE‐HC (F115)",1,0,visible,"<div class=""flex max-w-full flex-col flex-grow"">\n<div class=""min-h-8 text-message flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 whitespace-normal break-words text-start [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5"" dir=""auto"" data-message-author-role=""assistant"" data-message-id=""d57709d6-be12-478e-8ce5-846f919e94b6"" data-message-model-slug=""gpt-4o"">\n<div class=""flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"">\n<div class=""markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert dark"">\n\n<strong>Hoshizaki FM-120KE-HC (F115) Ice Flaker</strong> is a self-contained hydrocarbon ice maker that produces up to <strong>125kg of flake ice per 24 hours</strong>. Designed for efficiency and sustainability, it features an eco-friendly refrigerant, durable stainless steel construction, and advanced cooling technology, making it ideal for food preservation, healthcare, and beverage applications\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","<strong>Ice Flaker Self Contained Hydrocarbon (125kg/24hr) Hoshizaki FM‐120KE‐HC (F115)</strong>\n<ul>\n 	<li>125kg/24hr Production Capacity (Flake Ice)</li>\n 	<li>110kg/24hr Production Capacity (Nugget Ice)</li>\n 	<li>26kg Storage Capacity (Flake Ice) / 32kg Storage Capacity (Nugget Ice)</li>\n 	<li>Electronically Controlled</li>\n 	<li>Automatic Flush System</li>\n 	<li>Closed Water Circuit</li>\n 	<li>Electronically Controlled</li>\n 	<li><strong>Dimensions:</strong>\nW640mm x D600mm x H800mm (Legs add 89mm)</li>\n 	<li>Features:\n• Produces either Flake or Nugget (-N) ice.\n• Member of the Emerald Class, Hoshizaki’s range of climate friendly ice makers.\n• Can produce up to 125 kg of ice (flake) and 110 kg (nugget) per 24 hours (AT.10°C.WT.10°C).\n• Automatic flush system to reduce sediment build up.\n• Closed water circuit offers the ultimate contamination protection, by reducing the number of points at which impurities can enter the ice making process.\n• Electronically controlled to ensure an optimized ice making process under varying circumstances without the need for physical adjustments. Quality of ice is always consistent.\n• Easily cleanable air filter allows end-users to carry out routine cleaning schedules. Extends product life expectancy and reduces the frequency and costs of maintenance call-outs.\n• Stainless steel exterior with integrated door handles provides a hygienic and high quality finish.Specs:\n• Production Capacity (kg/24hr) Approx: 125(F) / 110(N)\n• Storage Bin Capacity (kg) Approx: 26(F) / 32(N)\n• Refrigerant: R290\n• Air Cooled</li>\n</ul>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,17780,"REFRIGERATION LINE > ICE MAKER & FLAKES, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/e4008865317358ed3b49963a8e922e6f7cc2a123_FM_80KE_121619a01_60_rev04.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Hoshizaki,,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,62,0,,,"Ice Flaker,Ice Flaker Self Contained Hydrocarbon,Ice Flaker Self Contained Hydrocarbon (125kg/24hr)",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"FM‐120KE‐HC (F115)",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,111100110000111000100011100110001100111000011110,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
19584,simple,,,"Ice Flaker Modular , (150kg/24hrs) Hoshizaki- FM‐150AKE‐HC‐SB (F128‐C101)",1,0,visible,"<h4 class=""g-color-black g-font-weight-500"">FM-150AKE-HC-SB FLAKER, MODULAR, HC</h4>\n<div class=""g-cutter03""></div>\nThis modular ice maker uses Natural Refrigerant R290, which is environmentally friendly and energy efficient. It produces flake ice, which is often used for produce display of fish, fresh food and bottled beverages. In the medical field, flake ice is also used for organ transportation. Utilizing the most efficient ice making process due to the unique auger system, the water consumption is equal to the ice production. The main characteristic of Hoshizaki’s flake ice is that ‘freeze-burn’ is prevented when displaying fresh fish or produce. This model has a stainless steel bottom and is configured with our storage bins.","<strong>Ice Flaker Modular , (150kg/24hrs) Hoshizaki- FM‐150AKE‐HC‐SB (F128‐C101)</strong>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Model name</th>\n<td>FM-150AKE-HC-SB</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Item Number</th>\n<td>F128-C101</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Product Title</th>\n<td>Flaker, Modular, HC</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Market Segment</th>\n<td>Catering, Education, Food Processing, Hospitality, Laboratory</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Production Capacity (KG/24H) approx.</th>\n<td>150</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Electric Connection Load (kW)</th>\n<td>0.405</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Electric Connection</th>\n<td>1/220 – 240V/50Hz</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Outside Dimensions W x D x H (mm)</th>\n<td>560 x 700 x 780</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Ice Type</th>\n<td>Flake</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Refrigerant</th>\n<td>R290</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Cooling System</th>\n<td>Air Cooled</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Product Configuration</th>\n<td>Modular</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Net Weight (kg)</th>\n<td>63</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Gross Weight Packed (kg)</th>\n<td>70</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Corresponding bin(s)</th>\n<td>B-301SA, B-501SA, B-801SA</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Efficient ice making process due to Hoshizaki’s unique FM auger system.</li>\n 	<li>Utilises all water brought into the machine; therefore water consumption is equal to ice production.</li>\n 	<li>Auger is made of double hardened stainless steel. Combined with carbon bearings, they work optimally in a tough and wet environment. Benefits include: longer product life expectancy and reduced maintenance costs.</li>\n 	<li>Hoshizaki ice makers are micro computer controlled, controlling the ice making process to perform at its best under varying circumstances, without having to make physical adjustments.</li>\n 	<li>Quality stainless steel auger and evaporator increase the life expectancy of these components and the whole ice maker, as well as reducing costly maintenance visits.</li>\n 	<li>An easily cleanable air filter allows end users to carry out a routine cleaning schedule, extending product life expectancy and reducing the frequency and costs of maintenance call-outs.</li>\n</ul>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,17257,"REFRIGERATION LINE > ICE MAKER & FLAKES, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/521b9b2494a13480552cb8addcf75a8105881ab9_FM_170AKE_B_301SA_rev00.max_rev02.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Hoshizaki,,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,57,0,,,"Ice Flaker,Ice Flaker Modular,(150kg/24hrs) Hoshizaki",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"FM‐150AKE‐HC‐SB (F128‐C101)",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110011110001111001110010110100110000100011000101,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
19589,simple,,,"Ice Maker Self‐Contained Cube  (22kg/24h) Hoshizaki- IM‐21CNE‐HC (M061)",1,0,visible,"<strong>Ice Maker Self‐Contained Cube  (22kg/24h) Hoshizaki- IM‐21CNE‐HC (M061)</strong>\n\nThis Hoshizaki IM-21CNE is a self-contained cube ice maker producing up to 22 kg of high-quality cube ice per 24 hours. Meeting even the strictest hygiene requirements, this true allrounder offers many application possibilities in segments including the foodservice and medical sector.","<strong>Ice Maker Self‐Contained Cube  (22kg/24h) Hoshizaki- IM‐21CNE‐HC (M061)</strong>\n\n<strong>Hoshizaki IM-21CNE-HC Self Contained Cuber Ice Maker(Air cooled):</strong>\n\nThis Hoshizaki IM-21CNE-HC is a self-contained cube ice maker producing up to 25 kg of high-quality cube ice per 24 hours. Meeting even the strictest hygiene requirements, this true allrounder offers many application possibilities in segments including the foodservice and medical sector.\n\nAll Cubers are equipped with an electronic control system. This ensures an optimized ice-making process, even under varying circumstances. Without additional manual assistance or adjustments required, our Cubers produce generous amounts of ice cubes, at a consistently high quality.\n\nSustainable\nThe IM-21CNE-HC uses refrigerant R290.\nThis natural refrigerant is not only climate-friendly but also boosts the machine, when it comes to performance and production capacity.\n\nMaterial\nThe exterior is made of stainless steel. The closed water circuit provides maximum protection against any type of contamination during the entire cubing process. All Hoshizaki machines are easy to use, clean, and maintain.\n\nUnique Technology\nA dedicated jet of fresh water is injected into each of the closed cells. Excess water leaves the closed cell through a set of outlets. The cell walls block the freezing water’s expansion from all sides while reaching down to -30°C during the cubing process. Thanks to the automatic rinse cycles, impurities such as minerals, are eliminated from the water resulting in the purest ice possible while your machine is protected from calcification and mineral build-up.\n\nSmart Design\nLike all Hoshizaki Ice makers, the IM-21CNE-HC is designed to last and comes with smart design extras such as a magnetic water pump without direct coupling. This element prevents leakage from the water circuit and improves the life expectancy of the machine.\n\nPerfect Fit\nWith outside dimensions W x D x H of mm, the IM-21CNE-HC is compact and is a perfect fit for small spaces.\n\nPlug&amp;Play\nThe smart plug-and-play design guarantees an easy and quick set-up.\n\n<strong>Specifications:</strong>\n<table class=""shop_attributes"" width=""684"">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Product series</th>\n<td>IM</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Model name</th>\n<td>IM-21CNE-HC</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Item number</th>\n<td>M061</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Product title</th>\n<td>Cuber, Self Contained</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Brand</th>\n<td>Hoshizaki</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Production Capacity (kg/24h) approx. (AT 10°C, WT 10°C)</th>\n<td>25</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Storage bin capacity (kg) approx.</th>\n<td>11,5</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Power supply</th>\n<td>1/220 – 240V/50Hz</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Electric Consumption (kW)</th>\n<td>0,225</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Heat Rejection (AT 32°C, WT 21°C) (kW)</th>\n<td>0,51</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Ice type</th>\n<td>Large cubes, Standard</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Ice cube size</th>\n<td>L (28 x 28 x 32 mm)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Refrigerant</th>\n<td>R290</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>CO2 equivalent (kg)</th>\n<td>0,165</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Cooling System</th>\n<td>Air Cooled</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Product configuration</th>\n<td>Self Contained</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Net weight (kg)</th>\n<td>34</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Gross Weight Packed (kg)</th>\n<td>39</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table class=""woocommerce-product-attributes shop_attributes"">\n<tbody>\n<tr class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--weight"">\n<th class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label"">Weight</th>\n<td class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value"">39 kg</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--dimensions"">\n<th class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label"">Dimensions</th>\n<td class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value"">40 × 45 × 70 cm</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--attribute_pa_units-per-box"">\n<th class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label"">Units per box</th>\n<td class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value""><a href=""https://www.muddle-me.com/units-per-box/1/"" rel=""tag"">1</a></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,9094,"REFRIGERATION LINE > ICE MAKER & FLAKES, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/imgprod_562_803_1728456697.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Hoshizaki,,,,,,,,,,1,2,0,,70,0,,,"Ice Maker,Ice Maker Self‐Contained Cube (22kg/24h) Hoshizaki",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"IM‐21CNE‐HC (M061)",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110100110010110010110011100110001100111001001001,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
19595,simple,,,"Ice Cube Maker Modular (125Kgs/24h) Hoshizaki- IM‐130ANE‐HC (M037‐D100)",1,0,visible,"<strong>Hoshizaki IM-130ANE-HC Ice Cube Maker:</strong>\n\nThis Hoshizaki IM-130ANE-HC is a modular cube ice maker producing up to 125 kg of high-quality cube ice per 24 hours. Meeting even the strictest hygiene requirements, this true allrounder offers many application possibilities in segments including the foodservice and medical sector.\n\nAll Cubers are equipped with an electronic control system. This ensures an optimized ice-making process, even under varying circumstances. Without additional manual assistance or adjustments required, our Cubers produce generous amounts of ice cubes, at a consistently high quality.\n\n<strong>Key Feature:</strong>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Sustainable\nThe IM-130ANE-HC uses refrigerant R290.  This natural refrigerant is not only climate-friendly but also boosts the machine, when it comes to performance and production capacity.\nThe exterior is made of stainless steel. The closed water circuit provides maximum protection against any type of contamination during the entire cubing process. All Hoshizaki machines are easy to use, clean, and maintain.</li>\n 	<li>Unique Technology\nA dedicated jet of fresh water is injected into each of the closed cells. Excess water leaves the closed cell through a set of outlets. The cell walls block the freezing water’s expansion from all sides while reaching down to -30°C during the cubing process.\nThanks to the automatic rinse cycles, impurities such as minerals, are eliminated from the water resulting in the purest ice possible while your machine is protected from calcification and mineral build-up.</li>\n 	<li>Smart Design\nLike all Hoshizaki Ice makers, the IM-130ANE-HC is designed to last and comes with smart design extras such as a magnetic water pump without direct coupling. This element prevents leakage from the water circuit and improves the life expectancy of the machine.</li>\n 	<li>Perfect Fit\nNeed to amp up your production capacity? The variable setups with modular bins and bases allow the user to mix and match depending on individual requirements and conditions. The dimensions of the IM-130ANE-HC are mm.</li>\n 	<li>Plug&amp;Play\nThe smart plug-and-play design guarantees an easy and quick set-up.</li>\n</ul>","<strong>Ice Cube Maker Modular (125Kgs/24h) Hoshizaki- IM‐130ANE‐HC (M037‐D100)</strong>\n\n<strong>Specifications:</strong>\n<table class=""shop_attributes"" width=""461"">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Product series</th>\n<td>IM</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Model name</th>\n<td>IM-130ANE-HC</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Item number</th>\n<td>M037-D100</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Product title</th>\n<td>Cuber, Modular</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Production capacity (kg/24h) approx.</th>\n<td>125</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Electric connection</th>\n<td>1/220 – 240V/50Hz</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Electric consumption (kW)</th>\n<td>0.635</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Ice cube size</th>\n<td>L (28 x 28 x 32mm)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Ice type</th>\n<td>L Cube – standard</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Refrigerant</th>\n<td>R290</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>CO2 equivalent (kg)</th>\n<td>0.33</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Cooling system</th>\n<td>Air Cooled</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Product configuration</th>\n<td>Modular</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Net weight (kg)</th>\n<td>68</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Gross Weight Packed (kg)</th>\n<td>79</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Corresponding bin(s)</th>\n<td>B-140SA, B-210SA, B-340SA</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table class=""woocommerce-product-attributes shop_attributes"">\n<tbody>\n<tr class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--weight"">\n<th class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label"">Weight</th>\n<td class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value"">79 kg</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--dimensions"">\n<th class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label"">Dimensions</th>\n<td class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value"">56 × 70 × 88 cm</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,17472,"REFRIGERATION LINE > ICE MAKER & FLAKES, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/IM-130ANE-HC-2.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Hoshizaki,,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,61,0,,,"Ice Cube Maker,Ice Cube Maker Modular (125Kgs/24h) Hoshizaki",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"IM‐130ANE‐HC (M037‐D100)",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110101001100110010101100110110001000110101001011,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
19605,simple,,,"Ice Storage Bin ‐ (210Kg Capacity) Hoshizaki- B‐210SA (G015)",1,0,visible,"<strong>Hoshizaki B-210SA (G015) Ice Storage Bin</strong> offers a <strong>210kg storage capacity</strong>, ensuring ample ice supply for commercial kitchens, bars, and healthcare facilities. Built with durable stainless steel and a corrosion-resistant interior, it maintains optimal ice quality while providing easy access and efficient storage management.","<strong>Ice Storage Bin ‐ (210Kg Capacity) Hoshizaki- B‐210SA (G015)</strong>\n<table class=""table table-striped"" width=""100%"">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=""uppercase"">Product</td>\n<td class=""uppercase"">B210SA</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=""uppercase"">Storage Bin Capacity</td>\n<td class=""uppercase"">217 kg</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=""uppercase"">dimensions</td>\n<td class=""uppercase"">762 x 820 x 1016 mm</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=""uppercase"">Weight (kg)</td>\n<td class=""uppercase"">47 (net) / 57 (gross)</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,8572,"REFRIGERATION LINE > ICE MAKER & FLAKES, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/imgprod_94_869_1706099430.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Hoshizaki,,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,59,0,,,"Ice Storage Bin,Ice Storage Bin ‐ (210Kg Capacity) Hoshizaki",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"B‐210SA (G015)",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110100001110110010101100001110000110110101001011,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
19607,simple,,,"Modular & Stackable Cube Ice Maker ‐ (240Kgs/24h) Hoshizaki- IM‐240DNE (E1CK‐D114 I)",1,0,visible,"<strong>Modular &amp; Stackable Cube Ice Maker ‐ (240Kgs/24h) Hoshizaki- IM‐240DNE (E1CK‐D114 I)</strong>\n\nThis stackable modular ice maker is part of a unique range of cubers; designed with hygiene as a priority. Each ice cycle is made with fresh water, ensuring only the highest quality of ice. The cubes are easily recognized by its precise shape, clarity and slow dilution. This is particularly important for ice that is used in premium beverages like cocktails, as it protects the integrity and flavour of the drink. This model is configured with our storage bins, and can be stacked to multiply the ice production.","<strong> Modular &amp; Stackable Cube Ice Maker ‐ (240Kgs/24h) Hoshizaki- IM‐240DNE (E1CK‐D114 I)</strong>\n<table class=""woocommerce-product-attributes shop_attributes"" aria-label=""Product Details"">\n<tbody>\n<tr class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--attribute_pa_product-series"">\n<th class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label"" scope=""row"">Product series</th>\n<td class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value"">IM</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--attribute_model-name"">\n<th class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label"" scope=""row"">Model name</th>\n<td class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value"">IM-240DNE</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--attribute_pa_net-weight-kg"">\n<th class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label"" scope=""row"">Net weight (kg)</th>\n<td class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value"">88</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--attribute_pa_gross-weight-packed-kg"">\n<th class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label"" scope=""row"">Gross Weight Packed (kg)</th>\n<td class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value"">101</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--attribute_pa_electric-connection-load-kw"">\n<th class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label"" scope=""row"">Electric connection Load (kW)</th>\n<td class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value"">1.33</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--attribute_pa_electric-connection"">\n<th class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label"" scope=""row"">Electric connection</th>\n<td class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value""><a href=""https://hoshizaki.com.sg/electric-connection/1-220-240v-50hz/"" rel=""tag"">1/220-240V/50Hz</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--attribute_pa_outside-dimensions"">\n<th class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label"" scope=""row"">Outside Dimensions W x D x H (mm)</th>\n<td class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value"">1084 x 700 x 500</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--attribute_pa_refrigerant"">\n<th class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label"" scope=""row"">Refrigerant</th>\n<td class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value"">R404A</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--attribute_pa_production-capacity-kg-24h"">\n<th class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label"" scope=""row"">Production Capacity (kg/24h)</th>\n<td class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value"">190~ 240</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--attribute_pa_ice-type"">\n<th class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label"" scope=""row"">Ice Type</th>\n<td class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value""><a href=""https://hoshizaki.com.sg/ice-type/l-cube-standard/"" rel=""tag"">L Cube – standard</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--attribute_pa_product-configuration"">\n<th class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label"" scope=""row"">Product configuration</th>\n<td class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value"">Modular</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--attribute_pa_corresponding-bins"">\n<th class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label"" scope=""row"">Corresponding bins</th>\n<td class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value"">B-801SA</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Unique ice making system that has an automatic rinse cycle. After every new batch of ice, the water reservoir drains and refills with fresh water.</li>\n 	<li>System comes with a magnetic water pump that has no direct coupling, which prevents any leakage.</li>\n 	<li>Closed water circuit offers the ultimate contamination protection, by reducing the number of points at which impurities can enter the ice making process.</li>\n 	<li>Electronically controlled to ensure an optimised ice making process under varying circumstances without the need for physical adjustments. Quality of ice is always consistent.</li>\n 	<li>Easily cleanable air filter allows end-users to carry out routine cleaning schedules. Extends product life expectancy and reduces the frequency and costs of maintenance call-outs.</li>\n 	<li>With stainless steel frame inside.</li>\n</ul>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,22610,"REFRIGERATION LINE > ICE MAKER & FLAKES, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Hoshizaki-IM-240DNE-Modular-Stackable-Cube-Ice-Maker-510x510-1.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Hoshizaki,,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,64,0,,,"Modular & Stackable Cube Ice Maker",,,"Modular &amp; Stackable Cube Ice Maker",,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"IM‐240DNE (E1CK‐D114 I)",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110110100100110011000110110010001010011010110101,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
19612,simple,,,"Ice Maker Modular & Stackable Cube ‐ (210Kgs/24h) Hoshizaki- IM‐240DNE‐HC (M071‐D100 )",1,0,visible,"<strong>Hoshizaki IM-240DNE-HC Modular Stackable Cube Ice Maker:</strong>\n\nThis Hoshizaki IM-240DNE-HC is a stackable cube ice maker producing up to 210 kg of high-quality cube ice per 24 hours. Meeting even the strictest hygiene requirements, this true allrounder offers many application possibilities in segments including the foodservice and medical sector.\n\nAll Cubers are equipped with an electronic control system. This ensures an optimized ice-making process, even under varying circumstances. Without additional manual assistance or adjustments required, our Cubers produce generous amounts of ice cubes, at a consistently high quality.\n\n<strong>Key Feature:</strong>\n<ul>\n 	<li>The IM-240DNE-HC uses refrigerant R290.  This natural refrigerant is not only climate-friendly but also boosts the machine, when it comes to performance and production capacity.</li>\n 	<li><strong>Material: </strong>The exterior is made of stainless steel. The closed water circuit provides maximum protection against any type of contamination during the entire cubing process. All Hoshizaki machines are easy to use, clean, and maintain.</li>\n 	<li><strong>Unique Technology: </strong>A dedicated jet of fresh water is injected into each of the closed cells. Excess water leaves the closed cell through a set of outlets. The cell walls block the freezing water’s expansion from all sides while reaching down to -30°C during the cubing process. Thanks to the automatic rinse cycles, impurities such as minerals, are eliminated from the water resulting in the purest ice possible while your machine is protected from calcification and mineral build-up.</li>\n 	<li><strong>Smart Design: </strong>Like all Hoshizaki Ice makers, the IM-240DNE-HC is designed to last and comes with smart design extras such as a magnetic water pump without direct coupling. This element prevents leakage from the water circuit and improves the life expectancy of the machine</li>\n 	<li><strong>Perfect Fit: </strong>Need to amp up your production capacity? These ice makers can be stacked and combined with modular bins and bases. This allows the user to mix and match depending on individual requirements, ice consumption, and space conditions. The dimensions of the IM-240DNE-HC are 1084 x 700 x 500 mm.</li>\n 	<li><strong>Plug &amp; Play: </strong>The smart plug-and-play design guarantees an easy and quick set-up.</li>\n</ul>","<strong>Ice Maker Modular &amp; Stackable Cube ‐ (210Kgs/24h) Hoshizaki- IM‐240DNE‐HC (M071‐D100 )</strong>\n\n<strong>Specifications:</strong>\n<table class=""shop_attributes"">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Product series</th>\n<td>IM</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Model name</th>\n<td>IM-240DNE-HC</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Item number</th>\n<td>M071-D100</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Product title</th>\n<td>Cuber, Modular</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Production Capacity (kg/24h) approx. (AT 10°C, WT 10°C)</th>\n<td>210</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Electric connection</th>\n<td>1/220 – 240V/50Hz</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Electric consumption (kW)</th>\n<td>0.93</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Outside dimensions W x D x H (mm)</th>\n<td>1084 x 700 x 500</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Ice type</th>\n<td>L (28 x 28 x 32mm)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Refrigerant</th>\n<td>R290</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>CO2 equivalent (kg)</th>\n<td>0.441</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Cooling system</th>\n<td>Air Cooled</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Product configuration</th>\n<td>Stackable</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Net weight (kg)</th>\n<td>88</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Gross Weight Packed (kg)</th>\n<td>96</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Corresponding bin(s)</th>\n<td>B-340SA, F-1025-52S, F-650-44S, F-950-48S</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table class=""woocommerce-product-attributes shop_attributes"">\n<tbody>\n<tr class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--weight"">\n<th class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label"">Weight</th>\n<td class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value"">101 kg</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--dimensions"">\n<th class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label"">Dimensions</th>\n<td class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value"">108 × 70 × 50 cm</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--attribute_pa_units-per-box"">\n<th class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label"">Units per box</th>\n<td class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value""><a href=""https://www.muddle-me.com/units-per-box/1/"" rel=""tag"">1</a></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,22610,"REFRIGERATION LINE > ICE MAKER & FLAKES, Kitchen Equipment, REFRIGERATION LINE",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Hoshizaki-IM-240DNE-Modular-Stackable-Cube-Ice-Maker-1.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Hoshizaki,,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,62,0,,,"Ice Maker Modular",,,"Ice Maker Modular &amp; Stackable Cube",off,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"IM‐240DNE‐HC (M071‐D100 )",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110111001001011000101100101100110000111001001101,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
19618,simple,,,"Proofing Cabinet Salva- AR‐22/93",1,0,visible,"<div class=""elementor-element elementor-element-c227e55 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor"" data-id=""c227e55"" data-element_type=""widget"" data-widget_type=""text-editor.default"">\n<div class=""elementor-widget-container"">\n\nThe Salva\n<h5 class=""serp-title"">Proofing Cabinet Salva- AR‐22/93</h5>\nallows direct proofing for a variety of doughs on trays. With its independent control over steam and dry heat generation, the AR-22 features a robust power system that ensures optimal steam conditions and temperatures, allowing for precise proofing control and superior dough quality. With adjustable slides for 22 trays (between 60 x 40 and 80 x 46) the unit is constructed entirely of stainless steel plate and features four swivel castors on the base for effortless mobility. The AR-22 offers a robust and high-performance proofing solution for bakers, facilitating direct fermentation processes with efficiency and reliability.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=""elementor-element elementor-element-d5c0679 elementor-widget elementor-widget-jet-listing-grid"" data-id=""d5c0679"" data-element_type=""widget"" data-settings=""{&quot;columns&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}"" data-widget_type=""jet-listing-grid.default"">\n<div class=""elementor-widget-container"">\n<div class=""jet-listing-grid jet-listing"">\n<div class=""jet-listing-grid__items grid-col-desk-1 grid-col-tablet-1 grid-col-mobile-1 jet-listing-grid--1693"" data-queried-id=""28322|WP_Post"" data-nav=""{&quot;enabled&quot;:false,&quot;type&quot;:null,&quot;more_el&quot;:null,&quot;query&quot;:[],&quot;widget_settings&quot;:{&quot;lisitng_id&quot;:1693,&quot;posts_num&quot;:6,&quot;columns&quot;:1,&quot;columns_tablet&quot;:1,&quot;columns_mobile&quot;:1,&quot;is_archive_template&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;post_status&quot;:[&quot;publish&quot;],&quot;use_random_posts_num&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;max_posts_num&quot;:9,&quot;not_found_message&quot;:&quot;No data was found&quot;,&quot;is_masonry&quot;:false,&quot;equal_columns_height&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;use_load_more&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;load_more_id&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;load_more_type&quot;:&quot;click&quot;,&quot;load_more_offset&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:0,&quot;sizes&quot;:[]},&quot;use_custom_post_types&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;custom_post_types&quot;:[],&quot;hide_widget_if&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;carousel_enabled&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;slides_to_scroll&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;arrows&quot;:&quot;true&quot;,&quot;arrow_icon&quot;:&quot;fa fa-angle-left&quot;,&quot;dots&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;autoplay&quot;:&quot;true&quot;,&quot;pause_on_hover&quot;:&quot;true&quot;,&quot;autoplay_speed&quot;:5000,&quot;infinite&quot;:&quot;true&quot;,&quot;center_mode&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;effect&quot;:&quot;slide&quot;,&quot;speed&quot;:500,&quot;inject_alternative_items&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;injection_items&quot;:[],&quot;scroll_slider_enabled&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;scroll_slider_on&quot;:[&quot;desktop&quot;,&quot;tablet&quot;,&quot;mobile&quot;],&quot;custom_query&quot;:false,&quot;custom_query_id&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;_element_id&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;collapse_first_last_gap&quot;:false,&quot;list_items_wrapper_tag&quot;:&quot;div&quot;,&quot;list_item_tag&quot;:&quot;div&quot;,&quot;empty_items_wrapper_tag&quot;:&quot;div&quot;}}"" data-page=""1"" data-pages=""1"" data-listing-source=""repeater"" data-listing-id=""1693"" data-query-id="""">\n<div class=""jet-listing-grid__item jet-listing-dynamic-post-28322"" data-post-id=""28322"">\n<div class=""elementor elementor-1693"" data-elementor-type=""jet-listing-items"" data-elementor-id=""1693"" data-elementor-post-type=""jet-engine""><section class=""elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-bce2115 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default"" data-id=""bce2115"" data-element_type=""section"" data-settings=""{&quot;jet_parallax_layout_list&quot;:[]}"">\n<div class=""elementor-container elementor-column-gap-custom"">\n<div class=""elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-9e49379"" data-id=""9e49379"" data-element_type=""column"">\n<div class=""elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated"">\n<div class=""elementor-element elementor-element-1dfbf9d elementor-widget elementor-widget-jet-listing-dynamic-field"" data-id=""1dfbf9d"" data-element_type=""widget"" data-widget_type=""jet-listing-dynamic-field.default"">\n<div class=""elementor-widget-container"">\n<div class=""jet-listing jet-listing-dynamic-field display-multiline"">\n\n&nbsp;\n<div class=""jet-listing-dynamic-field__content"">Aluminium-framed double glass door.</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section></div>\n</div>\n<div class=""jet-listing-grid__item jet-listing-dynamic-post-28322"" data-post-id=""28322"">\n<div class=""elementor elementor-1693"" data-elementor-type=""jet-listing-items"" data-elementor-id=""1693"" data-elementor-post-type=""jet-engine""><section class=""elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-bce2115 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default"" data-id=""bce2115"" data-element_type=""section"" data-settings=""{&quot;jet_parallax_layout_list&quot;:[]}"">\n<div class=""elementor-container elementor-column-gap-custom"">\n<div class=""elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-9e49379"" data-id=""9e49379"" data-element_type=""column"">\n<div class=""elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated"">\n<div class=""elementor-element elementor-element-1dfbf9d elementor-widget elementor-widget-jet-listing-dynamic-field"" data-id=""1dfbf9d"" data-element_type=""widget"" data-widget_type=""jet-listing-dynamic-field.default"">\n<div class=""elementor-widget-container"">\n<div class=""jet-listing jet-listing-dynamic-field display-multiline"">\n\n&nbsp;\n<div class=""jet-listing-dynamic-field__content"">Two stainless steel heating units are located within the cabinet's base.</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section></div>\n</div>\n<div class=""jet-listing-grid__item jet-listing-dynamic-post-28322"" data-post-id=""28322"">\n<div class=""elementor elementor-1693"" data-elementor-type=""jet-listing-items"" data-elementor-id=""1693"" data-elementor-post-type=""jet-engine""><section class=""elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-bce2115 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default"" data-id=""bce2115"" data-element_type=""section"" data-settings=""{&quot;jet_parallax_layout_list&quot;:[]}"">\n<div class=""elementor-container elementor-column-gap-custom"">\n<div class=""elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-9e49379"" data-id=""9e49379"" data-element_type=""column"">\n<div class=""elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated"">\n<div class=""elementor-element elementor-element-1dfbf9d elementor-widget elementor-widget-jet-listing-dynamic-field"" data-id=""1dfbf9d"" data-element_type=""widget"" data-widget_type=""jet-listing-dynamic-field.default"">\n<div class=""elementor-widget-container"">\n<div class=""jet-listing jet-listing-dynamic-field display-multiline"">\n\n&nbsp;\n<div class=""jet-listing-dynamic-field__content"">Two adjustable thermostats ranging from 30°C to 90°C, each featuring controls and indicator lights for easy operation.</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","<strong>Proofing Cabinet Salva- AR‐22/93</strong>\nAR-22 Direct Proofing Cabinet for Trays\nThe Salva AR-22 Direct Proofing Cabinet allows bakeries to streamline processes, enhance precision, and elevate standards.\nQuicker Preparation\nDirect fermentation eliminates the need for preparing a liquid culture, reducing the time and effort typically required for yeast preparation before fermentation.\n\nEnhanced Control\nAdding yeast directly to the wort or mash enables precise fermentation control by adjusting yeast quantity and fermentation temperature, ensuring the desired flavour profile is achieved.\n\nMinimised Pollution\nDirect fermentation mitigates contamination risks by bypassing yeast propagation in a liquid medium, protecting against bacteria or other microorganisms that may compromise the taste or quality of the end product.",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,21998,"COOKING LINE, Kitchen Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/imgprod_54_410_1706190802.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Salva,,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,69,0,,,"Proofing Cabinet Salva,Proofing Cabinet Salva- AR‐22/93",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,AR‐22/93,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,010010001001111001110011000110010101101101001101,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
19818,simple,,,"VEGETABLE SLICER MACHINE - PSP100",1,0,visible,"The <strong data-start=""4"" data-end=""39"">PSP100 Vegetable Slicer Machine</strong> is a high-performance kitchen tool designed for precise and efficient slicing of various vegetables. Engineered for durability and ease of use, it features sharp stainless steel blades and adjustable cutting thickness, making it ideal for restaurants, catering businesses, and commercial kitchens. Streamline food prep and achieve consistent slices effortlessly with the PSP100.","<strong>VEGETABLE SLICER MACHINE - PSP100</strong>\nCapacity: 200/300 Kg\nSpeed: 320 RPM\nPower: 550 W, 230 V, 50 Hz\nDim: 220x570x480 mm, 21 Kg\nModel: PSP100, Miska, Made in Italy",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,2000,"FOOD PROCESSING, FOOD PROCESSING > Vegtable Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2.webp,,,,,,,,,0,,Miska,,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,65,0,,,"VEGETABLE SLICER MACHINE,VEGETABLE SLICER MACHINE - PSP100",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,PSP100,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011000100110011001110011100100110001100111001101,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
19821,simple,,,"COFFEE GRINDER - 835-B",1,0,visible,"The <strong data-start=""4"" data-end=""28"">835-B Coffee Grinder</strong> is a powerful and reliable machine designed for precision grinding. Equipped with high-quality burrs, it ensures consistent grind sizes, enhancing the flavor and aroma of your coffee. Ideal for cafés, coffee shops, and home baristas, the 835-B delivers efficiency and durability, making it a must-have for any coffee enthusiast.","<strong>COFFEE GRINDER - 835-B</strong>\nHopper Capacity: 680 Gram\nEnergy-efficient 0.5 HP Motor\nAdjustable Grind thickness\nPower: 1/2 HP, 230 V, 50/60 Hz\nDim: 180x380x560 mm, 19.5 Kg\nModel: 835-B, Grindmaster, USA",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,5000,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Coffee Grinder",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/552.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Grindmaster,,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,65,0,,,"COFFEE GRINDER,COFFEE GRINDER - 835-B",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,835-B,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011000001100011001111001001110011101100101000111,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
19827,simple,,,"WHIPPING CREAM MACHINE = Minitronic 2",1,0,visible,"The <strong data-start=""4"" data-end=""43"">Minitronic 2 Whipping Cream Machine</strong> is a high-efficiency device designed for producing smooth, fluffy, and perfectly textured whipped cream. Ideal for bakeries, cafés, and dessert shops, it features advanced technology for consistent output, easy operation, and low maintenance. Enhance your desserts and beverages effortlessly with the Minitronic 2.","<strong>WHIPPING CREAM MACHINE = Minitronic 2</strong>\nElectronic Temperature Control\nPower: 500 W, 230 V, 50 Hz\nDim: 230x390x440 mm, 33 Kg\nModel: Minitronic 2, Hans KraƩ, Made in Germany",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,5000,"REFRIGERATION LINE > Ice Cream Machines, REFRIGERATION LINE",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Minitronic-2.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,Mussana,,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,60,0,,,"WHIPPING CREAM MACHINE,WHIPPING CREAM MACHINE = Minitronic 2",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"Minitronic 2",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,111100001100110000101100011110001111001110011000,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
19832,simple,,,"BUNN COFFEE BREWER 2 WARMER - VP17A-2",1,0,visible,"<div class=""flex max-w-full flex-col flex-grow"">\n<div class=""min-h-8 text-message flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 whitespace-normal break-words text-start [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5"" dir=""auto"" data-message-author-role=""assistant"" data-message-id=""708c89f7-4aa6-4c0a-baf6-4526130443d7"" data-message-model-slug=""gpt-4o"">\n<div class=""flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"">\n<div class=""markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert dark"">\n<p data-start=""0"" data-end=""377"" data-is-last-node="""">The <strong data-start=""4"" data-end=""34"">BUNN VP17A-2 Coffee Brewer</strong> is a durable and efficient pour-over coffee machine designed for commercial use. Featuring two warmers, it ensures a continuous supply of hot, freshly brewed coffee. Its stainless steel construction, fast brewing capability, and user-friendly design make it perfect for restaurants, cafés, and offices that demand high-quality coffee service.</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","<strong>BUNN COFFEE BREWER 2 WARMER - VP17A-2</strong>\n12 Cup Pourover Coffee Brewer\nWith 2 Warmers (Upper &amp; Lower)\nDecanters Sold Separately\nCapacity: 104 Cups(236 ml)\nPower: 2260 W, 230 V, 50/60 Hz\nDim: 213x490x503 mm, 12 Kg\nModel: VP17A-2, Bunn, USA",,,taxable,,0,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,2400,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Coffee Machines",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/6-21.webp,,,,,,,,,0,,BUNN,,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,64,0,,,"BUNN COFFEE BREWER 2 WARMER,BUNN COFFEE BREWER 2 WARMER - VP17A-2",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,VP17A-2,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110011100110110011001001100110011001100101000110,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
19834,simple,,,"JUICER EXTRACTOR - 28",1,0,visible,"<div class=""flex max-w-full flex-col flex-grow"">\n<div class=""min-h-8 text-message flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 whitespace-normal break-words text-start [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5"" dir=""auto"" data-message-author-role=""assistant"" data-message-id=""f2f1d411-0677-4e8b-bdc1-621f37d28e3b"" data-message-model-slug=""gpt-4o"">\n<div class=""flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"">\n<div class=""markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert dark"">\n<p data-start=""0"" data-end=""358"" data-is-last-node="""">The <strong data-start=""4"" data-end=""27"">Juicer Extractor 28</strong> is a powerful and efficient machine designed for extracting fresh juice from fruits and vegetables with ease. Built for commercial use, it features a high-speed motor, durable stainless steel components, and an easy-to-clean design. Ideal for juice bars, cafés, and restaurants, it ensures maximum juice yield with minimal effort.</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","<strong>JUICER EXTRACTOR - 28</strong>\nPowerful InducƟon Motor\nExtra Wide Feeding Chute\nOutput: 100 L/H\nPower: 1300 W\nDim: 480X320X570 Mm\nModel: 28, Brand: Santos, France",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,5600,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Juice Maker",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/santos.webp,,,,,,,,,0,,Santos,,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,60,0,,,"JUICER EXTRACTOR,JUICER EXTRACTOR - 28",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,28,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110100100101110010110100100110001101101001100101,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
19837,simple,,,"VEGETABLE PREPARATION MACHINE - CL55E2V",1,0,visible,"The <strong data-start=""4"" data-end=""45"">CL55E2V Vegetable Preparation Machine</strong> is a high-capacity, versatile solution for slicing, dicing, grating, and shredding a variety of vegetables with precision. Designed for commercial kitchens, it features a powerful motor, multiple cutting options, and a user-friendly design for efficient food prep. Perfect for restaurants, catering services, and food processing businesses.","<strong>VEGETABLE PREPARATION MACHINE - CL55E2V</strong>\nMODEL: CL55E2V\nFeed-Heads large output with stand\nInduction motor - All-metal motor base S/s mobile stand\nPower 1,100 watts Three phase: Speed 375&amp; 750 rpm\nLoad Capacity: 4.2 liters:\nGrass Weight: 62 kg\nDim without stand: 865x396x1272mm (LWH)\nMade by Robot Coupe, France",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,27285,"FOOD PROCESSING, FOOD PROCESSING > Vegtable Equipment",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/CL55E2V.webp,,,,,,,,,0,,"Robot Coupe",,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,65,0,,,"VEGETABLE PREPARATION MACHINE,VEGETABLE PREPARATION MACHINE - CL55E2V",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,CL55E2V,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011110011011011001100011000100100111010011100001,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
19861,simple,,,"Gas stove 4 burners - ELFU77A",1,0,visible,"<div class=""flex max-w-full flex-col flex-grow"">\n<div class=""min-h-8 text-message flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 whitespace-normal break-words text-start [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5"" dir=""auto"" data-message-author-role=""assistant"" data-message-id=""89a5f44c-4ba1-464c-8841-b73cc81efff9"" data-message-model-slug=""gpt-4o"">\n<div class=""flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"">\n<div class=""markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert dark"">\n<p data-start=""0"" data-end=""365"" data-is-last-node="""">The <strong data-start=""4"" data-end=""25"">ELFU77A Gas Stove</strong> is a high-quality commercial cooking range featuring <strong data-start=""79"" data-end=""104"">four powerful burners</strong> for efficient and precise cooking. Built with durable stainless steel, it ensures longevity and easy maintenance. Ideal for restaurants, catering businesses, and professional kitchens, this gas stove delivers reliable performance for high-volume cooking needs.</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","<table width=""416"">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width=""416""><strong>Gas stove 4 burners - ELFU77A</strong>\n- 4 hotplates: 2x 3.5 kW and 2 x6 kW - total 19 kW\n– Worktop rounded on all sides and control panel made of AISI 304 stainless steel\n– 4 removable enamelled cast iron burners\n– Stainless steel grates\n– Height-adjustable stainless steel feet\n- electrical ignition with 220 volt connection\n– Gas connection: 1/2″\n- Weight: 65 kg\n. Dim: 700 x 720 x 850 mm\nELFU77A /  MBM / Italy made.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,4791.6,"COOKING LINE > Cooker, COOKING LINE, Limited Sale, COOKING LINE > Cooker > Series 700",,,,,,,,,,,,0,,MBM,,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,57,0,,,"Gas stove 4 burners,Gas stove 4 burners - ELFU77A",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,ELFU77A,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110101100101010010100110101100001110010011100101,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
19866,simple,,,"Electric stove 4 burners - ELPR77A",1,0,visible,"<div class=""flex max-w-full flex-col flex-grow"">\n<div class=""min-h-8 text-message flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 whitespace-normal break-words text-start [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5"" dir=""auto"" data-message-author-role=""assistant"" data-message-id=""22f40f8a-03ff-434d-bb4c-22d449610b82"" data-message-model-slug=""gpt-4o"">\n<div class=""flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"">\n<div class=""markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert dark"">\n<p data-start=""0"" data-end=""396"" data-is-last-node="""">The Electric stove 4 burners - ELPR77A is a professional-grade <strong data-start=""50"" data-end=""76"">4-burner cooking range</strong> designed for high-performance commercial kitchens. Constructed with durable stainless steel, it ensures even heat distribution, efficient cooking, and easy cleaning. Perfect for restaurants, catering services, and food establishments, this gas stove offers reliability and precision for demanding culinary environments.</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","<strong>Electric stove 4 burners - ELPR77A</strong>\n<table width=""416"">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width=""416"">- 4 round hobs\n- 2x Ø 15cm/1.5 kW + 2x Ø 22.5cm/2.5 kW = total 8 kW\n- worktop rounded on all sides and control panel made of stainless steel AISI 304\n- the hotplates are equipped with overheating protection\n- with thermostat for optimal power regulation\n- optimal energy efficiency\n- Voltage: 400 volts / 3 N~ / 50 Hz\n– electric ignition with 230 volt connection\n– Gas connection: 1/2″\n– 1 grid is included in delivery\n– Weight: 50 kg\n. Dim: 700 x 720 x 850 mm\nELPR77A /  MBM / Italy made.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,4435.2,"COOKING LINE > Cooker, COOKING LINE, Limited Sale, COOKING LINE > Cooker > Series 700",,,,,,,,,,,,0,,MBM,,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,57,0,,,"Electric stove 4 burners,Electric stove 4 burners - ELPR77A",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,ELPR77A,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110101100110010010100110100100101110010011100011,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
19869,simple,,,"Gas stove 4 burners - ELFU77FG",1,0,visible,"The <strong data-start=""4"" data-end=""26"">ELFU77FG Gas Stove</strong> is a high-performance <strong data-start=""49"" data-end=""75"">4-burner cooking range</strong> designed for commercial kitchens. Featuring durable stainless steel construction, powerful burners, and user-friendly controls, it ensures efficient and precise cooking. Ideal for restaurants, catering services, and food establishments, this gas stove delivers reliability, durability, and superior heat distribution for professional cooking needs.","<table width=""416"">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width=""416""><strong>Gas stove 4 burners - ELFU77FG</strong>\n. 4 cooking zones: 2x 3.5 kW and 2 x6 kW\n. Oven with 3 levels: 6 kW / Total 25 kW\n– Worktop rounded on all sides and control panel made of AISI 304 stainless steel\n– Oven chamber made entirely of stainless steel\n– 4 removable enamelled cast iron burners\n– electric ignition with 230 volt connection\n– Gas connection: 1/2″\n– 1 grid is included in delivery\n– Weight: 90 kg\n. Dim: 700 x 720 x 850 mm\nELFU77FG /  MBM / Italy made.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,7088.4,"COOKING LINE > Cooker, COOKING LINE, Limited Sale, COOKING LINE > Cooker > Series 700",,,,,,,,,,,,0,,MBM,,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,60,0,,,"Gas stove 4 burners,Gas stove 4 burners - ELFU77FG",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,ELFU77FG,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,111101110001010010000011010100101101100011100011,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
19873,simple,,,"Gas stove 6 burners - ELFU7A",1,0,visible,"The <strong data-start=""4"" data-end=""24"">ELFU7A Gas Stove</strong> is a professional <strong data-start=""43"" data-end=""69"">6-burner cooking range</strong> designed for high-efficiency commercial kitchens. Built with durable stainless steel, it offers powerful and even heat distribution for precise cooking. Ideal for restaurants, catering services, and food establishments, this gas stove ensures reliability, durability, and optimal performance for demanding culinary operations.","<strong>Gas stove 6 burners - ELFU7A</strong>\n6 hotplates: 3x 3.5 kW and 3 x6 kW - total 28.5 kW\n-Worktop rounded on all sides and control panel made of AISI 304 stainless steel\n- 4 removable enamelled cast iron burners\n- Stainless steel grates\n- electrical ignition with 220 volt connection\nGas connection: 1/2""\n- Weight: 90 kg\nDim: 1100 x 720 x 850 mm\nELFU7A/MBM / Italy made.",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,6415,"COOKING LINE > Cooker, COOKING LINE, Limited Sale, COOKING LINE > Cooker > Series 900",,,,,,,,,,,,0,,MBM,,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,66,0,,,"Gas stove 6 burners,Gas stove 6 burners - ELFU7A",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,ELFU7A,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,,,011101110001010010100111101110000110010100100101,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
19876,simple,,,"4 ROUND PLATES ON ELECTRIC OVEN - ELPR77FE",1,0,visible,,"<table width=""416"">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width=""416""><strong>4 ROUND PLATES ON ELECTRIC OVEN - ELPR77FE</strong>\n- 4 round hobs\n- 2x Ø 14.5/22 cm/1.5 kW + 2x Ø 22 x 22cm/2.6 kW\n- lowered with dimensions 300x300 mm and power 2.5 kW. Indicator lights indicate the operation of each plate on the control panel. Worktop in AISI 18/10 steel with a thickness of 1 mm. Excellent alignment via joint cover.\n- Electric oven (kW): 5.3\n- Total power : 13.5 kW\n- Oven Dim: 560 x 660 x 310 mm\n- Voltage: 400V 3N 50/60Hz\n- Weight: 90 kg\n- Volume (m3): 0.8\n. Dim: 700 x 714 x 850mm\nELPR77FE /  MBM / Italy made.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,7642.8,"COOKING LINE > Cooker, COOKING LINE, Limited Sale, COOKING LINE > Cooker > Series 700",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ELPR77FE.webp,,,,,,,,,0,,MBM,,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,5,0,,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,ELPR77FE,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011111001011011010001001000100100101100011100111,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
19971,simple,,,"Slice Toaster - ET-DS-4",1,0,visible,"<div class=""flex max-w-full flex-col flex-grow"">\n<div class=""min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 whitespace-normal break-words text-start [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5"" dir=""auto"" data-message-author-role=""assistant"" data-message-id=""89b835b8-36ad-4361-a54c-8021a77386a8"" data-message-model-slug=""gpt-4o"">\n<div class=""flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"">\n<div class=""markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert dark"">\n<p data-start=""0"" data-end=""431"" data-is-last-node="""" data-is-only-node=""""><strong data-start=""0"" data-end=""27"" data-is-only-node="""">Slice Toaster - ET-DS-4</strong><br data-start=""27"" data-end=""30"" />The ET-DS-4 Slice Toaster is a high-performance commercial toaster designed for efficiency and precision. With its durable stainless steel construction and even toasting technology, it ensures consistent results for every slice. Ideal for restaurants, cafes, and bakeries, this toaster features adjustable browning settings, a user-friendly interface, and rapid heating for high-volume toasting needs.</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","<strong>Slice Toaster - ET-DS-4</strong>\nCap: 4 pcs\nMaterial: 201/304 Stainless Steel\nPower: 1.68 kW\nVoltage: 220-230/50Hz\n.Net weight: 4 kg\ndim: 300 x 225 x 215 mm.\nET-DS-4",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,420,"COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Sandwich Maker",,,,,,,,,,,,0,,Stilco,,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,66,0,,,"Slice Toaster - ET-DS-4",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,ET-DS-4,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,,,110101101100110010100010100100100111001100110101,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
20012,simple,,,"Bone saw 2020 - SM2020EC (SO2020ECO) (SM202AECO)",1,0,visible,"The <strong data-start=""4"" data-end=""56"">Bone Saw 2020 - SM2020EC (SO2020ECO) (SM202AECO)</strong> is a high-performance electric bone saw designed for precise and efficient meat cutting. Ideal for butcher shops, meat processing plants, and commercial kitchens, it features a powerful motor, durable stainless steel construction, and enhanced safety features for smooth operation.","SM2020EC (SO2020ECO)\n(SM202AECO)\nMODEL: SM2020EC\n(SO2020ECO)\n(SM202AECO)\nBone saw 2020 anodised V.230/50 ECO\nWorking tables:500x530mm\nMotor:hp1.5-kw 1\nAluminum Weight: 52 kg\nDim: 50x75x105 cm\nMade by SAP, Italy",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,6625,"FOOD PROCESSING, FOOD PROCESSING > Meat Slicer & Bone Saw",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/SEGAOSSI-SO-SM-1550-ECO-SO-SM-1830-ECO.webp,,,,,,,,,0,,SAP,,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,59,0,,,"Bone Saw 2020 - SM2020EC (SO2020ECO) (SM202AECO),Bone saw 2020",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110011100110111001000010011100011011001101001100,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
20016,simple,,,"TurboChef Microwave Oven, Rapid /Touch controls, standard JET BLACK (RAL 9005) – ECO‐9500‐805/BLACK",1,0,visible,"The TurboChef ECO-9500 high-speed oven has customizable menu settings that can hold 256 recipes for quick use. These settings can be adjusted manually, with a USB drive, or on Wi-Fi for added cost. To ensure the unit operates efficiently, it self-diagnoses any potential problems. Due to its internal catalytic converter, the oven doesn’t need a vent to eliminate grease and odor emissions, potentially saving operators significant capital. A single motor in the cabinet circulates air vertically to cook.\n\nCleaning the TurboChef ECO-9500 microwave convection oven is streamlined with one bottle of oven cleaner, one bottle of oven guard, two trigger sprayers, and an aluminum paddle. It comes with two aluminum pans and the oven rack is removable to accommodate various foods. The outer wrap and door are made of 430 stainless steel that remains cool to the touch to prevent burns. Because the cabinet is insulated, hot air doesn’t escape while cooking.","<h1 class=""product_title entry-title"">TurboChef Microwave Oven, Rapid /Touch controls, standard JET BLACK (RAL 9005) – ECO‐9500‐805/BLACK</h1>\n<table class=""woocommerce-product-attributes shop_attributes"">\n<tbody>\n<tr class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--weight"">\n<th class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label"">Weight</th>\n<td class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value"">54 kg</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--dimensions"">\n<th class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label"">Dimensions</th>\n<td class=""woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value"">59.7 × 40.9 × 54.6 cm</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<ul class=""tabs wc-tabs"">\n 	<li class=""woodmart_custom_tab_tab active""><a href=""https://yourkitchencenter.com/product/turbochef-microwave-oven-rapid-touch-controls-standard-jet-black-ral-9005-eco%e2%80%909500%e2%80%90817-uk/#tab-woodmart_custom_tab"">ABOUT THE BRAND</a></li>\n</ul>\nTurboChef Technologies, Inc. has pioneered the world of rapid cooking. With innovation and top performance in mind, TurboChef has redefined cooking efficiency by designing rapid-cook ovens that are versatile, user-friendly, and save energy. TurboChef ovens cook faster and produce consistent results without compromising quality.",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,23799,28000,"COOKING LINE",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ECo-9500.jpg,,,,,,,,,0,,"turbo chef",,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,66,0,,,"TurboChef,TurboChef Microwave Oven,Rapid /Touch controls",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,ECO‐9500‐805/BLACK,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,20018,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011110110001011000111010010110001000111101100001,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
20060,simple,,,"SQUERO COMBI OVEN - SQ12TCC",1,0,visible,"The <strong data-start=""4"" data-end=""35"">SQUERO COMBI OVEN - SQ12TCC</strong> is a high-performance, multifunctional combi oven designed for professional kitchens. It offers precise temperature control, steam and convection cooking modes, and advanced programmability for consistent results. Ideal for restaurants, bakeries, and catering businesses, the SQ12TCC enhances efficiency and culinary creativity.","""<strong>SQUERO COMBI OVEN</strong>\n. Tray capacity: 12 GN 1/1\nDistance between tray: 70 mm\n*Automatic clean system integrated\n- Touch controls and a 5” screen.\n. With nothing superfluous but all the essentials, this high-tech but extremely user-friendly oven offers all the most important functions and features capacitive touch controls and a 5” screen.\n. Max cooking temperature: 260°C\n. Frequency (Hz) 50 - 60 \n. Voltage: 380-415V 3N~/220-240V 3~\n. Power: 15,7 kW\n. Oven weight: 135 kg\n. Dimension: 937 x 890 x 1211 WxDxH\nSQ12TCC / VENIX / Italy made.""\n",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,27537,"BAKERY LINE, BAKERY LINE > Bakery Oven",,,,,,,,,,,,0,,Venix,,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,66,0,,,"SQUERO COMBI OVEN,SQUERO COMBI OVEN - SQ12TCC",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,SQ12TCC,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,,,011111100111110110000011010110000000110111100000,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
20063,simple,,,"SQUERO COMBI OVEN - SQ10TCC",1,0,visible,"The SQUERO COMBI OVEN - SQ10TCC is a versatile and efficient combi oven designed for professional kitchens. It features advanced steam and convection cooking technology, precise temperature control, and customizable programs to ensure consistent and high-quality cooking results. Perfect for restaurants, bakeries, and catering services.","<strong>SQUERO COMBI OVEN</strong>\n. Tray capacity: 10 600×400mm\nDistance between tray: 80 mm\n. With nothing superfluous but all the essentials, this high-tech but extremely user-friendly oven offers all the most important functions and features capacitive touch controls and a 5” screen.\n. Max cooking temperature: 260°C\n. Frequency (Hz) 50-60\n. Voltage 400V 3N ~  - 230V 3N ~\n. Power: 15,7 / 18,6**\n. Oven weight: 135 kg\n. Dimension: 937 x 890 x 1211 WxDxH\nSQ10TCC / VENIX / Italy made.""\n",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,24423,"BAKERY LINE, BAKERY LINE > Bakery Oven, COOKING LINE",,,,,,,,,,,,0,,Venix,,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,70,0,,,"SQUERO COMBI OVEN,SQUERO COMBI OVEN - SQ10TCC",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,SQ10TCC,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,,,011111100111100110100011010111000000110011100000,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
20065,simple,,,"SQUERO COMBI OVEN - SQ06TCC",1,0,visible,"The SQUERO COMBI OVEN - SQ06TCC is a compact yet powerful combi oven designed for professional kitchens. It combines steam and convection cooking for precise and efficient food preparation. With intuitive controls and programmable settings, it ensures consistent results, making it ideal for restaurants, bakeries, and catering businesses.","""<strong>SQUERO COMBI OVEN </strong>\n. Load cap:  6 TRAYS 600×400 – GN 1/1\n.  distance between trays : 80 mm\n. Power/Voltaqge/Freq: 10.5 kw/230 V – 1N /400 V – 3N/ 50-60-hz \n. Temperature:   260°C      \n. Weight : 118 kg\n. MANUAL COOKING- Convection cooking Mixed steam and convection cooking Steaming;Dry air cooking; Delta T cooking w/ core probe; Sous vide cooking\n. Dim:  937 X 821 X 875 WxDxH 937 X 821 X 875\nSQ06TCC / VENIX / italy made.""\n",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,19265,"BAKERY LINE, BAKERY LINE > Bakery Oven",,,,,,,,,,,,0,,Venix,,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,70,0,,,"SQUERO COMBI OVEN,SQUERO COMBI OVEN - SQ06TCC",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,SQ06TCC,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011111110010011101101110010110000010100101100000,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
