20070,simple,,,"BAKERY CONVECTION OVEN - SQ10D00",1,0,visible,"The BAKERY CONVECTION OVEN - SQ10D00 is a high-performance convection oven designed for professional bakeries. It ensures even heat distribution for perfect baking results, featuring precise temperature control, multiple baking modes, and a spacious capacity. Ideal for bakeries, pastry shops, and commercial kitchens.","""BAKERY CONVECTION OVEN\n. Cap: 10 600×400\n. Space between trays :  80 mm\n. Power/Voltage/Fre: 15,7 / 400V 3N ~ 230V 3N ~ 50-60 Hz\n. Temperature :   260°C\n. Weight : 153 kg\n. Technology Electric/Bakery convection\n. Automatic clean system integrated\n. A multifunction digital control system with 99 programs and the possibility of adding a “Self Clean” option.\n. With nothing superfluous but all the essentials, this high-tech but extremely user-friendly oven offers all the most important functions and features capacitive touch controls and a 5” screen.\n. Dimension: 937 x 827 x 1211 WxDxH\nSQ10D00 / VENIX / Italy made.""\n",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,17921,"BAKERY LINE, BAKERY LINE > Bakery Oven",,,,,,,,,,,,0,,Venix,,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,66,0,,,"BAKERY CONVECTION OVEN,BAKERY CONVECTION OVEN - SQ10D00",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,SQ10D00,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,,,011111100111110110000011010110000001101011100000,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
