20217,simple,,,"PROOFER - P9.1",1,0,visible,"The PROOFER - P9.1 is a high-quality commercial proofer designed to provide optimal humidity and temperature control for professional bakeries and food establishments. It ensures consistent dough fermentation, enhancing the texture, rise, and flavor of bread and pastries. With a spacious capacity and user-friendly controls, this proofer improves baking efficiency, making it an essential tool for achieving perfect, high-quality baked goods.","""PROOFER - P9.1\n. Model suitable for oven: L06D – L06M – L04D – L04M\n. Load capacity: 8 TRAYS 600×400 – GN 1/1\n. Space between trays: 75 mm\n. Power/Voltage/Frequency: 2 kW/ 230 V – 1N / 50-60 Hz\n. Temperature: 0-60° C\n. Weight : 49 kg\n. Dim: 920 x 830 x 860 WxDxH\nP9.1 / VENIX / italy made.""",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,4096,"BAKERY LINE, BAKERY LINE > Bakery Oven",,,,,,,,,,,,0,,Venix,,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,55,0,,,"PROOFER - P9.1,PROOFER",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,P9.1,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,110101110110110100101010010100101011001001101000,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
