20225,simple,,,"COMPACT COMBI STEAM OVEN - R10DC",1,0,visible,"The COMPACT COMBI STEAM OVEN - R10DC is a versatile and space-saving commercial oven designed for professional kitchens, bakeries, and food service establishments. It combines convection and steam cooking to ensure precise temperature and humidity control, delivering consistent, high-quality results. Ideal for baking, roasting, steaming, and regenerating food, this oven enhances efficiency, preserves food texture and flavor, and optimizes energy use in a compact design perfect for smaller kitchen spaces.","""<strong>COMPACT COMBI STEAM OVEN - R10DC</strong>\n. L oad Cap:  10 GN 1/1 \n. Space between trays : 10 trays of 40mm or 6 trays 65mm\n. Power/Voltage/Fre: 14 kw/ 400 V - 3N / 50-60 Hz.\n. Temperature :  30/260°C\n. Weight : 115 kg\n. Equipped w/: 2 powerfull motors \n- Digital control 99 programs \n- Bi-directional reversing fan system \n- Digital water injection regulation \n- Automatic pre-heating setting \n- N. 2 speed regulation \n- N. 4 cooking cycles for each program \n- SteamExhaust regulation \n- Halogene lights \n- Core probe integrated \n- (S3) Self Clean System Optional on request\n. Dimension: 530 x 842 x 910 WxDxH\nR10DC / VENIX / italy made.\n ""\n",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,18850,"BAKERY LINE, BAKERY LINE > Bakery Oven",,,,,,,,,,,,0,,Venix,,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,71,0,,,"COMPACT COMBI STEAM OVEN,COMPACT COMBI STEAM OVEN - R10DC",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,R10DC,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,,,111100101101110110000110000011000010010111100011,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
