22254,simple,,,"JUICE DISPENSER- single cylinder",1,0,visible,"Keep your beverages fresh and ready to serve with our Single Cylinder Juice Dispenser – ideal for buffets, events, or cafés. Made with durable stainless steel and a clear container for easy viewing, it's perfect for chilling and dispensing juice, iced tea, or other cold drinks with ease and elegance.","JUICE DISPENSER- single cylinder\nBowl Capacity: 16*1 ltr Material: Stainless Steel +PC\nLowest temperature (°C): -0-6\nVoltage: 220V/50-60hz\nPower: 145 w refridgeration\nCoolant: R410a / UK PLUG\nN. G. Weight: 10-13 kgs\nDIM: 375 265 700 mm\nMK-JD116SD/MKE-MATIC.",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,1350,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Juice Maker",,,,,,,,,,,,0,,MKE-MATIC,,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,63,0,,,"JUICE DISPENSER- single cylinder",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,,,110101110110010110000000101111101001100001001110,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
22270,simple,,,"4 SQUARE PLATES ON ELECTRIC OVEN - MPQ98FE",1,0,visible,"<strong>4 Square Plates on Electric Oven - MPQ98FE</strong>\nEfficient and durable electric oven featuring four square heating plates for even cooking. Ideal for versatile kitchen use, delivering consistent heat and easy maintenance. Perfect for both home and professional kitchens.","4 SQUARE PLATES ON ELECTRIC OVEN\n.Nr. Plates 3 kW 3\n4 kW 1\nThe cast iron fast-heating hot plates w/ safety device to prevent overheating are watertight fixed to the worktop.\n. Squared plates w/ dim: 300x300 mm &amp; power 3 &amp; 4 kW. Indicator lights show when each hotplate is working.\n. 1mm worktop in AISI 18/10 s/s. Excellent alignement w/joints.\nS/S cooking chamber w/ enameled bottom, S/S double-wall door with insulating casing.\n. El. oven: 6 kW S/S armoured heating elements (10 kW for maxi oven) placed on the bottom and on the top of the cooking chamber; thermostatic temperature control w/separate bottom/top temperature control for maximum cooking flexibility. 3 GN 2/1 rack support.\n. Electric oven (kW): 6\n. Total power (kW): 19\n. Oven dimensions - WxDxH (cm): 54 x 69,5 x 29\nSupply: 400V 3N 50/60Hz\nWeight (kg): 142\nVolume (m3): 1\nDim: 800 x 900 x 850 mm\nMPQ98FE/MBM/Italy made.\nINCLUDE ISO9001",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,16840.6128,"COOKING LINE > Cooker, COOKING LINE, COOKING LINE > Cooker > Series 900",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/MPQ98FE-2.webp,,,,,,,,,0,,MBM,,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,53,0,,,"4 Square Plates on Electric Oven - MPQ98FE",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,MPQ98FE,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,011101001111010000101101000110001111000011100101,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
