22305,simple,,,"Stainless Steel Kitchen Hood Wall type single-skin Without Fresh Air",-1,0,visible,"<strong>Stainless Steel Kitchen Hood – Wall Type, Single-Skin (Without Fresh Air)</strong>\n\nA durable, wall-mounted extraction hood made from high-grade stainless steel. Designed for commercial kitchens to efficiently remove smoke, heat, and grease without integrated fresh air supply. Ideal for setups with separate ventilation systems. Easy to clean with removable grease filters.","""Stainless Steel Kitchen Hood\n. Wall type single-skin Without Fresh Air\n. baffle filters: 500 x 500 mm\n. heating light\n. grease collection box\n. 18/10 Stainless Steel Sheet Thickness: 1.2 Mm\n. construction scotch bright finish 18/10 aisi 304.\n. . dim: 1000 x 1000 x 500 MM\nmariot made / uae.""",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,,"DRY STORE > Insect Killer",,,,,,,,,,,,0,,,,,,,,,,,,1,1,,,29,,,,"Stainless Steel Kitchen Hood – Wall Type",,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
22341,simple,,,"Stainless Steel Kitchen Hood Wall Type Double-skin w/Fresh Air System",1,0,visible,"<strong>Stainless Steel Kitchen Hood – Wall Type, Double-Skin (With Fresh Air System)</strong>\n\nPremium wall-mounted kitchen hood with double-skin stainless steel construction for added durability and insulation. Integrated fresh air system ensures balanced ventilation by supplying filtered air while extracting smoke, heat, and grease. Ideal for high-performance commercial kitchens. Features easy-to-clean surfaces and removable filters for maintenance.","""Stainless Steel Kitchen Hood\n. Wall Type Double-skin w/Fresh Air System\n. Baffle Filters: 500 X 500 Mm Heating Light.\n. Grease Collection Box\n. 18/10 Stainless Steel Sheet Thickness: 1.2 Mm\n. construction scotch bright finish 18/10 aisi 304.\n. Dimension: 1000 X 1000 X 500 MM\nmariot made / uae.""\n",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,2200,"Fabrication, Fabrication > Hood",,,,,,,,,,,,0,,"Mariot Fabrication",,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,55,0,,,"Stainless Steel Kitchen Hood Wall Type",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,,,110101100011011010100111001100101111000010110000,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
22342,simple,,,"Stainless Steel Kitchen Hood Wall type single-skin Without Fresh Air",1,0,visible,"<strong>Stainless Steel Kitchen Hood – Wall Type, Single-Skin (Without Fresh Air)</strong>\n\nA durable, wall-mounted extraction hood made from high-grade stainless steel. Designed for commercial kitchens to efficiently remove smoke, heat, and grease without integrated fresh air supply. Ideal for setups with separate ventilation systems. Easy to clean with removable grease filters.","""Stainless Steel Kitchen Hood\n. Wall type single-skin Without Fresh Air\n. baffle filters: 500 x 500 mm\n. heating light\n. grease collection box\n. 18/10 Stainless Steel Sheet Thickness: 1.2 Mm\n. construction scotch bright finish 18/10 aisi 304.\n. . dim: 1000 x 1000 x 500 MM\nmariot made / uae.""\n",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,1800,"Fabrication, Fabrication > Hood",,,,,,,,,,,,0,,"Mariot Fabrication",,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,55,0,,,"Stainless Steel Kitchen Hood Wall type",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,,,110101100011011010100111001100101111000010110000,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
22343,simple,,,"Stainless Steel island-type double skin Hood Wall type island-type single skin",1,0,visible,"Stainless Steel Hood – Island Type, Double-Skin\nHigh-quality island-mounted hood with double-skin stainless steel construction for enhanced durability and noise insulation. Ideal for central cooking stations, it efficiently extracts smoke, heat, and grease while maintaining a sleek, professional look. Suitable for demanding commercial kitchens.\n\nStainless Steel Hood – Wall Type, Island Style, Single-Skin\nA lightweight, single-skin stainless steel hood designed for wall installation in an island-style kitchen setup. Provides effective smoke and grease extraction with a space-saving design. Perfect for kitchens needing a cost-effective ventilation solution.\n","""Stainless Steel island-type double skin Hood\n. Wall type island-type single skin.\n. heating light\n. grease collection box\n. stainless steel sheet thickness: 1.2 mm.\n. exclude circulation system or ducting work.\n. 18/10 Stainless Steel Sheet Thickness: 1.2 Mm\n. construction scotch bright finish 18/10 aisi 304.\n. dim: 2000 x 2200 x 500 MM.\nmariot made / uae.""\n",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,7200,"Fabrication, Fabrication > Hood",,,,,,,,,,,,0,,"Mariot Fabrication",,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,62,0,,,"Stainless Steel island-type double skin Hood",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,,,110101110001110010100111100000011010100000111101,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
22344,simple,,,"Stainless Steel island-type double skin Hood double skin",1,0,visible,"Stainless Steel Hood – Island Type, Double-Skin\nRobust island-mounted hood with double-skin stainless steel construction for superior durability, insulation, and noise reduction. Designed for central cooking stations in commercial kitchens, it ensures efficient extraction of heat, smoke, and grease. Ideal for high-demand environments with 360° access.","""Stainless Steel island-type double skin Hood\n. Wall type island-type double skin.\n.  With Fresh Air System\n. heating light\n. grease collection box\n. stainless steel sheet thickness: 1.2 mm.\n. exclude circulation system or ducting work.\n. 18/10 Stainless Steel Sheet Thickness: 1.2 Mm\n. construction scotch bright finish 18/10 aisi 304.\n. dim: 2000 x 2200 x 500 MM.\nmariot made / uae.""\n",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,8800,"Fabrication, Fabrication > Hood",,,,,,,,,,,,0,,"Mariot Fabrication",,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,23,0,,,"Stainless Steel Hood – Island Type",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,,,110101100001110010100111100000011110100000111101,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
