23316,simple,,,"ICE TANK",1,0,visible,"Capacity: 210kg/ hr\n‐ Ice transparent and clean, can make the drink quickly cold,\nfor you to bring a more perfect drink taste!\n‐ The front air filter can be removed and washed, which is\nconvenient to remove and wash, prevent the condensate pipe\nfrom blocking and improve the ice making efficiency.\n‐ In addition to automatic cleaning, manual cleaning can be\nused to clean the air filter whenever you need it.\n‐ 304 stainless steel outer gram, circular arc door, take ice area\nis larger, easy to use.\n‐ Power : 220 V\n‐ Wattage : 1200 W\n‐ Ice Production : 208 Kg / 24 hrs\n‐ Weight : 114 Kg\n. dim: 780 x 840 x 1720 mm\nICE TANK FOR ZBF‐230","Capacity: 210kg/ hr\n‐ Ice transparent and clean, can make the drink quickly cold,\nfor you to bring a more perfect drink taste!\n‐ The front air filter can be removed and washed, which is\nconvenient to remove and wash, prevent the condensate pipe\nfrom blocking and improve the ice making efficiency.\n‐ In addition to automatic cleaning, manual cleaning can be\nused to clean the air filter whenever you need it.\n‐ 304 stainless steel outer gram, circular arc door, take ice area\nis larger, easy to use.\n‐ Power : 220 V\n‐ Wattage : 1200 W\n‐ Ice Production : 208 Kg / 24 hrs\n‐ Weight : 114 Kg\n. dim: 780 x 840 x 1720 mm\nICE TANK FOR ZBF‐230",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,2801,"REFRIGERATION LINE > ICE MAKER & FLAKES, REFRIGERATION LINE",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ICE-TANK-FOR-ZBF‐230.webp,,,,,,,,,0,,Brema,,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,16,0,,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"ICE TANK FOR ZBF‐230",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
