23743,simple,,,"EXPLORA COLOMBO 10 Grid High Tech Combi Oven",1,0,visible,"‐ Capacity: 10 TRAYS ‐ 600X400 ‐ GN 1/1\n‐ High Capacity Drip Tray in S/S AISI 304\n‐ Space Between Trays mm: 80\n‐ 7″ Colour Touch Screen Display Control System (Multi‐Lingual, use metric or imperial settings)\n‐ Connection Wi‐Fi and Ethernet\n‐ Single Core Temperature Probe\n‐ Optimal Climatic Control\n‐ Water Drainage system integrated into the cooking chamber\n‐ Automatic Wash System – with 3 levels of intensity and separate rinse cycle\n‐ Double Glazed door with tempered glass and air gap – easy access cleaning\n‐ Multi Phase Cooking with up to 40 different phases to include pre‐set phases\n‐ Multi‐Timer with two independent timers per tray\n‐ Fast Cooling Function\n‐ Net Weight (Kg): 121\n‐ Temperature: 30 – 270 °C\n‐ Power (KW): 15.8\n‐ Voltage: 400V 3N ‐ 50/60Hz\n. Exterior Dimension (WxDxH) mm: 870 x 850 x 1200\nPF7910‐PI7 / Tecnodom / DGD / Italy made","‐ Capacity: 10 TRAYS ‐ 600X400 ‐ GN 1/1\n‐ High Capacity Drip Tray in S/S AISI 304\n‐ Space Between Trays mm: 80\n‐ 7″ Colour Touch Screen Display Control System (Multi‐Lingual, use metric or imperial settings)\n‐ Connection Wi‐Fi and Ethernet\n‐ Single Core Temperature Probe\n‐ Optimal Climatic Control\n‐ Water Drainage system integrated into the cooking chamber\n‐ Automatic Wash System – with 3 levels of intensity and separate rinse cycle\n‐ Double Glazed door with tempered glass and air gap – easy access cleaning\n‐ Multi Phase Cooking with up to 40 different phases to include pre‐set phases\n‐ Multi‐Timer with two independent timers per tray\n‐ Fast Cooling Function\n‐ Net Weight (Kg): 121\n‐ Temperature: 30 – 270 °C\n‐ Power (KW): 15.8\n‐ Voltage: 400V 3N ‐ 50/60Hz\n. Exterior Dimension (WxDxH) mm: 870 x 850 x 1200\nPF7910‐PI7 / Tecnodom / DGD / Italy made",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,22632,"REFRIGERATION LINE > Display Chiller, REFRIGERATION LINE",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2