23745,simple,,,"TOP pizza rolling mill 45 cm GIOTTO D45 EASY",1,0,visible,". Diameter 45 cm\n. Min/max dough weight: 30-800g\n. Pasta weight: 30 to 800g\n. Outlet diameter (cm): 10 to 45 cm\n- Pizza rolling mill with two adjustable oblique rollers that allow you to obtain the desired thickness with millimeter precision.\n- This moulder is designed to roll out and extend cold dough for pizza bases, breads, pastas, cakes.\n- Made with specific materials to be in contact with food products: AISI 304 stainless steel and certified plastics.\n- Pizza sheeter ergonomically designed to facilitate the activity carried out by the operator and make cleaning easier at the end of use.\n- The underside of the appliance is accessible for cleaning without handling.\n- Voltage: 230/240V / 50-60 Hz\n- Power : 0.37 kW\n- Net / Gross Weight: 35.8 / 39.6 kg\n- Dim: 520 x 290 x H 690 mm\nMA/10-00-00-02E / PASTALINE / Italy made.",". Diameter 45 cm\n. Min/max dough weight: 30-800g\n. Pasta weight: 30 to 800g\n. Outlet diameter (cm): 10 to 45 cm\n- Pizza rolling mill with two adjustable oblique rollers that allow you to obtain the desired thickness with millimeter precision.\n- This moulder is designed to roll out and extend cold dough for pizza bases, breads, pastas, cakes.\n- Made with specific materials to be in contact with food products: AISI 304 stainless steel and certified plastics.\n- Pizza sheeter ergonomically designed to facilitate the activity carried out by the operator and make cleaning easier at the end of use.\n- The underside of the appliance is accessible for cleaning without handling.\n- Voltage: 230/240V / 50-60 Hz\n- Power : 0.37 kW\n- Net / Gross Weight: 35.8 / 39.6 kg\n- Dim: 520 x 290 x H 690 mm\nMA/10-00-00-02E / PASTALINE / Italy made.",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,2970,3960,"BAKERY LINE, Kitchen Equipment, BAKERY LINE > Rolling Machine, sale 11.11",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/MA10-00-00-02E.webp,,,,,,,,,0,,Pastaline,,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,10,0,,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,MA/10-00-00-02E,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,,,,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
