23930,simple,,,"Counter-top Chocolate Tempering Machine",1,0,visible,"Basin Capacity: 6 kg\n- 4.3 inch touch screen display with built-in multi-function program:\n- Three operating modes: Manual, Automatic &amp; Standby\n- Electronic dosing\n- Temperature management\n- Remote control and remote support functions\n- Melting and tempering time: 1 hour and 15/30 minutes\n- Vibrating table width: 52.5 cm\n- Heating system: 2 silicone heating elements for heating the basin 1 heating cable for heating the auger\n- Refrigeration unit: Gas 134 A\n- Consumption: 1.5 kW - 230 V 50/60 Hz\n- Weight: 67 kg\n- Basin diameter: 200 mm - Outlet pipe length: 270 mm\n- Dimensions: 470 x 500 x 840 H mm\nAdam K6 / BILAIT / Italy made.","Basin Capacity: 6 kg\n- 4.3 inch touch screen display with built-in multi-function program:\n- Three operating modes: Manual, Automatic &amp; Standby\n- Electronic dosing\n- Temperature management\n- Remote control and remote support functions\n- Melting and tempering time: 1 hour and 15/30 minutes\n- Vibrating table width: 52.5 cm\n- Heating system: 2 silicone heating elements for heating the basin 1 heating cable for heating the auger\n- Refrigeration unit: Gas 134 A\n- Consumption: 1.5 kW - 230 V 50/60 Hz\n- Weight: 67 kg\n- Basin diameter: 200 mm - Outlet pipe length: 270 mm\n- Dimensions: 470 x 500 x 840 H mm\nAdam K6 / BILAIT / Italy made.",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,25780,28644.44,"SNACK MAKER > Chocolate Machine, SNACK MAKER",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Adam-K6-IMAGE-1.webp, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Adam-K6-IMAGE-2.webp",,,,,,,,,0,,Bilait,,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,6,0,,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"Adam K6",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
23938,simple,,,"Counter-top Chocolate Tempering Machine",1,0,visible,"Basin Capacity: 12 kg\n- High quality food grade stainless steel that ensures strength and ease of maintenance.\n- The robust stainless steel construction ensures a long life and easy maintenance, while the ergonomic design makes it easy to use and clean.\n- It is ideal for artisan workshops that want to achieve a high production capacity. The machine can operate in a continuous cycle with an hourly production and tempering of 55 kg of chocolate.\n- Temper 12 kg of chocolate in about 10 minutes.\n- Hourly production: 55 kg\n- Main switch and emergency switch Interactive, intuitive touch screen panel including night mode, quick shut-down , reverse, temperature control and electronic dosing\n- Consumption: 1.5 kW - 230 V 50/60 Hz\n- Weight: 85 kg\n- Dimensions: 400/715 x 600 x 1409 H mm\nAdam K12 / BILAIT / Italy made.","Basin Capacity: 12 kg\n- High quality food grade stainless steel that ensures strength and ease of maintenance.\n- The robust stainless steel construction ensures a long life and easy maintenance, while the ergonomic design makes it easy to use and clean.\n- It is ideal for artisan workshops that want to achieve a high production capacity. The machine can operate in a continuous cycle with an hourly production and tempering of 55 kg of chocolate.\n- Temper 12 kg of chocolate in about 10 minutes.\n- Hourly production: 55 kg\n- Main switch and emergency switch Interactive, intuitive touch screen panel including night mode, quick shut-down , reverse, temperature control and electronic dosing\n- Consumption: 1.5 kW - 230 V 50/60 Hz\n- Weight: 85 kg\n- Dimensions: 400/715 x 600 x 1409 H mm\nAdam K12 / BILAIT / Italy made.",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,34848,38720,"SNACK MAKER > Chocolate Machine, SNACK MAKER",,,"https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/PRODUCT-IMAGE3-1.webp, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/PRODUCT-IMAGE5.webp, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/PRODUCT-IMAGE-2.webp, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/PRODUCT-IMAGE-1.webp, https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/poeurgffd.webp",,,,,,,,,0,,Bilait,,,,,,,,,,1,1,0,,3,0,,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,"Adam K12",field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,,false,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
