23952,simple,,,"Chocolate Melting Machine Digital",-1,0,visible,"<p>Basin capacity: 6 kg<br>- 4.3 inch touch screen display with built-in multi-function program:<br>- 2 operating modes: Manual &amp; Standby<br>- Electronic dosing, Temperature management<br>- Remote control and remote support functions<br>- Program open to future updates<br>- Safety fuses on the main components<br>- 1 Resettable auger motor fuse, 1 Inverter for direction reversal, 1 Pedal to stop the flow of chocolate, 1 Magnetic basin protection sensor. <br>- Two single-phase motors, Two reducers, Removable s/s auger. <br>- Consumption: 1 kW - 230 V 50/60 Hz<br>- Weight: 40 kg<br>- Dimensions: 460 x 360 x 805 H mm<br>Aya K6 / BILAIT / Italy made.</p>","Basin capacity: 6 kg\n- 4.3 inch touch screen display with built-in multi-function program:\n- 2 operating modes: Manual &amp; Standby\n- Electronic dosing, Temperature management\n- Remote control and remote support functions\n- Program open to future updates\n- Safety fuses on the main components\n- 1 Resettable auger motor fuse, 1 Inverter for direction reversal, 1 Pedal to stop the flow of chocolate, 1 Magnetic basin protection sensor.\n- Two single-phase motors, Two reducers, Removable s/s auger.\n- Consumption: 1 kW - 230 V 50/60 Hz\n- Weight: 40 kg\n- Dimensions: 460 x 360 x 805 H mm\nAya K6 / BILAIT / Italy made.",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,,"DRY STORE > Insect Killer",,,,,,,,,,,,0,,,,,,,,,,,,,1,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
