24690,simple,,,"Anfim Alba Coffee Grinder (Black)",1,0,visible,"<strong data-start=""58"" data-end=""93"">Anfim ALBA Professional Grinder</strong>: Italian-designed for high-volume espresso applications, the ALBA delivers unmatched precision with its 80 mm flat burrs and lightning-fast double shot in just 2.6 seconds. Featuring a 3.5″ touchscreen, three programmable recipes, stepless grind adjustment, and robust metal construction — all at an excellent value","[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text css=""""]<strong>Burr diameter:</strong> 80 mm\n<strong>Burr material: </strong>Special steel\n<strong>Burr grind life </strong>(median setting)<strong>:</strong>  1.500 kg\n<strong style=""font-size: 1rem;"">Voltage / Frequency / Phase*:</strong><span style=""font-size: 1rem;""> </span>\n<ul>\n 	<li>100 V | 50/60 Hz | 800/900 W</li>\n 	<li>110-127 V | 60 Hz | 700 W</li>\n 	<li>220-240 V | 50/60 Hz | 700/800 W</li>\n</ul>\n<strong>RPM: </strong>1500 rpm (50 Hz); 1800 rpm (60 Hz)\n<strong>Grinding capacity: </strong>~5,6 g/s @ 250 μm (50 Hz); ~6,4 g/s @ 250 μm (60 Hz)\n<strong style=""font-size: 1rem;"">Grinding time for single Espresso: </strong><span style=""font-size: 1rem;"">~1,3 s\n</span><strong>Bean hopper capacity: </strong>2.0 kg\n<strong>Dimensions (w x h x d): </strong>210 x 620 x 386 mm\n<strong>Net weight:</strong> 13 kg\n<strong>Shipping weight</strong>: 14.5 kg\n<strong>Color option**:</strong> Black, White[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,8300,"COFFEE & BAR LINE, COFFEE & BAR LINE > Coffee Grinder",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/Anfim-grinder-Alba.webp,,,,,,,,,0,,Anfim,,,,,,,,,,1,,0,,51,0,,,"Anfim Alba Coffee Grinder (Black",,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,Alba,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,default,,,true,backend,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,