24936,simple,,,"PAINTED BENCH DOUGH SHEETER",1,0,visible,"500 x 1000 mm\n‐ It is compact and with a design that allows the operator to work\ncomfortably.\n‐ The dough sheeter is perfect for multiple applications: from\npastry shops to hotels, catering, etc.\n‐ Existing options have been made even more advanced.\n‐ Optional: collecting dough tray, the display allows you to\nprecisely check the decrease of calibrator cylinders.\n‐ Cylinders opening (mm): 40\n‐ Cylinders diameter (mm): 80\n‐ Conveyor belts width (mm): 500\n‐ Power (kw): 0,55\n‐ Power (hp): 0,75\n• Weight: 140 kg\n• Voltage: 400V / 50 Hz/ 3 ph\n• Dim [mm]: 2340 x 980 x 650\nModel No. SHB50B100 / Z.MATIK / ITALY","500 x 1000 mm\n‐ It is compact and with a design that allows the operator to work\ncomfortably.\n‐ The dough sheeter is perfect for multiple applications: from\npastry shops to hotels, catering, etc.\n‐ Existing options have been made even more advanced.\n‐ Optional: collecting dough tray, the display allows you to\nprecisely check the decrease of calibrator cylinders.\n‐ Cylinders opening (mm): 40\n‐ Cylinders diameter (mm): 80\n‐ Conveyor belts width (mm): 500\n‐ Power (kw): 0,55\n‐ Power (hp): 0,75\n• Weight: 140 kg\n• Voltage: 400V / 50 Hz/ 3 ph\n• Dim [mm]: 2340 x 980 x 650\nModel No. SHB50B100 / Z.MATIK / ITALY",,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,16315,"DRY STORE > Insect Killer",,,https://mariotstore.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/SHB50B100.webp,,,,,,,,,0,,ZMATIK,,,,,,,,,,1,,,,4,,,,,,,,,,,,field_60befc9fc0fb7,SHB50B100,field_6387359a51f50,no,field_6540c7c45e610,no,field_6492d8387acaf,,field_6517fe43bc95f,no,field_6570174679980,no," ",0,default,default,default,default,default,default,default,0,0,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
